rts? In other words, physical exercise is good, but immunity is relatively poor?\"\n\n  \"Uh-huh.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, that\'s it.\n\nSonoko was curious: \"So, how good is Noriko\'s body actually?\"\n\n\"This one.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked left and right, then moved her body, borrowed strength from the walls on both sides of the narrow alley, and climbed up to the top of the three-meter-high wall in a few strokes.\n\nSonoko looked up, amazing, no wonder Noriko wears bottoming every day. Today, she is wearing white pumpkin pants, which are also very cute.\n\nKiko didn\'t want to be noticed, so she fell down, stretched out her hand and hung it on the wall, and then used her strength to kick to the opposite wall and fall, slightly flexing her body to cushion.\n\n\"Noriko is really handsome, just like kindergarten... It seems that there is something missing.\"\n\nSonoko directly applauded and praised, but looking at Noriko, who was embarrassed by the praise, she still felt that something was wrong.\n\n  what is it?\n\nShe thought about it seriously, yes, it\'s her temperament. The kindergarten\'s Noriko Amamiya is very handsome from her behavior to her expression. Now, even though her movements are very handsome, her expression is cute rather than handsome.\n\nAfter she told her feelings, Amamiya Noriko tilted her head. Does this still feel that there is a difference in personality?\n\nIt\'s really hard to do, but—\n\nShe has borrowed strength from Kudo Shinichi.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko saw Noriko\'s cheeks blushing slightly after hearing this, and she couldn\'t help but raise her brows. This matter is not simple, and according to her love master\'s nose, there is a sweet smell of love.\n\nBehind Noriko seemed to be gradually blooming pink petals, more like a girl in love than she had guessed before.\n\nSonoko quickly approached, lowered his voice and asked in a low voice, \"So what is ~www.readwn.com~?\"\n\nAs the future queen of reasoning, she understands very well at this moment that she must not directly ask who Noriko likes, but to continue the original words, continue the original topic that involves Noriko\'s romance, and inquire from the side.\n\nOtherwise, Noriko\'s intention of revealing it would frighten Noriko, and if she refuses to say anything at all, even though there is a love affair in front of her, but she cannot solve the truth, that would be too cruel to her!\n\nCompared to Noriko\'s romance, nothing else matters.\n\nSeeing that Sonoko was hooked, Amamiya Noriko\'s bright eyes flashed, and then she shyly whispered the reason in Sonoko\'s ear.\n\nSonoko opened his mouth wide, and for a while he was out of breath. After a while, he took a breath and said, \"Noriko really likes Shinichi?!\"\n\nNoriko quickly blushed and covered Sonoko\'s mouth with her hand.\n\n\"I don\'t know either. Sonoko is quieter.\"\n\nSonoko waved his hand: \"No, no, it\'s impossible to hold back.\"\n\nBecause what Noriko told her was really, really great! !\n\n\"Because, because Shinichi likes cute...\"\n\nWhen her ears heard Kiko\'s words, she immediately understood why Kiko changed from being handsome to being cute. It turned out to be the reason of Kudo Shinichi, because Kudo Shinichi didn\'t like her who was more handsome before. So Noriko changed herself for Shinichi and became a cuter and more likeable Noriko...\n\nAh, what a great romance—\n\nSonoko was intoxicated, and finally, there is a love that will grow up under her witness!\n\n\"It\'s fake, it\'s fake!!!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi almost suffocated in his chest across a wall, and Amamiya Noriko was talking nonsense while he was away! ! !\n\n​​');
