(386, 5, 66, 'Chapter 65: : Fugitive in the water park', 'Kudo Shinichi watched Matsuda Jinping up and down.\n\nEspecially for the eyes under the sunglasses, and the overly well-maintained hands.\n\nThings like shooting and fighting are absolutely necessary and definitely not the best option for a person to guess in this situation.\n\nAs for the others, there are police dog training, equipment maintenance, bomb disposal, investigation, psychological...\n\n\"Bomb defusing?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pondered for a moment.\n\nCompared with the others, this one is obviously suitable, and it is easier to use it as the best skill.\n\nMatsuda Jinpei showed a slightly surprised expression, but then smiled charmingly and prepared to announce the correct answer.\n\nAmamiya Noriko interjected, \"Is it typing?\"\n\nMatsuda Jinhei paused, and Kudo Shinichi turned his head to look at her, what strange answer are you talking about? Could a handsome police officer like him be good at typing skills that shouldn\'t appear?\n\nBut he also knew that if Noriko Amamiya said it, there would definitely be a problem\n\nMatsuda Jinping looked at this cute girl, the corners of his mouth curled up, and he snapped his fingers: \"Half and half.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi turned to look at him, you are good at skills, can you be serious?\n\nMatsuda Jinpei smiled slightly, \"typing is indeed what I am good at, but I am proud of it. At the same time, what I am also good at is still bomb disposal. After all, I am an expert in bomb disposal.\"\n\n\"So little sister, you are only half right, this little brother answered correctly.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pouted, if you are proud of typing fast, typing will soon become something you are proud of.\n\nIs your fast typing something that the police should be proud of?\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t expect to save more people because of this. It\'s a skill that comes in handy and is enough to be proud of.\n\nHowever, Matsuda Jinhei was very optimistic about Kudo Shin, \"Little boy, 