(387, 5, 17, 'Chapter 16: : Big brother who touches porcelain, come on!', 'The next day, Amamiya Noriko couldn\'t go to school with a cold again.\n\nKudo Shinichi and the three who got the news from the teacher\'s mouth are used to it but they are hesitant to say anything.\n\nIs this frequency really okay?\n\nSonoko guessed: \"Maybe the cold the day before yesterday wasn\'t all right.\"\n\nXiaolan was a little worried: \"Could it be because of yesterday?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was skilled enough to comfort them and said, \"It\'s not a big problem.\"\n\nIt\'s really not a big problem, just a little cold, Amamiya Noriko went for a relaxing morning run for a few kilometers when she woke up in the morning.\n\nThen, when I was going to sit in the cafe for a while, I saw a very magical scene at the intersection.\n\nA certain tall man with long hair wearing a black knitted hat, with brown skin, dark green eyes, cold and firm eyes, and a resolute face, suddenly walked to the road and used a classic technique of touching porcelain.\n\nIt was knocked out a distance and rolled to the ground.\n\nA beautiful and gentle woman with long black hair on her right forehead hurriedly stepped off the vehicle that was hit. Her sapphire blue eyes supported the man who was hit, full of concern and worry.\n\nMiyano Akimi, a woman who is somewhat similar to Maorilan, is beautiful, generous, considerate, and has a strong heart beneath her tenderness. She is a good sister who has always cared about her sister.\n\nAs for the person who touches the porcelain, it is naturally Shuichi Akai, who wants to use her hand to join the black organization, and is currently under the pseudonym Zhuxingda.\n\nAmamiya Noriko watched calmly by the side of the road, and a pinch of tender love sparked in front of her again.\n\n\"Really, generally speaking, seeing a lot of other people in pairs is a curse, and it will be difficult for you to break away from being single.\"\n\nBut she turned her head and thought, how would she reap the confession after being single, so there is no hurry, the curse is invalid.\n\n\"Is there any special reward for a key person like Shuichi Akai to confess to me?\"\n\nOver there, Shuichi Akai, who was knocked to the ground, keenly noticed the sight staring at him, and after a veiled inspection, he saw only a very young girl.\n\nWearing a winter sportswear, her slender figure looks a little wide in the coat, her dark medium-length hair is tied in a ponytail, and her neat appearance does not match her delicate and lovely face like a porcelain doll. Such a face Looking at him with a calm chest on the side of the road, a pair of star eyes with very direct eyes.\n\nHe is very familiar with this kind of gaze. It is the gaze that stares directly at the target character of the mission, and it is also the gaze that stares at the prey.\n\nToday\'s children really don\'t understand.\n\nAkai Shuichi put aside his distracting thoughts and concentrated on touching porcelain, highlighting a major, and was then sent to the hospital, where he was in hospitalization mode.\n\nDuring the hospitalization, he would gradually develop feelings for Miyano Akimi, they dated, and then met Miyano Akimi\'s sister who came back from the United States this year, and the top-minded scientist in the organization, Miyano Shiho, successfully entered the organization. internal.\n\nAnd then relying on his own ability to obtain the code name \'Rye (rye whiskey)\'.\n\nThe plan was originally like this. He started to be hospitalized and got to know each other with Akimi Miyano, who came to visit him from time to time because of guilt, and cultivated feelings for each other.\n\nBut the next day, Akemi Miyano visited him for a while, but after leaving, another person came in.\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her hand: \"Hello?\"\n\nAs soon as Akai Hidey saw this little girl, she immediately remembered that she was touching porcelain that day, no, the girl she saw at the scene of the car accident was a bit special because of her looks and eyes, and she had a deep memory.\n\n  \"It\'s you?\"\n\n\"Well, it\'s me.\"\n\nAlthough it was strange in his heart, Shuichi Akai still smiled gently and said, \"Little sister knows me? Is there anything you want to do with me?\"\n\n\"It\'s alright, I just think the way you landed that day was very handsome!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head, closing her eyes and pointing her fingers to aim and shoot.\n\nAkai Shuichi: \"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt underestimated, and raised the fruit basket in the other hand: \"What\'s the matter, I\'m here to visit you too.\"\n\n\"Thank you very much.\"\n\nAkai Hide took a look at the delicate fruit basket. Since it was not the peak season for fruit, such a basket of fruits was quite expensive, so he couldn\'t understand it even more.\n\n  \"how did you find me?\"\n\n\"Um... telepathy?\"\n\nAkai Xiuyi kept his smile on his face: \"Hehehe, do all middle school students like to play these things?\"\n\n\"Fortunately, the naive ones generally prefer it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko knew that his pseudonym was Zhuxingda, so naturally, she knew where the ward was by asking the nurse at the front desk. UU Reading www.uukanshu. com has such a lovely sister who wants to visit her brother, and the nurse is very enthusiastic.\n\n\"By the way, I\'m really sorry. I haven\'t introduced myself yet. I\'m Noriko Amamiya. I\'m in the first year of middle school. I\'m wearing the school uniform now. Is it a pity that it\'s not a sailor uniform?\"\n\n\"No.\" Akai Shuichi said calmly, \"I\'m Zhuxingda, nice to meet you.\"\n\nThen the two were speechless, and the scene fell into a very strange situation.\n\nAkai Shuichi looked at this inexplicable girl in his heart, wondering if it would affect his plans.\n\nAnd Amamiya Noriko sat down next to him, glanced at him from time to time, and then cut an apple to eat.\n\nAkai Hideo thought about it, isn\'t it a fruit basket for the patient?\n\nHowever, he noticed that Amamiya Noriko\'s technique of peeling apples was very neat and neat. The fruit knife turned back and forth gently, an apple was turned in her slender fingers, and the apple peel did not break until the end. Put it in the trash can.\n\nAfter eating the apple, Noriko Amamiya took a banana, and after looking at it, she felt that it was not ripe enough, it would be stiff and astringent, so she handed it to Shuichi Akai.\n\nAkai Shuichi: \"Thank you, I won\'t eat it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko also put back the fruit basket, got up and patted her skirt, \"Big brother, then I\'m leaving today, I have to go to school tomorrow, I wish you a speedy recovery? Or later, so that I can deepen my relationship with that sister. Feelings? That\'s not right, if you\'re discharged from the hospital sooner, you can go on a date, come on.\"\n\nAkai Shuichi watched her walk out of the ward, her sharp brows were slightly wrinkled, her inexplicable behavior from beginning to end was full of confusion, what was her purpose?\n\nIf it gets in the way of the plan, I have to ask Judy to investigate.'),
