f the classmate Amamiya Noriko he liked, today, let\'s confess again!\n\nAs long as I can run with Noriko and bathe in the brilliance of the rising sun...\n\nHe couldn\'t keep up, Amamiya Noriko ran very fast.\n\nAfter a few laps, he got rid of him, and he was so tired that he couldn\'t get the strength to continue to run. Only Xiaolan could bathe in the rising sun and run with Yumiya Noriko.\n\nOn the football field on the track, Kudo Shinichi and the members of the football club had mixed feelings. This, this was originally their Amamiya!\n\nEspecially the head of the football department, looking at the small handsome and lively Noriko Amamiya while running, she is as agile as an elf, even more cute than the weak Noriko Amamiya, he can\'t help but hold his head, his eyes are full of determination and determination. look.\n\nKarate club, here I come!\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at the way Xiaolan and Noriko were running together. He didn\'t know what to say. If Amamiya Noriko was speaking, it would be impossible to change her evil ways, right? What did she want to do?'),
(389, 5, 67, 'Chapter 66: : slide case', '\"Kiko, you\'re finally here?!\"\n\nSonoko waved at Amamiya Noriko from under the big bucket above.\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t want to go, because the high water fell from the vat, and the impact was quite strong.\n\nSonoko was staggered just now by Xiaolan\'s hold, and more importantly.\n\nIt will destroy the hairstyle and affect her beauty.\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved to Xiaolan and Sonoko, indicating that they would not go, and asked them to come over.\n\nBut Sonoko has to do it again, and specially came over and took Amamiya Noriko\'s hand over, waiting for the bucket to be filled with water to pour down once.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s face was calm. In such a hot weather, the water in the bucket is ice?\n\nAccording to the conventions in the world of Conan, guessing in an unexpected direction.\n\nA large block of ice may have been fixed in the bucket, and the victim\'s body was sealed in it. At the hottest time of noon, the ice cubes may have almost melted, and a body suddenly fell...\n\nWhat a shocking way for the victim to appear, at this time Xiaolan screamed and Xinyi ran over: \"Xiaolan, hurry up and call the police!!\"\n\nMatsuda Jinhei and Date Hang hurriedly shouted, \"The police are here!\"\n\nThen the victim\'s boyfriend ran out with tears in his eyes, the equipment maintenance worker in the water park panicked, the plumber passing by on vacation was shocked, and Shinichi\'s eyes swept across the faces of the three strange people, already in his heart. With some certainty.\n\nThe suspects were among the equipment maintenance worker at the water park, the victim\'s boyfriend, and the plumber who was passing by on vacation.\n\nAfter Xin Yi found all kinds of clues to help, after reasoning, he came to the conclusion that the murderer was—\n\nOne of the three.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up and saw that the water in the bucket was about to fall down, and there was no ice cubes. You could see the bottom of the bucket, and there was actually a sign on the side: Heatstroke prevention cooling area, people under 120cm and under a certain weight should not stand in this area.\n\nShe raised her feet and stepped out. Before she was poured out of water, let\'s go first, so that no corpses would fall.\n\nBut Sonoko took her hand: \"Noriko can\'t always play alone.\"\n\nMy good sister is poisonous. Facing the impact of the pouring water, Noriko Amamiya could only raise one hand to block it and step on the ground with both legs.\n\nXiaolan was also worried about Noriko\'s body and wanted Sonoko to let Noriko leave, but she could only hold her head with both hands.\n\nIn fact, Sonoko stumbled under the dumping of the super-sized bucket of water. She was held tightly by Yumiya Noriko before she sat down on the ground.\n\nBut she was soaked all over again.\n\n\"Noriko, are you alright? The water is so big this time.\"\n\nSonoko touched the water on her face, spit it out, and said vaguely, still caring about Noriko Amamiya.\n\n\"I\'m fine.\"\n\nWhat else could Amamiya Noriko say? She raised her hand to help Sonoko wipe her face, so she could open her eyes and prevent water from getting in.\n\nSonoko opened her eyes and saw the face that was so close and reflected in front of her, and she gently wiped it for herself, tsk tut, \"No wonder so many boys confessed to you, Noriko, it\'s so tempting.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko rolled her eyes slightly, \"Let\'s go, Shinichi is looking for us.\"\n\nXiaolan wondered, \"Xinichi is here too?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded: \"Well, I ran into him just now.\"\n\nThen there was a murmur in my heart, Xiaolan and Sonoko didn\'t know Shinichi was there? Xinyi knew that they were also there. This straight man wants to watch beautiful swimsuits by himself?\n\nSonoko said immediately, \"Okay, let\'s go and let him see if our swimsuits look good.\"\n\nShe didn\'t forget to wink at Noriko Amamiya, obviously she was going to show Shinichi what Xiaolan\'s swimsuit looked like.\n\nAmamiya Noriko can only say that Sonoko has too much motivation in this regard, is it a perpetual motion machine in love?\n\nLeading Xiaolan Yuanzi over there, Amamiya Noriko was a little puzzled that everything in the barrel was normal, thinking that it would be good to catch the prisoner before everything was done, but the tourists who came down from the water slide next to her told her The idea is shattered.\n\nSliding down the slide was a completely motionless corpse, with a **** wound on the neck, along with a stream of reddish-stained water.\n\nXiaolan and Sonoko were stunned for a while, then looked at the corpse in front of them, and they both screamed subconsciously at the same time.\n\nAmamiya Noriko covered their eyes quickly, and immediately looked up at the integrated water slide, which was winding, straight and curved. No suspects could be seen. There were two slides on each floor. The murderer Probably went straight from another slide.\n\nLifeguards in the water park are everywhere. Immediately, some lifeguards noticed the abnormality here and ran over while shouting at other people.\n\nAmamiya Noriko rubbed the heads of Xiaolan and Sonoko, and asked them to go to the lifeguard sister to soothe the fright. Find the number of floors where the slide is, and find another slide on that floor and the slide entrance below.\n\nBut I didn\'t see any other tourists nearby.\n\nOn the other side, there were tourists who later found the body screaming in panic, and there were also lifeguards who rushed to the scene to maintain order and keep the tourists away.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked around at a person who was not unusual.\n\n\"Can you run away under my nose?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko lowered her head and took out her phone from the waterproof bag: \"Shinichi, there\'s a case here and someone was killed.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi who was with Date Hang Matsuda Jinhei heard the words and stood up abruptly. Xiaolan was still there, so he quickly said, \"I\'ll be there soon!!\"\n\nDate Hang wondered, \"What\'s wrong?\"\n\nMatsuda Jinhei took off his glasses and said calmly, \"What happened to that little girl?\"\n\nShinichi Kudo said in a succinct manner: \"The victim has appeared.\"\n\nAfter speaking, they ran out first. Date Hang and Matsuda Jinhei looked at each other, and the two immediately got up and followed.\n\nAt the same time as getting up, Matsuda Jinping quickly typed a text message and sent it to the police officers at the water park to arrange arrangements.\n\nOriginally, he really passed by, and Air Date was the coordinator of the operation, but since he was here, there was no need for fighters to direct the operation.\n\nAlthough he has not joined the search class, he is still better than Date Hang in this respect.\n\nOn the way to the scene of the crime, Matsuda Jinpei sent a few text messages, arranged for more people at the entrance and exit of the water park, and determined whether each tourist who left the water park was suspected based on the characteristics of the fugitives.\n\nThe people who were looking for fugitives in the water park went to the scene of the crime, and they were responsible for watching everyone who was suspected and left the scene in a hurry.\n\nAt the same time, the central control room directly takes over the monitoring of the water park to determine the situation in the water park.\n\nThen he called for support, medical care, etc. After everything was arranged, Matsuda Jinpei slowly put on his sunglasses on the way to run over, and his eyes under the black lenses were unusually calm and cold.\n\nEvery loss of life should be taken seriously, and every person who takes someone else\'s life should be punished accordingly.\n\nAfter arriving at the scene, Matsuda Jinhei and Date Hang showed their police IDs and asked everyone present to stand aside.\n\nMatsuda Jinping\'s cold eyes swept across everyone\'s faces under his sunglasses, and every little movement and complexion change was in his eyes.\n\nDate Hang squatted down to check the corpse~www.readwn.com~ After looking at the wound, he raised his head and looked at the bottom of the slide, where the victim slipped down. The corpse was soaked in neither deep nor shallow water. There were ups and downs, and several lifeguards moved the body to the water\'s edge.\n\nI can\'t say what happened to them. Soaking in water for too long will indeed affect the clues on the victim\'s body. At the same time, soaking in water is not good for the preservation of wounds.\n\nIt\'s just that it\'s impossible to determine what state the body was in at the time. Date Hang looked at the two little girls over there. They were the first witnesses, and they were still being comforted by Kudo Shinichi. It is impossible to ask anything.\n\n\"She was head down and face up, Uncle Police.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pulled Laida Hang\'s sleeve and said timidly.\n\nDate Hang looked at this unusually beautiful little girl, but she didn\'t expect that she would be able to stand up and give clues.\n\nHe hurriedly asked about other situations, but Amamiya Noriko had nothing else to tell him, and now he can only look at the people present over there.\n\nDate Hang and Matsuda Jinhei looked sharply at every suspect among the people present.\n\nAt the same time, Matsuda Jinhei\'s eyes under his sunglasses also fell on Kudo Shinichi. After comforting his two friends, this little boy also swept his eyes at everyone, looking for investigation, which is very suitable for being a detective.\n\nTurning his head slightly, he found that besides the three of them, there was another person watching the crowd.\n\nThe little girl named Noriko Amamiya glanced around calmly, not looking casually, but earnestly looking for suspects.\n\nMatsuda Jinhei\'s gaze fell back to the crowd.\n\n\"So, who is the murderer...\"\n\n—\n\nPS: Kiko\'s fish pond: 972832771.\n\n​​');
