(390, 5, 36, 'Chapter 35: : Can Uncle Gin sign me?', 'Amamiya Noriko didn\'t know that she had been discovered when she was looking at gin.\n\nWhen she saw Jin Jiu turn around, she also turned to study whether to arrange a chance encounter for Jin Jiu.\n\nBeing confessed by gin, it\'s exciting to think about it...\n\nIt may also be too violent to death. Gin is an emotional killer.\n\nIn short, she won\'t intervene when Gin kills a traitor. How can small arms and legs compare to Gin\'s Beretta M92F?\n\nGin is not vodka, it does not have the sunset red buff.\n\nSeeing Gin disappearing backwards from the 6F railing, Amamiya Noriko also completely retracted her gaze. They should be making preparations, and dealing with traitors is also a skill. Gin is a management team that is struggling on the front line.\n\nIn terms of the number of traitors, the winery said that no other organization would dare to say that. Akai Shuichi hasn\'t even entered the winery yet.\n\nJust as her cell phone rang, Chieda Riho was looking for her.\n\nI have already chosen what to eat. I passed the Sichuan hot pot first. I already have a high fever, and then I eat spicy and hot. Do you want to get steam?\n\nSo Chieda Riho balanced and didn\'t eat hot pot and sukiyaki.\n\nSpeaking of the difference, sukiyaki is generally not cooked with mutton, and there is no spicy option in the first impression.\n\n  what is this?\n\nMalatang is also spicy.\n\nHowever, and hot pot are not the same food at all, she can\'t ask too much.\n\nAmamiya Noriko decided to go back and import another wave of hot pot ingredients to satisfy herself, but first, she took a bite of the sukiyaki with a pile of meat in front of her. Eat it and increase her physique. If you don’t eat a little more, how can you consume enough energy? The conservation of energy can be said a bit.\n\nEmi Amamiya watched her daughter eliminate beef, and felt that this must not be inherited from her, it should be her father\'s.\n\nChieda Riho really wanted to hit Noriko Amamiya with chopsticks to remind her to pay attention to her image, but considering that Noriko Amamiya is not feeling well today, it is not easy to have such an appetite.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was just 7 minutes full when she heard a sudden exclamation in the shopping mall outside the sukiyaki store. Japan is very careful about the quietness of such occasions. Generally, this is not the case. Say something amazing happened.\n\nAs soon as her chopsticks stopped, she thought that the gin should be doing it.\n\nJust as she was about to go out to take a look, Chieda Riho stared at her in front of her, \"I don\'t know what happened outside, but it must be very chaotic. It\'s better for Noriko to sit here.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted, but she glanced at the door of the sukiyaki shop, and then she was not ready to go out.\n\nBlack clothes, black hats, black trench coats, long silver hair, and it is gin.\n\nShe subconsciously wanted to stretch out her hand to put on the mask, but then she felt that it might attract some attention, so she simply looked at the door of the sukiyaki shop so curiously.\n\nMost of the people were also looking at the door, not knowing what was going on outside, and some people with similar food got up and went outside to check the situation.\n\nGin lowered the brim of his hat and walked into the store, and naturally glanced around the store at random, and there was no pause when he swept over to Amamiya Noriko.\n\nBut still noticed that the little girl blinked her eyes when she saw him, and then looked at her with wide eyes.\n\n\"You really noticed me.\"\n\nGin calmly passed by and sat down at the next table, looking at the menu attentively, paying a little attention to the pile of beef dishes in front of her at the table of Amamiya Kiko: \"I really like meat.\"\n\nChieda Riho, however, had a tense body when Gin passed by, and her peripheral vision locked tightly on Gin.\n\nSeeing that Amamiya Noriko was still looking at the person who made her feel dangerous, she whispered, \"That person is not simple, don\'t keep looking at him.\"\n\n\"Oh?\" Amamiya Noriko whispered, \"What did Sister Qianzhi notice?\"\n\n\"It\'s quite dangerous, it must be someone who has seen blood.\"\n\nChieda Riho said in a low voice with a calm expression on her face.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded. Sister Chie is still not as observant as Kudo Shinichi. As soon as Kudo Shin saw Gin\'s eyes, he could tell that it was the eyes that killed a lot of people and didn\'t care at all. What a pair of death gods. Eye.\n\nChieda Riho stretched her hand to her pocket and took out her mobile phone, as if she was browsing the web, but in fact, she didn\'t want to alarm the dangerous person, and was going to send an email to get the bodyguard to come over.\n\nAfter the kidnapping incident, Amamiya Ludou sent a few more bodyguards to his daughter, but they wouldn\'t follow him at any time. Usually, Chieda Riho is enough.\n\nShe now judges that she cannot protect Noriko Amamiya\'s safety 100%, so she is ready to shake people.\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave her a piece of beef, blinked and said, \"No need, we are definitely safe.\"\n\nBecause Jin Jiu had just dealt with a traitor, it should be that the gun was not fired, and it might have caused an accidental death.\n\nThen basically, I won\'t attack them here. No matter how I look at them, they are just three ordinary beautiful girls, and they don\'t threaten anything, right?\n\nOnce you start, disguising the traitor\'s death as an accident will be in vain.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is also thinking about eating a sukiyaki quietly. If the gin can\'t come over, it\'s just a shot, right?\n\nHowever, Chieda Riho still didn\'t feel safe, so she told him to eat quickly and leave early.\n\nEmi Amamiya was unsure from beginning to end, so she heard that it was right to eat quickly.\n\nHe also lowered his head and started to eat, so he stopped ordering, and occasionally quietly looked at what the gin was doing.\n\nHe wasn\'t doing anything, he just sat there waiting for the food to be served.\n\n\"Could it be that Gin likes sukiyaki?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it carefully, but she didn\'t remember having this hobby, but she tried to turn her body around, imitating the sitting angle of Gin, and after turning her head, she thought, \"Gin is this. Out of the corner of the eye can see her side.\n\nBecause Gin has long silver hair and a hat, she\'s not even sure.\n\nBut the feeling is the problem. Gin definitely doesn’t want to go out of the mall at this time. If the police find that the accident was not an accident, it is impossible to check everyone in the mall. people.\n\nSo Gin will enter a certain store and will not leave the mall at this time, but the question is, why is sukiyaki? Why does it happen to be her Sukiyaki?\n\nAmamiya Noriko first assumed that Gin had noticed him, and the reason was unknown, but at this time, she must not do anything that would make Gin suspect.\n\nShe originally wanted to go to Miyano Akimi and Miyano Shiho in the future, but she canceled it for now. It had already attracted Gin\'s attention. If she met Shirley again at this time, she would be even more suspicious.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while while eating the meat, and felt that Gin should have found herself looking at him downstairs before, but she didn\'t notice it at the time, so Gin was concerned about why she was looking at him at that time.\n\n\"How did I see the gin at that time?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, thinking that Gin had already tried her best, worship, yes, worship.\n\nWhen Chieda Riho went to check out at the counter, Amamiya Noriko got up and walked over to Gin, went straight to Gin, and looked at him prettily.\n\nJin Jiu raised his head slightly in response, but his cold eyes did not fluctuate.\n\nThen he heard the little girl he had been observing quietly whisper: \"Uncle, you must be a big star in this dress, right? Can you sign me?\"\n\n\"...\"\n\n​​'),
(391, 5, 93, 'Chapter 92: : 2nd generation fat man', '\"Little sister, what\'s your name?\"\n\nWhen the little fat man smiled, the fat on his face was crowded together, and his eyes almost disappeared.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is also me. It\'s easy for other people to think that you closed your eyes when talking to others.\n\nShe doesn\'t discriminate against Fatty, but it\'s okay for this Fatty to greet him with a smile, his grin is about to come out, and his squinted eyes look up and down at her, his eyes are very unpleasant.\n\nBecause the storage space for spare clothes is limited, it is just such a white dress. Although the skirt is long to the calf, it looks fresh and refined in summer.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled brightly and said, \"Have you seen enough?\"\n\n\"Of course I haven\'t seen enough. What\'s your name? Which one does it belong to? My father is the Nancun police inspector, and the head of the traffic department. I\'m Nancun Takaya.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pursed her lips and smiled and said, \"I heard your father cracked a smuggling case recently?\"\n\n\"You know that, of course. In fact, I happened to be at the scene that day, and the truck driver looked very dragged. I saw that he was upset and stopped him. I didn\'t expect to hide a lot of things.\"\n\n\"But in fact, I\'ve already seen that there\'s something wrong with that guy. There are still a lot of good things. A bunch of chemicals that seem to be banned, and they don\'t look very valuable. They were all handed over by Dad.\"\n\nSpeaking of this, Takashi Minamura couldn\'t help but speak proudly. After speaking, he felt that he just happened to be not handsome enough, and changed it to his own eyes to see the problem.\n\nHow, so handsome, no girl would not be tempted, right?\n\nTakashi Nanmura proudly stroked his greasy bangs with his fat hands, dashingly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, she understood, and when she turned back, she arranged an encounter with Master Qin. He happened to hear the words intact, and he would give you a ride on the Distillery Express Hell Express, which is more dashing.\n\n\"I didn\'t keep the chemicals because they didn\'t look like they were worth anything, but it\'s nice to have a small box, and there are capsules that I don\'t know what to use. I tell you, it must be a fake drug, but It\'s the kind of non-genuine medicine that really works, and it\'s expensive.\"\n\n\"I didn\'t keep those chemicals, but I kept the finished product. I\'ll go back and see what medicines are there. All medicines are good. It saves the trouble of buying them.\"\n\nTakashi Nanmura was talking to himself, and gradually began to look like he was losing his mind. When Noriko Amamiya heard the last look, you were taking too much medicine, right?\n\n\"Second-generations who remove the main characters are really scumbags. No wonder they can be used as a reason for the murderer to commit the crime.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko smacked her lips and took out the disposable gloves for chicken eating from the skirt.\n\nTakashi Nanmura\'s eyes lit up, \"Ah, I was thinking that you are a little small, maybe you have less fun. I didn\'t expect you to bring it with you.\"\n\n\"Well, can\'t you take it with you?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tore open the package, put on disposable gloves, and stretched her fingers.\n\nNanmura Takahashi looked at it in astonishment. Hunger was different from what he thought.\n\n\"Hey—\"\n\nMinamura Takashi slapped a straight fist next to his head, and the wind brought him to his senses.\n\nAmamiya Noriko flicked her wrists to move her muscles and bones, and then her slender hands clenched into fists, and the hurried fists kept swept past Takashi Nanmura\'s head, each time it almost hit him by the slightest error.\n\nNanmura Takashi felt the torrential wind and rain rubbing his fist past his ears. The sound of the wind was coming one after another, and it was about to smash into his ears. He couldn\'t help but his face was tense and hard, and his face gradually turned pale.\n\nHe squeezed out a few words between his teeth: \"You bastard, who are you...\"\n\n\"I\'m here to let you feel the love of society, huhu.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko exhaled, and the speed of the punches increased. At the moment when Takaya Nanmura\'s lips trembled, he subconsciously took a step back, and he closed his fists and bent his arms, \"Stunning uppercuts with full proficiency.\"\n\nNanmura Takao suddenly suffered a severe blow to his jaw, and he rolled his eyes in pain and lost consciousness.\n\nAmamiya Noriko stretched out her hand and pressed the head of Takashi Minamura, who was about to collapse, against the wall on one side, letting him slowly lean against the wall and slump in the corner.\n\nIn the first fight of fighting boxing learned in Hawaii, he knocked down with one punch, full score.\n\nThe gloved hand grabbed the opponent\'s back collar and dragged the person to the most corner. Yuanzi\'s room was originally in the corner of the top floor, and generally no one would come here.\n\n\"Buzz.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at the phone that vibrated in his pocket, and it was a message from his father: \"The man next to me is Nancun police inspector. He wants me to marry my precious daughter to his son. It\'s whimsical. And his son\'s behavior is very bad, if you see the fat man, try to avoid it.\"\n\n\"It\'s whimsical, yes, yes.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was satisfied with her father\'s response and replied, \"Okay, I will avoid them. You and your mother should try not to get close to them.\"\n\nThat adult policeman is probably Master Qin\'s real target.\n\nThen he threw Nancun Takashi in the corner and went to the bathroom of Yuanzi\'s room to wash the disposable gloves away.\n\nAmamiya Noriko went out and went back to the banquet. She had already opened the trumpet, but she was delayed by that fat man.\n\nBoth scumbags and scumbags have no meaning at all, and they won\'t add points without a heartfelt confession, wasting her time.\n\nHowever, it’s still okay to provide a little clue. Go back and turn the fat man over to the police, and casually mention his drug use as an enthusiastic citizen. As for him saying that he was beaten by a beautiful girl, it’s a matter of opinion. Whether the police officer will believe it or not is a matter of opinion. A drug addict.\n\nIt doesn\'t matter if you believe it, her face is rarely used.\n\nAfter she went out for a while, Kudo Shinichi, who was looking around, walked to the corner of Sonoko\'s room and looked inside.\n\n\"Where did Amamiya go?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pondered, he saw that Amamiya Noriko should be heading towards her father, but he had already turned around in the background~www.readwn.com~ did not see Amamiya Noriko.\n\nOriginally, after being reminded by Noriko Amamiya, Shinichi Kudo turned his detective instincts into full force and went around the banquet to collect any suspicious information.\n\nOf course, he would not be left behind in the backstage, but in the backstage, Chieda Riho was seen bringing Amamiya Ludou and Amamiya Emi over, but their daughter Amamiya Noriko was not seen.\n\nIt stands to reason that Amamiya Noriko reminded him that he was going to her father later, why are they not together again?\n\nHe was in a very complicated mood, feeling that Amamiya Noriko was the person with the most suspicious points in the audience.\n\nHe walked around this corner at will, and at the corner at the end of the aisle, he frowned when he saw the fat man collapsed on the ground.\n\n\"Victim?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi squatted down and probed. His breathing was normal, and he seemed to just fall asleep.\n\nWhy do you sleep here for no reason?\n\nKudo Shin took a look at the back of the other\'s head and neck, and there seemed to be no injuries, which made people want to find out.\n\nEven though he patted his face, he couldn\'t wake up.\n\n\"Sorry, this is to collect clues to help you find out what\'s going on.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi put a handkerchief into his chest pocket with a handkerchief, and slowly took out a small packet of white powder.\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s face turned dark, a drug addict?\n\nHe thought that he had finally found a breakthrough in Amamiya Noriko\'s vague suspense, wasting his expression.\n\nWhen he was speechless and prepared to tell Officer Mumu about them, the slight footsteps approaching made him feel chills. The moment he turned his head suddenly, he was slashed by a palm knife. The last moment he lost consciousness, he saw a wheat-colored skin. He picked up the small bag of powder in his hand.'),
(392, 5, 97, 'Chapter 96: : she feels ok', 'The chaotic scene did not gradually recover until there was no more movement, and the security personnel finally came in handy.\n\nMainly because of the sound of explosions and being shot one after another before, they easily mistakenly think that the robbers who **** gems are gangsters with firearms, and these security guards who do not have gun licenses dare not come forward at will.\n\nThe police and his party did not bring in guns because they attended the banquet as police representatives instead of being in charge of security.\n\nUnder the extremely chaotic situation, Megumi Police Officer Sato Date Hang and his party were all doing their best to make the guests who were running around crouch down, not to run around at the scene.\n\nIn this way, even if the bandits have any conditions, it is easy to negotiate, and the lives of civilians are the most important.\n\nFortunately, it seems that after the gem was snatched away, the culprits also fled directly.\n\nAt this time, Officer Mumu looked at the corpse of the police officer in Nancun, his face was darker than Xiaohei, he took out his mobile phone and called angrily to ask for support!\n\nAnd Amamiya Noriko went directly to the room to change back to the original appearance after confirming that the gin and vodka had left.\n\nIf they don\'t show up again at this time, Xiaolan Yuanzi and the others will really be worried.\n\nHowever, it seems a bit inappropriate to look clean.\n\nAmamiya Noriko lowered her head and lifted her skirt, buttoned up some wall powder and sprinkled some powder on the wall. As for the disgraced face, it\'s useless. At most, it can only affect her image but not cover her face.\n\nWhen she went outside, she saw Kudo Shinichi first, and she couldn\'t help but feel deeply ashamed. This is the real embarrassment for others, and she was too fake. She could only grab the skirt and rub it to make some wrinkles, and learn from Kudo Shinichi. .\n\nAmamiya Noriko patted the dust on Kudo Shinichi\'s body, it was a bit too much, she chose to withdraw her hand to symbolically blow the dust off his body.\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s face turned black: \"What are you blowing across half a meter...\"\n\nApparently, after patting it, one hand of dust disliked him.\n\nAmamiya Noriko simply reached out and patted the dust on him, and asked, \"What\'s wrong with you?\"\n\nSpeaking of this Kudo Shinichi, his face was expressionless: \"Those idiots, they are squeezing into the elevator when the power is cut off. Their brains are really good.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko seemed to have seen the scene of Kudo Shinichi being squeezed by the elevator and almost squeezed into patties, so he could only pat his head pitifully and said, \"Learning detective may not save the world, I suggest studying medicine.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"...\"\n\nDon\'t take the opportunity to shake my ideals!\n\nUnhappily, he patted Kiko Amamiya\'s hand away. Kudo Shin patted off the ashes from his body in one or three times. He turned his head to look at the banquet scene where order was gradually restored from the chaos, \"Has the prisoner escaped?\"\n\n\"Well, maybe, it was so chaotic at the time, I didn\'t see it clearly.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, and the drinks all ran away.\n\nKudo Shin took a look at Amamiya Noriko, and carefully glanced at Amamiya Noriko\'s face, don\'t pretend, you don\'t want to get dirty on your face, even getting dirty on your skirt is a little bit stingy, this person must have been just now Incredibly safe.\n\nHe didn\'t want to expose it, and asked Amamiya Noriko to take care of Xiaolan Yuanzi and the others, and then went straight to the corpse of the Nancun police inspector.\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head and let him go, working with so much wine, and it was intricate work, it was time to test Kudo Shinichi\'s skills.\n\nAmamiya Noriko walked over to Xiaolan Yuanzi\'s side. After seeing her, both Xiaolan and Yuanzi rushed over to hug her, and then checked her body for any injuries, making Amamiya Noriko a little helpless.\n\nBut don\'t touch it, it\'s not good to touch something under the skirt.\n\nThe two of Xiaolan Yuanzi were fine, at most they were a little frightened.\n\nThe weak Amamiya Noriko was of course safe and sound even hiding in the toilet.\n\nXiaolan stretched out her hand and patted the ashes on Kiko Amamiya\'s skirt, her eyes filled with concern: \"Fortunately, Kiko was in the toilet just now. It was a mess outside. By the way, have you seen Shinichi?\"\n\n\"Xinyi is fine, he went over there.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pointed to the place where several police gathered there, it was the Nancun police station.\n\nXiaolan understood in an instant, and the reasoning frenzy started again.\n\nShe also didn\'t go over there to find Shinichi, and met with Kiko Yuanzi to find her elders.\n\nSuzuki\'s family is still easier to find. Suzuki Jiroji was jumping on the edge of the broken glass showcase on the stage, angrily accusing the gangster of the crime.\n\nHe was basically knocked down by Tou Zi as soon as the gate was opened. The situation behind him was heard from other people. After hearing the gem was taken away, he angrily scolded the waste of the security company, and shouted for dismissal and so on. .\n\n\"It was really taken away.\" Yuanzi said helplessly, but she said very excitedly: \"However, at that time, I vaguely saw someone standing up to fight the bandits, and kicked the bandits away with one kick. Now, if someone hadn\'t set a black gun, that person would have defeated the gangsters.\"\n\nAmemiya Noriko: \"...Niu Niu.\"\n\nAs expected of your professional intelligence dealer, could you still notice this at that time?\n\nBut she didn\'t have to worry about being recognized. At that time, the light in the venue was still very dark, and only the light from the blasted glass came in. Sonoko couldn\'t see her clearly, and she had changed her face.\n\nJust left a hero\'s legend in Sonoko\'s heart.\n\nXiaolan asked; \"Did that person get hit by a gun?\"\n\n\"It shouldn\'t be. I don\'t have any blood in the stands. It seems that I rolled over and avoided the bullets. It\'s super handsome.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pursed her lips and listened, don\'t use adjectives to exaggerate. At that time, she completely noticed from Toko\'s face and eyes that there might be a sniper from behind her, so she avoided it in advance.\n\nNo normal person can do that.\n\nMaori Kogoro went to the police to join in the fun. His reverse reasoning was in play, and the whole incident gradually turned to a twisted and bizarre direction, which was really hard to fathom.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also found her parents and Chieda Riho, and everything was fine, so she told Sonoko Xiaolan to go to her parents first.\n\nChie Riho was relieved after seeing her, because she couldn\'t find Amamiya Noriko to protect Amamiya Emi, and she was always worried that Noriko was abducted again.\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked secretly, indicating that she was completely ok, Chieda Riho nodded, understanding, it was good that she was not kidnapped.\n\nAmamiya Lu Dou saw his daughter came back, so he buttoned back a few buttons of his suit. If the situation was dangerous, his fighting power would be okay.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that she was completely fine, and then looked at her father: \"How do you say?\"\n\n\"The situation is a bit complicated. Intuitively, the death of the police officer in Nancun is strange. It is too coincidental to say that the death was caused by a broken glass.\"\n\nPeople like Amamiya Ludou would not believe in coincidences in the first place.\n\n\"You\'d better go abroad with us for a while.\"\n\nHe knows that his daughter has been very good since kindergarten, so he can talk directly to each other.\n\nAs early as he came back from Hawaii some time ago, he felt that he was not very handy in using the Japanese company. Many people who used to feel excellent were transferred and resigned. Although the general situation has not changed much, he even talked about the benefits of various aspects. More objective and seems to be moving in a good direction.\n\nBut the problem is not in my own control~www.readwn.com~ The development in a good direction can finally fall into my own hands or not.\n\nMore importantly, in his careful thinking just now, he also discovered that only the roof of the Amamiya Building can be shot flat to the showcase, which makes him feel very insecure.\n\n\"Let\'s go ahead as soon as possible, and go abroad to rectify the company on the Japanese side.\"\n\nIt\'s too unsafe to stay in Japan. He would always bomb and kidnap his daughter. If he stayed in Japan for rectification, he couldn\'t fully guarantee the safety of his family.\n\nNoriko Amamiya is not too worried. The winery is not a pure murder organization. With the power of the Amamiya consortium, cooperation is not impossible, and the winery will not solve problems by killing everything. The transaction achieves its purpose.\n\nJust like the episode of Xinyi getting smaller, the winery does not necessarily only kill what people want, but also trades it.\n\nBesides, she still has Uncle Gin\'s signature, and she is good sisters with bourbon, rye whiskey, scotch whisky, and Shirley, and she thinks it\'s ok.\n\nThe winery\'s strongest action team is whether her people have it or not.'),
(393, 5, 18, 'Chapter 17: : Familiar for a while, Xiuxiu', 'The next day, Amamiya Noriko came to take a look at Shuichi Akai after the club activities.\n\nIt is impossible for Akai Shuuichi to confess with her heart. This is what she observed yesterday and the conclusion she drew from the original work.\n\nShuichi Akai approached Akemi Miyano to join the organization, but at the same time he broke up with Judy, who he was dating, saying that he couldn\'t fall in love with two people at the same time.\n\nTo make him confess, he had to give up Akemi Miyano, which made Noriko Amamiya more difficult. Shuichi Akai even gave up his ex-girlfriend Judy for the mission.\n\nShe doesn\'t have time to hang around here every day.\n\nSo let Akai show a confession, cross it out, and change it to let Akai show familiarity.\n\nMaybe she will appear in Shuichi Akai\'s sniper scope in the future?\n\nJust don\'t pull the trigger so ruthlessly.\n\nTherefore, Amamiya Noriko is now sitting beside the hospital bed, taking care of what she should eat and drink.\n\nFamiliarity doesn\'t have to do anything, surprises have miraculous effects, and making them curious is also useful.\n\nBesides, she\'s really not free. While eating the little strawberries she bought, she opened the envelopes she found in the shoe cabinet when she was in school.\n\nThe love letter, to be honest, it was the first time I received it, and the children in elementary school didn\'t know how to play it.\n\nThe main idea in the letter is that she is very attractive when she is quietly watching the football next to the football field. She looks very cute and so on. I hope she can see her at the back of the teaching building after school...\n\nAmamiya Noriko folded the envelope and stuffed it back without changing her face. After she opened the shoe cabinet and saw it, she put it in her schoolbag and didn\'t open it on the spot.\n\nCan you still catch up with rejection when you go back to the teaching building now?\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the sky and felt that it would be too cruel to go all the way back to refuse. She didn\'t know who the person was or was still there, so she just assumed that nothing had happened.\n\nThere was no signature in the main letter, and there was still suspense, thinking that she would know when she went to the teaching building, and she could only treat the other party as Xiao Hei.\n\nI really miss Xiao Hei\'s evil smile and white teeth.\n\nAkai Shuichi thought her reaction was quite interesting, and asked in a distinctive voice, \"Love letter?\"\n\n\"Well, I really received the wishes of classmate Anonymous, but unfortunately, there is no way to respond.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko regretted that she didn\'t receive any attributes.\n\nAkai Hidey looked at her quite used to it: \"Is it possible that many people like you at school?\"\n\n\"Let\'s get rid of the difficulties and doubts, I just sat by the side for a while and fell in love.\"\n\nAkai Shuichi calmly said: \"I\'m not sure it\'s because of your personality, you don\'t look like a normal female junior high school student at all, right? Will it be popular?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko squinted at him: \"Big brother, I found out that you started Kudo Shinichi, will Miyano Akimi like you?\"\n\n  \"Uh…\"\n\nMiyano Akimi\'s bewildered voice came from the door, and there was a bit of blush on her face.\n\nAkai Shuichi and Amamiya Noriko turned their heads stiffly, because they were all staggered, Miyano Akemi had not seen Amamiya Noriko before.\n\n\"That...I forgot to take the key. Hello, are you Zhuxingda\'s sister?\"\n\n\"Yes, sister Akimi~ I\'m Noriko Zhuxing.\" Noriko Amamiya turned to look at Shuichi Akai.\n\nAkai Shuichi can only nod his head in cooperation.\n\nMiyano Akemi smiled and said, \"You two are so good. I also have a younger sister.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked: \"Huh? I also want to see sister Mingmei\'s sister!\"\n\n\"Okay, I\'ll introduce you to her when she comes back. My sister is very smart.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, thinking that I know, what is the concept of a 17-year-old top scientist, Xiaoai nb.\n\nI felt like I was a 100-volt light bulb in the ward, and I was always stared at by Akai Shuichi out of the corner of my eye, so Amamiya Noriko left.\n\nThe next day in good health, I went to school with Kudo Shinichi and the others.\n\nKudo Shinichi was full of exploratory spirit: \"Kiko, what have you been busy with these two days? Run away as soon as the club activities are over.\"\n\n\"I went to see the patient.\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nKudo Shin-Xiaolan and Sonoko both turned to look at her. Are there too many sick friends?\n\n\"What\'s so strange, you are also my patients.\"\n\nThe three of them felt a little overwhelmed.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned to look at the three high school students who were leaning against the telephone pole in front of them. They were not the uniforms of Tedan Middle School, but other schools.\n\nAnd the whole body exudes the smell of a bad boy, specifically referring to the red mohawk hairstyle, the kelp bangs covering the eyes, the explosive head and the smell of inferior cigarettes that can be smelled from a distance.\n\nThe high school student with a mohawk head took a sip of cigarette between his fingers and stood in front of them: \"Which one is Noriko Amamiya? Are you?\"\n\nHe quickly locked the target, because Noriko Amamiya was very close to the description he heard, with beautiful long hair and a cute face.\n\n\"It\'s really cute...\"\n\nAfter muttering to himself, he stretched out his hand to grab Noriko Amamiya: \"Little sister, come with us.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled confidently, reaching out to twist his dirty hands.\n\n\"Stop!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi stood up, raised his hand and clapped the other\'s hand away: \"Hey, you are high school students anyway, but your behavior is really clumsy, comparable to elementary school students.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who was about to show her hand just now, wanted to pull him away. You blocked my showtime.\n\nBut Xiaolan and Sonoko, whose sisterhood is stronger than Jin Jian, also stood in front of her without any fear.\n\nDo I look so weak? Can you give me a chance?\n\nMo Xigan crooked his mouth and pushed his palm towards Kudo Shinichi: \"The kid in middle school is very courageous, UU reading www.uukanshu.com must be honest in front of seniors.\"\n\nTo be honest, Kudo Shinichi just graduated from elementary school in the first year of junior high, and his body can\'t compare with the high school students who have basically gone through the development period.\n\nIt\'s just that he has also been trained to play football since he was a child, and he is not stupid enough to stand and wait for the opponent to make a move before reacting.\n\nOnly then did Mo Xigan lift his hand, Fuji Shinichi had already reached out with both hands, twisted the opponent\'s wrist and pulled down, twisted his backhand, and with a scream, Mo Xigan\'s arm was dislocated.\n\nIt is very simple to grab with one hand. Kudo Shinichi, who aspires to become a famous detective, has seen it in books, but it is also the first time to use it in actual combat.\n\nMo Xigan screamed, turned his head and woke up his two stunned companions: \"Hurry up and help!\"\n\n  \"oh oh!\"\n\n\"Don\'t be too arrogant, little brat!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi clenched his fists with both hands in front of him, his heart beating fast, nervous and excited, not afraid, but eager to try.\n\nHe has been determined to become a great detective like Sherlock Holmes since he was a child, and today is his first battle to protect the weak!\n\n\"Bang—\"\n\nThe tall, afro-haired fat man in front of him suddenly fell to the ground, and as soon as Kudo Shinobi looked down, he saw Noriko Amamiya, who was leaning over his legs.\n\n  \"asshole!\"\n\nThe skinny Kelp head roared when he saw this, raised his fist, and suddenly fell down with his chin raised.\n\nKudo Shinichi felt a white shadow flashing in front of her eyes, and Amamiya Noriko was still keeping her legs high, her white shoes were tall, and it was obvious that she had hit the opponent\'s chin hard just now.\n\nAmamiya Noriko put down her feet, fluttered her hair that was messed up because she was too handsome, her soft eyes like cherry blossoms sparkled, and said with a soft and glutinous voice.\n\n\"Don\'t ignore me, this is my showtime.\"'),
(394, 5, 35, 'Chapter 34: : Gin~', '\"Sister Chie also came to eat together.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pulled Chieda Riho out of the car.\n\nLooking at the crowded square, Chieda Riho also felt that she needed to take care of her, so she did not refuse.\n\n\"What is Kiko going to eat?\"\n\n\"Eat Sichuan hot pot.\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nQianzhi Lisui searched in her mind, and finally located a foreign place name across the sea, and also synchronized the knowledge of Sichuan hot pot characteristics.\n\nChie Riho stretched out her hand and grabbed Noriko Amamiya: \"No, you have a high fever and still want to eat that spicy food?\"\n\n  \"what???\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was shocked and said to her: \"Eating hot pot can reduce fever.\"\n\nEmi Amamiya nodded in agreement, because she had never eaten it and wanted to try it.\n\nThen Chieda Riho saw that she felt guilty.\n\nChieda Riho went straight to the road sign to see what restaurants in the mall would be more suitable.\n\nAmamiya Noriko found a vending machine and bought a bottle of water, then sat down on the bench next to the vending machine.\n\nIf you have a fever or a cold, you should drink more water, and your throat will dry quickly.\n\nAmamiya Emi also sat down beside her daughter and asked a little puzzled, \"How come no one has come to talk to her until now?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko rolled her eyes, took off her mask and drank water.\n\n  \"a bit sweet.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked down at the origin of the mineral water brand, not Nongfu Spring, right?\n\nA man in a suit in the middle of the mall looked down at his watch to observe the time, with a magazine in his other hand.\n\nHe frowned, young people nowadays really have no sense of time at all, they are just a nicer looking vase, and they have the guts to be late.\n\nNot wanting to waste time waiting, he raised his head to leave, but suddenly saw two girls sitting beside the vending machine over there.\n\nA beautiful and somewhat natural high school girl, a cute and outrageous junior high school girl who took off her mask, her cheeks were a little flushed, and her clear eyes looked at the mineral water in a trance.\n\nHe was still muttering something.\n\n\"...Mount Fuji\'s snow water, a gift from nature? It\'s too beautiful to think about, at most I\'ll give you a porter.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave her mother the water and put the mask back on.\n\nEimi Amamiya curiously looked at the packaging and advertisement of the water bottle, \"Does Noriko want to go skiing? Shall we go skiing next week?\"\n\nA voice sounded in front of the two of them: \"The snow in Hokkaido is still very beautiful.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Amamiya Emi looked up at the man in front of them.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes opened and closed: it is not so easy for a middle-aged uncle to confess.\n\nEmi Amamiya: Why is he an uncle? No little brother?\n\nThe man in the suit felt that he was being underestimated, so he reached out and patted the magazine he was holding.\n\n\"Hello, two beautiful young ladies, I\'m Sando Mokishi, the artist manager of Cherry Blossom Performing Arts and Culture Company. I\'m currently looking for models for the magazine.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Amamiya Emi nodded politely, and then there was no more.\n\nEmi Amamiya is so beautiful that she is always the spokesperson for her husband\'s Amemiya Consortium. Although it\'s like Amamiya Ludou coaxing his wife to play the house, she must have been caught by a group of people in the past, such as the reception and banquet of the Amemiya Consortium abroad. Surrounded by rich ladies.\n\nThis kind of small county magazines really didn\'t have much appeal to her.\n\nFor Amamiya Noriko, as soon as she appeared in a magazine, she would definitely be popular, and she made her debut three times in a row, but have you seen any big star who can often be confessed face-to-face?\n\nOn the contrary, fewer people will be able to confess.\n\nShe couldn\'t effectively refuse those confessions from the magazines on the screen. She felt that it was troublesome enough to refuse the love letters stuffed in the shoe cabinet.\n\n  simple is the best.\n\nSantang Hongan felt that the atmosphere was gradually stiffening, so he said straight to the point: \"The two have such beautiful looks, are you interested in trying them out on the road of acting? Maybe there will be many fans.\"\n\nEimi Amamiya blinked at Noriko Amamiya: \"Is Noriko interested?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head, suddenly her neck froze and she looked to the side.\n\nA person is riding up the escalator in the middle of the shopping mall, tall and slender, with a black trench coat and top hat, long white hair, and extremely sharp eyes...\n\nAh... Shirley...\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook off her messy thoughts and was a little curious: \"Why is Gin here?\"\n\nWith so many people in the mall, she doesn\'t have to worry about being affected by the explosion. Gin is mostly to clear out traitors, and at most a small explosion won\'t blow up the entire mall.\n\n\"Mom, I\'ll go shopping there first. Sister Chie will call me after she chooses where to eat.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head and left a sentence, got up and went to the elevator.\n\nIt\'s a pity that Sandou Honkishi saw the beautiful girl leave, but luckily there is another high school girl who is also very beautiful... Wait?\n\nThe beautiful girl just now called this mother?\n\nHe looked at Emi Amamiya in astonishment.\n\nAmamiya Emi blinked: \"Oh, I\'m sorry, that kid just likes to be in a hurry, so he said he wanted to call his sister outside.\"\n\n\"Madam...you\'re really young...ha...haha...\"\n\nSantang Honishi is extremely rigid, and as an artist manager, he can even misread this situation, which is very bad.\n\nNo, the main reason is that the other party is too deceptive.\n\nA fairly long and pretty girl trotted over from one side and waved: \"I\'m sorry, Mr. Manager, because the traffic jam is over.\"\n\nSantang Honishi feels that this is a normal person, UU reading www.uukanshu. Com waved his hand: \"It\'s okay, find a place to talk.\"\n\nHowever, she still gave her business card to Emi Amamiya: \"If you and your daughter are interested, you can contact me.\"\n\nThe girl who trotted over was surprised, did she have a daughter at such a young age? How old are you supposed to be, baby? Shooting children\'s clothing?\n\nSantang Hongan hurriedly led her away stiffly.\n\nOn the other side, Amamiya Noriko, who was wearing a mask, followed Gin at a certain distance, and she didn\'t dare to get too close. She tried her best to observe from the corner of her eye. Maybe she could be found by pulling some air.\n\n3F Stair entrance.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at Gin and walked in, and she couldn\'t follow him all of a sudden. Whoever takes the stairs when there is nothing in the mall, he will be bumped into immediately when he enters.\n\n\"But why did you start entering the stairwell on the third floor?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko took the escalator all the way to the fifth floor, and looked at the 4F and 5F halfway through. She didn\'t notice any suspicious people, but she saw Miyano Akimi and Miyano Shiho who were quite unexpected in the cafe on the 4th floor.\n\n\"Oh, I finally came back from America.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was quite pleasantly surprised, but then she found out that Gin appeared on the 6F, leaning against the railing and looking in the direction of a man in a suit shop opposite the 5F.\n\nWhen she looked at Jin Jiu, her eyes narrowed slightly, and the corner of her mouth twitched, revealing a rather sinister smile.\n\n\"As expected of the gin who went further and further on the road of killing traitors.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko praised, but he didn\'t go further and further, for the next two years he was surrounded by traitors.\n\n6F.\n\nGin, who was already staring at the target, suddenly noticed his sight, turned slightly and glanced in the direction of sight from the corner of his eye.\n\nA little girl wearing a mask, this look... is it worship?');
