(395, 5, 73, 'Chapter 72: : Girl\'s stuff and Ota-kun', 'Kudo Shinichi and Xiao Ran chatted casually, while Sonoko\'s eyes were always on the hair rope on Kudo Shinichi\'s wrist.\n\nThis is too exciting.\n\nShe looked at Xiaolan cautiously, but Xiaolan didn\'t notice this at all.\n\nDamn, does Shinichi Kudo carry Ran with a girl outside? ! !\n\nSonoko\'s barren chest is full of loyalty, and the sister\'s boyfriend must test himself to defend it.\n\n\"Yuanzi, Xiaolan, are you also shopping?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who was carrying a lot of things, said in a happy tone, Sonoko was pleasantly surprised, Noriko has returned from an overseas trip... But she immediately realized that the hair rope belonged to Noriko?\n\nAh, this...\n\nHer eyes kept switching between Noriko and Xiaolan. After the last time, she thought that she could be sure that Noriko and Shinichi were innocent, but now...\n\nIs it time to stand in line again?\n\nShe hugged Noriko stiffly, Sonoko helped Noriko get some things, and then carefully observed, she was too difficult.\n\nAmamiya Noriko hugged Xiaolan again and said, \"Xiaolan, you see Shinichi doesn\'t help me with anything.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: Cow.\n\nHe simply and neatly took over what was left in Noriko Amamiya\'s hand, you can stop.\n\n\"Well, it\'s not that Shinichi doesn\'t help me with things at all.\"\n\nXiaolan was helpless, she was used to it. After Shinichi bullied Noriko, she came to her when she was wronged, as if she was someone from Shinichi.\n\nShe glanced at Shinichi and knew that you didn\'t bully Noriko, but couldn\'t you take care of Noriko?\n\nKudo Shinichi returned a helpless expression, at least saying that he did not bully Noriko Amamiya. As for taking care of him, he felt that he needed to be taken care of.\n\nWhile Noriko was chatting with Xiaolan, Sonoko stretched out his hand and pulled the hair rope on Kudo Shin\'s hand, then released it, and slapped it on Kudo Shin\'s hand.\n\nShin Kudo was speechless to Sonoko\'s mindless behavior: \"What are you doing?\"\n\nSonoko patted him with his backhand and said in a low voice, \"Do normal boys have hair ropes for girls other than their girlfriends??\"\n\nKudo Shinichi wondered for a moment, then looked at the hair rope on his wrist...\n\nAfter a short silence, his eyes moved from the hair rope to Xiao Lan over there.\n\n\"Quickly take this thing away!!!\"\n\n\"What are you doing for me!! It\'s Kiko\'s!\"\n\n\"Anyway, I can\'t take this thing with you! It\'s fine for you to take it!!!\"\n\nSonoko didn\'t answer instinctively, Kudo Shinichi and her stalemate for a long time, Xiaolan over there wondered: \"What are you doing?\"\n\nKudo Shin put his hands behind his back for a moment, his eyes drifted to the clouds in the sky: \"What can I do, the weather today is really good.\"\n\nYuanzi: \"...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi, who can\'t see that you are shrewd and wise, hides it in a panic, and can be so rough.\n\nNo matter how Xiao Lan didn\'t notice it, she would still feel that Xinyi was a little weird.\n\n\"What is Shinichi hiding?\"\n\n  \"No.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi used a calm tone that would not arouse suspicion at all.\n\nXiaolan said softly, \"Then stretch out your hand to take a look?\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nSonoko looked at Kudo Shinichi\'s stiff appearance. From her side, she could see Kudo Shinichi\'s hand behind his back, but quietly trying to untie Amamiya Noriko\'s hair rope.\n\nBut there is a problem that Kudo Shinichi was helped to carry a bunch of things of Noriko Amamiya, and with his hands behind his back, he was a little bit unable to take off the hair rope.\n\nIn a hurry, he already had the heart to die. Before she dies, it is enough to bring the culprit, Noriko Amamiya, too.\n\nInnocent like Kiko Amemiya, she looked at the sweaty Kudo Shinichi beside Xiao Lan in confusion, what was she playing?\n\nCould it be that there is a little yellow book hidden behind Xinyi?\n\nThis is very exciting.\n\nSonoko, who understands the most, is watching this scene. When it\'s over, Noriko looks curious. It seems that Noriko is\n\n  Unaware.\n\nThen why is Noriko\'s hair rope on Kudo Shinichi\'s wrist?\n\nXiaolan finally couldn\'t bear Xinyi\'s secretive look. She wanted to see what Xinyi was playing with her? !\n\nIf you do something bad, let Xinyi have a taste of his own karate success!\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi saw this, he could only sigh, and stretched out the two hands that were carrying Noriko Amamiya\'s things from behind.\n\nThere\'s nothing strange about it, Xiaolan looked at Kudo Shinichi\'s face suspiciously, what is Shinichi hiding?\n\nSonoko next to him silently gave a thumbs up. She could see that Shinichi took off Noriko\'s hair rope at the last moment. When she stretched out her hand, the palm of her hand was up, and the hair rope was sandwiched between her index and ring fingers. see.\n\nThis is great.\n\nSonoko finally breathed a sigh of relief, for Shinichi and Xiaolan, she was heartbroken.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was beside Xiaolan and saw that her hair rope was missing from Kudo Shinichi\'s wrist, she wondered, \"Shinichi, where is my hair rope?\"\n\nThere were no expressions on Kudo Shinichi and Sonoko\'s faces.\n\nSonoko\'s heart wailed for a while: \"Kiko... Take a look at the atmosphere and then talk——!!\"\n\nFortunately, Shinichi Kudo flipped the palm of his hand and changed a little magic so that the hair rope appeared in his hand, causing Xiaolan to be surprised: \"When will Shinichi become magic?\",\n\n\"Small idea.\" Shinichi smiled slightly, and then squeezed out the words to Noriko Amamiya: \"I\'ll give you a rope—\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko took the hair rope and put it on her wrist. She asked Xiaolan in confusion, \"Is Shinichi murdering me?\"\n\n\"No, that\'s what Shinichi is like.\"\n\nXiaolan thumped Kudo Shinichi and coaxed Noriko.\n\nKudo Shinichi received Xiaolan\'s annoyed punch and felt like his ribs were broken.\n\nBut in general, survived.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at Kudo Shinichi\'s sigh of