errain, and riding a horse with a big sister freely on the grassland...\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled with admiration: \"It\'s great, there is such a great way to vacation, but unfortunately my health is not good, if only I could try it out.\"\n\nKaruta-senpai gently patted Noriko Amamiya on the head: \"Next time you have a chance, Noriko can go with me on vacation, it\'s very interesting.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes flashed and she nodded her head: \"Well, it would be nice if it was possible.\"\n\n\"Well, there will be a chance. Okay, Kiko, let\'s go in, senpai has to perform her duties.\"\n\nKaruta-senpai pulled the armband of her Disciplinary Committee member and said to Noriko Amamiya.\n\nBoth of them are subordinate departments of the student union, and it is easy to meet each other at ordinary times, so they know each other well.\n\nAfter saying goodbye to her, Amamiya Noriko walked towards the school, scratching her head in her heart. She was able to meet her classmates in Hawaii. Fortunately, ordinary people couldn\'t think of Amamiya Noriko and her in Hawaii as the same person.\n\nShe took a small mirror out of the pocket of her skirt, and Kiko Amamiya took a look at it and wiped her brows with her fingertips. Shouldn\'t she be a little softer and look more harmless to humans and animals, so that the one who chugs in Hawaii will be with the rain. Miyako is okay.\n\n\"Good morning, Yu, Amamiya-san, long time no see.\"\n\nWhen Amamiya Noriko was looking in the mirror, suddenly someone next to him greeted him awkwardly, Amamiya Noriko put away the mirror out of courtesy, turned around and said with a small mouth: \"Good morning...Osaka Black Chicken, ah, isn\'t it? , Da Tian-san?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was a little uncertain and had to re-examine this brother. Since she was a classmate who had known her twice earlier, she still had an impression. Although she didn\'t quite remember whether she had confessed to herself, it shouldn\'t be this one in her memory. Hue?\n\nAt least the skin tone is darker...N degrees.\n\nAmamiya Noriko asked softly with concern: \"Ota-san...Are you okay? Did you eat something wrong and get poisoned?\"\n\nYou black, you won\'t get sunburned like this. Where do you leave the African brothers?\n\nDa Tian waved his hands hesitantly and said, \"No, no, it\'s not because I ate something wrong, I just went to Hawaii to play too much, and I was exposed like this. I just came back from Hawaii yesterday.\"\n\n\"Is that so...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, dare you all like to go to Hawaii during summer vacation?\n\nIs the risk of my exposure so great?\n\nBut then again, if she thought about it carefully, when she was riding a Kawasaki Ninja on the road, she seemed to occasionally see a black teenager playing on the coast next to the road.\n\nWhen driving an all-terrain vehicle, from time to time, I can see a black teenager playing grass skiing.\n\nWhen riding a horse... a black teenager is always unable to get on a horse...\n\nSo...is that just you?\n\n\"It\'s really unbelievable.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at his complexion, sighed inwardly, and then said: \"Oda-kun should also pay attention to sun protection when playing, it is very important to take sun protection measures, you can avoid getting tanned or sunburned, next time you must be sure Remember it.\"\n\nOta-san listened to Yumiya Noriko\'s tone of voice telling him that he was so serious, and was so moved. big relationship.\n\nUnexpectedly, Kiko still remembers him all the time, not forgetting to tell him to get sunburnt and sunburn.\n\nReally, it\'s really touching, woo woo woo-\n\nMingming, obviously he wanted to be more manly. I hope that one day he will be remembered clearly by Kiko Amamiya...\n\nAmamiya Noriko saw that his dark face seemed to have reddish circles under the eyes, black and red... I really didn\'t see it, changed the subject, and said with concern: \"Oda-kun, do you have sunburn? Or just sunburn? blacken?\"\n\nDa Tian-kun was