ish that he rejected after his confession.\n\nEven if she refuses, she will breastfeed the other party and make the other party\'s CD speed up. The next time she continues, it\'s usually not in the state of Dae Tian. It\'s like an excited first confession.\n\nThen she will definitely let the fish lure. It doesn\'t matter if she\'s not sure, just let the other party confess and try it.\n\nHowever, this person is really not as easy to confess as other people, and the difficulty is similar to that of the second confession, which is really strange.\n\nAmamiya Noriko can\'t understand this, because Ota-san has already confessed first-hand through love letters, and then there is no news, so it is not so easy to confess a second time.\n\nHer actions for her first confession were a little bit lackluster~www.readwn.com~ At this time, she just arrived at the school and had nothing to do, and she needed a good start, so Noriko Amamiya was welcome.\n\nSeeing that it was almost brewing, Amamiya Noriko buried her head and whispered, \"Ota-san\'s family or something... No way...\"\n\nThe shy look completely blew up the powder keg in Daejeon\'s heart. He waved his hand and said in a buoyant voice: \"Amamiya-san, there is no malice in inviting you to my house, and, besides, I like you!! From the first The first time I saw Amamiya classmates, I fell in love with her, she is so simple, cute, and like a weak elf, I can\'t help but want to hold it in my hand and cherish it.\"\n\n\"But I was sorry at that time, so I could only put a love letter in your shoe cabinet for Amamiya-kun. I hope you understand my intention. Although Amamiya-kun probably didn\'t see it in the end, my intention is real. !!\"\n\n\"Amamiya, I like you, be my girlfriend——!!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was embarrassed, and she was ready to interpret the law. She refused to give her a hand and then took a mouthful of milk. However, the girl who walked behind Ota-san seemed a little familiar.\n\nAfter rejecting it first, then say, \"I reject.\"\n\nLearning ability +1.\n\nThen Amamiya Noriko looked at the girl behind Ota-san, and the other party smiled kindly at her: \"Ota-kun always talks nonsense like this, I\'m really sorry for embarrassing you, Amamiya-san, I will fix him.\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nDa Tian turned his head stiffly, and his face turned pale when he saw the girl: \"No——!!!!\"\n\n\"Sorry, Ota-san, I don\'t like people with dark skin very much. Go ahead, I\'m going to the classroom.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko apologetically added the reason, then waved her little hand and left first.\n\n​​'),
(396, 5, 15, 'Chapter 14: : Tears are too expensive', 'The three people who were observing secretly guessed very close, but the truth was still beyond their imagination.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was also quite surprised.\n\nShe always pays attention to the point of being sultry, turning love into friends, everyone is innocent, you confess to me and refuse, everyone is still good brothers.\n\nAnd she is a very responsible person. If you express your heart to confess, I will never give a vague response. Rejection is rejection.\n\nAnd it will completely eliminate your unnecessary thoughts and guide you to work hard for a better future.\n\nAfter all, no matter how much you confess, you can\'t increase your attribute points.\n\nTo be honest, this perfectly increases the experience of failing confessions, and a 300-word five-star praise with a picture is not too much.\n\nBut in fact, before she confessed, she was arrested as a mistress.\n\nWith a question mark on his face.\n\nIn my heart, I said that after I refused and confessed, it would be ok for you to treat me as a mistress, as long as you have some attributes, and I rejected all of them, it\'s not a mistress, right? But the premise of all this is that you haven\'t confessed yet!\n\nShe is extremely innocent.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at the sky, there was no snow in June but Dou E in April.\n\nAfter sighing, she looked innocently at the emotional eruption between Senior Yamaki and his childhood sweetheart.\n\nHow they used to be irrelevant.\n\nAs long as you know that Yamaki has no feelings for his childhood sweetheart, he fell in love with her, a cute girl from the sky, and formed a small spiral Asura field.\n\nThe childhood sweetheart did not allow Yamaki to confess to Amiya Kiko, because she had been in love with Yamaki for so long since she was a child.\n\nYamaki is hesitant between Amamiya Noriko and his childhood sweetheart, and it is difficult to make a decision. He likes Amamiya Noriko, but he doesn\'t want to hurt his childhood sweetheart at this time. He still has deep feelings accumulated over time.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was already yawning and sleepy.\n\nWhy don\'t the two of you talk about your childhood feelings first, and tell me first so that I can reject it.\n\nI\'m in a hurry, but I still have to look innocent and show the grievances of a victim.\n\nYamaki comforted his childhood sweetheart for a long time, seeing Amamiya Noriko standing crunchy and silent for a while, her delicate and pretty face was full of weakness and embarrassment.\n\nHe felt distressed for a while, and blurted out: \"I like both of you, I want both!\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nThe childhood sweetheart\'s beautiful eyes stared, Amamiya Noriko was also shocked, and finally, finally confessed.\n\n\"But is it effective to have two at the same time?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko is a little unsure, and it is slightly more difficult for him to confess after refusing, but she never hesitates in refusing!\n\n\"Senior Yamagi, I\'m very sorry, as expected, I still can\'t do it. You two are a natural pair!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said while paying attention to the system prompt. She couldn\'t help but smile when she heard Agility +1.\n\nThe overly bright smile made the two of Yamaki sluggish.\n\nSenior Yamaki stretched out his hand and said, \"Amamiya-san, you\'re not...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko expressed her apologies, restrained her joy, and tilted her head when she heard the words: \"Don\'t you like the senior?\"\n\nShanmu said blankly, \"Well...\"\n\n\"So it\'s the most common misunderstanding in the world to think that the other party actually likes you. Besides, if you confess, you will definitely succeed. Of course, if you confess like Azusagawa Sakuta, you can still get a high score. Unfortunately, I am not a mai. Sister, I really wasn\'t there at the time.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in a gentle tone, raising her fingers and finally spreading her hands when giving an example, \"Also, senior made a speech of a scumbag.\"\n\nWhen Shanmu\'s classmate was lost, childhood sweetheart sauce said angrily: \"What do you mean? Shanmu likes you very much!\"\n\nAlthough Amamiya Noriko could see that her childhood sweetheart is a girl with a strong personality by not letting Yamaki confess, but this statement was a bit too brainless, which caused her to be stunned for a moment.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a look at the current situation.\n\nTo put it simply, it seems that B, who has a good relationship with A since childhood, confessed to C, but A likes B and does not allow B to confess to C, but after B confesses to C, he is rejected, and A is very much to C who rejected B. hostile.\n\n\"I\'m C, how innocent I am.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko scratched her head, she was forcibly innocent.\n\nSeeing her pitiful appearance, childhood sweetheart A immediately became even more annoyed: \"You are still pretending to be very innocent, you are a **** who plays with other people\'s feelings at will!\"\n\n\"Harmony...\"\n\nYamaki stretched out his hand and pulled his childhood sweetheart, but after being glared at, he could only withdraw his hand.\n\nAmamiya Noriko wiped the corners of her brows to remove a bit of weakness, her eyes were clear and charming like a galaxy, and then she glanced at childhood sweetheart A in a leisurely manner, pacing casually, and at the same time using a voice that only the two of them could hear.\n\n\"Do you know why we will go online? Why are the men you like in fact average, you don\'t do anything when you encounter this kind of problem, you want girls to make decisions, and there is no man like Azusagawa Sakuta, you dare to say that you want all of them, who Gave him the courage and confidence? It\'s you idiot.\"\n\n\"I used to read the sand sculpture news and I thought how could a girl do this kind of operation, but I didn\'t expect it to happen. If you take your feelings as your everything, you can get what you pay for. Such a girl is too cheap and stupid. , childhood sweetheart, Senior A?\"\n\nThe childhood sweetheart A seemed to have been stepped on the tail, and pointed at Noriko Amemiya with gnashing teeth: \"You are just playing with other people\'s feelings, don\'t think that you can deceive everyone by crying and crying like a victim!\"\n\n  \"try it?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said softly, her eyes were red, she turned around, as if she raised her hand to wipe her tears, and when she looked back, her eyes were hazy with tears. He said stubbornly, \"Tears are too expensive, so it\'s just eye drops.\"\n\nchildhood sweetheart A is not sure why: \"???\"\n\nAnd Yamaki behind her was moved by Amamiya Noriko just now, and she was blocked by her. He didn\'t see the expression of Amamiya Noriko just now, but he could see his childhood sweetheart raised his hand, Amamiya Noriko. She turned around and came back with tears in her eyes.\n\nThe process was free to use his imagination, but at this time, a figure came a few steps between Amamiya Noriko and childhood sweetheart A, and simply said, \"Senior, if you want to bully Noriko, pass me first!\"\n\nIt was Mao Lilan who had a serious face and never retreated.\n\nSonoko also came to Amamiya Noriko to comfort her, help her speak, and form a united front.\n\nAnd Kudo Shinichi took the detective to see through the random tricks of Noriko Amamiya, and approached the more keen sense of smell to distinguish the difference between the smell of tears and eye drops.\n\nAmamiya Noriko secretly spread her hands, although she had expected it, it was like a married person fell in love with her, and then was torn by her original partner, but it was a bit early.\n\nJapanese junior high school students are still too busy. She left her hometown for puppy love. In the morning, the school podium read the eight-hundred-character review. If you dare to press the playground with your friends after the evening self-study, if the distance is less than 30cm, there may be an instructor who will come and take a look at you. .\n\nAfter thinking about it for a while, in Sonoko\'s eyes, he seemed to be bullied and aggrieved, speechless.\n\nShe couldn\'t hold back her temper, she glared at the senior Yamagi who was originally favored by her: \"Thanks I still favor you, there is no way to protect Noriko!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko came back to her senses, does she need protection?\n\n\"Noriko would be better off marrying me than marrying a man like you!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"...\"'),
(397, 5, 10, 'Chapter 9: : absolutely reject', '\"Kiko is really... so amazing and popular...\"\n\nSonoko Suzuki, whose eyes were full of stars, secretly looked at Noriko Amamiya and the boy who confessed to her under the tree over there.\n\nShe is very pure, just envy the feeling of being liked by boys. As for who it is, the handsome guy who passes by at first sight will do!\n\nKudo Shinichi and Maurilan were also watching, and Maurilan was more envious than Sonoko.\n\n\"Is that what it looks like when you line up to confess?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi twitched the corners of his mouth, Amamiya Noriko was really bad, she didn\'t even give these boys a chance to confess one day.\n\nAs far as he knew, these boys asked Amamiya Noriko if she had time after school full of expectations and nervousness. Noriko Amamiya nodded thoughtfully, and then detailed the spare time to the minute.\n\nShe gave each person about five minutes of appearance, and there were two minutes between each person for her to rest and adjust.\n\n\"Amamiya-san, I really like you, you are very beautiful, cute, gentle, considerate... Anyway, please marry me!\"\n\n\"Pfft...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko has always had a thoughtful and dignified attitude of listening to others\' thoughts, but she couldn\'t help but burst out laughing.\n\nAsking for marriage is the first.\n\nA child who just graduated from kindergarten in the first grade, she couldn\'t bear to destroy his simple and beautiful fantasy.\n\n\"I\'m sorry, I couldn\'t help laughing, but I refused, because, look, to get married, you have to have a room, right? In Kyoto, a single apartment of more than ten square meters costs several million yen. Do you have to live in a 100-square-meter apartment? If you have a house, it has to be renovated, right? The decoration can’t be casual, a few million is a small amount for a set, right? You have to buy a car, and the car has to be housed…”\n\nAmamiya Noriko arrived almost five minutes before she stopped abruptly and asked, \"Do you have 1,000 yen in pocket money now?\"\n\nThe child\'s body and mind have been greatly impacted. Although he has left with no eyes at this time, I believe he will be able to cheer up and work hard to make money in the future.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the time, next.\n\nThe three children peeking over the teaching building were discussing.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko thinks that Noriko may have succeeded because she said a lot!\n\nMo Lilan is not sure, but she thinks it shouldn\'t, because Noriko Amamiya is still waiting for the next one.\n\nKudo Shinichi is certain that it is impossible to succeed. He thinks that Amamiya Noriko is just enjoying the process of rejecting other people\'s wishes. Is it still fun to promise?\n\nIn short, Amamiya Noriko rejected the children who finished the football team that day. Even those children who were not in the quota for that day, but who usually played together, she generously counted them into the punishment list.\n\nHe also had to teach them to use their hearts, and if they refused, it would be effective, and a dozen attributes were added all at once.\n\nSo the next day she couldn\'t go to school with a high fever...\n\nAs a child, it is easier to have a high fever. It\'s not a big problem. It\'s almost better every few days. Going to school to harvest a wave of condolences makes the plan more comfortable.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who kindly followed Xiaolan Yuanzi to visit a doctor, scolded for a while, because Amamiya Noriko used a weak setting, which made it easier to win sympathy, and was about to become a class pet.\n\nAsahi\'s classmates took great care of her.\n\nAlthough Kudo Shin found out early in the morning that Noriko Amamiya was constantly catching a cold and fever, but he looked at Noriko Amamiya pretending to be sick, which was too rough.\n\n\"Hey, do you have to be so exaggerated?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wondered: \"Huh? I really have a cold, I\'m a patient.\"\n\n\"The problem is that your frequency...\"\n\n\"You said this, if it wasn\'t for my physique that was too difficult to obtain, would I be like this?\"\n\n\"What are you talking about? Confused?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave him an irritated look, then lay on the table with a sick and comfortable look, and coughed a few times: \"I\'ve been coughing recently. I\'ll take you up a bit later.\"\n\nShe doesn\'t mind anyway. The more colds she has, the stronger she is.\n\nAnd it\'s an old tradition in the world of Conan to catch a cold at every turn.\n\nShinichi Kudo looked indifferent: \"I don\'t catch a cold so easily.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at him, how often will Conan catch colds in the future, and raise a flag in front of me while I have a cold?\n\nIt\'s still Xiaolan and Sonoko who feel bad for her, and it\'s impossible to count on Kudo Shinichi, a straight man with advanced cancer.\n\nIn elementary school, Noriko Amamiya manages with ease.\n\nThe teachers\' impression of her is that she is knowledgeable, gentle, quite intelligent, and very talented in learning. Generally speaking, she is a child of everyone else.\n\nAs for elementary school students, those who are too one-sided usually think that Amamiya is cute, beautiful, kind, and very capable, and then her health is not very good, so take care of her and so on.\n\nThe children who were rejected by her and confessed can be a little more comprehensive.\n\nThen there was no chance of confession, Amamiya Noriko was very democratic, everyone only had one chance, and no attribute points were added for more.\n\nIn a blink of an eye, the graduation ceremony of the elementary school was over, and after the holidays, I was promoted from Didan Primary School to Didan Middle School.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Shinichi and Xiaolan Yuanzi are still in the same class, so they are very spiritual.\n\nHer first two years of elementary school life were quite rich.\n\nGo through the elementary school courses in a relaxed way. In class, learn cultural lessons, disguise, and on weekends, you can play with Yuanzi Xiaolan and the others, or go to teacher Kuroba Rouichi to learn.\n\nBut when she was in the third grade, Kuroba Rouichi disappeared during the magic show when she was performing escape techniques. She was assassinated by a mysterious organization. In the early years, Kuroba Rouichi got revenge when he met Kuroba Chikage.\n\nNot a winery.\n\nRumors are basically that the black feather thief died, and her mother, Kuroba Chikage, was also looking for clues abroad.\n\nBut Noriko Amamiya is unbelievable, and I have to ask why, because the original book uses a vague statement and does not specify death. Generally, this way of writing, the old thief of the author wants to do something.\n\nIn the next few years, he continued to teach himself the art of disguise, and then played with elementary school students between his palms. UU Reading www.uukanshu.com\n\nThe opening ceremony of Didan Middle School.\n\nIt\'s not surprising that Noriko Amamiya delivered a speech as the representative of the new students as always.\n\nBecause in fact, she was promoted from Didan Elementary School to Middle School. As the best graduate of Didan Elementary School this year, it is normal for her to be selected as the representative of the freshmen to give a speech.\n\nShe wrote an essay on the level of middle school students, and she had to bring some drafts that were written by elementary school students.\n\nDidan Middle School is much bigger than elementary school and has many times more students. On the stage, she noticed many familiar faces and some unfamiliar ones.\n\nThe point is the unfamiliar ones, all of them have to be her attribute points. As for the familiar ones, they have basically been conquered by her, so let\'s just forget about the second-week games without reward.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was in the audience, carefully noticed Noriko Amamiya\'s line of sight. He subconsciously watched it a few times, and when he saw some raw faces, he understood.\n\n  here we go again.\n\nBecause by the time of the sixth grade, the strategy was basically completed, so Kudo Shinichi felt that Amamiya Noriko was a lot more peaceful, but he didn\'t expect that as soon as he entered junior high school, it sprouted again.\n\nAlthough Amamiya Noriko was smiling on the stage at this time, she spoke in a clear and light voice, politely thanking everyone, and wishing for the new student, looking so elegant and perfect.\n\nBut Shinichi Kudo felt that what Noriko Amamiya was actually saying should be:\n\n\"Get to know me well at this time, confess to me, and then be rejected by me!\"\n\nIn a sense, it\'s like salute each other before the karate competition, but after the start of the fight, the opponent will be completely eliminated with one blow, and there will be no chance at all.\n\nKudo Shinichi would like to call it \"absolute rejection\".'),
(398, 5, 84, 'Chapter 83: : super strong', 'Kudo Shinichi couldn\'t say anything through the wall.\n\nHe can understand that if Amamiya Noriko can use him as a shield, she must have encountered a special situation.\n\nI guess it\'s the same now, what was discovered by Sonoko, and then asked that he had to say this to distract Sonoko?\n\nUnderstand, understand, but don\'t expect him to understand, Amamiya Noriko can pull out as a shield, let alone a football team, right?\n\nWhy is it him?\n\nHe is too difficult.\n\nI can only hope that Sonoko won\'t talk nonsense everywhere, but since that fellow Amamiya Noriko will speak to Sonoko as a shield, it probably won\'t make the problem bigger.\n\nShin Kudo looked up at the sky, then took a black cauldron and left first. He came out to play with Xiaolan, and he had to make sure that Xiaolan couldn\'t hear what was said over the wall, otherwise it would be terrible.\n\nin the alley.\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya faced the peach blossoms in Suzuki Sonoko\'s eyes, she felt very uncomfortable. Sonoko, are you an aphrodisiac?\n\nShe shyly avoided Sonoko\'s gaze and said softly, \"It\'s too embarrassing, don\'t talk about this, let\'s talk about my personality...\"\n\nHard to catch.\n\nSonoko reached out and grabbed the slender shoulders of Amamiya Noriko, \"Noriko\'s personality is very cute, there is no problem, let\'s tell the story of you and Shinichi?!\"\n\nJust count.\n\nNoriko Amamiya has black lines all over her head. She and Kudo Shinichi can\'t tell any stories. If you say it, the people will collapse on the spot. She has used Kudo Shinichi\'s tools on the spot enough. From time to time, I will make a pit, and let Kudo Shinichi carry the black pot.\n\nOf course, there were times when I told Kudo Shinichi to stay away from gin and cherish life. She and Kudo Shinichi are old sisters. The question is, what can I do for him with a cute personality?\n\nDoes it count as being malicious? With such a lovely childhood sweetheart as her, does it count as being envied by others?\n\nUnexpectedly, Amamiya Noriko can only talk about soldiers on paper.\n\nAnyway, she is also shy and introverted, so she simply expressed her affection for Shinichi, so that Sonoko\'s love brain can continue, and she doesn\'t pay attention to other issues.\n\nSonoko couldn\'t force her good friend to express all her inner feelings, so she could only stop when she reached the limit.\n\nIt\'s great, Noriko has vague feelings for Shinichi, that guy is really happy, with Xiaolan and Noriko...\n\n...\n\nYuanzi hugged his head in pain, as if the headband was made of gold. He forgot what to do with Xiaolan!\n\nSonoko, who was once again caught in the vortex of standing in line, was also troubled by her own difficult choice.\n\nIf she had to make a decision between Xiaolan and Noriko, it would be better to let the handsome guys not be interested in her in this lifetime.\n\nVicious enough.\n\nSonoko made a poisonous oath and decided to be impartial and to be a notary in the relationship. After all, both of them are good sisters, and her handsome guy has not yet been found.\n\nIf it really doesn\'t work, let Noriko give up on the scumbag Shinichi, because compared to Xiaolan, Noriko really doesn\'t have to worry that no one likes her, and she will be responsible to Noriko.\n\n\"This should be the perfect solution, tentatively.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko breathed a sigh of relief, almost, she almost explained it in the vortex of the training field, fortunately she is the queen of love.\n\nHaving already assumed the solution in the future, Sonoko felt a lot more relaxed, and decided not to ask Noriko any more.\n\nIn the future, no handsome guy will be interested in her anymore, that would be too miserable.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko coughed lightly and changed the subject: \"Then Noriko\'s current body, if she doesn\'t have a cold or fever, how good is it?\"\n\n\"This...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was also relieved that she didn\'t have to continue buffing Kudo Shinichi. She felt very guilty towards Shinichi.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked around to see if there was anything that could show her strength, so Sonoko\'s attention shifted slightly.\n\nUncle Goldfish on the ground suddenly opened his eyes and looked at the sky blankly. What happened? Why did he faint on the ground, what about the super cute little girl?\n\nIt seemed that he was attacked by that little girl, and he lost consciousness with a single blow.\n\n\"Yes!! It\'s spicy enough, uncle, I like you like—\"\n\nHuo Ran got up, and the wretched uncle who endured the pain in his jaw growled and saw Noriko Amamiya next to him, and his words suddenly stopped.\n\nIt was as if he had already seen a picture of himself being knocked down by another blow.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko took out her mobile phone and called the police. The female voice on the phone was asking what was going on. Amamiya Noriko said in a frightened tone to the phone: \"Uncle, if you do this again, I will Call the police!\"\n\n\"Hehehe, you report it, I want to see how you report it!\"\n\nFrom the wretched uncle\'s point of view, this little girl was just trying to frighten him and threaten him. She didn\'t believe it at all, so she rushed over and called the police or something. After taking you down, I\'ll see how you call the police——\n\nThrowing himself into the air, he saw the little girl lowered her body slightly, and said in a frightened tone, \"Woo woo--\"\n\nThen he saw the little girl rushing towards him, and the speed was so fast that he felt a heavy blow to his chin~www.readwn.com~ His eyes turned up uncontrollably with his head, and he was directly aware of the fragmentation. He fell to the ground and fainted.\n\nFrom Sonoko\'s point of view, it was entirely Noriko Amamiya who kicked the huge and wretched uncle with a high kick. She made a booing gesture.\n\nOn the phone of Noriko Amamiya, the policewoman asked anxiously: \"Little boy? How are you, little boy? Where is the location?!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in a tone of attempted victimization: \"The police officer sister is fine. Fortunately, a passing big brother used my shoes to defeat the bad uncle, and then the big brother left directly. He is really a good person.\"\n\n\"Are you okay? Shoes?\"\n\n\"Well, my shoes.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked down at her round-toed leather shoes. Will she be taken away as evidence?\n\nThen he talked about the location, and asked the police to take this wretched uncle away and attempt to molest the girl. How many years is it here?\n\nThe police said they would be dispatched soon. Amamiya Noriko ended the call first, then sat aside and took off her shoes. Then she said that this bad uncle took off his shoes and wanted to do something bad, but the big brother who passed by took the shoes and gave them to him. few times.\n\nNo one should believe that she is so cute, but she is only 12 years old, and a petite little girl can kick a wretched uncle down, right?\n\nTo admire her, Sonoko alone is enough.\n\nSonoko looked at Noriko\'s eyes almost glowing, so handsome, is this the real Noriko?\n\nShe looked at Kiko\'s little feet wearing white silk and said, \"Shall I go buy Kiko\'s shoes?\"\n\n\"Okay... But Sonoko can stop pinching first, my feet are fine...\"\n\n​​');
