(399, 5, 60, 'Chapter 59: : More than 1 point cute', 'Going to sing karaoke, Amamiya Noriko won the favor of more than a dozen senior sisters.\n\nIt\'s a pity that it\'s not good for them to confess, otherwise, a dozen attribute points will be credited to the account.\n\nBut in general, I have gained a lot today, at least capturing the hearts of a bunch of athletes.\n\nAfter she got home and had a good sleep, she had a premonition that tomorrow would be a busy day.\n\nIt was indeed a busy day. As soon as she arrived at the gate of the school, yesterday the captain of the basketball team from the other school came to confess to her with a bouquet of roses.\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t even know the name of this person, but that didn\'t prevent her from rejecting it.\n\n\"Physical +1\"\n\nVery good, Amamiya Noriko accepted the attribute points with satisfaction, and then comforted the other party: \"Don\'t give up, basketball is all you have, senior, I\'m just passing by.\"\n\nAccording to Japanese law, maybe marrying a basketball is okay?\n\nThe captain of the basketball team was stunned, watching Amamiya Noriko waving a small hand at him and then leaving, his back gradually disappeared, and he could not help muttering: \"Although you are a passer-by in my life, Amamiya, but you have left such an important memory, I I will definitely try to fall in love with basketball and put more effort into it!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko had a little more physique, her face flushed red, and her footsteps drifted a lot. As soon as she arrived to prepare for the morning practice on the football field, she saw the head of the football department waiting for her outside in advance.\n\n\"Minister, what\'s wrong?\"\n\n\"Ah... It\'s nothing, I just wanted to ask what Noriko thinks of me?\" The football minister coughed lightly, and was almost flabbergasted by the minister\'s call from Noriko Amamiya.\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya saw that he was about to confess, he already understood.\n\nThen he started to praise: \"What do you think? I think the director is very good. He leads very powerful team members, and usually trains very hard...\"\n\nThe football minister vaguely felt that the line of sight of Noriko Amamiya began, and there was an air of immortality.\n\nHe quickly calmed down and said calmly and humbly, \"Amamiya said that I\'m good, but I can say that I\'m good, but it\'s an exaggeration to say that my teammates are amazing. It\'s nothing, training hard is what you should...\"\n\nAfter speaking, she expressed her admiration for Noriko Amemiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko opened her mouth: I refuse.\n\n\"Physical +1.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded. Today\'s explosion rate is quite high.\n\n\"For someone as good as the minister, he will definitely find someone more suitable. I\'m not good enough.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko bowed her head and said humbly,\n\n\"Nothing, Amamiya is the best in the football club. Who dares to say that Amamiya is not good enough, Minister, I will play him as a football.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wanted to say that Kudo Shin felt that she had a problem every day, but when Kudo Shin was not here, it was a little less fun.\n\nNoriko Amamiya comforted the minister who was quite sad in his heart. The minister was very moved. The lovely and gentle Amamiya, even if she rejected him, would worry about him comforting him.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that this is a normal operation, otherwise you will be trapped in love in the future, become one of the prisoners, want to murder me, and disguise the murder scene, stand in a place with poor light and laugh like a little black, and then be inexplicable with the other two people Suspected suspects stand together and are chosen one of three by Conan?\n\nTwo people walked into the football field.\n\nThe other team members gave Noriko Amamiya a surprise. After many years, since the kindergarten mowing, a group confession event finally happened.\n\nThe members who made the decision expressed their hearts to Noriko Amamiya, sincerely and sincerely hope that Noriko Amamiya would agree and choose herself.\n\nAfter Kiko Amamiya finished speaking one by one, she took a deep breath and said with a flushed face, \"Everyone is really gentle.\"\n\n\"However, I refused. I don\'t know who I like among everyone, maybe because I\'m still young...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s small face showed regret and self-blame, causing the football team members to wipe their hands at a loss, not knowing how to speak out.\n\nFortunately, Amamiya Noriko seemed to see them like this, and hurriedly waved her hands: \"Yes... I should know in the future, I hope everyone can find someone they really like, not because of Noriko...\"\n\n\"Understood, it has nothing to do with you Amamiya, I just like Amamiya.\"\n\n\"No one else is as cute as Amamiya!\"\n\n\"As long as there is Amamiya!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes were misty and moved, and she was scratching her head in her heart.\n\nAre you not happy to let you live?\n\nIt seems that my charm is a little stronger, although it is very pleasant, but because their future confession has no effect, so Amamiya Noriko will not give them a chance to confess.\n\nEither release the fish, or fry the fish.\n\nA member of the football department patted the minister: \"Has the minister confessed yet?\"\n\nThe minister shook his head: \"It\'s okay, I\'m very pleased to see that you have successfully expressed your heart.\"\n\nWhen the members heard the words, they couldn\'t help showing their moved expressions.\n\nThe minister nodded, his face didn\'t change and he had the demeanor of a minister.\n\nIt\'s just that after seeing Noriko Amamiya looking at him with a pure face, she quickly blinked frantically, hoping that Amamiya would understand.\n\nSo he was waiting for me outside, was he sneaking away?\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought I was so innocent, can I understand what you mean?\n\nBut for the sake of your physique, you can understand.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who had just changed his jersey and arrived at the edge of the football field, looked at the situation inside, shook his head and walked over. He was still too young.\n\nAfter being harvested by Noriko Amamiya, she will definitely turn around and leave the football club.\n\nJudging from his observation, although Amamiya Noriko likes the feeling of being confessed by others, she doesn\'t like repetition, and it\'s gone once alone.\n\nThe football club has no unconfessed personnel worthy of her memory.\n\nThinking about it, Kudo Shinichi saw that Amamiya Noriko found him over there, and waved at him, the smile on his face was a little too cute.\n\n\"Xinichi, are you here? I\'ve been waiting for you for a long time.\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s heart skipped a beat, as if he hadn\'t confessed to Noriko Amamiya.\n\nLooking at it again, after Amamiya Noriko called him by his name intimately, behind the smiling Amamiya Noriko were the resentful football club members.\n\nThe minister\'s resentment even held up half the sky alone.\n\nShinichi Kudo has clearly decided to base his happiness on the pain of others.\n\n\"Noriko Amamiya, you are poisonous—\"\n\nThe situation of the football club has come to an end for the time being. The members of the club who were touched by the cute appearance of Noriko Amemiya cheering on yesterday have joined together and expressed their hearts together.\n\nDie without regret.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also embarked on a new journey.\n\nDuring the lunch break at noon, I was invited by the head of the school basketball department to have dinner together, and the other party took the opportunity to confess at the dinner table.\n\nAmamiya Noriko refused, because she was still young.\n\nIndeed, everyone in the basketball team is too tall. She doesn\'t like to look up at others. It\'s like drying clothes for an hour, but using a clothes drying pole to fork them up. Her neck will be very tired.\n\n\"Senior, don\'t be discouraged. I hope seniors don\'t dislike it, eat more meat, and play basketball better in the future.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko had finished eating, and gave him the slightly fatty char siu left in the bowl.\n\n\"Amamiya...\"\n\nAlthough the basketball minister is tall, he is still a very emotional person. Because of Noriko Amamiya\'s move, his eyes are wet.\n\n\"Don\'t worry, Amamiya-san, I will definitely become the power forward of the national team and live up to your expectations of Amamiya.\"\n\n  \"come on…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was a little unacceptable to the appearance of a big man who was nearly 1.8 meters tall and chewed fat with tears in his eyes, so he said reluctantly.\n\nDon\'t cry, don\'t cry, the macho sheds tears, and mother is afraid.\n\nAfter coaxing the basketball minister here, Amamiya Noriko went to the back of the teaching building again in the afternoon and arranged for another general of the basketball department.\n\nThen I went to a club activity, divided the bag of biscuits I bought, and fed it to the fish in the fish pond.\n\nAfter half of the club activity time, Amamiya Noriko said that there was still work as a member of the club, so it was time to go to work.\n\nToday, I just confessed and was rejected by myself. The atmosphere of the football stadium is still a little weird. Sitting in the auditorium, Amamiya Noriko felt that these people looked at him from time to time.\n\nFor work, of course, I went to various clubs to get acquainted with each other, mainly the basketball club. In the past, I showed my face very appropriately, and a classmate was enthusiastic and directly confessed.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is very grateful to accept this little power.\n\nAmamiya Noriko wanted to hang out in the school, but was discovered by Ran who had ended the club activities.\n\nSeeing that her face was a little red, Mao Lilan reached out and touched her forehead, \"Niko, you have a high fever, go home and rest.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko touched it herself: \"It seems, I\'ve become stronger again.\"\n\nXiaolan resolutely helped the burnt Noriko to the gate of the school, Chieda Riho should be outside the school and can take Noriko to the hospital or go home.\n\nThe other school basketball team members who were waiting outside Didan Middle School on the way took bouquets of flowers and sincerely wanted to confess.\n\nXiaolan was worried about her friend\'s health, so she pulled Noriko Amamiya directly by: \"Sorry, Noriko is not feeling well, I\'ll talk about it next time if there is anything else!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko can only wave with one hand: \"I refuse—\"\n\nLearning ability +1.\n\n\"Really, what time is it?\"\n\nXiaolan grabbed her and said angrily while looking for Chieda Riho\'s car.\n\n\"Ahaha... I have to respond to people\'s wishes and courage.\"\n\nAfter finding Bentley Mulsanne on the side of the road, Xiao Lan stuffed Noriko Amemiya onto the co-pilot, helped her fasten her seat belt, and then urged, \"Take care of your health, if it\'s serious, I can ask for a leave of absence for Noriko tomorrow.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s attitude was cooperative: \"Mmmm.\"\n\nXiaolan said to Qianzhi Lisui: \"Sister Qianzhi, Noriko has a cold, so I\'ll ask you.\"\n\nChieda Riho nodded, \"Yes.\"\n\nThen Xiao Lan closed the car door, waved her hand and watched the car drive away.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was also checked by Chieda Riho with the back of her hand again, and it was a little high.\n\n\"It\'s okay, the fever will subside in two days at most.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko is used to it, it is worth it anyway, this is just a small symptom in the process of her body getting stronger.\n\nChieda Riho glanced at her in a good mood, and the little smile on the corner of her mouth lingered.\n\nThen Amamiya Noriko had a high fever for two days when she returned, and Chieda Riho had to take care of her all the time. Fortunately, the fever started to subside after the first day, otherwise she would have to go to the hospital for an injection.\n\nEarly the next morning after the fever subsided, Noriko Amamiya sat in the co-pilot, and Riho Chieda drove her to school on the way.\n\nAmamiya Noriko yawned, feeling weak. She had a high fever and slept a bit more in the past two days, and she lost her sense of taste after taking antipyretics.\n\nAlthough I know it\'s just a minor after-effect, it will be fine in two days, but I\'m very uncomfortable. I don\'t eat anything.\n\nChieda Riho was basically concentrating on driving, but occasionally glanced at Noriko Amamiya\'s weak look: \"Kiko should sit in the back.\"\n\n  \"why?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was idle in a small notebook, writing down some characteristics of every person who might confess to her. This is a notebook that can make the world a better place. She heard this and asked casually.\n\n\"Because there is a child seat.\"\n\nChieda Riho looked at Amamiya Noriko wearing a seat belt, she felt a little too big, and she could sleep in the back.\n\nHigh fever is very hard.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, making sense, \"But I like the co-pilot\'s seat, and now I have to sit in the co-pilot if I can\'t sit in the main driver\'s seat.\"\n\nChieda Riho concluded, \"You don\'t have the chance to take the lead driver.\"\n\nAs long as she is there.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted, holding the book up and looking out the window.\n\nSeeing a side-by-side white convertible car, a middle-aged uncle in a suit and leather shoes and sunglasses, pressing the steering wheel with one hand and smoking a cigarette in the other.\n\nThe co-pilot had a large handful of roses fastened with seat belts.\n\nShe couldn\'t help raising her eyebrows: \"Is this going to show love?\"\n\nIndeed, it could only be a show of love, because this uncle is dressed in a pink suit, so it is estimated that he must be a bright red suit for the proposal.\n\nAmamiya Noriko held her chin to look at the interior of his car. The whole thing was quite distinctive. He was a broken second-hand car (Porsche), and he was also a small boss.\n\nPresident Oda is driving his Porsche to a beautiful woman he met in a bar recently, and is about to take him down with romance and money~www.readwn.com~ He is holding the car while waiting for the red light. The window flicked the soot, and turned to look at the Bentley Mulsanne next to him. Yes, I bought a car and drove it back.\n\nSuddenly, his eyes were attracted by the force and he couldn\'t take it away. The girl in the passenger seat of this Bentley Mulsanne showed a little weakness on her delicate and radiant profile.\n\nThe small nose and thin lips that are naturally pink, and the lovely cheeks that seem to be radiating bright eyes all the time.\n\nPeople\'s heart was immersed in it all at once, and it was not until gradually away that the traffic police raised his hand and knocked on his car, looking at him strangely, and President Oda suddenly woke up like a dream.\n\n\"It\'s already the green light, sir, why haven\'t you started it yet?\"\n\n\"My heart has been activated.\"\n\nThe traffic policeman nodded, lowered his head and wrote a ticket and pasted it beside his car.\n\nPresident Oda shook his head: \"You have no idea how charming that girl just now is.\"\n\n\"Girl? How old?\"\n\nPresident Oda is quite confident: \"Elementary school or just entering junior high school.\"\n\nThe traffic policeman nodded and turned to the walkie-talkie: \"All departments pay attention, I found a target with bad tendencies towards young children.\"\n\nPresident Oda: \"...\"\n\nBentley Mulsanne.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was still holding her chin to look in front of the car.\n\nChieda Riho still glanced at her occasionally. When she was waiting for the red light to look at Noriko, she saw the process of the car owner from seeing Amamiya Noriko to being completely lost.\n\n\"Noriko, aren\'t you a little more cute?\"\n\nSpeaking of this, Amamiya Noriko smiled sweetly: \"Well, what time is it?\"\n\nChieda Riho nodded in understanding, which was indeed more than a little.\n\n​​'),
(400, 5, 28, 'Chapter 27: : efficiency of double', 'The day after Xin Xiaolan Yuanzi visited the hospital, Amamiya Noriko was discharged from the hospital.\n\nBecause there really isn\'t much damage in essence, only the back that was hit by the electric shocker and the bruises on the wrist.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s mother, Amamiya Emi, and her cousin Chieda Riho came to take her home.\n\n\"Noriko terrified her mother this time. No matter where she goes next time, at least let Riho accompany her?\"\n\nAfter her daughter was officially discharged from the hospital, Emi Amamiya rubbed her daughter\'s face and warned her with a serious face, completely ignoring her daughter\'s boredom.\n\nAside from her looks, what she inherited from her mother is a soft and glutinous voice. With an innocent expression, she is completely harmless to humans and animals. Anyway, even if she speaks seriously, she has no sense of majesty at all.\n\nChieda Riho answered, \"Kiko, I will pick you up from school every day from now on.\"\n\n  \"Fine.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, even if she said no, it is estimated that Chieda Riho will come to pick her up in the afternoon. This elder sister is very stubborn and has been educated very strictly since she was a child. She is very serious about herself and others\' requirements.\n\nChieda Riho drove them home.\n\nAs soon as Amamiya Noriko finished changing her shoes at the entrance, she saw her father get up from the sofa and look at her. After confirming that her daughter was fine, she said, \"Welcome home.\"\n\n\"Ahaha, there was a little accident this time, but it\'s not a big problem.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko spread her hands and went to the refrigerator to get a can of drinks to drink.\n\nAmamiya Ludou was sitting on the sofa and saw that his daughter was not frightened by this incident at all. He was relieved and helpless, \"This is not a small accident. I heard from the police that you saved yourself this time.\"\n\nHe still has a little relationship with the police, and he can basically understand the same thing.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said modestly: \"Forget it, it\'s a coincidence, a coincidence.\"\n\n\"I\'ve discussed with your mother that I\'m going to live abroad in the next two years, and I\'m going to hear your thoughts.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at her mother after hearing the words, and Amamiya Emi nodded seriously and said, \"Lu Dou doesn\'t think Japan is very safe. Don\'t worry about it, baby girl, I\'m worried that something will happen again.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways at her father, Amamiya Lu Dou didn\'t change his face: \"I think what your mother said is quite different, but the meaning is similar.\"\n\n\"Oh...\" Amamiya Noriko pulled her voice meaningfully, then nodded and said, \"I agree, but I\'m not planning to go abroad. In fact, it\'s pretty safe for me to stay here alone, right?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thinks it\'s good and safe for them to go abroad, but it\'s boring to go abroad by herself.\n\nIn a few years, the real fun is just beginning.\n\nAfter this small kidnapping case, she has roughly figured out the level of evil forces in the general public.\n\nIt\'s pretty good, and you can get guns, that\'s all.\n\nAfter a few years into the plot, the biggest evil force is the winery, and the winery, to a certain extent, is quite confident...\n\nLooking back for an opportunity to familiarize yourself with \"Kiele\", \"Bourbon\" and \"Scotch whisky\".\n\nBut both of her parents disagreed, so how could she rest assured that her youngest daughter would be alone in the country.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pulled Chieda Riho over: \"Isn\'t there sister Riho, right? Hey?\"\n\nChieda Riho looked at Amamiya Noriko\'s cute face, and nodded calmly, \"I will take good care of Noriko.\"\n\nAmamiya Ludou and Amamiya Emi were still a little uneasy, but Amamiya Noriko said that she didn\'t have to decide now. She would wait two years to see, she still has the ability to take care of herself as a junior high school