do Shinichi couldn\'t stand it any longer, \"People who want to confess to you are even more anxious than you, UU reading www.uukanshu.com, but to confess to you at this time is not a complete incomprehensible idiot.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was surprised: \"As expected of the detective Kudo Shinichi-kun.\"\n\nShin Kudo said without any modesty: \"Of course, I\'m completely capable of helping the police solve cases, right? Did you pronounce it wrong when you praised me?\"\n\n  \"No.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted, and Kudo Shinichi was very proud because she saw a problem that the police did not see from her solution to the two kidnappers.\n\nThis person is like this. As a detective, he is very strong. In other respects, he is helpless.\n\nAmamiya Noriko suddenly had a flash of inspiration: \"Shinichi-kun?\"\n\n\"Hi...\"\n\nThe sudden intimacy of the address made Kudo Shinichi shudder.\n\n\"If Shinichi-kun can help convey that, in fact, my wounded heart needs to be confessed to be healed...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi covered his face in pain: \"You can find Sonoko for this kind of thing!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was taken aback for a moment. It makes sense. It seems that you have seen through the nature of Sonoko\'s intelligence dealer, but that\'s not enough.\n\n\"Sonoko is in charge of the girls, and you are in charge of the boys.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi squinted at her, \"Are you finally not letting go of girls?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was stunned again, what are you talking about, Sonoko is in charge of conveying information from girls, and the ultimate goal is boys, but after Kudo Shinichi said this, the girl\'s confession also counts.\n\nShe nodded, \"Yes, I used to have double efficiency in front of me, but I didn\'t cherish it. Now that I lost it, it was still too late.\"\n\nShinichi Kudo felt deeply that he was a sinner, and he must solve more cases in the future to make up for the Pandora\'s box he released.'),
(401, 5, 23, 'Chapter 22: : The disappearing couple', 'The place where Noriko Amamiya and his party were going to see the cherry blossoms was on the hills on the outskirts of Mikacho.\n\nThere is a mountain on both sides of the road that is lined with cherry trees. When the cherry blossoms bloom in spring, you can enjoy the beautiful scenery of the cherry blossoms on both sides of the road on the way up the mountain. There is a very beautiful scene on the video website.\n\nJust after parking at the foot of the mountain, and looking up the mountain, you can appreciate the beauty of cherry blossoms.\n\n  \"finally reached.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko let out a sigh of relief after getting out of the car. It wasn\'t because of fear of an accident on the way. The juvenile detective team basically only got to the destination every time before a murder happened.\n\nNext is the highlight. She looked around, was there any victim who was suspected of dying suddenly?\n\nSome other people parked in the parking lot at the bottom of the mountain, obviously planning to go up the mountain, and there were also many young couples.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at the pink mountain: \"It\'s a good place to sprinkle dog food.\"\n\nNext to him, Shinichi Kudo looked sideways, what exactly is your focus?\n\nHe went to the back of the car to get Noriko Amamiya\'s backpack. He couldn\'t help but pause when he stretched out his hand. Recalling the weight of this thing, it seemed that one hand would not work.\n\n\"I\'ll come by myself.\"\n\nA slender, white palm next to him grabbed the bag and carried it behind his back.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at her faintly, \"You are too strong.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was slightly annoyed: \"How can you say such a weak girl.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi turned around and looked at the mountain with complicated eyes. No matter how high the mountain was, it couldn\'t be higher than Amamiya Noriko\'s bad taste.\n\nXiaolan also got out of the car and asked, \"Kiko, how do you feel?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko spread her hands: \"Xiao Lan is really worried. They said that I don\'t get motion sickness. Now I can sprint for 100 meters.\"\n\nBecause it was inevitable that she was a little restless on the way, Xiao Lan thought it was motion sickness.\n\nBut there are indeed many bends on the way, and the edge of the road is close to the ravine. She is mainly worried about what to do if the car rolls over. It is difficult to explain things like the halo of death.\n\nIn the end, he still patted the **** of death: \"It\'s all up to you!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was too lazy to care about her. He usually stabbed himself every day, but suddenly it\'s up to you to say anything. What\'s the matter? Does it have anything to do with him?\n\nI really don\'t want to pay any attention, but I\'m really curious.\n\nOriginated from the abyss-like curiosity in the detective\'s heart.\n\nDr. A Li said, \"Have you brought everything? Ready to go up the mountain.\"\n\nSeveral people were ready to respond. Dr. A Li was actually quite motivated to climb the mountain. It is a pity that he is still a little younger. In a few years, he will be discouraged and forced to go on a diet by Xiao Ai.\n\nStart going up the mountain.\n\nAlong the way, Dr. Aga took a camera to photograph a lot of cherry blossoms blooming on both sides of the mountain road, and then he was exhausted. Noriko Amamiya still overestimated him.\n\nA few people stopped and walked, Xiaolan and Sonoko took the camera and took pictures with great interest.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was on the side of the road, poking the drooping cherry blossom branches with her fingertips, feeling like nothing would happen.\n\nSonoko saw Noriko\'s eyes light up, she stretched out her hand and gently moved the petals of the cherry blossoms. Her eyes were full of pink cherry blossoms, full of the romantic atmosphere of a girl.\n\nShe pressed the shutter quickly to satisfy her anomaly: \"Kiko is so pretty, if only she wore a cherry blossom-colored