ytail, was a valiant mess.\n\nKudo Shin, who got out of the car to help her carry her luggage, had a meal for a long time, thinking what are you going for? Survive in the wild? Are we just going to see the cherry blossoms?\n\n\"Isn\'t it too much to wear a kimono in a place full of cherry blossoms? Why are you dressed like this?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said earnestly: \"You don\'t understand.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi reached out to help her carry the bag to the trunk of the car, but his hand sank and almost didn\'t hold it!\n\nHow did Noriko Amamiya carry it! ?\n\nAlways unable to show that his strength is less than that of a girl, Kudo Shinichi gritted his teeth and mentioned the trunk.\n\nTurning his head, he saw Amamiya Noriko smiling, but the head that was knocked on by a plain hand shrank, and the one who covered his forehead looked very aggrieved.\n\nChie Riho, the cousin and driver of Noriko Amamiya, was wearing a suit and nodded slightly to Kudo Shinichi and the others: \"Then I\'ll ask you, miss.\"\n\nShin Kudo was very fond of this eldest sister who could subdue Noriko Amamiya, and said quickly, \"Don\'t worry, we will definitely take care of Noriko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko squinted at him with a squinted chest, this kid isn\'t my sister\'s control, right?\n\nPutting on a cap, Noriko Amamiya got into the car, Sonoko and Xiaolan were both watching her.\n\n\"What\'s wrong?\"\n\nXiaolan shook her head: \"No, Kiko looks very handsome like this.\"\n\nSonoko: \"It\'s super cool.\"\n\nThen the two of them said together, \"We\'re going to see the cherry blossoms~www.readwn.com~Aren\'t we going to camp?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko reiterated that this was prepared to see the cherry blossoms.\n\nBut it is also necessary to prevent accidents or murders that may occur on the way to the cherry blossoms.\n\nIn this Conan world, she can\'t think of the possibility that accidents won\'t happen unless...\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at Kudo Shinichi, who was seated in the co-pilot and fastened his 