he Mobile Group of the Police Department of the Metropolitan Police Department, and will be transferred to the serious crime team of the Search Section 1 in two years.\n\nThen he and Sato worked as a colleague for seven days and sacrificed.\n\nHalf of the reason for the sacrifice was to save people, and he exchanged his life for the prompt of the next bomb placement site to avoid a larger civilian casualty.\n\nThe other half of the reason is that he is too handsome.\n\nDate Hang... World events are unpredictable, so hard to figure out!\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang... Zhigao\'s belief and slightly dramatic sacrifice.\n\nThe last one of the idols of the Police Academy\'s five-member group, Touko Amuro, no, it\'s Jianggu Ling, so there\'s nothing to say, so go ahead with the beliefs of the other four.\n\nThe water surface of the large swimming pool is nearly 40cm lower than the ground here, and there is a ladder next to it to go up. Two people can lean against the ground by the pool to block their figure on the water surface.\n\nHowever, if you continue to swim like this, it will obviously be noticed by two people, so Kudo Shinichi Amamiya Noriko confirms it again: \"Can you dive and swim there?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled cutely: \"Of course.\"\n\nKudo Shin nodded, that\'s not normal, no problem.\n\nMainly, Amamiya Noriko usually looks like she is not good at swimming in swimming lessons, so she hides in the shadows and does not go to the swimming pool to get sunburned. Indoor swimming pool, otherwise don\'t even think about her getting into the water and basking in the sun.\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t be sure of Noriko Amamiya\'s swimming skills.\n\nIt\'s just that from the distance from the shore just now, Noriko Amamiya\'s water is quite good.\n\nIn swimming lessons, it looks like it\'s just a costume, a hard costume.\n\nNow I can\'t entangle with Noriko Amamiya about this. Kudo Shinichi watched her dive into the water, and immediately lowered her head and put on her goggles and submerged herself.\n\nHowever, before he could swim out, he felt a heavy blow on the surface of the water. In the sight of the water, he saw the figure of a strong man, with strong and manly muscles, black swimming trunks, and directly hugged him. Suddenly appeared above the water.\n\n\"Little brother, are you alright?\"\n\nDate Hang looked down at Kudo Shinichi and asked aloud.\n\nKudo Shinichi silently took off his swimming goggles, \"It\'s okay, I\'m just diving, uncle.\"\n\nSeeing that he was all right, Idahang felt relieved. He felt as if he had made an oolong, so he couldn\'t help scratching his head: \"Hahaha, he\'s actually not an uncle, he\'s not yet 30 years old.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi has black lines all over his head, are you really a policeman?\n\nBut he turned his head and saw that Amamiya Noriko was lying leisurely on her swimming ring? ?\n\nSeeing him look over, Noriko Amamiya blinked, but suddenly it occurred to her that if both children sank, they could easily be regarded as drowning, right?\n\nSo it\'s enough to sink a Kudo Shinichi.\n\nIt\'s just that Air Date\'s speed was too fast, she just surfaced to the surface and saw Air Date jump into the water and fish out Kudo Shinichi with quick eyes and hands.\n\nNo diving opportunities are given, diving is forbidden.\n\nOn the other side, Matsuda Jinping just took off his sunglasses and stood up. The little girl who was about to rescue had already surfaced on his own and climbed onto the swimming ring to lie down. He could only put on his sunglasses and sat back to watch his friends and being picked up. the little boy over there.\n\nDate Hang told Kudo Shinichi to be careful when playing, and then went back and sat under the umbrella.\n\nShinichi Kudo found Noriko Amamiya afterward, with a stern face.\n\nCan you be a little less tricky and a little more sincere?\n\nTomoki Amamiya held back his laughter and apologized in a good voice. Then, let\'s see what he\'s going to do now?\n\nShin Kudo glanced at her, and swam straight over to Date Hang and Matsuda Jinping.\n\nAmamiya Noriko curiously swam over with the swimming ring, and heard Kudo Shin\'s pair of Date Hang and Matsuda Jinhei showdown.\n\n\"You must be policemen, right? This body looks like it\'s been exercised frequently. It\'s not the kind of muscle strength that comes from fitness, but the muscles that are naturally exercised because of work.\"\n\n\"In addition, the eyes always observe the people passing by, intentionally or unintentionally, are you writing down the characteristics of each person? Find and identify the prisoner, or follow a lot of times, you will develop this habit, you must be the Metropolitan Police Department. The detective from the Search Division? Which department is the Search Division I?\"\n\n\"As for this big brother with glasses, he shouldn\'t be a front-line police officer, maybe he\'s from the police department or supervision?\"\n\nDate Hang showed a slightly surprised expression, Matsuda Jinhei also said \"Oh?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi saw from their expressions that what he had guessed was almost the same as the real situation, so he spoke out confidently.\n\n\"So, what kind of case will happen here? I\'m junior high school detective Kudo Shinichi. I can help you solve the case.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave a small applause. She is well-founded, convincing, and close to the truth. Is this the junior high school detective, Kudo Shinichi?\n\nDate Hang is okay to say, but Matsuda Jinhei is a cool and arrogant handsome guy. He hooked the corner of his mouth and said, \"Little brother, what do you think I am best at?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at him calmly. If he speculates on what the other party is best at, then it is equivalent to speculating on the specific work content of the other party.\n\nIn this tone, it must not be a skill that most police officers know.\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, was she typing?\n\n​​');
