(404, 5, 68, 'Chapter 67: : the situation is complicated', 'After a while, police officers arrived at the scene.\n\nA cordon was drawn around the corpse, and a curtain was erected to block the view, and the forensic doctor examined the wounds of the victim.\n\nThe police were collecting the statements of the people present one by one.\n\nYumiya Noriko, who was comforting and coaxing Xiaolan and Sonoko, looked at each other with Officer Meguro, and looked at Amamiya Noriko\'s innocent gaze, the latter felt very bad, and for the third time...\n\n\"Sato, come here.\"\n\nOfficer Meguro asked Sato Mikazu, who came later, to deal with Amamiya Noriko, and went to discuss with Date Hang and Matsuda Jinhei himself.\n\nMiwako Sato, who is a smart woman in dress and short hair, feels that she is not particularly good at coaxing children.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko coaxed her well.\n\n\"Is Kiko okay?\"\n\n\"It\'s alright, thank you Sato sister, I was just a little scared at first, but now it\'s completely fine.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head and whispered, \"If you are not afraid, you have to be afraid, otherwise you are not a normal person.\n\nHowever, Sato thinks that a girl with a simple and cute personality like Noriko Amamiya has recovered her mood so quickly, which is still a bit abnormal.\n\nIt can be seen by comparing Xiaolan and Yuanzi.\n\nCould it be the aftermath of the previous kidnapping case?\n\nSato asked Noriko Amamiya\'s confession again, and then told her not to go too far, and then went to coax Xiaolan and Sonoko to ask for the confession.\n\nAfter Amamiya Noriko agreed to Sato, she sat on her own swimming ring and glanced at the people present who were being questioned by the police.\n\nThe little head started.\n\nOn the other side, Shinichi Kudo was also contemplating sorting out clues and ideas, but after all, he was not at the first scene, so he always felt that something was wrong.\n\nIt seems that the police officers over there have figured out the identity of the victim, and they are determining whether anyone at the scene has anything to do with the victim.\n\nKudo Shinichi really wanted to listen to it, but was stopped by Officer Meguro and told him to stay here and not run around.\n\nOfficer Mumu knew Shinichi, the classmate of Maori\'s younger brother\'s daughter Xiaolan, and the son of Kudo Yusaku. They are all descendants of old acquaintances. Since this is the case, he should not be allowed to approach the scene to prevent the child from leaving a shadow in his heart. manage.\n\nShinichi Kudo pouted, seeing that Xiaolan and Sonoko were being taken care of by Police Officer Sato, and seeing Noriko Amamiya\'s eyes scrutinizing the prisoner, he came over and said, \"Do you have any clues?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, then shook her head: \"No, I\'m just watching the changes in their expressions.\"\n\nKudo Shin nodded, not bothering her anymore, and went to the side to look for other clues.\n\nHe came too early. He didn\'t see as many things as Amamiya Noriko, but he also found a lot. For example, he saw the victim\'s wound.\n\nThe wound that incised the aorta in the neck was not a sharp knife, but a sharp object pierced and then pulled horizontally. the fugitive.\n\n\"It is now known that the murderer did not flee the scene, and the whereabouts of the murder weapon are unknown.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi looked around, and there were police officers searching on the slides, but nothing came of it.\n\nHis eyes fell on the group of people present. If the wound is not a sharp weapon, the possibility of women committing crimes will be weakened to a certain extent.\n\nThe water here is only as deep as the calf, and it is crystal clear. If it is just thrown into the water, the police can find it after a scan.\n\n\"Murderer, weapon, motive...\"\n\nThe thoughts in Kudo Shinichi\'s mind were sorted out one by one. For the first time, he encountered a completely real case and saw the lost life. His heart was restless.\n\nOn the other side, Amamiya Noriko watched everyone\'s expressions one by one. At the same time, she and Kudo Shinichi\'s reasoning progress was about the same, but she was there right away and knew who was definitely not suspicious. ,\n\nConsidering the murder weapon...\n\nAmamiya Noriko had a flash of light, walked to the edge, looked around, and found a special life-saving buoy.\n\nIt\'s the big red stick that lifeguards often carry. It\'s usually made of high-density foam and has strong buoyancy.\n\nShe remembered that it was thrown to the shore before the second lifeguard who arrived at the scene ran over.\n\nIt looks like it came from other swimming pools to the slide, because the water on the slide is shallow, so I can\'t use this thing.\n\n\"But what about actually?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up and down, and found an incision the size of her palm on the surface, which could completely hide a knife or something inside the surface.\n\nIt\'s just that I still haven\'t seen the murder weapon. It can be said that the murderer accidentally made a hole and didn\'t hide any weapon.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, dragged the life baton back, and sat on the side in a relaxed manner, staring straight at the lifeguard who arrived second, one looking white and tender, tall and thin at all. Murderer man.\n\n\"Watch—\"\n\nZuo Tian\'s lifeguard, standing calmly among the crowd, made himself not very conspicuous, but he did not deliberately hide it.\n\nTwo years ago, he had an argument with a colleague, and he endured it for a while. When he got home, the more he thought about it, the more angry he became.\n\nThe next day, he asked the other party to kill him on the grounds of apology.\n\nThen he fled the life of incognito in other places, and committed another robbery and murder because of poverty.\n\nHe has been pursued by the police for two years, but his hiding is perfect.\n\nUnexpectedly, the victim seemed to have recognized him a few days ago, so he might