 girl finally found another boy, slightly tugged at the other\'s clothes, and then approached as if to say something, the boy took the life baton.\n\nThen the little girl trotted to one side.\n\nZuo Tian glanced at the boy and then turned his gaze back to Noriko Amamiya.\n\nIf Kudo Shinichi looked back at him just now, it means that Amamiya Noriko told Kudo Shinichi that he was the murderer, and he couldn\'t help but look back at him. If he didn\'t look back, it means he hasn\'t said anything.\n\nThen, just deal with that little girl and run away...\n\nKudo Shinichi looked confused when he took the life-saving stick that Amiya Noriko put into him.\n\nWhy did you suddenly give him this?\n\nHe also said that the weather is good, there is only one truth, and it is completely open-mouthed nonsense.\n\nAfter Amamiya Noriko left, he looked down and checked the lifesaving stick. Generally speaking, Amamiya Noriko has a bad personality and strange hobbies, but he doesn\'t do meaningless things, or when he is the most boring, he is also playing with cold jokes. .\n\nI really saw him and saw the scratches on the lifesaving sticks. Generally speaking, the surface material of the lifesaving sticks is of high quality and not easy to be scratched, and the lifesaving equipment cannot be used if it is damaged...\n\nAfter a while, Kudo Shinichi suddenly raised his head and looked at the crowd over there. It was easy to see that one person was missing.\n\nAnd it seems to be a lifeguard!\n\nHe turned his head and looked around and saw Noriko Amamiya, and hurriedly ran over to grab a police officer: \"Did a lifeguard leave from here just now?!\"\n\n\"Ah, yes, he\'s not feeling well. He went to the toilet over there. He just went in and hasn\'t come out yet... Eh, little brother??!\"\n\nKudo Shin ran straight over. If he guessed correctly, the murderer was probably a lifeguard who had already escaped from the toilet and went to find Noriko Amamiya!\n\nAmamiya Noriko seems to have discovered something, but it can\'t be fully proved, so she plans to induce the murderer to do it.\n\nRunning over to talk to him was a threat to the murderer. She had the guts to tell others what she had discovered.\n\nBut in order for the murderer to chase after him, I only said to him unintelligible words, that is, just make an appearance, and I couldn\'t tell him, to prevent him from turning back and being seen by the murderer.\n\n\"Doesn\'t she know how dangerous this is?!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi ran to the toilet, and sure enough, no one saw it, and the window behind the toilet was opened.\n\nHe directly turned over and landed on the lifeguard on the ground.\n\nKudo Shinichi got off the lifeguard\'s back and looked at the situation with a complicated expression.\n\nLying on the ground, with his face buried in the lifeguard, lying in a big shape, one calf is still hanging on the wall on the toilet side, it looks like he was thrown into the street when he opened the window.\n\nBut he looked at Noriko Amamiya, who was spreading his hands on the side.\n\nCan this still be jumping through the window and hitting the street?\n\nIt must be Noriko Amamiya who has done the poisoning~www.readwn.com~ This is good, no problem.\n\nHe looked at the lifeguard\'s tragic condition and said, \"So, what\'s the situation?\"\n\n\"I just tripped over him a little while he was turning over the window.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gestured a little.\n\nKudo Shinichi took a deep breath: \"What do you want?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said embarrassedly, \"I want Shinichi-kun, do me a favor.\"\n\n……\n\n\"Brother Police, I found that the lifeguard was not in the toilet and fell outside. It\'s so strange, does he want to escape?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pulled the shirt of the police officer who was in front of the lifeguard to go to the toilet. The police officer\'s expression changed when he heard this. Could it be that the guy is the murderer and wanted to escape?\n\nIf you ran away for him, wouldn\'t you be finished?\n\n\"Bring your uncle to catch that bad guy!!\"\n\nThe police officers immediately handcuffed the unconscious murderer who \"turned over the window and jumped into the street\".\n\nKudo Shinichi also said \"Ah Lie Lie\" and \"It\'s weird\" at the right time, and pulled out the life stick, and Zuo Tian\'s complexion was not the tanned complexion that lifeguards often have. This is his own suspicion.\n\nAfter being woken up, Zuo Tian\'s lifeguard struggled like crazy: \"Damn!! That old woman, **** it, dares to plot against me!!!\"\n\n\"I won\'t let you go after I come out—\"\n\nIf you ask him if he loses his mind, he doesn\'t answer at all, just cursing frantically.\n\nUpon seeing Noriko Amamiya\'s face, Kudo Shin said, \"He\'s not talking about you, is he?\"\n\n\"Do you think I look like an old woman?!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko stomped him hard, making Kudo Shinichi jump in pain.\n\nThe situation is more complicated.\n\n​​'),
(405, 5, 85, 'Chapter 84: : sin', '\"Ha... It seems that there aren\'t any good shoe stores nearby?\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko came back with a pair of clogs and looked at Noriko awkwardly.\n\n\"...\"\n\nThis is what Amamiya Noriko didn\'t expect. Is there such an operation?\n\nBut yes, there are flea markets here, and there aren\'t any serious shoe stores. You can buy geta, but it feels like this place fits the temperament.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was sitting on the curb at the side of the alley, still wearing her own small round-toed leather shoes. I can only hope that the police will not really use her shoes as physical evidence...\n\nMore importantly, Sonoko only brought her a pair of clogs, and she had no foot pockets, so her stockings could not be worn.\n\nSonoko also bought some cookies and came back and sat and ate them with her.\n\nAfter a while, two police officers, a woman and a man, rushed over quickly. After seeing the situation in the alley, they were a little sluggish.\n\nTwo little girls were eating biscuits in the alley, and a sturdy middle-aged uncle was lying on the side, not moving.\n\nThe female police officer squatted down to check the situation of the two little girls. There seemed to be no major problems, and she greeted them very politely.\n\n\"Hello, children, how is the situation? Tell my sister in detail.\"\n\nAs a girl frightened by the wretched uncle, Amamiya Noriko, of course, chose to let Sonoko speak. Sonoko was truly indignant to fight for Noriko, and described the wretched uncle as heinous and heinous.\n\nNot to mention that the wretched uncle is not a handsome guy, even if he is a handsome guy, he can\'t easily forgive her friend who dares to bully her Suzuki Sonoko.\n\nThe female police officer comforted Sonoko with shame, while the other two male police officers squatted down to check the condition of the prisoner who attempted the crime. They were breathing normally and were not conscious.\n\nThere is a relatively obvious spread of skin redness around the chin and the chin. It is obvious that he has suffered a heavy blow. A blunt weapon, preliminary judgment, may be more than once.\n\nOne of the male police officers gestured with his index finger and thumb. The area that was directly hit was small. He looked at the toe of the girl\'s small leather shoes, and it seemed that they were indeed about the same size.\n\nWhat the operator said was actually true. The passers-by used the little girl\'s shoes to defeat the wretched uncle who was conspiring against children.\n\nAnother male police officer couldn\'t help shaking his head: \"It\'s really getting worse, morals are deteriorating, and people are still children. Recently, there have been more and more prisoners of this type. When I was on duty last time, I caught a green light at the intersection and didn\'t leave. , I actually care about prostitution, I heard that there is a rich man, obscene!\"\n\n\"Dirty! Such a cute little girl, she actually had a crooked mind, and brought it back for a strict trial!\"\n\n\"Strict trial!\"\n\nThe two people dragged the suspect away, and the female police officer received their instructions and set her eyes on Noriko Amamiya\'s shoes.\n\nAmamiya Noriko understood, she simply took off her shoes and gave them to her.\n\nThen she took off her white stockings and put on the clogs that Yuanzi bought for her with her bare feet. It was a very strange combination. She wore a white shirt with a small white skirt, and she wore clogs with bare feet, but it was acceptable.\n\nThe female police officer looked at Amamiya Noriko\'s helpless face, covered her mouth and smiled, praising her for her cuteness. Sonoko said it was her choice, and of course Noriko looked cute in it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko: Yes, all of you are right, why don\'t you try wearing clogs with bare feet?\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Sonoko were also brought back together, so it is impossible to put them back directly.\n\nWent to the Metropolitan Police Department to sit for a while, anyway, after simply recording the confession, nothing happened to them, just waiting for the parents to pick them up.\n\nAs for a righteous person who acts bravely and does not keep his name, he should have a uniform figure in the shadows, and he can\'t see his hairstyle or appearance. He can only see the other party\'s gentle eyes and white teeth when he smiles.\n\nAfter recording the confession, Amamiya Noriko took Sonoko to search for a lesson to see acquaintances.\n\nBefore entering, she met Date Hang at the door holding a circulation board, Amamiya Noriko waved her small hand: \"Uncle Date Hang?\"\n\n\"Oh! It\'s you, Amamiya... Noriko, right?\"\n\nDate Hang was also stunned for a moment, then opened his eyes wide and smiled, touching his beard, still had the impression that something happened when he was in the water park.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded lightly, then introduced Sonoko: \"Well, this is my friend Suzuki Sonoko.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko said skillfully, \"Hello, uncle!\"\n\nBecause there is usually another uncle Kogoro Mori.\n\nIdahang said enthusiastically: \"Hello, what are you doing here? You can\'t just wander around.\"\n\nSonoko immediately recounted what happened to them. Date Hang and Sonoko immediately shared the same hatred, and angrily prepared to teach the suspect over there a lesson. Sonoko wanted to follow along to see it.\n\n\"...You go, I won\'t go.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved her hand, she is the one who has taught that guy a lesson so far, so what are you going to see now?\n\nConsidering that the victim does need to be careful when seeing the prisoner, especially a little girl like Amamiya Noriko, so Date Air asked her to find Sato, and by the way, help him hand over the circulation board to Sato, while he went to Look at the prisoner.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took the circulation board and glanced at it curiously. Dareqing has something to do with Sonoko. It is a building of the Suzuki consortium that is capped and is preparing to hold a banquet. After the capping, there will be a precious gem on the top floor for a short time. It is for everyone to enjoy for a short time, and this gem has been stolen and robbed many times before, and it has been stared at by many people. The Suzuki Consortium has made full preparations and will definitely not be stolen.\n\nBut just in case, I hope the police will send someone to act as a representative.\n\nThis circulation board is to see who is willing to go to the search class, and sign up independently, because it is really going to be a representative, and there are only a few places. The Suzuki consortium has found a security company to be responsible for the security aspect. There is no need for the police to go too far. many people.\n\nShe saw that Air Date had filled in her name, so of course she would go there.\n\n\"Tude.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko knocked on the door, and a police officer who searched for a class came to open the door for her. When she saw it was a little girl, she was stunned: \"Little boy, why are you like this?\"\n\n\"Uncle Date Hang asked me to help spread this.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko held up the circulation board in her hand.\n\n\"This, just give it to me...\"\n\nThe police officer stretched out his hand to take the circulation board in the hand of Amamiya Noriko, but Amamiya Noriko retracted his hand to avoid it, and said with a serious face: \"I will pass it on to every police officer\'s uncle in person.\"\n\nThe police officer didn\'t know whether to laugh or cry. After all, it was Date Hang who said so, so he let Noriko Amemiya into the office of the first search section.\n\n\"Where is Sister Sato?\"\n\n\"Oh, you still know Sato, she\'s over there, my brother is with you—\"\n\n  \"No thanks.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at how attentive he was in an instant, understood, refused, Sato Miwako is really a flower of the police department.\n\nAmamiya Noriko easily found the location of Sato Miwako, and gave Sato Miwako a surprise.\n\n\"Why is Noriko here?\"\n\nSato Miwako was taken aback for a moment, then smiled and pulled Yumiya Noriko\'s little hand.\n\n\"Of course it\'s specifically to see Sister Sato.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said obediently.\n\nThen he inadvertently said that the original record was like this, which caused Sato Miwako to be puzzled, and inadvertently said that it was okay, the bad guy had already been caught.\n\nSato Mikako saw that Amamiya Noriko met a bad guy again, so he asked and checked, and found that he had indeed met a bad guy again.\n\nAnd it\'s still of such a vicious nature that the opponent must be given a taste of the iron fist of the law.\n\nAmamiya Noriko chatted with Sato Miwako, and then went around and searched for a lesson, and read the circulation board carefully for everyone, including Officer Megumi, of course.\n\nAs a matter of course, he wrote a name and prepared to go. His role is still guaranteed, and he can be present in most cases, especially if the design involves police representatives, banquets, etc., he can still appear in the police department.\n\nI didn\'t see Shiratori Ren Saburo and Takagi Shibu, and the two of them didn\'t arrive at the time to search for the first lesson.\n\nBasically, they came here after Matsuda Jinhei died.\n\nAfter a circle, Amamiya Noriko and Sonoko were picked up by their respective parents, and the ones who came to pick her up were Chieda Riho and her mother Amamiya Emi who were driving.\n\nEmi Amamiya sighed with mixed feelings: \"I didn\'t expect a daughter to be more worrying than a son. She completely inherited her mother\'s genes, so she would be easily targeted by bad people with bad intentions?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko rolled her eyes, are you praising me or praising yourself? Can you be serious as a mom?\n\nThe more serious one is Chieda Riho. While driving, she glanced at Noriko\'s delicate and somewhat helpless face through the rearview mirror while she was driving.\n\nShe said, \"Noriko will still have to take me with her when she goes out.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in her heart that it was too difficult for me, and the seriousness of Chieda Riho would reduce a lot of fun and increase a lot of restraints.\n\nAnd every time it\'s okay to go out quickly, and when Chieda Riho doesn\'t have to worry about it, a bad guy will pop up to increase the probability of her encountering threats outside, making it more difficult for her to go out alone.\n\nShe still needs to improve. Next time, just beat up the bad guy who was looking for her trouble and let it out, and then don\'t call the police or do anything.\n\nEmi Amamiya suddenly remembered, and took out an exquisitely crafted invitation card from her small bag to give to her daughter.\n\n\"This is given to my mother by someone who met the Suzuki family at the Metropolitan Police Department. They invited our family to their weekend banquet. It seems that another building has been built. Why do so many buildings need to be built?\"\n\nIt\'s convenient to be bombed and there\'s still some leftovers, Amamiya Noriko said.\n\nShe took the invitation and looked at it, and it really was what she saw at the police. Yes, she will take a look at it when the time comes. The current personnel have basically gathered together, including Date Hang, Sato Miwako, Officer Megumi, and her Amamiya. Noriko, Suzuki Sonoko, the people of the Suzuki Foundation.\n\nIt is expected that Kudo Shinichi, Maurilan and Mauri Kogoro will not be left behind by the garden.\n\nDr. Agsa may also go.\n\nMaybe gin and vodka will also join in the fun... This is more imaginary.\n\nIn short, as far as the current lineup is concerned, it is completely enough to make up a case.\n\nLet her wait and see.\n\nWhen they went to school the next day, as expected, Kudo Shinichi and Xiaolan were also sent invitations by Sonoko, as well as their respective parents.\n\nKudo Shinichi flipped through the invitation card and didn\'t care much. The banquet or something was not very interesting.\n\nH