(406, 5, 4, 'Chapter 3: : An introduction to Jiangzhou before the apprenticeship', 'nap time.\n\nJiang Zhou, who was ready to start, finally walked past the children\'s nap room.\n\nHe felt a little stunned and uneasy. The crime and pressure of kidnapping the young child had already emerged in his mind.\n\nOn the way through, I glanced at Noriko Amamiya\'s sleeping face. This kid doesn\'t usually like to talk, but he is also a very quiet and well-behaved type. If he succeeds, he and his wife will treat her as their daughter and start over.\n\nThen the wife\'s mental illness will definitely improve.\n\nHe walked out through the door on the other side, with the pain of inner struggle on his face, just in time to hear the conversation of the two female teachers.\n\nTomoka Mikan said in surprise, \"A black van?\"\n\n\"Yes, it has been parked at the back door of the kindergarten. Should we call the police?\"\n\nTomoka Mikan nodded: \"Just in case, write down the license plate number by the way!\"\n\nJiang Zhou Lunjie hurriedly said, \"Well, shall I go over and check the situation?\"\n\nMigan Yuka turned her head: \"Mr. Jiang Zhou, be careful.\"\n\n\"Then I\'ll trouble you.\"\n\nJiang Zhou Lunjie nodded, then ran out, constantly thinking about his wife\'s decision to abduct a child and start over again.\n\nHe ran to the van window and said, \"Don\'t do it! This kind of thing!\"\n\nHowever, he found that the person in the car was not the brother-in-law he was about to attack, but a strange man wearing a cap and sunglasses.\n\nWhen he was stunned, Kudo Yusaku slowly took off his sunglasses and said with a smile, \"Why don\'t you stand in the rain talking and sit on the co-pilot?\"\n\n\"You, who are you?!\"\n\nYusaku Kudo put on his glasses and smiled naturally, \"I\'m just a novelist just emerging.\"\n\nInside the Rice Flower Nursery.\n\nKudo Shinichi is still standing behind the door, vigilant for the arrival of the criminal. As a future detective, he cannot tolerate crimes happening in front of his eyes!\n\nSuddenly someone tapped him on the shoulder from behind, and Kudo Shinichi was startled and quickly jumped away.\n\n\"The response is very fast, it\'s hard work.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at Amamiya Noriko, who was standing leisurely on the side, and opened his mouth in surprise, but Amamiya Noriko gave a booing gesture, and quickly stopped his voice.\n\n\"The children are still taking a nap.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi lowered his voice: \"You should be sleeping too! Didn\'t you get sleeping pills in your meal?!\"\n\nAfter speaking, looking at Amamiya Noriko\'s leisurely look, she instantly remembered that she stopped talking after briefly talking to him before eating, and she has been eating silently since then, chewing very seriously. It looks like you didn\'t swallow it at all, did you?\n\nShe probably vomited in the toilet on the way to take a nap on the excuse.\n\nWhen cleaning up the dishes, she also went first alone, maybe she didn\'t eat much at all, right?\n\nAfter thinking about it clearly, Kudo Shinichi was speechless: \"It\'s a shame you can pretend to have a mouthful of rice.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her eyebrows and said, \"Little detective, why do you think sleeping pills are in the rice?\"\n\n\"???\"\n\nKudo Shinichi reacted immediately. In the past, most of the lunches were served with milk, but today it was freshly squeezed juice. The sleeping pills must have been put in the juice of Amiya Noriko, and the rice was always in the pot, and it was a child. It\'s not easy to start with the food, and the dishes are the same.\n\nOnly the juice is distributed, and unlike milk, which is packaged, Jiang Zhou Lunjie has the opportunity to distribute the medicine juice to Noriko Amemiya.\n\nHe found out that he should have thought of such a simple thing, but Noriko Amamiya didn\'t say a word during the meal, which made him preconceived, thinking that Noriko Amamiya was having a fake meal.\n\nHe couldn\'t help but said, \"What if there is also medicine in the meal?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was surprised: \"So I really didn\'t even eat food, but I want to point out the mistake that you think sleeping pills are more likely to be in rice or vegetables. It\'s really hard to put a mouthful of rice in my mouth. It was really hard work.”\n\nKudo Shinichi doesn\'t want to talk, I was led astray by you.\n\nHe asked the question he wanted to know the most: \"Did you already know that he was going to attack you?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said innocently: \"What to do? It\'s just because I have taken sleeping pills, so I feel that there is something wrong with Teacher Jiang Zhou. Just in case this happens today, it is impossible for me to skip meals every day.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi breathed a sigh of relief, he thought Noriko Amamiya knew all about it.\n\n\"How do you know you\'re on sleeping pills?\"\n\nAlthough she hadn\'t experienced it before, Amamiya Noriko pondered: \"You wake up and find that you\'re about to wet the bed, so if you haven\'t woken up before, you\'ll feel a problem.\"\n\nKudo Shin turned his eyes, now he felt that Amamiya Noriko would definitely not let such a humiliating thing happen to her, so he wouldn\'t believe it.\n\nBut he is not easy to ask about this kind of thing, so he can only keep his mouth shut.\n\nWhat if, what if it was actually true?\n\nHe will definitely be beaten by Noriko Amamiya again.\n\nThe next day, Jiang Zhou Lunjie didn\'t come, and he won\'t come in the future. This matter is basically settled.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thinks the plot can be trusted, except for the inexplicable cameo of the victim.\n\nAfter that, there were no incidents. Noriko Amamiya began to concentrate on rectifying her own system. The world of Conan is not a peaceful world.\n\nEspecially in Japan, the frequency of incidents on the bright side is ridiculously high, but over the past few years, secretly, the FBI in the United States, MI6 in the United Kingdom, CSIS in Canada, BND in Germany, Zero in Japan,