yebrows and looked at Noriko Amamiya, who was surrounded over there, \"She definitely doesn\'t think so.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was surrounded by children chatting, her head was big, her face was expressionless for a while before she got out, and after the graduation ceremony was over, she had time to come and see them.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko excitedly said to her, \"Kiko, we will be elementary school students from now on!\"\n\nThis feeling is similar to graduating from a primary school, feeling that I finally got rid of the title of a primary school student. How is it actually?\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded: \"Elementary school, it\'s not bad.\"\n\nKudo Shin said, \"I thought you should also look down on elementary school.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved: \"What are you talking about, there are more children in elementary school, which is a good thing.\"\n\nHow many children are there in a kindergarten?\n\nMao Lilan agreed: \"Kiko will definitely be able to make more friends in elementary school, right?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi has black lines all over her head, she is going to play with more people.\n\nAmamiya Noriko chatted with them for a while, and when she saw her mother coming to pick up her mother at the school gate, she said goodbye to them first.\n\n\"Anyway, bye elementary school.\"\n\nShe has been staring at the events since the beginning of elementary school for a long time.'),
(407, 5, 92, 'Chapter 91: : It\'s time, number up', 'On the way towards her father, Amamiya Noriko suddenly saw her father\'s palm swinging towards her.\n\nIt means to keep yourself out of the past.\n\nIs there a situation?\n\nAmamiya Noriko sat in the corner and observed.\n\nNext to Amamiya Ludou was a fat man with a strong officialdom. When he spoke with a big belly, he gestured a lot in the official voice, which was a bit funny.\n\nBut at the same time, he is also very pompous, with a sturdy bodyguard with him.\n\nAmamiya Ludou didn\'t bring a bodyguard with him at the banquet.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it, it seemed that she came with the police, she only noticed her father, and to be honest, she thought that the fat man was a police officer and didn\'t care too much. This kind of banquet police officer came as a police representative. Showing your face is normal.\n\nShe looked at Officer Mumu next to her, she was a little helpless next to the fat man, but she couldn\'t say anything.\n\nIt was obvious that the rank was higher than that of Officer Mumu, and the rank was overwhelming. She took a closer look. The rank was police inspector, and it was two ranks higher than Officer Mumu\'s police department. The former Nagano County Police Headquarters Chief of Search Section Kuroda. Hei\'s rank is police inspector, the one of one of Rum\'s suspects.\n\n\"Wouldn\'t the winery\'s purpose be him?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pondered, the probability is still relatively high, her father... Although the suspicion is quite high, it is not a big head.\n\nHer gaze quietly fell on Gin\'s side, paying attention to the direction of their gaze.\n\nBut because the distance between Amamiya Ludou and the fat man was relatively close, it was hard to tell.\n\n\"Are you an idiot? You can talk like a celestial official so much, what\'s there to talk about?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko held her chin and waited for a long time to chat there. At this time, more and more people arrived at the banque