d and put the phone back.\n\nChieda Riho watched as her hand holding the phone fell under the table, and when she came out again, she was already empty-handed and clearly put the phone away.\n\n\"Next time, don\'t mess with your clothes, at least don\'t mess with your dresses.\"\n\n\"How can it be called a design that uses space ingeniously? My needlework is not bad, right?\"\n\nMiyajiko said shyly, and then her expression returned to her cute and cute look: \"Who is that fat uncle next to Dad?\"\n\nChieda Riho glanced at it and replied without expression: \"The section chief of the traffic department of the Metropolitan Police Department seems to have recently seized a batch of smuggled goods, and it is expected that he will be raised to the police.\"\n\n  \"Oh?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko finds it interesting, the victim\'s suspicion is even greater.\n\nChieda Riho lowered her voice: \"What do you want to do?\"\n\nFrom her point of view, Amamiya Noriko is cute and lovely to ask someone for information, but most of them are doing bad things.\n\n\"It\'s nothing, I don\'t do anything to him.\" Amamiya Noriko said sweetly, \"Sister Riho help me call my parents to the backstage, please.\"\n\nSeeing that Amamiya Noriko was acting like a spoiled child at the end, Chieda Riho nodded.\n\nAnd Amamiya Noriko looked at Gin again, got up and went back to Sonoko\'s room to lock it, reached out to the side of her waist to unzip the zipper, pinned the slender shoulder straps to the sides, and the delicate black dress slipped off.\n\n\"Bang dang.\"\n\nWearing only pumpkin pants and a tube top, Amamiya Noriko bent down and took out a small cosmetic bag from the inner pocket of her skirt, sat on the bed in Sonoko\'s room, pinned her hair with a pin-like hair clip, and pursed her lips and smiled at the mirror. , start makeup.\n\nIf the trumpet is not used, there is probably no chance for her to appear in this good show.\n\nAfter a while, a girl with a heroic face looked at herself in the mir