(408, 5, 27, 'Chapter 26: : I think it\'s ok', 'Officer Mumu felt confused.\n\nThe woman who was in a coma had scars from being electrocuted. The explanation was reasonable. Noriko Amamiya\'s fearful appearance when they came made people feel pity, and Noriko Amamiya also had wounds from being electrocuted.\n\nShe was afraid of what the woman would do to her when she woke up, so she used an electric shocker, which is understandable.\n\njust...\n\nHow can there be a feeling like Kogoro Mouri\'s presence analysis, that kind of discomfort... being completely deviated from the correct answer.\n\nHe glanced at Noriko Amamiya, who Sato went back to comfort, and said that this little girl seemed to know Mouri\'s brother.\n\nShe was the little girl in the bombing of the Amamiya Building a few years ago, right? A friend of the Maori brother\'s daughter.\n\nI hope that the children will not leave psychological shadows, so I have to leave this to Sato.\n\nThe police tried to bring up the man\'s body in the mountain stream, but in the end, the man was thrown into an impersonal shape, especially the neck and spine, which were completely twisted and broken. The muddy body was handed over to the forensic doctor.\n\nSitting in the police car and being held by Sato, Noriko Amamiya saw the corpse that was brought up. Although it was immediately covered up, the tragic situation was undoubtedly very tragic.\n\nThis ruthless and ruthless man was her breakthrough from beginning to end. Who told him not to drive? The woman wanted to run in the last 5th gear, but Noriko Amamiya still accepted it. No wonder she was driving on a road with a lot of curves.\n\nAs for this man, the only chance is to draw a gun instantly when she is pinched to death, instead of trying to break her wrists with both hands.\n\nThere are trachea, carotid artery and vagus nerve in the human Adam\'s apple. Fingers stuck on the Adam\'s apple was her most stable hand at that time, hitting the Adam\'s apple or temple might fail, like she failed to deal with this man on the mountain, and her fingers got stuck. Adam\'s apple, unless the Adam\'s apple is gone, he will never be able to break free.\n\nAlthough she looks slender, her strength can really allow her fingertips to pierce the skin tissue and pull out the Adam\'s apple.\n\nIt\'s just that thanks to his wrong choice of suffocation and panic, Amamiya Noriko\'s wrist was bruised.\n\nSato Mikako also took off her jacket when she was checking whether there were any other injuries on Noriko Amamiya\'s body, but she didn\'t even notice it.\n\nWhen Sato saw it, he felt sorry for her and scolded the robber: \"It\'s too daring, Noriko rest assured, we will definitely bring each other to justice.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that Sato Miwako is the most handsome beauty besides her. She is worthy of being the police flower of the Metropolitan Police Department. She can walk fast in high heels.\n\nShe suddenly remembered that she hadn\'t reported safety to Xin Xiaolan and the others, and said, \"Officer Sato, can I make a call to tell my friends that I\'m all right?\"\n\nSato gave her the phone: \"Yes.\"\n\nAfter thanking her, Noriko Amamiya called Dr. Aga\'s cell phone. Xin Xiaolan and the others didn\'t have a cell phone yet, but they should all be with Dr. Aga. After all, it would be quicker to solve the problem on their own.\n\nAfter connecting, Dr. A Li\'s voice came out: \"Hello? Who is it?\"\n\n\"Doctor, I\'m Noriko, I\'m fine.\"\n\n\"Noriko?! Are you all right—are you really all right? If you are threatened by a gangster, just be silent for a second. We have already called the police.\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko couldn\'t help being silent for a second. The latter part was the voice of Kudo Shinichi, who obviously robbed Dr. Akasa\'s mobile phone. Did this guy think that if the gangster asked her to make a call, he wouldn\'t be listening?\n\nKudo Shinichi thought she was still in danger, and quickly said, \"Can you see anything near