hout a whole corpse, death without evidence, and flawless efforts.\n\nThe woman died after several days of rescue.\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t know if it was her own electric shock or was she bleed to death by hitting the glass? tetanus? In short, no one confessed to her.\n\nIt is worth mentioning that the mastermind behind it was quickly caught. The mobile phones of both men and women have enough evidence, and the last call record of the man\'s mobile phone pointed the clues directly to each other.\n\nIt is a rival company of the Amemiya Consortium. Because they are worried that the two major consortiums of Amemiya and Suzuki will join hands to defeat it, they want to destroy the meeting between the two sides next week.\n\nDue to business reasons, the main forces of the Amamiya family are distributed all over the world. In Japan, there is still no more absolute power than the Suzuki family, so they are going to arrest the daughter of the Amamiya family to force them to give up their cooperation with the Suzuki Foundation.\n\nBut the result was that their own murderous kidnapping was jailed, the company was leaderless, and a large number of black histories were found involved, which quickly fell apart, and the essence was absorbed by the Amemiya consortium in the same industry.\n\nYumiya Noriko could see that, with such a resolute act, her father must have also shot angrily~www.readwn.com~ Today, Amamiya Noriko was still paralyzed on the hospital bed, but if there was no accident, she would be gone the next day. You can get out of this place.\n\nAnd at this time, Shinichi Kudo came to visit the doctor alone.\n\n\"To be honest, things are actually not what the police reported at all, right?\"\n\n\"There are still a lot of suspicious points. The simplest one is that the police officers didn\'t find it. If you don\'t know how to use a gun, how can you grab a gun decisively? And as far as I know, it\'s a p220 pistol. I guess if it\'s such a small space, In such an emergency, you don\'t have time to pull the hammer, but if it\'s a double action, the trigger force on the first shot is full 10 pounds, don\'t you think the trigger is stuck?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at her and threw one question after another.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko picked up a pen next to her, put her thumb against the body of the pen, and twisted the barrel with her slender index finger, as if pulling the trigger was so easy for her.\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko held her chin and admired his dark face: \"10 pounds? I think it\'s OK, I have to tell Xiaolan that you still bullied me when I was hospitalized.\"\n\nXiaolan and Yuanzi, who just walked outside the ward, came in together and asked in confusion, \"Huh? Is there something for Kiko to ask me for?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi made an ok gesture quietly in front of him with Xiaolan on his back.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said harmlessly to Xiaolan, \"Xiaolan, I won\'t bring any gifts when I come to see your new family!\"\n\nXiaolan blushed: \"Ji, Jizi, what nonsense are you talking about!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi gave a thumbs up, and Amamiya Noriko glanced at him with disdain.\n\nOn the other hand, Sonoko also winked at Noriko Amamiya and gave a thumbs up. Obviously, she highly recognized the act of bringing the two together. She was the main force in bringing together Xiaolan and Shinichi.'),
