sadvantage?\n\nTo actually make Noriko Amamiya suffer, what kind of fairy is this Suwon classmate? It is necessary to learn to learn.\n\nAfter arriving in the classroom, Amamiya Noriko buried herself in taking notes. Yui Mizuhara\'s notes were not bad. Otherwise, Amamiya Noriko would pull her out of the fish pond, and the other fish would be obedient.\n\nXiaolan found out that Kudo Shinichi went to chat with Suwon-san, so she passed away a little jealous.\n\nSonoko took a look at the small Shura field over there and didn\'t worry about Xiaolan at all. Suwon-san liked Kiko at first glance.\n\nAs Amamiya Noriko wrote the note, she saw Sonoko approaching and looking at her, her eyes wide open.\n\n\"What is the garden doing?\"\n\nSonoko touched his chin: \"I found that Noriko seems to be a little prettier than yesterday.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko really put up a forefinger: \"Well, I\'m 1 o\'clock cuter than yesterday, just 1 o\'clock.\"\n\n\"I want to learn! Noriko taught me - to make all the men in the world fall in love with me.\"\n\nSonoko howled and hugged Noriko Amamiya, begging.\n\n\"…\"\n\nShe also thought if she could make some sense, so she could only think about it, and she couldn\'t teach it.\n\nBut Sonoko is not easy for her, Kudo Shinichi, and later Conan, after serious reasoning, came to a conclusion: \"No one will be interested in Sonoko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko put down her pen and nodded and said, \"I will help Sonoko at noon. Did Sonoko bring a lunch box?\"\n\nYuanzi shook his head and asked curiously, \"No, does it matter?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, and then said cutely, \"Sonoko will know when the time comes.\"\n\n  \"Oh…\"\n\nSonoko responded, but actually wanted to ask, Noriko, what did you grow up eating so cute?\n\n  Until noon.\n\nSonoko sat next to Amamiya Noriko\'s seat and faced her, her eyes sparkling.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s slender fingers pinched her face and tried her hand. Second Miss Suzuki\'s skin is still pretty good.\n\nSonoko blinked: \"How t