(411, 5, 46, 'Chapter 45: : Visit the Amamiya family', 'Since Noriko Amamiya started to coordinate affairs of her club committee, Shinichi Kudo rarely saw her in the football club during club activities.\n\n  congratulations.\n\nBut these guys in the football club have no passion at all, and they look forward to Noriko Amemiya coming every day.\n\nAmamiya Noriko has only been here once in recent days, just to cooperate with the sports department to see the situation of the football club almost a month after the start of school.\n\nBecause of the presence of Noriko Amamiya, the head of the sports department of the student union saw the complete football club and was quite amazed. He had to feel that the level of our school\'s football club was a top team capable of competing in national sports competitions.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who had been playing for a few days in the football club like Yan eggplant, didn\'t want to talk.\n\nIn other words, Amamiya Noriko came to fight chicken blood.\n\nThe football club, tennis club, etc., are all under the Sports Department of the Student Union. Others include the Literature and Art Department, the External Relations Department, the Propaganda Department, and the Life Department.\n\nHer club members connect all clubs, and none of them leak. Anyway, she entered the big reservoir and started casting the net.\n\nAfter inspecting the tea art club this afternoon, I actually went to drink tea and chat with the senior sisters of the tea art club.\n\nThe tea art club is great, and they are basically gentle and knowledgeable seniors.\n\nAmamiya Noriko briefly recorded the strengths and characteristics of the tea art club, and prepared for the school\'s activities in the future. This is a duty.\n\nAfter getting it done, Amamiya Noriko went out of school to prepare to go home. On weekends, Xiaolan Yuanzi Shinichi and the others came to the house as guests, so they still had to make some preparations.\n\nAs soon as he left the school gate, he was handed to him by a large bouquet of roses.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the bright red roses in amazement, \"Okay, I\'ll give it to you for nothing.\"\n\nBehind the rose, there was an unspeakable face, not ugly, but there were some scratches on his face that had not healed, and he said sincerely and affectionately: \"Miss Amamiya, I fell in love with you from the first sight I saw you. With you, become my fiancee!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t take the roses, she glanced at him up and down, she was wearing a decent suit, and it seemed to be a high-end product. Anyway, she was not very familiar with the expensive brands in the world of Conan, and she knew that this guy was probably a The rich second generation is right.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the wound on his face, although it was good to confess directly, but wouldn\'t it have to wait for the scratch on his face to heal?\n\nAnd this face has never been seen before, is it the fish you caught?\n\nIt\'s hard to tell if a stranger comes over just to make a confession.\n\nIf Kudo Shinichi was here, he would know who this rich second generation was. He had just planted a bush a few days ago, and he must have been deeply impressed.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko didn\'t know what she had done a few days ago because of her looks, so she blinked: \"Who are you?\"\n\n\"Cough—\"\n\nFu Erdai cleared his throat and prepared to introduce himself. After thinking about it carefully, it was a bit presumptuous to confess like this, although Noriko Amamiya thought it was very good.\n\n\"Ah...\" Amamiya Tomiki suddenly opened his mouth, as if he just remembered something: \"That... I\'m sorry, I refuse, and then I have something to do today, so I\'ll go first, I wish you a good face. The injury will recover soon.”\n\nFu Erdai held roses in his hands and watched Noriko Amamiya\'s back lightly leave and turned into a sculpture.\n\nHis driver got out of the car and patted him on the shoulder, and said with relief: \"Master, next time will definitely.\"\n\n\"...It\'s all because you hurt my face!!! I noticed it!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko trotted around the corner and walked leisurely.\n\nOf course it doesn\'t matter, but looking at the guy\'s appearance, it seems like he wants to talk at length, so there\'s no need to listen, he\'s already confessed, he refuses to take attribute points and it\'s over.\n\nIt\'s not that they didn\'t confess that they still have to go fishing with long lines.\n\nHe took a few attribute points indifferently.\n\n\"Kiko has been confessed again~\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head when she heard the words, Sonoko caught up from behind at some point.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko teased: \"Didn\'t that guy look serious just now? He had to confess with a wounded face.\"\n\n\"It\'s the first time I\'ve seen him, and maybe he\'s the young master of a rich family, but it\'s not really sincere.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko had a worried look on her face, although she was really sincere, she actually received attribute points.\n\nSonoko nodded earnestly when he heard the words: \"Playboy or something, Noriko really has to be careful.\"\n\nThen she expressed that she was looking forward to going to Noriko\'s house on the weekend, and also said that Xiaolan\'s father would also go there.\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her brows, will Kogoro Mouri come?\n\nThis staffing seems to be able to trigger the case, Kudo Shinichi, Xiaolan, Sonoko, Sonoko\'s father and uncle, Mouri Kogoro, these six, the theatrical version is relatively easy to appear.\n\nAnd with Sonoko\'s father, Shiro Suzuki, and his uncle, Jiro Suzuki, I always felt that the phantom thief Kid would be bubbling.\n\nHowever, this probability is relatively small. As soon as the Kuroba Pirates did not know where to go, Kuroba Kaito has not inherited the title of Kaitou Kid.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is already ready to fight anyway. If the Conan theatrical version is played at home, there is a chance that it will explode on the spot.\n\nAfter two days, the weekend finally arrived.\n\nThe Suzuki family came quite early because the two families were close to each other. The Suzuki family was mainly composed of the parents of Sonoko Suzuki Shiro and Suzuki Tomoko, and her uncle Suzuki Jiroyoshi.\n\nAmamiya Ludou and Amamiya Emi, the couple, and Amamiya Noriko were all at the door to welcome them as guests.\n\nBecause the Amamiya family is an old-fashioned Japanese mansion~www.readwn.com~, the Suzuki family came to visit in a kimono instead of a suit for the occasion.\n\nThe Amamiya couple and Amamiya Noriko are naturally the same.\n\nAmamiya Noriko wears a blue-colored, sakura-patterned kimono with small sleeves. Small sleeves are generally used for evening parties and other occasions where you can dress casually. She doesn\'t like strict dress.\n\nMoreover, the sleeve length of Xiaozhen Sleeve is a graduation-style two-foot sleeve, because the sleeves are relatively short, it will give people a cute impression.\n\nSonoko is the same, but she is a wheat-yellow kimono with a calamus pattern. The meaning of calamus is to win, ward off evil spirits...\n\nAfter meeting each other\'s parents and greeting each other, the two also looked at each other in private and blinked.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko said that it is indeed your garden.\n\nAnd Sonoko said that Noriko\'s appearance in a kimono is so cute that it makes one\'s heart skip a beat.\n\nThis was also felt by Kudo Shinichi, who came by Mouri Kogoro\'s car. When he saw Noriko Amamiya, his heart skipped a beat, and he really shouldn\'t have come.\n\nSeeing Yumiya Noriko\'s well-behaved and sensible appearance, as a junior accompanying him, he felt that his heart was beating violently, and there was a big word on his head, but he boasted that the heart of a Sherlock Holmes disciple was calming him down, and he would pay attention to it. Focus on everyone present and analyze everyone\'s situation.\n\nI am getting into the habit of being a detective.\n\nMouri Kogoro also felt almost the same. Usually, he felt uncomfortable when he saw Noriko Amamiya, let alone now, and he mainly felt quite restrained, and his suit was a little out of place.\n\n\"Rich people...\"\n\nWhat are you mumbling about? Xiaolan glared at her father, then went with Kiko Yuanzi, complaining in a low voice that she was not asked to wear it together.\n\n​​'),
(412, 5, 33, 'Chapter 32: : Tennis Club', '\"Kiko...\"\n\nAfter a while, Maorilan also went to the changing room of the tennis court.\n\nSeeing the tennis suit that Amamiya Noriko was wearing, she knew it must be Sonoko\'s masterpiece.\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved at Xiaolan to show that she didn\'t care: \"I don\'t have any clothes, Sonoko borrowed them from me.\"\n\nXiaolan looked at Sonoko, who had also finished changing her clothes, and said angrily, \"Sonoko, how could you let Noriko really wear this outfit?\"\n\nSonoko ran over to help Amamiya Noriko tidy up the neckline, \"It\'s alright, Noriko is completely fine.\"\n\n\"How come it\'s alright, those boys will definitely keep staring at Noriko.\"\n\nXiaolan squatted down and helped Amamiya Noriko pull the hem of her clothes, but it was basically useless. Sonoko bought a slightly shorter one on purpose.\n\nXiaolan was distressed: \"Really, why don\'t Kiko wear school sports uniforms?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko sighed, Xiaolan is still gentle, but! For her, school uniforms are more shameful than tennis uniforms.\n\nAt least this is just a short skirt, not a miniskirt, and this tennis skirt actually looks very similar to a pleated skirt, the only difference is the material.\n\nSo Amamiya Noriko comforted: \"Xiao Lan is fine, I\'m good at tennis.\"\n\nSonoko on the side laughed: \"Oh hoho, in front of my tennis queen, Noriko dares to say that tennis is great!\"\n\nXiaolan said angrily, \"Sonoko, you can\'t bully Noriko, a layman, you are from the tennis club.\"\n\n\"It\'s okay, I\'ll have a try with Sonoko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko got up.\n\nSonoko is quite confident: \"I will let Noriko know the fun of tennis. Will Noriko help me with makeup next time I lose?\"\n\n  \"sure.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded.\n\nBecause Suzuki Sonoko has a really high level of tennis, she remembers a 30-0 match against Xiaolan in one episode, and Xiaolan was completely abused.\n\nIf it wasn\'t for Sonoko mentioning Kudo Shinichi, who was very resentful at that time, Xiaolan wouldn\'t be angry at max, and play a powerful tennis ball that Sonoko couldn\'t even react to.\n\nFurthermore, the school tennis club is relatively strict, and there are not many girls like the football club, and it is not the prince of tennis, so there will not be a situation where Noriko Amamiya goes to the football club and is treated as a treasure.\n\nSo entering the school tennis club requires an assessment. Since Sonoko can come in, it means that her technical level is not bad.\n\nXiaolan reminded: \"Kiko, don\'t force yourself.\"\n\nSonoko can still guarantee peace of mind: \"It\'s okay, I will take care not to hurt Noriko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the others in the tennis club. There were actually quite a few girls, and there were very few first-year girls. They were all senior sisters who were in the second grade or above, and all of them were in great shape.\n\nWhen several male members saw Noriko Amamiya and Maurilan here, their eyes immediately straightened.\n\nXiaolan\'s tennis clothes are normal, and she has a beautiful and gentle temperament. Noriko Amamiya\'s refreshing hairstyle with a ponytail is very rare, not to mention this very eye-catching tennis dress.\n\nSonoko had forgotten what her purpose was to invite Noriko to come. She couldn\'t wait to communicate with the tennis club members and asked them to play on a court.\n\nThe other tennis club members were also curiously watching from the side of the court.\n\nAnd a bunch of people from the football club arrived later, but they could only watch from outside the tennis court.\n\nThere are only four words in their hearts, and it is a worthwhile trip.\n\nThere are quite a few girls in tennis skirts, including Noriko Amamiya, Maurilan, and... Suzuki.\n\nMaurilan looked at these boys outside the tennis court strangely, because there were many wearing jerseys, and she immediately found Xinyi who mixed in.\n\nKudo Shinichi was stunned and smiled awkwardly, but it was not a loss anyway.\n\nThe match between Sonoko and Noriko also begins.\n\nSonoko asked Amamiya Noriko to serve, and Amamiya Noriko threw it at the serving point and served.\n\nSonoko was ready, and ran lightly to hit the ball back.\n\nBecause they can\'t play the stunts like Prince of Tennis, two people serve, catch, catch, catch...\n\nThe only thing that can be seen is that the faster the ball is served, the faster it is returned, and the two of them run faster to catch the ball.\n\nIt took half a day for the score to be close.\n\nSonoko took the lead for the time being.\n\nIn the football club, the amateurs watch the fun and the whole process, while in the tennis club, the amateurs watch the doorway.\n\nThey can see that Amamiya Noriko\'s footwork is getting more and more flexible, the movements are getting faster and faster, the stepping is getting more and more accurate, and the strength when receiving the ball has not weakened.\n\nSonoko was the first to be found in front of her. She began to struggle more and more to catch Noriko\'s ball. On the other hand, Amamiya Noriko just started to sweat a little, as if she had just started to warm up.\n\nAmamiya Noriko can only say that she refuses so many basic attribute points obtained by confessing, and she usually insists on exercising and fitness, and it is not in vain.\n\nHer skills may not be as good as the garden.\n\nBut her speed, reaction is faster, more accurate, and more powerful. She is still learning, and she will only get stronger and stronger.\n\nTired the tennis queen Sonoko.\n\nAfter her defeat, her tired feet were weak, and she was supported by Amamiya Noriko and Xiaolan.\n\n\"From now on... Noriko will be the queen of tennis...\"\n\n  \"I do not want.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head, she didn\'t have the queen form.\n\nAfter supporting Sonoko and sitting down, Amamiya Noriko discovered the football club members outside the stadium. She waved her hand and smiled embarrassedly. UU reading www.uukanshu.com\n\n\"Saved—\"\n\n\"Rainbow Palace is amazing!\"\n\n\"Amamiya, you are the best!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s head full of black lines was drowned out by the cheers from the side. Didn\'t you come because you were worried that Noriko Amamiya would be poached? Now she is more likely to be dug up!\n\nThinking about it, he also saw that the head of the school tennis club talked to Noriko Amamiya in the past.\n\nThe head of the tennis club is a third-year senior. She is mature, gentle, and temperamental. She has a good figure, especially her long legs, which are incomparable to Amamiya Noriko and the others.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the tennis skirt with white legs in front of her. The head of the tennis department was very beautiful and had a perfect temperament.\n\n\"Does Amamiya like to play tennis?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said honestly: \"Well... I don\'t know, it\'s my first time playing.\"\n\nThe head of tennis couldn\'t help covering his mouth in surprise, and then seriously held Kiko Amamiya\'s small hand: \"Sister likes Amamiya more, she was born for our tennis club! Join us!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, is this a confession?\n\n\"I\'m so sorry, senpai...I...\"\n\nBefore Amamiya Noriko waved her hand, before she could finish speaking, the football club\'s mourning rang out from outside the tennis court.\n\n\"No! Amamiya-chan—!\"\n\n\"Our football club can\'t live without you!!\"\n\n\"Don\'t abandon us!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shouted \"nice\" in her heart, and said with an embarrassed look on her face, \"So... I\'m sorry, senior.\"\n\n\"It\'s alright, there are still many opportunities, and Rain Palace can come to visit us often in the future.\"\n\nAfter speaking, the head of the tennis department turned to look at the group of football club members, and decided that none of the girls in the tennis department could have anything to do with these people.\n\n​​');
