(413, 5, 74, 'Chapter 73: : Incredible!', 'Seeing Ota-kun being dragged to the corner of the corridor by the girl carrying a chicken, Noriko Amamiya sincerely prayed for him.\n\nI hope it won\'t leave a psychological shadow, and I can confess to her a second time in the future.\n\nAs soon as I started school, I gained a little attribute point, which was a good start.\n\nAmamiya Noriko returned to the classroom and politely greeted a classmate whom she hadn\'t seen in the summer vacation.\n\n\"This has already been confessed once.\"\n\n\"These two opportunities have been used up.\"\n\n\"Oh? I haven\'t confessed yet.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko counted it carefully, but the students in the class haven\'t quite figured it out yet. After all, rabbits don\'t eat grass at the edge of the nest.\n\nNo hurry, take your time, the classmates don\'t need to hurry the most.\n\nThere is no concept of class division in Didan Middle School. It will be from the first grade to the third grade. When they are approaching graduation, it will be their last chance to see if they can hold back.\n\nAnd if you fail to confess, you may not meet again in the future, so you won\'t have much concern.\n\nAmamiya Noriko has a lot of experience, she was very busy when she graduated from elementary school.\n\n\"Niko, long time no see, let me help you.\"\n\nJust as Amamiya Noriko was about to put down her schoolbag, the person next to her took over her schoolbag and helped put it away.\n\n\"Student Yui, long time no see.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko sat down and said politely.\n\nYui Mizuhara is very snake-skinned, so she created an opportunity to take pictures of her secretly, and secretly tried to improve Noriko Amamiya\'s favorability to her.\n\nIn a basketball game, she went to a cameo cheerleading team inexplicably, and she made it up.\n\nIt seems that there was also a sneak shot of Noriko Amamiya jumping and cheering.\n\nThen I usually take good care of Noriko Amamiya, help her take out the trash, borrow notes, and often come to ask her how she is doing, will she feel uncomfortable?\n\nOnce Noriko Amamiya came to school with a fever, she was able to make a cup of antipyretic.\n\nShe often comes to eat with her at noon, and she is very keen to exchange food with herself. Sometimes she will bring soup for her to drink.\n\nIt can be said that with such comprehensive care, ordinary people have long since fallen.\n\nBut Noriko Amamiya, who is proficient in this way, didn\'t give her a chance and kept the heat under control.\n\nNo matter how much she sets fire to it, it won\'t work.\n\nAfter all, she has already been fished by Suwon Yuyi in troubled waters, so she will not be given a chance, and she will even be kicked out of the fish pond.\n\nSuwon Yui also knew that because the first time it seemed to go too far, it made Noriko angry, so Noriko has always been wary of herself.\n\nBut she believes that these are not problems. The pure and kind Noriko will one day be hugged by her and rubbed against her soft body.\n\nSuwon Yui returned to her seat, took a deep breath, memorized the fragrance of Noriko\'s body, lowered her head and raised a pen on the notebook to write.\n\nToday, Qing, I haven’t seen you for a long time. Noriko, who just started school, is also very cute and healthy. It’s worth watching us silently. From today onwards, you can see Noriko every day, and you don’t have to only see photos. .\n\nXiaolan Yuanzi and Shinichi came in through the door of the classroom, and after greeting the classmates, Yuanzi came over to Amamiya Noriko and said, \"Long time no see Noriko~\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko cooperated: \"We only met yesterday.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko was very satisfied with Noriko\'s response: \"When I think about Noriko, I can live a night like a year.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko laughed dumbly, who are you sonoko flirting with? I haven\'t shown my handsome side yet.\n\nShe lowered her head and said softly like a mosquito: \"I miss Yuanzi too.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko looked at Noriko\'s embarrassed, shy look, she couldn\'t help her heart surging, she covered her nose and raised her head.\n\nKiko is really, really heartwarming.\n\nKudo Shin, who was watching, opened his mouth and was shocked. Noriko, are you going to tease Sonoko?\n\nNormally, the king would occasionally want to have a few tricks with Hei Tie.\n\nOf course, the garden is made of black iron, and normally it is bronze.\n\nBut the garden that took off the headband, not to mention the king, just sticks there, not to mention the extraordinary master.\n\nReally, has she ever seen a girl who is more simple and unpretentious than the headband garden?\n\nI met with Xiaolan Yuanzi Shinichi yesterday, so I don’t need to talk about what I did during the summer vacation, but Xiaolan asked Noriko what plans for this semester?\n\nMainly the karate club. Although it was very happy to have Kiko to accompany her, it was obvious that Kiko\'s body was not suitable for the karate club. She felt that Kiko was here to accompany her.\n\nAlthough she was very moved, she hoped that Noriko could be in a relatively suitable club.\n\nDid Kiko Amamiya know that Xiaolan still has this level of consideration?\n\nAs expected of the gentle Lan Jiang, but she has not finished karate, so she is definitely not going to leave for the time being. As for the next club, let\'s take a look at the situation. First of all, she may go to the basketball club. She has already played well last semester. foundation.\n\n\"Well, it\'s alright, I also want to watch Xiaolan in karate, she\'s super handsome with flying kicks.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head and smiled at Xiaolan.\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s neck stiffened, what are you doing? What you want to do to Xiaolan, Xiaolan is impossible to confess to you!\n\nXiaolan responded with a smile. In that case, she would also take good care of Noriko in the Karate Department. It would be a good thing if she could give Noriko a proper workout.\n\nThe club\'s plan has yet to be decided, but Amamiya Noriko remembered her student union club member, and went to the Yilai Student Union after school.\n\nThe members of the associations are very hardworking. Every association has arrangements to go for an assessment. The assessment score of each association directly affects the level of the ministry\'s funds.\n\nIf you find that a certain society has no meaning to exist, you can also nominate the waste department to deal with it.\n\nTo a certain extent, Amamiya Noriko is the enemy of most of the protagonists who save the waste.\n\nHowever, this power is not very useful to Amamiya Noriko. She can mainly go to other clubs in an open and honest way to make everyone familiar with her.\n\nThen there are the exchange competitions between the sports department and other schools.\n\nShe can go to cheer on the sports department, supervise their training or something, and have another legitimate opportunity to capture.\n\nIt is the Outreach Department of the Student Union that connects these exchange competitions with other schools.\n\nAmamiya Noriko still comes to the External Relations Department quite often, because the exchange match with other schools is really a good opportunity, the more the better. For details, please refer to the friendly match between the basketball team and the basketball team of the other school last semester.\n\nHowever, when I came to the External Relations Department, I found that there were quite a few familiar people.\n\nDisciplinary committee member Karuta-senpai, cheerleader Aoi Motohashi, and head of the External Relations Department Hayakawa Haruka-senpai.\n\nThere is also Yui Mizuhara.\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who opened the door, was stunned for a while. Is there any relationship between these people?\n\nKaruta-senpai smiled kindly at Noriko Amamiya, Aoi Motohashi blinked, she really likes Noriko Amamiya, she really wanted to pull her into the cheerleader team and shine.\n\nAs for Yui Mizuhara, she smiled slightly, a little surprised, but she seemed to think the encounter with Noriko was a good one.\n\nThe Minister of External Relations, Haruka Hayakawa, sitting behind the desk is a very temperamental girl. After all, she is the Minister of External Relations, and she is quite good at dealing with people and communicating.\n\nSeeing it was Kiko Amamiya, her eyes flickered for a moment, and then she said with a smile, \"Is there any business for Kiko to come here? We just came to discuss the plan for this semester.\"\n\n  \"plan?\"\n\nAlthough Amamiya Noriko didn\'t let go of the moment when her eyes flickered, Wen Yan was still slightly attracted by the two characters of the plan.\n\nCan you tell me, in addition to your foreign affairs director, there is another member of the Disciplinary Committee, Karuta-senpai, a cheerleader, Aoi Motohashi, a first-year fisher in troubled waters, Yui Mizuhara, and none of the other members of the foreign affairs department. What girl group?\n\nCan we discuss a serious plan?\n\n\"Well, then let me also hear what Hayakawa-senpai\'s plan is?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko also sat down and listened to their plan.\n\nThere are no major highlights. It is mainly for friendly matches with other schools, and the arrangement of exchanges. For example, the External Liaison Department is responsible for liaising with other schools, cheering the cheerleaders, and the Discipline Committee maintains order. As the level of the exchange competition improves, it is best to raise it to a traditional level.\n\nThe beginning of the plan was also due to the basketball game last semester, which can be said to be very successful.\n\nDuring the game, the basketball level displayed by both sides far exceeded the normal level, and even a few good seedlings have been discovered by the district sports committee, and they are ready to cultivate basketball players who will become the peak of the future.\n\nHayakawa Haruka believes that this is because the level of the two sides in the competition has been improved, and more exchanges of this kind can be held.\n\nCurrently, there are tennis clubs, soccer clubs, baseball clubs, basketball clubs, archery clubs, cheerleading teams, etc. that have been pre-planned. The more the better.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it, and it seemed that all the sports departments were spared.\n\nIt\'s... it\'s great too, she\'s definitely there to cheer on every exchange game, and the task of inspiring everyone\'s little universe is left to her. Now everyone has two chances!\n\nAfter listening to the plan, Amamiya Noriko and the others watched, that\'s all? What does Yui Mizuhara do? Fishing in muddy waters?\n\nMizuhara Yui vaguely felt Noriko\'s resentment towards herself, and she couldn\'t help but reflect again, was the original operation correct? does it worth? Are you sorry?\n\n  No.\n\nNot at all, just because the soft \"I like it\" sounded beside my ears.\n\nMy heart melted.\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt that there seemed to be something they couldn\'t say in front of her, so she was very cooperative and didn\'t ask any more questions after listening to the plan, and left first.\n\nAfter she left, she went to the football club to get Shinichi Kudo out.\n\nHe went through the situation and said, \"That\'s it, can you figure it out in five minutes?\"\n\nKudo Shin looked at her expressionlessly.\n\nYou left the football club and still brought this with you?\n\nAmamiya Noriko was puzzled: \"I am a member of the society.\"\n\nThere is no explanation for this reason, Kudo Shin said directly: \"I can\'t reason it out, and I haven\'t seen the specific changes in their expressions or tone of voice when they talk to you, and I didn\'t see their reactions the first time you entered. , just relying on your oral recitation, it is difficult to determine the accuracy, and your subjective guess may be wrong.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at him suspiciously: \"That\'s it?\"\n\nKudo Shin dismissed: \"What\'s the strange point between them—\"\n\n\"Suwar Yui? I see, the problem is why Suwara Yui got into it.\"\n\nAfter Kudo Shinichi\'s suggestion, Amamiya Noriko reacted instantly. She had been wondering why Yui Suhara fished in troubled waters, but it didn\'t seem very strange, because it was Yui Mizuhara.\n\nKudo Shinichi wouldn\'t think it was normal for Yui Mizuhara to be there, because from Noriko Amamiya, he could see that the other three people needed to exist in that situation, and the plan was also reasonable.\n\nBut he wouldn\'t think it was normal for Suwon Yuyi to appear there.\n\nHowever, before he finished speaking, he didn\'t enjoy the fun of easily reasoning out clues and then explaining them to be worshipped, so he was cut off by Amamiya Noriko backhandedly.\n\nSeeing Amamiya Noriko turn around and trot away, Kudo Shin once made up his mind, next time he will say two words and let Amamiya Noriko cut his beard.\n\nBut at the same time, he pondered for a while, and reasoned carefully about Noriko Amamiya.\n\nHe doesn\'t know the cause of the process, but from the current results, the results are not a bad thing for Amamiya Noriko.\n\nBecause Karuta-senpai, Aoi Honhashi, and Haruka Hayakawa from the External Relations Department have a good attitude towards Noriko Amemiya, right?\n\nKudo Shinichi touched his chin, and he felt that it was not only good, but he seemed to take care of Amamiya Noriko more often. When Amamiya Noriko relayed to him, she could feel that she was instinctively reassuring to them. Just out of curiosity.\n\n\"Rare.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi really thinks it\'s rare, this time Amamiya Noriko is not on the way to let others confess. UU reading www.uukanshu.com\n\nAmamiya Noriko went back to the classroom, no matter what they were doing, she remembered something.\n\nShe went to the External Relations Department after school, and Suwon Yui was actually faster than her. She probably didn\'t pack anything, which means she was ready to pack her schoolbags before returning home.\n\nSo, is the phone here?\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head and saw the phone on Yui Suwon\'s desk.\n\n\"Well, I\'m sorry, I don\'t have the idea of ​​peeping at the privacy, I\'m here to eliminate the evidence.\"\n\nThe evidence of the crime is of course the recording made by Yui Suwon at the beginning. Noriko Amamiya has not made up her mind for a long time, compared to Yui Suwon who was still swimming in her own fish pond.\n\nBut she had already decided that it was time to kick Suwon Yui out of the fish pond, otherwise she felt that Suwon Yui would accidentally take incredible photos.\n\nPiracy is prohibited.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took out Suwon Yui’s phone, um, it’s a flip button phone, it doesn’t have a password, it’s relatively backward, this is why Amamiya Noriko doesn’t use a phone, because it’s too small to take pictures, the pixels are poor, the only good feature Just emails and chat rooms.\n\nShe flipped through it, and found an entry in the recording \"Kiko-chan likes it. MP3\"—delete!\n\nAfter neatly deleting it, Amamiya Noriko glanced at the chat room with a few red dots, clicked it, and removed the red dots.\n\nClick to open, there is only one chat room.\n\n【Kiko\'s sisters】\n\n\"...\"\n\nPoisonous, Amamiya Noriko opened her eyes and looked at it. Since it is her sister\'s chat room, she also has the right to watch it, right?\n\nAfter opening it and taking a look, Amamiya Noriko\'s face blushed.\n\nIncredible!\n\n​​'),
(414, 5, 29, 'Chapter 28: : I love you~', 'Kudo Shinichi is a person with correct judgment and a strong sense of justice and responsibility. He has no tolerance for criminal behavior, but he also puts his life first.\n\nAlthough life is not involved this time, he feels a great responsibility.\n\nSo the next day, I threw away all the things of yesterday, including Noriko Amamiya asking him to help, and the things he accidentally opened.\n\nIt was no surprise that Amamiya Noriko found out that he was not helping, generally speaking.\n\nI told Kudo Shinichi first, as long as it\'s not too much, no matter what, Kudo Shinichi won\'t make trouble even if he doesn\'t help.\n\nI went back to Yuanzi, but for now, I have to make up for the courses I missed in the past few days.\n\nAmamiya Noriko asked Suwon Yui, who should take good care of her, to borrow notes.\n\nThis student Yui Suwon is also a sports committee member. In the physical education class, she takes the initiative to explain to her and the physical education teacher that her health is not good, her physique is poor, and she cannot exercise vigorously, highlighting a weakness.\n\nLet Amamiya Noriko have the right to go to the health room to sleep in the gym class.\n\nThe problem is that a girl as delicate as her is more attractive to the way she works hard in gym class.\n\nYui Mizuhara lowered her chances of being confessed by ten percent.\n\n\"Notes? Of course you can, Noriko just call me Yui, Suwon-san sounds awkward.\"\n\nSuwon Yui took Amamiya Noriko\'s hand and said in an intimate and serious manner.\n\n\"Student Yui...\"\n\n\"Yi-Yi-, you don\'t need to add honorifics.\"\n\nYui Suwon taught Noriko Amamiya how to pronounce correctly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, you won, can you give me the notes quickly, or I\'ll find someone else.\n\n\"Yuyi!\"\n\nYui Mizuhara nodded in satisfaction and took out the note: \"Hmm, here, this is the language note. I remember that Kiko only needs this, right?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways, why did she remember my only imperfection so clearly.\n\nShe still thanked softly, \"Thank you, Yuyi.\"\n\n\"You\'re welcome.\" Yui Suwon said generously, and then said, \"Will you go to the cafe with me after school? I know the cakes from the family are delicious.\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, she just came to borrow a note, Jiang Taigong is fishing, please take the bait.\n\nShe also put away the fishing rod that had not been lured and had no hook, and made an appointment to go to the coffee shop in the afternoon.\n\nThen in the evening when the two came out of the cafe, she had another good sister.\n\nJust as fat people and thin people are often easy to become good buddies, they both have the same reasoning.\n\nAmong the girls, the heroic Suhara Yui is very fond of Amamiya Noriko, who is harmless to humans and animals. She is cute and has no possibility of threatening her, so she will naturally get close, just like hippos and toothpick birds.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was stunned from beginning to end.\n\nTo a certain extent, her harmless personality seems to be more effective for Yui Mizuhara than most boys.\n\nBut it didn\'t work. She took Yui Suwon as the object of her confession, but Suwon-san only wanted to be good sisters with her.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thinks about it carefully, and then she understands, does your brotherhood not only want to be your brother, but also want to fall in love with you?\n\nThe road to expand the business is a long way to go, and all of them are steep as the Huashan plank road.\n\nShe was thinking about it in her heart, it seemed that it would be better to catch a few more fish. The panic reaction of the boys when they looked at her was also quite interesting.\n\nYui Suwon looked lost after seeing Amemiya Noriko in the cafe, and asked, \"What is Kiko thinking?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko subconsciously said casually, \"I\'m wondering if anyone likes me.\"\n\nAfter she finished speaking, she felt that something was wrong, and she whispered in a calm voice, \"No one like me will like it, right?\"\n\nSuwon Yui\'s eyes softened long ago, she heard the words and gently hugged Noriko Amamiya in her arms: \"Why, I like Noriko, I\'m really sorry for not discovering Noriko\'s anxiety sooner!\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was embarrassed to refuse.\n\n\"But I refuse.\"\n\nRefusing to confess successfully, random points: Constitution +1.\n\nAmamiya Noriko immediately backhanded and added happily, \"I also like Yui, but that\'s not acceptable.\"\n\nSuwara Yui was rejected by Yui Amemiya before she had time to respond, and she was rescued by Noriko Amamiya. It can be seen that Noriko Amamiya won\'t recognize the superb level of the system after taking the points.\n\nSuwon Yui was stunned for a while~www.readwn.com~ Seeing that her liking was mistaken for that kind of liking by Noriko, her heart was stirred and she found that although her intention was conveyed, it seemed that the meaning was wrong, although she was rejected, But it doesn\'t seem to have been rejected, mysterious and mysterious.\n\nIt\'s hard to figure out.\n\n\"Does Noriko like me?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked and nodded softly: \"I like it~\"\n\nFor girls who contribute a little physique, you can get special rewards.\n\nYui Suwon seemed to be in the clouds, her whole body was light and fluttering, she couldn\'t help but press the play button, and the soft and glutinous voice of Noriko Amemiya came out from her phone: \"I like it~\"\n\n\"I like it~\"\n\n\"I like it~\"\n\nSuwon Yui looked down at Noriko, whose face was gradually turning crimson, and whispered, \"I like Noriko too.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko resisted the urge to grab the phone with the shadowless hand, and squeezed two words between her teeth: \"Delete...\"\n\nSuwon Yui thought she was aggrieved and was speechless and wanted to cry, so she quickly said, \"I won\'t let other people listen.\"\n\n  \"Really?\"\n\nSeeing Noriko\'s blushing face raised and her eyes looking straight at herself, Yui Suwon said seriously, \"Of course.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at her for a long time. Not far from the school, there were many students from Didan Middle School around. She turned her head and said, \"I\'m going home.\"\n\nSuwon Yui said thoughtfully: \"Be careful of the idiot, I\'ll take Noriko home.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wished she would beat a lunatic to vent her anger, and thinking of how she looked when she was listening to her recording in private, she thought that your behavior was even more lunatic than a lunatic.\n\nIn contrast, the simple boys in the school are much cuter.\n\nAt least open a fish pond to make up for this wounded heart.\n\n​​'),
