(417, 5, 70, 'Chapter 69: : 2.0', 'If you reject others a few times, you won\'t add any more attribute points.\n\nIt\'s not like she hasn\'t tried it, it\'s useless to let people tell you that it\'s useless. How could Sonoko add attribute points for the second time, and the system message that popped up suddenly made her realize.\n\n\"Ding! System upgrade 2.0 version 100%——\"\n\n  Oh?\n\nAmamiya Noriko had a bold idea.\n\nCan you catch the fish you have caught?\n\nCan you fish three times?\n\nAmamiya Noriko was still holding Sonoko\'s hand and gently squeezed her palm: \"Is Sonoko feeling better now?\"\n\n\"No, I still feel so scared, Kiko...\"\n\nWhen Sonoko heard this, she shook her head decisively, and then wanted to hug Noriko Amamiya, but she was restrained by the seat belt.\n\n\"Sit down obediently.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko touched Sonoko\'s head.\n\nSonoko felt Noriko\'s gentle touch and said seriously, \"If only I were a boy, I would definitely marry Noriko home.\"\n\n\"I\'m sorry but I can\'t, Sonoko is a girl.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko finished her refusal, but she didn\'t respond. It seemed that she still wouldn\'t give her a fish three times.\n\nBut it doesn\'t matter. Go back and do the football team first, and make sure you don\'t lose money. I believe there are still many people who are willing to try it for the second time.\n\nIt\'s like this, if you give up after a failed confession, is that your true love? Dirty! You are greedy for beauty, you are just trying to see if you can succeed!\n\nOf course, with your heart, Amamiya Noriko welcomes them to give it a try.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is ready to open up the permission of the second confession to give them hope again.\n\nChieda Riho was driving in front, glancing at the rear-view mirror from time to time, and it could be seen that Noriko\'s eyes flickered with hope.\n\nWhat are you expecting?\n\nAmamiya Noriko asked Chieda Riho to send Sonoko back to Suzuki\'s house before returning home. The trip to the water park was too short. After returning, Amamiya Noriko made a small plan for a second confession.\n\nAfter going back to school after the weekend, Noriko Amamiya went to the football club for a serious morning practice. Serious girls are the cutest.\n\nThe members who had already confessed began to think again.\n\nAmamiya is so cute, it\'s too bad to give up after only confessing once without success.\n\nAnd the first time Amamiya didn\'t completely reject it, maybe there is still a chance?\n\nIf this second confession is successful—\n\nEveryone in the football club was fervently planning a confession, and suddenly someone found out that the minister was not there.\n\n\"What about the minister?\"\n\n\"The Minister must still not be ready to fight with us. He obviously likes Amemiya very much.\"\n\n\"Touched.\" \"Tears.\"\n\n\"For this confession, you must bring the minister with you.\"\n\nWhen the football minister came back from outside the stadium, he heard the words and asked: \"What do you bring me?\"\n\n\"Of course I confessed to Amamiya-kun. Together, we will not forget the captain this time!\"\n\nThe football minister shook his head and encouraged them: \"No need, no need, you must do your best! I will watch you succeed!\"\n\n\"Minister!!\"\n\n\"The Minister is really touching!\"\n\n\"We will take the minister\'s share together!!\"\n\nThe minister looked at each of them excitedly and went to find Amamiya-san. He couldn\'t help feeling quite emotional, all his members were doing well.\n\nJust when I saw them come back after a while with a low expression, I couldn\'t help but feel... relieved.\n\nSure enough, it is not so easy for everyone to confess successfully.\n\nIt\'s not just that I confessed and was rejected.\n\nFeeling much better.\n\nThe minister used to comfort his team members: \"Don\'t give up, everyone, Amamiya is just young and doesn\'t understand the beauty of love. We have a long way to go, but one day we will succeed.\"\n\nWhen Amamiya Noriko came back and saw that they seemed to be holding an oath ceremony, everyone clenched their fists and shouted.\n\n\"I will definitely make Amamiya not refuse to confess!!!\"\n\nShe tilted her head: \"dream?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi felt the same way, but what frightened him even more was that Amamiya Noriko actually began to enjoy the second confession someone made to her.\n\nThe condition is getting worse.\n\nHe seemed to have seen the scene of Noriko Amamiya turning over the person she had rejected before to confess, and then rejecting it again, maybe not twice, but three or four times...\n\nThese people who have repeatedly confessed and been rejected are also old patients.\n\nThinking about it, he saw Noriko Amemiya walking over and asked, \"Is Shinichi contributing to me once?\"\n\n  \"I reject.\"\n\nShin Kudo refused calmly.\n\nNot to mention, the feeling of rejecting Amemiya Noriko is actually not bad.\n\nAmamiya Noriko rolled his eyes at him and looked at the members of the football club over there, her eyes gratifying.\n\nIt\'s time to leave the football club.\n\nEveryone in the football club is really gentle and energetic, and the atmosphere is so good that it makes people reluctant to leave.\n\nHowever, no one can confess to him anymore.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes fell on Kudo Shinichi again.\n\nShinichi Kudo turned his head to look elsewhere, should he leave the football club, and would it be dangerous to stay there?\n\nAmamiya Noriko submitted an application for departure the next day. The minister heard the bad news and felt angina. Could it be that Amamiya didn\'t like it after being confessed by too many people yesterday?\n\nAmamiya Noriko hurriedly shook her head gently, shaking her head and explaining: \"No, it\'s because my body is not suitable for sports clubs, I hope the minister can bring the football club better and better, everyone. They are all gentle people.\"\n\nThe minister understood that Amamiya didn\'t want her to have other thoughts and wanted to attribute the reasons to herself. While deeply moved, she felt that she should speak out for the entire football club.\n\n\"Amamiya, Minister I, must be the most gentle one in the football club, right?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave a thumbs up in her heart, your minister is still your minister after all, she raised a gentle and bright smile and said sweetly.\n\n\"Well, the Minister is really a good person.\"\n\nWhen the football minister heard the words, his heart softened, and he quickly waved his hand and said, \"Hey, this, this is not to be taken seriously, no matter what, I am humble, minister, I just have a gentle heart.\"\n\nWhile being modest, he giggled as he looked at Kiko Amamiya, with a delicate smile like a flower, a small face that was exquisite and delicate, and a soft smile that curved into crescent eyes...\n\nThe heart that was restless last week and calmed down after being rejected is now restless again.\n\nSuch a lovely Amamiya, do you really not confess for the third time? ! !\n\nThere are only three things to do, this time I will definitely do it. Amamiya has already been completely amused by me, and success is just around the corner! ! !\n\n\"Amamiya, I love you!!!\"\n\nThe simplest confession, the fullest heart, everything is in these five words! !\n\n\"I\'m sorry, Minister, but I still refuse. I don\'t have any idea of ​​falling in love yet.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko held back her smile and said apologetically.\n\n\"In the words of the minister, there are more people who are better than me...\"\n\nThe minister raised his hand: \"It\'s okay, Amamiya, you don\'t need to comfort me.\"\n\nHe smiled, it was impossible to give up, and after being rejected, Amamiya-san showed apologetic and worried consolation on his face. This kind of feeling will melt his heart...\n\nNext time, definitely.\n\nThe last hope of the football department is still going on!\n\nThe minister was considerate of Noriko Amamiya\'s physical condition, and agreed, but it felt unacceptable to disagree, because after they got together last week, Noriko Amamiya had a high fever for three days.\n\nI feel that keeping Amamiya in the football club is not good for her. As long as Noriko Amamiya is healthy, the football club will always be her home!\n\nAfter Noriko Amamiya left, the minister was alone for a moment, and saw Kudo Shinichi looking for him again.\n\n\"Kudou-san, what\'s wrong?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi said that he was ready to retire.\n\nHe had a feeling that he would soon be arranged by Noriko Amemiya, so he planned to run away first. No matter how the minister kept him, he would leave in order not to suffer from Noriko Amamiya\'s murderous hand.\n\nWhen the minister heard that he was about to retire, he hurriedly said, \"Why does Kudo-san want to retire? You are the future leader of the football club!\"\n\n\"It would be a pity to retire.\"\n\nAfter making up some random reasons, Kudo Shinichi\'s withdrawal from the department went smoothly. Next, what other department should be considered.\n\nThe minister failed to retain him, so he could only shake his head. Kudo Shinichi, his skills are indeed very good, but unfortunately, he plans to hand over the position of football minister to Kudo Shinichi in the future.\n\nIt\'s just that after a while, Kudo Shinichi came back and tore up his application for resignation.\n\nKudo Shinichi said calmly, \"I will stay in the football club forever.\"\n\nThe minister nodded blankly: \"What happened?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi has a complicated mood: \"I met Noriko Amamiya at the Karate club.\"\n\n\"The karate club?\"\n\nThe minister nodded, then got up and patted Kudo Shinichi on the shoulder: \"Kudo, the football club will be handed over to you. To be honest, I once had the heart to become the head of the karate club.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi glanced at him and said to the point: \"Noriko Amamiya will definitely reject you, and she is still a member of the society, so you have a better chance of being the head of the football department, right?\"\n\nThe minister nodded calmly and made sense: \"It seems that the football department still needs me.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t figure out when the minister would be beaten to death by his members.\n\nAfter Noriko Amamiya left the football club, the football club gradually returned to normal during the semester, and Kudo Shinichi was very pleased.\n\nAnd karate club, **** training ground.\n\nWhenever Noriko Amamiya was watching in a karate suit, everyone who practiced would be open to all.\n\nUnder such circumstances, Xiaolan began to quickly show her talent.\n\nBecause the head of karate also takes good care of Noriko Amamiya, she seldom asks her to compete or practice. It is good to have Noriko Amamiya on the side, and it can also inspire other members, which is perfect.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also learned the fighting skills of karate.\n\nThe first semester of middle school passed quickly in a busy time.\n\nMainly, everyone has two chances.\n\nIn Noriko Amamiya, all beings are equal, and everyone gives you the opportunity to confess twice. There is no way to do it. After the second confession is rejected, it is not 100% attribute points.\n\nAfter she tried it, the probability that she got it was 1 in 5, and only one of the five people added attribute points.\n\nAt first, she thought that the other party had no intentions, but in fact, it was useless to make the other party confess with full intentions several times.\n\n20% of those who refuse the second confession will have a probability of adding attribute points.\n\nConsidering that she only re-harvested the first time, the overall attribute points only increased by about 20%.\n\nIt\'s good after all, Amamiya Noriko is satisfied.\n\nShe really went to the karate club to learn something, Amamiya Noriko believes that it must be difficult to train a karate master like Xiaolan in the karate club of Didan Middle School.\n\nIt is indeed similar to what she thought. Everyone in the karate club is talented, and their strength and level are quite powerful.\n\nAs a member of the karate club, and then a member of the student union, she has watched the exchange competition with other middle schools, and also watched the karate club competition in the high school. She feels that her karate club is more powerful.\n\nAt the end of the semester, the club activities of the karate club naturally stopped during the summer vacation.\n\nSonoko ran over to the karate club to look for Ran and Noriko. She wanted to bring Kiko to her school tennis club from the beginning, but Amamiya Noriko came to Xiaolan considering that everyone in the tennis club already knew a lot. here.\n\n\"Is the Noriko family going to travel abroad again during the summer vacation?\"\n\nSonoko was in the changing room of the karate club, watching Amamiya Noriko and Xiaolan changing clothes, and asked curiously.\n\n\"Well, go to Hawaii.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko lowered her head to pull the zipper of her skirt and nodded.\n\nXiaolan and Yuanzi are both a little envious. Xiaolan plans to find a way to reconcile her father and mother during the summer vacation, while Yuanzi will visit many family members of the Suzuki family.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in her heart that I wasn\'t going on vacation, I was going to sign up for n training courses.\n\nBefore leaving, she went to sing a K with Xiaolan Yuanzi, Amamiya Noriko tried her best to stop her, but Kudo Shinichi was still taken by Xiaolan.\n\nFortunately, Kudo Shinichi has self-knowledge~www.readwn.com~ Otherwise, the K-room tragedy will happen.\n\nBut it was also the first time he knew that Amamiya Noriko sang was outrageously beautiful, with a voice like a lark, and the soft singing had a unique charm, and the feeling was indistinguishable from the original song.\n\nNow, he couldn\'t even open his mouth in front of Noriko Amamiya. Otherwise, Noriko Amamiya knew that he was obsessed, and felt that he would be ridiculed by Noriko Amamiya without any effort.\n\nOf course, Amamiya Noriko has long known that, rather than having the opportunity to mock Shinichi, she prefers Shinichi not to speak.\n\nBy the way, Chieda Riho was present, she was in charge of opening the room, and she could hear Noriko sing, but Amamiya Noriko could not sing at home.\n\nThe day after a few people sang K for the last time before the summer vacation, the Amamiya Noriko family packed up and got on the plane to go abroad early.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is worried that Gin will drop a bomb under her boss\'s company building again.\n\nGoing out in the world of Conan is risky.\n\nAlthough her life is basically not in danger, it is not good to suffer.\n\nBring the parachute anyway.\n\nAnd the seat should be close to the cockpit of the plane to avoid inexplicable robbers hijacking the plane. She can stand up for the first time to maintain world peace.\n\nIf the situation is really urgent, it should be enough for her to learn simple driving now. Maybe, probably, she will be punished.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned off the energy-saving mode anyway, ready to deal with all possible emergencies.\n\nIt\'s just that she glanced at her father and mother. Not long after she took off, Amamiya Emi was leaning on the shoulders of Amamiya Ludou and fell asleep.\n\nSeeing her father\'s gentle appearance, Amamiya Noriko rolled her eyes.\n\nChie Riho looked aside, turned her body sideways, and Noriko could also lean on her shoulder.\n\n​​');
