(418, 5, 77, 'Chapter 76: : Don\'t disappoint Amamiya\'s expectations.', '\"Twice...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi kept away from Amiya Noriko with a dark face, this person is poisonous.\n\nAmamiya Noriko chased after him: \"Tell me what project you participated in, I can go and cheer you on!\"\n\nKudo Shin has always refused.\n\nDid Noriko Amemiya cheer him on?\n\nAbsolutely ineffective, but his stupid opponents, probably because Noriko Amamiya was watching and cheering, became as powerful as how much adrenaline they played.\n\nHe has seen it through.\n\nSeeing that Kudo Shinichi has entered the time of a sage and is immune to all poisons, Amamiya Noriko pouted and went to find Xiaolan and Sonoko to play.\n\nAs for the school sports events, she also participated in the long jump and high jump.\n\nDon\'t give other people a chance to take a second look, end the game in an instant, win two gold medals and continue to be weak and cute.\n\nShe is a humble person, she just likes to be confessed by others, forget about things that are too showy.\n\nOnly by being an approachable person can others have the courage to confess.\n\nNow it is very difficult for her to let others confess. The children in junior high school do not have the courage to try if they fail to confess. They only confess when they think that their confession will be successful.\n\nAmamiya Noriko has to spend a lot of time on the inspiration and courage aura.\n\nIf she had put herself in a weaker position at the beginning, the fish pond would have doubled by now.\n\nThe young lady of the Amamiya family also discourages many people. Noriko Amamiya herself did not publicize this at all.\n\nAnd Amamiya\'s surname is not a surname that can be seen casually on the street.\n\nThese are all things that can\'t be helped. Let her pretend to be poor... Actually, she is really not good at it.\n\nThe school sports meeting.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was dressed in sports clothes, wearing a slightly wider sports jacket to cover the man,