Kiko shouldn\'t be reluctant. Even if you know that your motor nerves are good, it\'s not okay to force your body like this.\"\n\nSonoko also asked Noriko to rely on herself, and the two took Noriko aside to rest.\n\nThe onlookers were a little relieved. Was Amamiya still in good motor nerves? It\'s just that the body is too weak.\n\n\"Amamiya, who managed to win two gold medals by himself, is so cute.\"\n\n\"It\'s so distressing!\"\n\n\"Amamiya who wants to prove himself is awesome.\"\n\n\"If you let Noriko in my arms, you can get better faster, right?\"\n\nAll the boys turned their heads to look at the person who spoke last, who seemed to be a senior senior sister, and only a girl who said this sentence would not be beaten to death.\n\nI don\'t know why recently, but there seem to be a lot of senpai like this.\n\nVery robbed of their presence.\n\nObviously they are the ones who love Amamiya the most! ! !\n\nAmamiya Noriko went to the side to rest, mainly to avoid direct ultraviolet rays. Every extra minute of exposure to the sun is at risk of darkening by one degree.\n\nThere are Osaka Black Chicken and Jinggoku Ma in the front, and Ota-san in the back. Black is terrible, and it will cancel out her cuteness exponentially.\n\nKudo Shinichi also came over to see Amamiya Noriko halfway through. He also saw Amamiya Noriko’s performance just now. He was still a human being, which was more in line with Amamiya Noriko’s hidden strength, although he didn’t know why it suddenly happened this time. Expose.\n\nUsually, Amamiya Noriko hides too many times. He thinks that Amamiya Noriko should not sign up for any projects, but cheers and cheers in the audience, so that others will be fascinated by her and break through their own limits. .\n\nHowever, it is clear that Amamiya Noriko herself doesn\'t seem to be worried~www.readwn.com~ He doesn\'t need to worry too much.\n\nInstead, he should worry about what to do with his sports.\n\nHe just came over to take a look, and Kiko Amamiya didn\'t notice anymore, and smiled gently at him. With this smile, Kudo Shinichi felt that he had gone a little further.\n\nKudo Shinichi went, the team competition is relatively advanced, and starting from the junior year, his 4x100-meter relay will arrive immediately.\n\nKudo Shinichi took a deep breath as he stood in his last position.\n\nTurning his head and looking around, he saw no sign of Noriko Amamiya among the cheering and cheering audience.\n\nIt seems that Amamiya Noriko is not planning to do anything?\n\nNo, no, Kudo Shinichi immediately denied the idea, even if Noriko Amamiya did bad things, it was impossible for him to do nothing.\n\n  This is for sure.\n\nHe carefully combed it, what was unusual about today\'s Amamiya Noriko, what was strange, what was something he didn\'t notice.\n\nHe reasoned in his mind, and at the same time he was looking around, maybe Noriko Amamiya would not appear until the last moment, which was also in line with her operation.\n\nHowever, it doesn\'t seem to have appeared in the end, but the third stick seems to be coming soon.\n\nKudo Shinichi took a deep breath, lowered his body slightly, and stretched his hand back to take the baton.\n\nBefore that, he looked back and visually measured the distance between the third classmate and him.\n\nSo close, so close that the baton was about to be stuffed into his mouth.\n\nThe third classmate handed the baton to him, and shouted with all his strength as if he was about to collapse, \"Don\'t let down Amamiya\'s expectations—!!!\"\n\nWhat the **** did you do, Noriko Amamiya?\n\n​​'),
(419, 5, 41, 'Chapter 40: : Kudo Shin 1 Discovery', '\"Morning Amemiya, are you free in the afternoon? Come and play in our tennis club?\"\n\n\"Good morning, sorry, it shouldn\'t work.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko trotted and waved in response to the senior from the tennis club.\n\nNot long ago, I went to the tennis club to find Yuanzi and Xiaolan to play ball. If I went so soon, the people in the football club would cry with her and beg him not to leave.\n\nJust like some children, can you be more mature and come to confess to yourself?\n\nAmamiya Noriko still thinks that people should have self-confidence. Maybe what you like will also like you, just waiting for your confession. This kind of thing is completely possible!\n\nAs for whether to agree or reject, Amamiya Noriko: Does it matter?\n\nAmamiya Noriko arrived in the classroom, and while greeting each other with her classmates, she glanced at Kudo Shinichi curiously.\n\nHe is actually burying his head in writing and drawing, what are you doing?\n\nJust ask the information dealer Suzuki Sonoko about this kind of thing.\n\nYuanzi complained: \"He is researching the case, it seems that he asked Xiaolan\'s father about the cases he encountered when he was still in the Metropolitan Police Department. Really, Xinyi likes these, can you talk to Xiaolan? There\'s some progress.\"\n\n  \"Uh-huh.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded and accompanied Sonoko to denounce Shinichi.\n\nKudo Shin glanced at them, the detective\'s hearing was very keen.\n\nHowever, he did get a case that felt a little problematic from the chat with Kogoro Mouri.\n\nIt was also the case of the escalator in the shopping mall that Noriko Amamiya talked to him before.\n\nThis case happened to police officer Mumu and Kogoro Mouri by chance. They talked while chatting, but Kogoro Mouri was not there at the time of the case.\n\nOfficer Mumu was mainly very depressed. An incident happened nearby. He rushed over to check the scene carefully, but found that the deceased died simply because he accidentally fell off the escalator.\n\nAlthough it is a sad fact.\n\nMouri Kogoro frowned, feeling that this matter is not simple.\n\n\"There must have been a beautiful woman who caught his attention at that time.\"\n\nOfficer Mumu\'s head was covered in black lines, \"Do you think everyone is the same as you?\"\n\n  \"Hahaha…\"\n\nMouri Kogoro laughed and scratched his head.\n\nHowever, Officer Mumu remembered the Amamiya Noriko he met that day, nodded and said, \"Speaking of which, the lady of the Amamiya family was there that day.\"\n\nWhen Maori Kogoro heard the words, he immediately waved his hands with little interest: \"Although that kid is a beauty, right?\"\n\nIn the past, it was good to say that after he became a detective, he was often despised by Noriko Amamiya, who came to play at Xiaolan\'s house.\n\nBeing despised by such a brat took a huge blow to his self-esteem. Xiaolan also warned him that Noriko was not in good health and was not allowed to smoke in front of him, and at the same time ordered him to clean up the house.\n\nSo where there is Noriko Amamiya, he can\'t smoke, drink and throw away the cans, there can\'t be ashtrays in the ashtray, and there can\'t be **** in the trash can.\n\n  too painful.\n\nSo no matter how good-looking Amamiya Noriko is, she is immune, just like Concubine Eri.\n\nThis is also the thing that Kogoro Mori and Shinichi Kudo, who he also hates very much, complain the most.\n\nKudo Shinichi can understand his feelings a little.\n\nAfter all, he still faced Amamiya Noriko all day at school.\n\nIn the escalator case, he started from the simplest way of thinking, whether there was anything unusual during that person\'s accident.\n\nWithout understanding this, there is no way to bring in the possibility of homicide rather than accident.\n\nKudo Shinichi went to investigate after the club activities a few days ago, and finally found a problem.\n\nThe deceased was single and not wealthy, but after he went to the mall to ask, a high-end men\'s suit store received him.\n\nAnd the clerk told him that the gentleman had suddenly become rich recently, and his behavior was quite vulgar but very rich.\n\nHugely rich.\n\nThis is what the clerk who was bribed by Kudo Shinichi clerk said.\n\nToo real.\n\nSo Kudo Shinichi can assume that UU reading www.uukanshu. com The deceased has recently become rich through some channel, and someone has been eyeing the money, or someone has offended on the way to become rich.\n\nAfter further investigation, he found that the deceased did not seem to have a serious job at first, and often hung out in places such as bars and dance halls.\n\nIt was a bit difficult for him to enter that red area.\n\nOn the first day of the first year, she still seemed relatively immature, and she was easily stopped.\n\nAfter investigating this, Shinichi Kudo stopped temporarily, and could only go slowly in other directions, so he was sorting out the clues he got.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Sonoko and Xiaolan who joined later chatted for a while, and saw that Kudo Shinichi was still seriously scribbling over there, looking like he was thinking seriously.\n\nShe could only narrow her eyes a little, and saw a little bit of Kudo Shinichi\'s content.\n\nSo physique is a good point. In all aspects, her eyesight is very good.\n\nSeeing Kudo Shinichi\'s simple drawing of a model of an elongated escalator, she knew what was going on.\n\n\"Do I have a chance to help Gin fix the tail?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pondered, for the sake of the signature, and if the current Kudo Shinichi came into contact with the winery, there would be an unpredictable chemical reaction.\n\nSimply put, it will explode.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, if Kudo Shinichi went to be slapped by Gin now...\n\nNow, there is no APTX-4869 for Kudo Shinichi.\n\n\"It\'s my turn to perform.\"\n\nAfter school, Amamiya Noriko went to the club to ask for a leave and left school alone.\n\nKudo Shinichi watched the figure of Amamiya Noriko leaving the school from the teaching building, his eyes were quite confident.\n\n\"Sure enough, you know what happened at the mall. Although you don\'t want me to check, it\'s impossible.\"\n\n​​'),
(420, 5, 87, 'Chapter 86: : Who is this man?', 'The car stopped at the entrance of the building, and Chieda Riho, who was wearing a manly dress with her hair up and her hair up, went to the back of Noriko Amamiya to open the door. One hand gently held up the small hand that Amamiya Noriko was holding.\n\n  \"specialized.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko moved her lips with a smile without changing her face.\n\nChieda Riho smiled and hooked the corners of her mouth. She did feel a little weird. She and Amamiya Noriko didn\'t know who they were, but now they\'re all serious.\n\nEveryone is an actor.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is wearing a night starry sky-colored suspender dress. A layer of black gauze is dotted with sparse and evenly distributed sequins. It looks as beautiful as the stars on a summer night.\n\nIn essence, it is similar to the dress she usually wears, but in terms of details, it is more rigorous, delicate, elegant and artistic.\n\nThe shoes are sandals, of course not the kind that cost five yuan a pair. The bright black leather belt is made of genuine leather, and the small pendant water droplets on the outer ankles refract the light into a colorful halo.\n\nAt least her mother, Amamiya Eimi\'s aesthetic is very online, and she didn\'t get high heels for her. The heels are just a little higher, so it doesn\'t affect anything.\n\nAmamiya Noriko arrived early to meet Sonoko. Amamiya Ludou and Amamiya Emi also received invitations, but they didn\'t come so soon.\n\nThe person in charge of welcoming guests at the Suzuki family\'s hall knew that Amamiya Noriko was a friend of his young lady, and he did not check too much. After receiving the invitation, he let Amamiya Noriko and Chieda Riho go in.\n\nThe main one is the eldest young lady of the Amamiya family. She has a distinguished status, is slender and cute. How can there be a threat? The other is obviously a personal attendant. The Amamiya family will definitely not let dangerous people protect their young lady.\n\n\"You all have to check carefully next. There is no room for mistakes in our Suzuki chaebol banquet, and not a single dangerous person is allowed in!\"\n\n  \"Yes!\"\n\n  \"Yes, Not Bad.\"\n\nListening to the imposing responses of the security guards, the person in charge nodded with satisfaction. This spirit was indeed hired by the consortium at a high cost.\n\nWhat kind of thieves, thieves and robbers, staring at their gems, there is only one fate, that is, they are caught, ask the strongest lawyer, and sentence them to life imprisonment!\n\nAmamiya Noriko had already taken the elevator to the top floor. She also paid attention to it. There are five elevators in total, two on the left and right, and a sightseeing elevator in the middle. You can see a good scenery through the glass, and at the same time feel The feeling of rising heights.\n\nThis is a VIP elevator, and most people can\'t get on it.\n\nOf course Noriko Amamiya will do it.\n\nOnly the two of them were in the elevator, Chieda Riho said in a soft voice, \"Miss, with all due respect, are you going to do something bad? This is a banquet at your friend\'s house?\"\n\n\"How come, Sister Qianzhi, do you look like I\'m going to do something bad when I dress so beautifully?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said angrily.\n\nChieda Riho nodded more and more affirmatively: \"Yes.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head slightly, her reserved image still showing a small smile: \"What about the trust between people?\"\n\nChieda Riho moved her neck, forget it, you\'re cute, just be happy.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her eyes to the front of the surrounding blocks that she could gradually see as the elevator ascended. Due to her constitution, her eyesight was completely full. When she stared attentively, her pupils responded, not to mention the telescope, and her normal vision was 1.3. Times can still play out.\n\nSo she saw a nice car, a black Porsche 356A.\n\nTo be fair, gin is good at blasting, but blasting buildings shouldn\'t be a hobby.\n\nYou can let go of this young mansion that just had its capping ceremony.\n\nBut seeing that the black Porsche didn\'t park under the building, or downstairs across the road, Amamiya Noriko guessed that it might be a passing gin, don\'t be too nervous.\n\nA little episode of looking at the scenery in the elevator, seeing the Porsche drive away without stopping, it shouldn\'t be a big problem.\n\nFinally reached the top floor, the sixty-sixth floor.\n\nAmamiya Noriko lifted her legs out of the elevator and glanced at the arrangement on the top floor.\n\nThere is no special situation. Most of the space on the whole floor is not separated. At first glance, the line of sight will be quite wide. Therefore, there are several huge weighing columns, which are decorated and painted quite elegantly, and the dark red of the carpet. phase contrast.\n\nA table of seats, all the seats on one side are facing the chairperson\'s platform. At present, nothing can be seen when the curtain falls.\n\nHowever, when the gems were exhibited at the beginning, the gem showcase that was now placed under the host would be raised to the host, and then the curtain would be lifted, allowing everyone to appreciate the precious gems of the Suzuki consortium.\n\nBelow the host desk on this floor is the sixty-fifth floor. There are no rooms, and the whole is a vault-like design. No one can invade it, so the Suzuki Foundation is very relieved that it is only possible during exhibitions. It will be stolen, but with the eyes of so many people watching it during the exhibition, if something happens, they can immediately find it.\n\nThis is what the intelligence dealer Suzuki Sonoko told her. She doesn\'t know more details. Of course, these security arrangements do not need to concern her, the second lady.\n\nAfter reading the layout of the venue, Noriko Amamiya looked at the people. Because she arrived early, it hadn\'t even started yet. There were only a few guests, most of whom were waiters, who were cleaning or making the final arrangements.\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced briefly, then took a serious look.\n\nSure enough, the waiter with wheat-colored skin and pale blond hair is Toko, right?\n\nDown Valley Zero, Amuro Toru, Bourbon.\n\nTou Zi... The emperor of part-time work, why do you put this part-time job on hold again? How did you do it?\n\nAlthough it feels like fate, things have become more complicated. She just wants to keep it simple, not stealing her heart this time, just stealing something else.\n\nChieda Riho followed him out of the elevator. Behind Noriko, she first glanced at the situation on the top floor with a scrutinizing gaze, and after seeing where Noriko was looking, she followed.\n\nShe didn\'t find anything unusual, and she wouldn\'t think there was anything strange about Amuro.\n\nSometimes some foreign bodyguards are quite normal, at least on the surface, at least Toru Amuro should be a foreign bodyguard arranged by the Suzuki consortium.\n\n\"Sister Qianzhi, come this way.\"\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko took her hand and seemed to avoid the man\'s vision, which made her have to care a bit.\n\nWho is this man?\n\nWhen did Kiko from her family know such a man?\n\n​​'),
(421, 5, 44, ': Chapter 43: Kudo Shin 1: Cancer', 'Not to mention that Jinjiu went to the air, Amamiya Noriko was safely brought to the door by the police uncle all the way.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who happened to be in front of her house, couldn\'t help but say, \"Have you finally committed a crime?\"\n\nThe police patted his head, \"How could such a cute little girl commit a crime, she is lost.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s face darkened, you still say I committed a crime.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at Noriko Amamiya, so do you still have this kind of attribute?\n\nThe police left after exhorting him. Shin Kudo looked sideways, \"Where\'s my notebook?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said aggrieved: \"It was taken away by someone else.\"\n\nUpon hearing this, Kudo Shinichi asked, \"Is there someone who looks a bit like me?\"\n\n\"Well, did you change your hairstyle to rob me?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi rolled her eyes at her. The question of who that person is still needs to be studied, but.\n\n\"You still committed a crime, stealing.\"\n\n\"What are you talking about, do I commit a crime? I only make people want to commit a crime, and stealing things only steals their hearts.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko seriously pointed out his mistake.\n\n\"Be careful, be humble, not everyone will be confused by your appearance.\"\n\n\"Who is immune?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked, her eyes widened so that Kudo Shinichi could clearly see her amber pupils as mysterious as agate, crystal clear.\n\nIt was as if I saw Noriko Amamiya\'s pure heart like a clear spring in the desert, reflecting the pure sky clearly.\n\nSometimes eyes can speak.\n\nKudo Shinichi smiled confidently: \"I\'ll be immune, it\'s impossible for me to be deceived by your appearance.\"\n\n\"Straight man, straight enough...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave a thumbs up.\n\nShinichi Kudo rolled his eyes and said something in a mess: \"Don\'t talk about this, did you go over there with my notebook?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head very obediently: \"No.\"\n\n\"You know what I didn\'t say?\"\n\n\"Tsk.\"\n\n\"Stupid your lips, is that where you can go? What are you going to do if you are sold?\"\n\n\"Let them count the money for me?\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko apologized, \"I\'m sorry, I know Shinichi is worried about me, but when talking to Shinichi, his mouth has its own thoughts.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi has a dark face, if Noriko Amamiya is like this to others, it\'s fine, but this phenomenon is only for him, it\'s a disease!\n\n\"It has to be changed!\"\n\n  \"Ah ha ha…\"\n\nWhen Kudo Shin saw Noriko Amamiya\'s smile, it was obvious that he knew he was wrong.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also believes in Kudo Shinichi, and her true nature is exposed. After all, it is very tiring to pretend to be in front of Kudo Shinichi every day. His detective power is max, and even a little unreasonable small flaw may be pulled by him and turn the whole situation upside down. turn.\n\nIn a thousand episodes, how many murderers have suffered this kind of murder.\n\nTherefore, Kudo Shinichi was honored to experience the real Noriko Amamiya.\n\nIf he had known that he would look like this, he would probably have long ago said \"Ah Lie Lie\" and pretended that he didn\'t understand Noriko Amemiya at all.\n\nIn this way, Amamiya Noriko won\'t at least put him in a separate fish pond like he is now. This fish pond is as wide as the sea.\n\nIt\'s full of the hidden side of Akiko Amamiya...\n\nDark as abyss.\n\n\"Speaking of business, do you know the truth about the escalator case? And you even took the notebook in which I recorded the clues. What do you think—\"\n\n  \"Want sleep…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko yawned, looked wearily at Kudo Shinichi, rubbed the sleepy tears from the corners of her eyes, and looked at him stubbornly.\n\nKudo Shinichi had nothing to say: \"...Okay, you won.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled triumphantly, and then asked, \"Do you want me to take you home? It\'s dangerous for a boy to walk on the street alone at night.\"\n\nKudo Shin turned around and left.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was right, Kudo Shinichi came to her house to find her because she didn\'t know where she went.\n\nThe main reason was that the boy in the Hongfan district made him feel inexplicable, and at the same time he couldn\'t see Noriko Amemiya, so if he was afraid of losing her, Xiaolan really didn\'t know how sad he was when he looked back.\n\nFortunately, although he was lost, he was just lost, but Amamiya Noriko would still get lost, and he almost couldn\'t hold back his laughter just now.\n\nAs for this case.\n\nKudo Shinichi pondered while walking on the road, and put it on hold for the time being.\n\nHe has roughly delineated the three directions of Amamiya Noriko, the boy who claimed to be Kuroba Kuito, and the real murderer of the escalator case.\n\nBut things seemed to be a little more complicated than he imagined, UU reading www.uukanshu.com Amamiya Noriko was preventing him from contacting him inside and out.\n\nAlthough there is a nasty taste of refusing other people\'s confessions, this person is very kind to his own people, Xiaolan and Yuanzi, and his special treatment...\n\nFor Noriko Amamiya\'s sake, and because things were too complicated, the famous detective put things down for the time being.\n\nEarly the next morning, Shinichi Kudo found Noriko Amamiya who was playing football on the football field.\n\nRarely, She Bao was actually allowed to play football.\n\nThen he was out of breath after running a few steps. He was taken care of by other football club members and let the water go, and kicked the football into the goal.\n\nThe goalkeeper worked very hard, tried his best, tried his best to avoid the football, and was ready to make a leap at any time to actually help Noriko Amamiya put the ball into his own goal.\n\nIt\'s just that Amamiya Noriko didn\'t use him either. She pretended to be weak, and she kicked the football straight into the goal with a fluttering kick.\n\nThe members of the football club let out a cheer, congratulating Noriko Amemiya for her good start!\n\nBoth teams are, especially the goalkeeper.\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t take it any longer, it was too dark. These are not football players, they are actors.\n\nUnder Amamiya Noriko\'s voice, \"I\'m so tired, I\'m going to rest for a while, cheer up\", the two teams in the football club who were cheering for Amamiya Noriko\'s goal collided violently in an instant.\n\n\"Amamiya-san is waiting for me to score!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi said to Amamiya Noriko early, and then suggested, \"You\'re almost a disaster for the football club. Have you considered other clubs?\"\n\nHe felt that Amamiya Noriko was not suitable for this kind of team sports club, it was too cancerous.\n\n\"Um... other societies?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked.\n\n​​'),
(422, 5, 54, 'Chapter 53: : Sister Shiho', '\"Noriko really scared me. He suddenly sent a message calling for help, and Zhuxingdai found a bad guy who said he had kidnapped you. What happened?\"\n\nMiyano Akemi looked at Amamiya Noriko up and down with concern, and asked if she didn\'t see anything wrong.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded: \"I was kidnapped, but the police brother rescued me and has already caught the bad guy.\"\n\nAs a matter of fact, Jiang Gu Ling is a police officer from the Ministry of Public Security.\n\n  \"Oh?\"\n\nAkai Shuichi was slightly surprised. He had fought against that person before, and he said that his strength and quality were quite qualified, but his skills were insufficient, and he was restrained to death by his Jeet Kune Do.\n\nAs far as fighting is concerned, ordinary police officers in the criminal department are not necessarily the opponents of that person.\n\nIt\'s not easy for the police to catch the other party so quickly.\n\nOf course Tou Zi is not simple, but this time the main thing is that his gun is not simple. He is rich and self-willed, and he just added a silencer.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at Shuuichi Akai, it turns out that guy bumped into you too, no wonder he looked a little injured, was he beaten?\n\nIt\'s miserable.\n\nAs soon as Akai Hidey saw her looking at him, she nodded to her, Amamiya Noriko blinked, although there was nothing, it was okay to seem to have a tacit understanding of the password.\n\nAmamiya Noriko continued to briefly talk to Miyano Akimi about the situation. She was innocent anyway, but she was kidnapped just by looking at the scenery with binoculars.\n\nIt sounds a little familiar.\n\nAfter speaking for a while, a calm voice rang from the side.\n\n\"Sister, are you all right?\"\n\nAkemi Miyano turned her head and nodded to her sister, then put her two hands on Amamiya Noriko\'s shoulders and pushed her in front of her, \"Kiko, this is my sister Shiho, this is Amamiya Noriko, I met him outside. I wanted to introduce it when I was young, but Noriko ran too fast.\"\n\n  \"Uh…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was suddenly pushed in front of Miyano Shiho, looking at Miyano Shiho, who was only 13 years old. The later Ai-chan is very cute. When he has no expression, he is quite cold. Although he is small, he is already a little adult. temperament.\n\nWhen you meet Shiho Miyano, there will be a feeling that you have been analyzed by her.\n\nA bit similar is Kudo Shinichi. When Kudo Shinichi sees a new character, he will carefully observe each other\'s habits, hobbies, and some subconscious little actions, so he can always find a lot of points that the police didn\'t notice all of a sudden.\n\nBesides, he usually arrives at the crime scene before the police, after all, the crime scene is next to him.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was stared at by Miyano Shiho and suddenly didn\'t know how to say hello.\n\nTo say that Miyano Shiho is older now, he is only 13 years old, only 2 years older than her, not to the level of Miyano Shiho who is 17 years old, but not as young as Xiao Ai, he only went to elementary school when he became Haibara Ai. Grade, she is now in the first year.\n\nMiyano Akimi, who pushed Amamiya Noriko to Miyano Shiho, laughed and said, \"What\'s wrong? Don\'t you really want to meet Shiho? Don\'t know what to do after meeting?\"\n\nShe always wanted Shiho to be friends with her peers, and it was too lonely for her sister to keep doing those scientific experiments.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is simply the best choice. She has a cute and simple personality, kind-hearted, and considers other people. At the same time, she is also lively as a child. It is best to be a good friend of Shiho.\n\nIt\'s just that Kiko seems a little helpless when she sees Shiho. Although she\'s cute, Miyano Akimi thinks that her sister\'s appearance is too serious. Noriko will be scared.\n\nMiyano Shiho was simply looking at Noriko Amamiya.\n\nIn general, I am a little cuter than the photos my sister showed her