mei\'s sister might indeed make girls excited, right?\n\nAnyway, today has already dropped to zero +1, Miyano Shiho +1, Amamiya Noriko happily went shopping with Miyano Shiho.\n\nAlthough Miyano Shiho is only 13 years old, he is still very active when shopping, and it is mainly in some fashion stores, clothes, shoes, bags, and also in some stores to look at lipstick, so he does not look like a 13-year-old. girl.\n\nAmamiya Noriko has been holding hands by Miyano Shiho all the time. When Shiho looked at the lipstick, she also stood aside and didn\'t go too far.\n\nShe picked up a DHC olive lip balm and looked at it. This one is quite famous. It has many exports. The price is close to the people. The lipstick tube removed is so ugly.\n\nSeeing that Amamiya Noriko had taken this, Miyano Shiho picked up the trial pack on the side and pulled off the cap to show Amamiya Noriko the lipstick tube, \"This is too ugly, it\'s not good.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes lit up, she nodded her head, and so did I.\n\nThe two of them were looking at lipstick, while Akemi Miyano and Shuichi Akai were looking at lipstick. Akemi Miyano looked at the two children and said, \"They seem to be very happy.\"\n\nAkai Hide nodded and picked up a pink lipstick: \"Do you like this?\"\n\nMiyano Akimi watched for a while, then smiled and shook her head gently. Why don\'t you go and choose with those two children?\n\n​​'),
(423, 5, 50, 'Chapter 49: :too difficult', 'The top floor of the mall.\n\nThe Cuphu shopping mall building has only five floors in total, and the sixth floor is the rooftop.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is now locked in the stair compartment on the rooftop.\n\nBecause she was very cooperative and seemed harmless to humans and animals, Amamiya Noriko was just locked here, and then the camouflage man left, ignoring the delicate little girl at all.\n\nBut before she left, she took her phone away, and she was planning to use it for something. It was obvious that she was going to go fishing for Jianggu Ling.\n\nAmamiya Noriko understands it too well.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned around in the small cubicle, putting some sundries, shelves and pallets, etc. The light in the cubicle came from a small window close to the ceiling, and Amamiya Noriko drilled into it. It\'s not as narrow as it used to be, and it can\'t be switched on and off.\n\nTherefore, the whole compartment is quite stuffy, and it depends on the crack of the door for a little ventilation.\n\nShe cooperated for a while and then didn\'t want to stay, she was suffocated, and she was worried about the safety of her and Tou Zi\'s photo.\n\nReaching out and grabbing the door handle, it was locked from the outside, and her white, weak and slender arms pressed down.\n\n\"Crack—\"\n\nThe door handle held on for a while, unable to bear her favor, and broke directly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a look at the two thick doorknobs, so she could not use such delicate and inferior doorknobs, how could she open the door like this?\n\n...\n\nThe first floor of the mall.\n\nKyogu Ling stood at the entrance of the shopping mall with a cold face, holding Noriko Amemiya\'s cell phone in one hand.\n\nIn the other hand is a crumpled note.\n\n\"If you don\'t want her to be in trouble, come to the rooftop of the mall.\"\n\nHe still recognized Noriko Amamiya\'s mobile phone. When he was photographed, he looked at the camera and had a memory of the appearance of a mobile phone.\n\nWhen the other party noticed, he didn\'t find it, and he also arrested the little girl. Although he didn\'t know the child, he was a Japanese public security policeman, and he was also the mission target of the organization. In this case, there is no need to What are you worried about.\n\nThe camouflage man changed his eye-catching camouflage suit into casual clothes, wearing a pair of sunglasses and a fisherman\'s hat. On the third floor, leaning on the glass railing, he glanced at Jianggu Ling at the entrance of the shopping mall, and the corners of his mouth twitched slightly.\n\n\"Prey, you should bring me entertainment.\"\n\nAfter taking a look, he immediately turned to the side, his eyes would be attracted to each other.\n\nThat\'s true, but the perception of the premise of mutual discovery is sharp, and Gu Ling\'s perception is even sharper than his. When he turned around, Ya Gu Ling raised his head slightly and locked him from half of his back.\n\nJiang Guling squinted slightly: \"I found you.\"\n\nShuichi Akai, who was taking the escalator from 4F to 5F with Miyano Akemi, looked down at the person who turned around outside the railing on the third floor.\n\nThere is no more suspicious target than this person. When leaning on the railing, the muscles of the arms show the strength of the years of exercise, not fitness work or the like, but actual combat, the hardness of the muscles and skin.\n\nThe dark complexion looks like it has been exposed to the sun all year round.\n\nIt\'s a pity that he can\'t see the target the other party is looking at from his angle here.\n\nAkai Shuichi tilted his head to Miyano Akimi and said, \"You go up to find Noriko first, and I\'ll deal with him.\"\n\nMiyano Akimi looked at him indifferently and nodded, \"Be careful.\"\n\n  \"nothing.\"\n\nAfter the elevator reached 5F, Shuichi Akai walked to the stairs, and Akemi Miyano hurriedly found Noriko Amamiya on the 5F.\n\nOn the other side, Kudo Shinichi