 Shuichi\'s Jeet Kune Do is extremely superb. Whenever his arm movements try to induce elbow strikes, Akai Shuichi has been punching his arm, making the camouflage man almost have the illusion of a fractured arm.\n\nAnd his knee strike was even more unbearable. Akai Hideyuki\'s slanted heel slammed into his thigh like an electric shot, and the buds of the knee strike vanished.\n\nIf it was a calf bone, Shuuichi Akai might be able to kick it off with such force.\n\nShiliang\'s pure Jeet Kune Do is the master\'s brother Shuichi Akai. Shiliang\'s pure fighting power can be referred to as Xiaolan'),
(424, 5, 94, 'Chapter 93: : Gin, Vodka, Bourbon', 'Wheat-skinned hands picked up a small packet of white powder, dipped a little and sniffed it in front of his nose.\n\nA touch of sour vinegar.\n\n\"There are such scumbags in the Japanese police.\"\n\nAkai Hidey rubbed his fingers to wipe away the white powder, and looked down at the fat man who was slumped on the ground.\n\n\"It just so happens that I also have a mission, and the right should be to help the Japanese police get rid of the scum.\"\n\nAkai Shuichi picked up the fat man by the back collar and dragged him away. Before leaving, he glanced at the boy who fell to the ground. It was not a big problem, but he was unlucky. In order to prevent him from telling the police immediately, he could only be knocked out. .\n\nJust looking at the way he took things through the handkerchief just now, it seemed like a professional detective.\n\nIt doesn\'t matter, I didn\'t look at his face, and he didn\'t see his face, so he just pretended that nothing happened.\n\nAkai Shuichi dragged Fatty to the corner, and then pushed a dining car where the banquet started serving dishes, covered with a white cloth, stuffed Fatty into the ground of the dining car and pushed it towards the elevator.\n\nJust before leaving, Shuichi Akai\'s stern gaze fell on Gin and Vodka. What was the mission of the two of them? No plans to leave yet?\n\nIf it wasn\'t for the fact that he didn\'t expect Gin to appear here, he would definitely set up a trap to catch Gin. Now, the situation in the arena is too complicated and it is not suitable to do anything.\n\nWe can only complete the task first and improve the trust of the organization.\n\nThere will definitely be a chance later, and I will grab the gin again.\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who had been walking towards Gin, noticed Shuichi Akai\'s gaze, and then looked at the dining cart he was pushing. With a move, she went back to take a look, and saw that Shinichi Kudo was miserably on the ground, and the fat man was nowhere to be seen.\n\nAlthough the top floor of Yuanzi\'s house is covered with a carpet, you are too miserable.\n\nKudo Shinichi was poisoned by Akai Shuichi, which was unexpected by Amamiya Noriko.\n\nHe could only bend down and carry Kudo Shinichi to Sonoko\'s room to sleep slowly, leaving a note by the way before leaving.\n\nAfter going out, Shuuichi Akai was nowhere to be found on the entire floor. It seems that Shuichi Akai\'s mission should be that fat man Takashi Nanmura. Silence.\n\nWell, the traces of Noriko Amamiya should also be dealt with.\n\nIt\'s just that the reason why he originally planned to find Gin and deal with Fatty was gone.\n\n\"Is Noriko still in your room? The banquet is about to start.\"\n\n\"Well, I said to take a break, it should be better soon.\"\n\n\"Let\'s see if Noriko has a fever again.\"\n\nXiaolan and Sonoko passed by Amemiya Noriko. They didn\'t recognize Amamiya Noriko after the disguise, but they all glanced at her. From Sonoko\'s somewhat amazed eyes, it could be seen that the current Amamiya Noriko\'s appearance was also different. not bad.\n\nAmamiya Noriko responded with a polite smile.\n\n\"Xiao Lan, that one was also a beauty just now, so she\'s a little worse than Noriko.\"\n\n\"It\'s really beautiful, and she looks very gentle and generous, but don\'t talk about people behind their backs.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her eyebrows, isn\'t she as beautiful as a small size?\n\nIt seems that the level is still limited. If you can, of course you want to open more. If you can\'t do it, then two numbers are one level. Two beauties, the possibility of being suspected of being disguised by the same person is very small, right?\n\nBut... Shinichi Kudo is still sleeping there in Sonoko\'s room, right?\n\nI hope they will let Shinichi sleep a little longer, it\'s not easy to be brutally murdered by Shuichi Akai.\n\nAt least, Xiao Lan\'s iron fist is gentler.\n\nNoriko Amamiya turned her head to look at the banquet. At this time, the people were almost there. The famous people who received the invitation in twos and threes toasted and talked to each other. The atmosphere was quite harmonious. No thought of talking to the past.\n\nIt looked a little lonely, so Noriko Amamiya decided to give them a toast.\n\nOf course, not by yourself.\n\nAmuro Toru came back after delivering the wine and picked up the plate to continue delivering the wine and food, but saw a note on the plate and three glasses of wine.\n\nHis face darkened slightly, with a solemn gaze, the three glasses of wine were gin, vodka, and bourbon.\n\nGin is gin, also known as gin.\n\nThe delicate font on the note reads: \"Mr. waiter, help me give these two glasses of wine to those two people, I see that none of them speaks, they look so pitiful, and I will order the rest for you. \"\n\nAmuro looked at the note, but he was using the corner of his eye to check whether there were suspicious people nearby. Some prisoners would like to stay at the crime scene or return to the crime scene to see how others reacted and the situation when they found the scene, so as to judge the danger. Or safety, or even to satisfy inner thoughts.\n\nBut there doesn\'t seem to be anyone nearby who deserves attention.\n\nA suspicious voice suddenly sounded beside him: \"Brother waiter, is this juice or water? Can you drink it for me?\"\n\nToru Amuro\'s face returned to normal in an instant, with the smile that a service type should have, looking at this beautiful girl in a white dress, it seemed that she didn\'t quite understand, and regarded the transparent and clear Dutch gin as water.\n\nHe put away the note without a trace, and said with a gentle smile, \"Little sister, this is not water or juice, it\'s alcohol that is impossible for minors to drink.\"\n\n\"Alright then, thank you big brother, I\'ll see if there\'s any juice.\"\n\nThe little girl thanked him and went to look for juice.\n\nToru Amuro also picked up the wine and walked towards the gin and vodka. UU Reading www.uukanshu.com\n\nHe didn\'t understand why this mysterious person knew their code names in the organization clearly, but it didn\'t seem like he was going to do anything.\n\nMainly, he has more identity than gin and vodka, so he can\'t help but worry more.\n\nRather than worrying about it alone, it\'s better to let the gin and vodka use their brains too.\n\nToru Amuro brought the wine over, Jin Jiu glanced at the wine in his wine plate with cold eyes.\n\n\"Bourbon, what do you mean?\"\n\n\"Don\'t be angry this guest.\" Amuro waved his hand and said in a low voice, \"I don\'t know who sent me here.\"\n\nVodka lost his voice: \"He knows our identity?\"\n\nJin Jiu checked Bourbon\'s face for a while, and after a while his eyes were cold: \"Don\'t ignore it, continue with the mission.\"\n\nAmuro smiled and said, \"Is this really good?\"\n\nJin Jiu said coldly: \"I don\'t know what your mission is, I hope you won\'t get in the way of me.\"\n\n\"Of course, then this glass of wine is my own, so I\'ll keep it for myself.\"\n\nAmuro put down the gin and vodka and left with his glass of wine.\n\nGin glanced at Gin, how could he drink this kind of wine of unknown origin, but it seemed that someone was deliberately joking with them.\n\nThe corners of Gin\'s mouth twitched.\n\nNo one, can joke with him, no one.\n\nVodka picked up his glass of vodka and shook it, \"Brother, it\'s actually Polish vodka? Why not Russian vodka.\"\n\nGin glanced at him and ignored it.');
