(425, 5, 57, 'Chapter 56: : Your joy, I received', 'It was almost lunchtime, and Amamiya Noriko and Xin Xiaolan Yuanzi went home.\n\nAt least have to go to the luncheon.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Sonoko changed back to their kimonos, and asked Xiaolan to wear them together, wearing Noriko Amamiya\'s.\n\nAfter Amamiya Noriko helped her fasten her belt, she heard Xiaolan say, \"It seems a little tight.\"\n\n\"Then let me relax?\"\n\n\"It\'s not... it\'s the whole, it\'s okay, that\'s it, Noriko.\"\n\n  \"it is good.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, then looked at Xiao Ran, they were all about the same height, Xiao Ran wouldn\'t be fat either.\n\n\"Why do you have men\'s kimonos?\"\n\nShinichi Kudo dressed in black and obedient while walking away to manage.\n\nWhen she saw Xiao Lan wearing a plain yellow background with plum pattern and small sleeves kimono, she couldn\'t help but be taken aback for a moment.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at his straight eyes and said, \"This is my kimono.\"\n\nXiaolan turned her head to find Shinichi looking at her, and said, \"How is it? Noriko\'s kimono looks good, right?\"\n\n  \"well enough.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi tilted his head and looked away, mainly because people looked good.\n\nXiaolan was puzzled.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at these two people next to them, Shinichi, you apologize for my kimono first, what do you mean it\'s okay, it\'s beautiful!\n\nBut Sonoko mysteriously pulled her away, Amamiya Noriko was puzzled: \"What is Sonoko doing?\"\n\n\"Of course, don\'t disturb them!\"\n\nSonoko looked serious.\n\n\"…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that when she turned around, she would complete them, otherwise, Sonoko, it would not be easy for you to worry about it, that\'s why.\n\nShe saw that Suzuki Sonoko was very interested in bringing together Xinlan, and it was entirely out of interest.\n\nAt the luncheon.\n\nWith channels all over the world, the owner of the Amamiya chaebol with inestimable overseas liquidity, Amamiya Ludou, the owner of the Amamiya family.\n\nShiro Suzuki, chairman of the largest emerging consortium in Japan, the Suzuki Consortium.\n\nThe former detective of the Metropolitan Police Department\'s Search Section 1 is now Kogoro Mouri with a detective.\n\nThese three people have already finished talking this morning.\n\nCurrently drinking and chatting very happily.\n\nShiro Suzuki has a relatively easy-going personality, and is a strict wife, so he just sips with him from time to time, and mostly chats.\n\nAmamiya Kiko\'s father, Amamiya Ludou, has a casual personality, and there is no pressure to accompany Mouri Kogoro to drink.\n\nXiaolan secretly punched her father in the waist and ribs, which made his exaggerated laughter stop a little.\n\nAmamiya Noriko basically lowered her sense of presence throughout the whole process to eat. This luncheon should be made by a famous chef from a famous restaurant outside. They are all very good Japanese dishes.\n\nShe only smiled politely and sweetly when she was praised by the elders of other families. It was quite frequent.\n\nNoriko Amamiya is not someone else\'s child. Whoever praises her, she praises whoever\'s child.\n\nShinichi was praised by her soft voice, and the two wars were about to leave first.\n\nIt’s been almost ten years since I started kindergarten, and I’ve never been praised so much by Noriko Amamiya. He’s very smart. He will definitely be a great detective in the future.\n\nTo be honest, Kudo Shinichi was a little scared.\n\nAfter being complimented by Amamiya Noriko, Amamiya Noriko\'s father Amamiya Lu Dou glanced at him from time to time, looking up and down, Mouri Kogoro occasionally glanced at him, but it was an admiring look, Amamiya Noriko is a troublesome kid. Yes, boy, you have courage.\n\nXiaolan tugged Shinichi\'s sleeve in private, and whispered for unknown reasons, \"What\'s wrong with you, Shinichi? It looks like you\'re sweating a lot.\"\n\n\"It\'s nothing, it\'s just a little hot.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pretended to be a little hot and wiped his forehead, looking at Noriko Amemiya\'s innocent gaze.\n\nHe figured out a very important question, Amamiya Noriko\'s character is so excessive, it may be because of distorted emotional values, only like the feeling of others confessing to her, but not really moved, emotionally flawed.\n\nIn other words, if you arrange a boyfriend for Noriko Amamiya, her personality should be somewhat restrained...\n\nKudo Shinichi thought and shook his head again.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s hobby is to enjoy other people\'s confessions, and what she likes is the feeling of rejecting others\' confessions.\n\nLetting her stop being eccentric is no less than letting her stop fishing.\n\nHe suddenly looked away, instead of worrying about the other people who were being played by Amamiya Noriko in the palm of his hand, he might as well rescue himself first. He was a victim of Amamiya Noriko\'s hidden eccentric character.\n\nKudo Shinichi let out a long sigh and thought contentedly in his heart, \"Go back to school and have fun seeing those idiots being played with by Noriko Amamiya.\"\n\nToday they are not the protagonists, the elders are.\n\nThe Amamiya family was led astray by Noriko Amamiya. Anyway, a few of them finished their meal first and left the table. The elders continued to chat.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took Xin Xiaolan Yuanzi to play flying chess.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took off with a single-handed dice technique.\n\nXiaolan took off with the Ouhuang buff with one hand.\n\nSonoko prayed devoutly, but the takeoff failed.\n\nKudo Shinichi tried to grasp the number of dice landing points, but failed.\n\nThis is basically the result. Shinichi, who is highly intelligent at playing cards and mahjong, may still be very strong, but how could Noriko Amamiya give him a chance.\n\nHappy times are always short-lived. In the middle of the afternoon, the elders finished their visit and prepared to leave.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko and Kudo Shinichi, whose faces were covered with notes, tore off all the notes on their faces, and Xiaolan also followed.\n\nAfter sending them off, Amamiya Noriko asked Amamiya Lu Dou what they talked about when she came back.\n\nAmamiya Ludou nodded and said, \"It\'s mainly the business cooperation between the two sides. Anyway, we have no conflict of interest. At the same time, to deepen the relationship, we can ask the Suzuki family to take care of you when we go abroad.\"\n\nBecause it is a global business, the frequency of Amemiya and his wife going abroad is quite intensive.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, knowing that her father was planning to settle abroad for them in the future, and she was making arrangements in Japan alone.\n\nShe doesn\'t need to arrange such a complete arrangement at all, but there is nothing wrong with cooperating with the Sonoko family, so it doesn\'t matter.\n\n\"It\'s just that if the guy from Kuaidou steals the Suzuki consortium every day in the future, will it affect the two shares?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it, it shouldn\'t be in the way, hurry up, my own.\n\nIt\'s better to be more prepared for the building blasting machine - the winery.\n\nThis time, Amamiya Ludou also called Mouri Kogoro for crime prevention reasons. He also has a relationship with the police, but the police cannot help her protect her daughter every day.\n\nAnd the daughter occasionally visits her friend Xiaolan\'s house, so it is necessary to count on Maori Kogoro.\n\nAt least he was a detective from the previous investigation class. Now, as a detective, he should be more aware of the approaching danger.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also probably guessed what her father was thinking. Really, if she thinks too much, she may also protect Kogoro Mouri by the way.\n\nMaori Kogoro\'s strengths lie in over-the-shoulder falls and skilled and precise marksmanship, as well as his brain power when relatives and friends encounter cases, and sometimes find problems earlier than Shinichi.\n\nHowever, there are distance restrictions, marksmanship, and Kogoro Mouri is not equipped with a gun now, and relatives and friends encounter cases. Does this mean that someone has already had an accident?\n\nThe requirement to trigger Mouri Kogoro\'s seed explosion was too harsh, and Amamiya Noriko felt embarrassed, so it might be better to anaesthetize him.\n\nConan, the truth has long been known.\n\nAnd this time, after the Golden Week, which started with several collaborations, came to school again.\n\nAfter school, Kudo Shinichi put on his jersey and went to the football club, only to find that the people in the football club were filled with righteous indignation.\n\n\"Damn, those guys in the basketball club actually have the guts to invite our Amamiya to watch the game!\"\n\n\"It\'s too much. It must be because Amamiya is pure and kind and won\'t refuse!\"\n\n\"You can\'t let them off so easily!\"\n\n\"We\'re going to watch the game too!!\"\n\n  \"Walk!!\"\n\nThe members of the football club moved towards the gym with enthusiasm.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who just finished changing his jersey: \"...\"\n\nAre you from the football club, not Noriko Amemiya, the fan club?\n\nKudo Shinichi followed him expressionlessly.\n\nAs soon as they entered the stadium football club, they saw Noriko Amamiya in the auditorium.\n\nBut instead of leaning over, they chose to sit in the auditorium across from the basketball court.\n\nKudo Shinichi understood the filth of these guys from the perspective of sitting down.\n\nBut his heart did not fluctuate, because even though Noriko Amamiya was innocent and cute on the surface, but elusive in private, she was dressed in unexpectedly innocent, nothing to look at.\n\nAs the only serious artificial Fuji Shinichi is watching basketball seriously.\n\nOn the basketball court in the gymnasium, the two teams are playing fiercely. At this time, everyone is Sakuragi Huadao, and everyone is Rukawa Feng. If you want to ask why it is so fierce, it is because of the rain in the auditorium on one side. Miyakiko cheered them on with the cheerleading balls.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was also a little unresponsive, so she flicked the cheerleader **** from time to time.\n\nIt was given to her by the cheerleader sister, because the other team on the basketball court is from another school, the cheerleader sisters invited her as a surprise~www.readwn.com~ In order to inspire the fighting spirit of the school basketball team!\n\nBut I didn\'t expect that the basketball team members of the other school would start the microcosmic runaway state after they found Noriko Amemiya in the auditorium, and the away game was also extremely tough.\n\nAs a member of the student union, Noriko Amamiya was invited by the cheerleading sisters for the reason of inviting her to inspect the basketball club and the basketball team from other schools.\n\nOf course, she is also here to let the basketball club members know of her existence, so they can confess to me—— like this.\n\nBut after seeing the members of the football club opposite, she reached out and waved the colored ball to say hello.\n\nWhy are you sitting over there? I still have a place next to me.\n\n  \"Oooo!!!!\"\n\nThe members of the football club let out a low roar, Amamiya still cares about the football club! !\n\nAny basketball club is rubbish. It is so hard to play a foreign school basketball team, why not let them play in the football club! !\n\nThe cheerleading seniors were stunned by the shouting of the football club members opposite, and turned to look at Noriko Amamiya, who made this noise by one person.\n\nThe leader of the cheerleading team, the third-year senior sister Aoi Motohashi, ran up to the auditorium, begging a little embarrassedly in Noriko Amamiya\'s ear.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko waved her hand quickly, saying that it\'s okay, didn\'t she just jump?\n\nI\'m wearing safety pants, it\'s okay.\n\nAoi Motohashi looked at Noriko Amamiya with a cute face, she thought that this lovely junior elementary school girl...\n\nShould wear stripes or animals.\n\nAmamiya Noriko stood up and looked at the basketball and football clubs who responded clearly. I received your joy!\n\nEveryone is ready to confess to me.\n\n​​'),
(426, 5, 12, 'Chapter 11: : I have a lot of fish ponds', 'Kudo Shinichi is no longer as naive as he was in elementary school, so he will not be arrogant when facing Xiaolan. Quan treats himself as a disciple of Sherlock Holmes and can\'t care about girls.\n\nAnd although Kudo Shinichi won\'t admit it, Xiaolan is his first love in kindergarten...\n\nAmamiya Noriko knows everything, so with Xiaolan around, she is invincible, because Kudo Shinichi is really straight, so she doesn\'t care whether she is a beauty or not. she.\n\nHowever, he is still a detective, and he is not sensitive enough.\n\nUpon seeing Noriko Amamiya, Shin Kudo smiled victoriously at him. The originally delicate and lovely face had to make a treacherous smile. He even raised his head and showed a white neck, telling him that he had won.\n\nHe rolled his eyes and saw that for Lan\'s sake, he didn\'t care about her.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was then pulled by Suzuki Sonoko to study what club to join. Any club would do, but it couldn\'t be too girly. Wouldn\'t it be a dungeon to play, and give the boys a chance.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko agrees very much: \"That\'s it, I\'m researching which club has more handsome guys, then let\'s go to a club with more handsome guys!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that if she wanted to pursue it like this, then I would simply go to an all-boys club and become a social treasure.\n\nBut that\'s not enough. She\'s the only girl in the club, and she\'s very concerned about her plans.\n\nAmamiya Noriko lifted her bangs, \"I think I\'m pretty handsome too.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko watched for a while. Noriko\'s face was relatively petite and cute, and she was naturally childish, but her brows were full of energy, and she had shoulder-length short and medium hair, and said seriously: \"It\'s pretty handsome among girls, but Ji Are you having long hair?\"\n\n\"I think long hair is troublesome, but I think little boys like long hair.\"\n\n  \"Eh???\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko seemed to hear an incredible expression, because she has always had short hair! Is it because of this reason that no handsome guy likes it?\n\nSeeing this, Noriko Amamiya waved her hand: \"Sonoko\'s short hair is enough, or short hair is suitable for Sonoko.\"\n\n\"Hey, I think so too. If it wasn\'t for short hair, I wouldn\'t be able to wear this headband. It must be that the handsome guys didn\'t notice the beauty of my short hair. Noriko\'s long hair must be prettier.\"\n\nSeeing that she cared so much about headbands, Amamiya Noriko was going to say \"Take off the headbands, you are also a beauty\" and just forget about it.\n\nThe little Suzuki Sonoko from the main kindergarten is very cute with a bow headband. She has been used to watching it for so many years.\n\nMoreover, Sonoko really likes to wear a headband, which is also a habit since kindergarten. If he can\'t persuade him, he may need to speak, but Jingjizhen, the man, may also like headbands.\n\nXiaolan also joined the topic. The three of them made an appointment to join the club the next day. If there is no accident, there will be many clubs on the school road tomorrow to attract new people.\n\nAs for Kudo Shinichi, he has decided to go to the football club to play.\n\n\"Kiko, you can also come to the football club.\"\n\nAnd he is also going to pull Kiko Amamiya. As long as there are two of them in the football club, they will definitely be able to sweep everything.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it and thought it was possible, so she abandoned Xiaolan and Sonoko the next day, and went to join the football club with Kudo Shinichi.\n\nOriginally, the people who welcomed the new members of the football club were not very interested, because the freshmen were all freshmen from elementary school, and their physical development in adolescence might not have started yet, so they didn\'t have much hope for the physical fitness of the new members of the club.\n\nHowever, the seniors who were recruiting new members of the club saw the beautiful girl who was going to join the football club, eh, that\'s great.\n\nAs for Kudo Shinichi by the way? Well, buddy, you can fill out an application form and go.\n\n\"Student Amamiya, welcome, why did you choose to join our football club?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko put her slender fingers against her chin and thought for a while: \"Because I look forward to the appearance of seniors running around the football field and sweating, it feels very handsome.\"\n\n\"As expected of someone from our football club! You can understand our romance. How many classes does Amamiya have in a year?\"\n\n\"Um...Is it written on the application form?\"\n\n\"Oh, so that\'s the case.\" The senior in charge of recruiting new members glanced at the club application form and wrote down the class of the lovely junior, and then comforted the senior in the tone of the senior: \"Don\'t worry, Amamiya-san, our football club has always taken great care of newcomers. And the atmosphere is very good.”\n\n\"Ah, well, the seniors must be very easy to get along with.\"\n\n\"Mmmmm, of course.\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was completely ignored on one side, took a deep breath. Except for him, Amamiya Noriko and other boys had such a soft tone. Boys who didn\'t know the truth would completely fool her, thinking she was a weak, innocent and lovely woman. child.\n\nActually, Amamiya Noriko started complaining to him when he left.\n\n\"Can anyone who plays football talk like a taxi driver? It\'s so enthusiastic, you\'ve been talking to me for a long time.\"\n\n\"Apologies to most of the football players and taxi drivers, UU reading www.uukanshu.com and what happened to the taxi drivers?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko snorted coldly and did not reply to his question.\n\nKudo Shinichi rolled his eyes and asked, \"How are you preparing for club activities? Can you still play like in elementary school?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko sighed and said softly, \"No, I have to take care of the excess self-awareness of the junior high school students during their adolescence. If I abuse them, maybe they won\'t confess to me.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pouted and ignored it, seeing that Xiaolan and Yuanzi were waiting for them at the school gate.\n\n\"Are you going home together?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s house and theirs are not very easy to go, and because of the taxi incident, Amamiya Noriko ordered his father to assign her a driver, but occasionally Amamiya Noriko will walk a distance with them, or Let\'s go to the park and play together.\n\n\"No, I\'ll play nearby.\"\n\nShin Kudo looked sideways, and Noriko Amamiya said that playing is relatively rare: \"Huh?\"\n\n\"Go to the arcade to play games, or play billiards.\" Seeing Kudo Shinichi\'s surprised look, \"What? I have a lot of fish ponds, not only in school fishing.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi said he was going to see her fish pond.\n\n\"Oh, let\'s go.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wanted to call Xiaolan and Sonoko by the way, but Kudo Shinichi stopped her, because it was too early for Xiaolan and Sonoko to go to a place like the arcade.\n\n\"Xinichi, why don\'t you worry about me? Or do you want to follow me just because you\'re worried that I will suffer in the game hall?\"\n\n\"I\'m here to see how you bully other people.\"\n\nShin Kudo put one hand in his pocket and pouted, but he was undeniably a little worried. After all, Amamiya Noriko is only 12 years old now, so the game arcade is still not very safe, right?'),
(427, 5, 82, 'Chapter 81: : low-level villain', '\"In the dark, only you are dazzling, and you light up the world. I love you—\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Melancholy had a conversation about youth sadness and pain literature with the purpose of discussion.\n\nMelancholy is completely attracted by Noriko Amamiya\'s literary talent, which is more than his sadness and melancholy, but with the light of hope.\n\nDeeply fascinated by Noriko Amamiya, literate people can say \"I love you\" more deeply and poetically.\n\nBecause it\'s romantic.\n\n\"No, no, I\'m a happy person, you should be happy too.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved her hand and declined with a bright and healing smile.\n\nYou\'ve gone from sadness to romance too quickly.\n\n\"Agility +1\"\n\nThe melancholy man lowered his head: \"I\'m a human being, I\'m sorry.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko apologized: \"I know someone loves me, but I seem to lack the ability to love someone.\"\n\nThe melancholy man\'s eyes were deeply attracted by Amamiya Noriko, Amamiya Noriko was fine anyway, so he gave him a set of psychotherapy.\n\nlest he say \"I hope you can remember me, remember that I lived like this and passed by you\", and then died on the spot.\n\nShe doesn\'t want to inherit the Conan Death buff.\n\nWhen he left the melancholy booth, the other party had undergone a psychological treatment, and his mental state was only slightly worse than that of a normal person. When he went back to eat, drink, and sleep, he should be able to become a normal human being.\n\nThe only thing that is a bit uncertain is that Amamiya Noriko vaguely saw a touch of devotion in the eyes of the other party looking at her...\n\nThis is also... not a big problem!\n\nThere are many church members in the world, and it is enough to integrate into the society well.\n\nAfter leaving the booth, Yuanzi, who was watching with a question mark all the way, finally couldn\'t help hugging Amamiya Noriko, choking and comforting: \"Kiko, it turns out, it turns out that you are not easy to whimper... It\'s alright. , I\'ll be here in the future!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was hugged and tilted her head. It was really not easy for me. For such a confession, I almost recalled several super depressing books. It was too difficult and too painful.\n\nBut there was nothing else, Amamiya Noriko comforted Sonoko for a while, and what she said was only in the novel.\n\n\"Little sister, have you encountered anything sad? Have you been bullied by others? Do you want your uncle to avenge you?\"\n\nA sturdy figure stood in front of them and said in a rough voice.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at the other party, she was not a supporting role qualified to appear in the original book, it should be just a little monster created in a flea market with a more complicated environment, she also raised a smile and said: \"It\'s okay, I haven\'t been caught. People bully, don\'t need uncle\'s help, thank you.\"\n\n\"Isn\'t it really necessary? Then uncle can take you to see goldfish?\"\n\nUncle Zhuang showed a wretched smile with a scruffy mouth and looked at Yunomiya Noriko and Sonoko up and down. Chi Guoguo\'s gaze made Sonoko a little panicked, and he pulled Yumiya Noriko\'s wrist. There are many people, as long as they shout loudly, someone will save them, right?\n\n\"It\'s alright, Sonoko will wait for me here.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko patted her hand and comforted her.\n\n\"Kiko...\"\n\n  \"nothing.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said softly.\n\nThen he turned around, glanced at Uncle Zhuang, raised his legs and walked to the side alley, while taking a rubber band and hair rope from his pocket to tie his hair into a single ponytail.\n\nAmamiya Noriko went straight into the alley, and Wei Shu naturally followed. For the 12-year-old Amamiya Noriko, a tall figure almost blocked the alley.\n\n\"Do you have anything to say, uncle?\"\n\nWei Shu Mi showed a wretched smile, and let out a strange laugh: \"Hehehe-\"\n\n\"The laughter is too ugly.\"\n\nBefore he could let out a triumphant voice, he felt a heavy blow to his lower jaw, his head jerked up, as if he had thrown his consciousness out, he couldn\'t feel his body, he turned his eyes around and looked upward as his body fell.\n\nAmamiya Noriko moved her ankles, because she was not high enough, she had to jump up and kick.\n\nLooking at the guy lying on the corpse, he tilted his head.\n\n\"That\'s it, come out to do bad things? Apologize to the prisoners in this world who were caught by Conan, for bringing down the average level!\"\n\nGathering up his courage, he found Sonoko, who followed the wooden stick, and stared blankly at the situation: \"Ki, Kiko, you...\"\n\n​​'),
(428, 5, 75, 'Chapter 74: : sisters', '\"Kiko\'s sisters\" chat room.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s face blushed, but she continued to scroll up the chat records.\n\nThe latest one was posted this morning.\n\nKaruta: Ah, I was greeted by Amemiya at the school gate this morning. She was cute and polite as always. In Hawaii, I could only watch another girl who was similar to Noriko relieved. It was too painful.\n\nMizuhara Yui: Envy.\n\nHayakawa Haruka: Envy.\n\nAoi Motohashi: I envy, if Noriko came to the cheerleading team, I would be able to see Noriko dancing.\n\nAfterwards, Karuta also posted a back photo of Noriko Amamiya after entering the school gate. Others praised and praised Noriko Amamiya\'s back photo.\n\nFrom the lightly brushed strands of hair that look soft and smooth, and the thought of being caressed constantly, to the small back of the body, if it is very soft in her arms, it must be very comfortable and fragrant.\n\nThen to the uniform\'s small skirt, exquisite white and tender thighs, black knee socks, slender legs, and small leather shoes.\n\nMizuhara Yui: That\'s awesome.\n\nHayakawa Haruka: How does it feel to hold Kiko\'s little feet in stockings?\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya saw this, she couldn\'t help but move her feet. Why should my feet be held in your hand?\n\nThere are still a bunch of ideas to exchange information on guessing the feel of the hand, and the chat record was not stopped until the last class time.\n\nGoing up, it\'s yesterday. Basically, I\'m excited to see Noriko Amamiya today.\n\nThe topic of guessing how cute tomorrow\'s Amemiya Noriko will be after a summer vacation continued until three in the morning.\n\nGoing forward is the summer vacation period when there is not much news. Basically, every now and then there is someone who makes a fuss about nothing. I really miss Amamiya and so on.\n\nAfter the summer vacation, I looked forward to the content that made Noriko Amamiya blushed and unsightly.\n\nAll are her own photos, stolen from various angles and under various circumstances.\n\nShe drank water, pulled down her hair, stretched her waist, talked to other people, acted cute, acted coquettishly, and slightly annoyed. She was taken a lot of photos with her cute appearance.\n\nEvery photo will be praised and praised by these sisters.\n\n\"Noriko sipping water has always been so cute! Set it as wallpaper!\"\n\n\"Noriko\'s way of stretching is so cute, like a kitten, set it as a wallpaper!\"\n\n\"Noriko\'s aggrieved appearance is also super cute, it makes people feel distressed, set it as a wallpaper!!\"\n\nThis kind of news is the second most common, and Amamiya Noriko seems to have seen a bunch of people using their mobile phones to set her usual photos as wallpapers.\n\nAs for the most news, it\'s \"prprpr\", \"hehe\", \"sucking\" and so on.\n\nReally, the sisters are all LSPs.\n\nEspecially those photos of her skirts, which are just right, on a scale that doesn\'t speak much.\n\nThe provocative sisters always guess whether the little sister Noriko wears \"stripes\", \"animals\", \"fruits\" or \"pure white\" every day.\n\n\"Not wearing it? Who came up with it?!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at it, and it was Haruka Hayakawa, the Minister of External Affairs who proposed this option. I didn\'t expect your serious minister to have such a **** idea?\n\nThen the one who always took this kind of photos and sent them out was a senior from the photography department.\n\nI, Amamiya Noriko, remember it.\n\nThen she continued to watch for a while. Although her face was a little red and hot, her eyes were still flashing fast when she looked at the phone screen.\n\nAfter a long time, she put down her phone and let out a long sigh of relief. In general, she was a support club that actively wanted to hug her.\n\nAlthough there are a few very astringent rotten girls who prefer ghs.\n\nBut because they are all girls, they are looking for her cuteness rather than her body. Amamiya Noriko can understand that there are not many people who are indifferent in front of her cuteness.\n\nIt\'s just that this feeling is rather strange, and it\'s the first time for her. If you want to describe it specifically.\n\nHu Ge joined his male fan support group—\n\nAmamiya Noriko wrote down the names of all the people in the chat room on her list.\n\nShe has quite a few \'sisters\', even dozens of them.\n\nI usually focus on fishing for boys, but it seems a little lax for girls. Going through all these dozens of attribute points is quite considerable. It is basically the first time, and it is possible to obtain attribute points stably.\n\nAmamiya Noriko put back Yui Suwon\'s cell phone, and first went to **** the senior from the photography department.\n\nStealing is prohibited.\n\nShe is a person with many secrets.\n\nThe boys in the football club knew that Noriko Amamiya was a very conservative character. She wore safety pants under her skirts. All they could do was guess the color of the safety pants every day and pray for the birth of a miracle.\n\nAnd these girls don\'t seem to be as good as boys in this regard, like this senior from the photography department, who took a lot of photos of her skirts, but didn\'t even see the safety pants, and was keen to guess in the chat room.\n\nAt least the degree of being captured by Amamiya Noriko\'s cuteness is relatively high.\n\nAmamiya Noriko just went to inadvertently, and fell on the ground a little naturally, this senior sister\'s eyes straightened, as if she had discovered a new world, she tried her best to hold back and pull out the camera to capture this scene. Impulses in chat rooms.\n\nIt\'s more important to help the fallen Yumiya up first, and at the same time help Yumiya to straighten her skirt.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thanked her seniors weakly. Although the photography department\'s senior was an LSP in the chat room, she was quite restrained and shy in reality. He waved his hand to indicate that he should, and was a little embarrassed.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes were smiling like crescent moons, and she said softly, \"It\'s clear that Noriko accidentally fell, why is Senior Sister being shy, Senior Sister is very cute.\"\n\n\"Chee-\"\n\nSeeing Amamiya Noriko\'s bright smile, the senior from the photography department blushed suddenly, as if steam was coming out of her head.\n\n\"Senpai, are you okay? Your face is very red? Will it be hot?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko reached out and pressed the back of her hand to the forehead of the photography department senior, feeling the temperature.\n\n\"It\'s okay, I\'m very good at fever.\"\n\nSenior Sister of Photography Department felt that Amamiya Noriko\'s lovely face was close at hand, and cared for herself gently and kindly. She felt stuffy in her chest, dizzy in her head, and her face was hot. The vision outside the outline of Amamiya Noriko began to blur. Zhang Kawaii cared about her little face with a worried expression and maintained a very high clarity.\n\nIs this the focus?\n\nThe thoughts in her mind couldn\'t help but blurt out in her vague consciousness. Even she didn\'t know what she was talking about. She said a lot and expressed her thoughts.\n\n\"Well, I can feel the feelings of senpai, but I refuse, senpai can\'t take pictures of people secretly in the future. It\'s not right. If you want to see Noriko, you can come and play with Noriko at any time, right?\"\n\nRejection, the wording of the candid photo made the blurry consciousness of the photography department senpai clear, and she panicked, but Amamiya Noriko didn\'t seem to blame, on the contrary, the gentle words made her relax again, as if soft, in the clouds. On, consciousness is light.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the unconscious senior, and stretched out her hand to support her body easily.\n\n\"I\'m really super A, can\'t I bear it?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko took the senior to the health room and asked the health care teacher to take care of her. She first looked at the photos in the senior\'s camera. After reading it, she felt that she was very nervous, and she clearly left. It\'s a cute route, this senior\'s accomplishments in this area are really not easy.\n\n  delete all.\n\nThere is nothing to save, and she doesn\'t want her photos to be seen by others. Although she can\'t see anything, she doesn\'t want to look very lustful.\n\nAs for whether Senior Sister will be heartbroken when she wakes up, of course it\'s impossible.\n\nAt that time, she was weak and puzzled and said, \"Sister, why do you still take these photos? If you want to see it, you can come and find someone else.\"\n\nIt\'s ok. As for really coming to see her, it\'s impossible!\n\nBy the way, Noriko Amamiya took a look, but this senior student didn\'t have the recording of Yui Suwon in her cell phone. It seemed that classmate Yui had at least not heard it to others.\n\nShe had been waiting for the senior sister from the photography department to wake up, gaining a lot of favorability, and comforting the somewhat restrained and shy senior sister, Amamiya Noriko left first.\n\nOtherwise, if the other party seems to be beside her, her heart is beating very fast, so don\'t faint again.\n\nAmamiya Noriko then went to the External Relations Department.\n\nIt seemed that the meeting of Amamiya Noriko\'s sisters had ended. After she knocked on the door, only Haruka Hayakawa was still sitting behind the desk.\n\nSeeing that it was Kiko Amemiya, she smiled slightly and said softly, \"Why is Kiko here again?\"\n\nIf it wasn\'t for seeing the chat records in the chat room and knowing that she was second only to the senior in the photography department, it would be difficult to regard the two as one person.\n\nOne is the elder sister who wants to touch her stockings feet, and the other is the dignified and temperamental Minister of External Relations.\n\nPeople are indescribable.\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head and said weakly, \"I fell outside just now and thought of Hayakawa-senpai here to sit down.\"\n\nHayakawa Haruka heard the words, got up from behind the desk, checked it, only to see that there was some dust behind Amamiya Noriko\'s skirt, and there were also a few places where the line was scratched on the knee socks.\n\n  \"What happened here?\"\n\n\"I accidentally fell, but it\'s actually nothing.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko scratched her head and said it was okay.\n\nOf course, it doesn\'t matter, but it was arranged by the senior sister of the photography department to fall on the ground. She couldn\'t bear to have any flaws in her delicate, white, tender and delicate skin.\n\nHayakawa Haruka reached out and patted the dust on the skirt behind her, and then asked her to sit down first.\n\n\"Why are you so careless, Noriko is so cute, it\'s not good to leave scars.\"\n\nHayakawa Haruka squatted down to check whether there were any scars on Noriko Amamiya\'s legs. It looked like the over-the-knee socks were scratched. \"Noriko, take off the over-the-knee socks so that I can check if there is any injury.\"\n\nSeeing Amamiya Noriko sitting shyly, bent down and stretched out her hands to slowly take off her knee socks, her slender and fair calves were gradually exposed, and her small and exquisite jade feet gradually appeared. Hayakawa Haruka swallowed saliva subconsciously.\n\nThe dream seems to be coming true.\n\nI really want to film this scene, **** it, but I can\'t do it in front of Noriko.\n\n\"Hayakawa-senpai, don\'t keep looking at it...\"\n\nLooking at Noriko Amamiya\'s embarrassed and shy expression, Hayakawa Haruka smiled slightly, \"It\'s okay, senpai, help Noriko to see if she\'s injured, it\'s not good if such a beautiful foot has scars.\"\n\nLightly supporting Noriko Amamiya\'s little foot, Hayakawa Haruka checked it carefully, and it seemed that she didn\'t see any wounds or scars. It seemed that Noriko\'s feet were not injured.\n\nIt would be a pity if such a beautiful foot was injured.\n\nSlowly putting down Yumiya Noriko\'s foot, Hayakawa Haruka\'s heart moved, and she reached out and touched Amamiya Noriko\'s ankle, making sure that she was not injured.\n\nSeeing Yumiya Noriko\'s little feet shaking, she seemed to subconsciously want to retract her feet, her cute toes were tightly rounded, and her pink toenails were so cute, she comforted her: \"Maybe it\'s not an injury, No wounds can be seen, but there may be injuries in the legs.\"\n\n\"Let senpai help Noriko take a good look.\"\n\n  \"Um...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko responded softly like a mosquito.\n\nIt doesn\'t matter that she\'s a girl anyway. Although it\'s a little uncomfortable to be touched like this, on the other hand, it proves that she can fish with her feet.\n\nAfter touching Hayakawa Haruka for a while, Amamiya Noriko shrank her feet and reminded in a low voice, \"Senior Hayakawa... Are you alright?\"\n\nHayakawa Haruka\'s jade feet stroking softly shrank back, and subconsciously said, \"Well, I\'m fine.\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nAfter speaking, she saw Amamiya Noriko looking at herself with pure and puzzled eyes, she nodded calmly and smiled: \"I mean, I\'m optimistic, Noriko does not seem to be injured, but Be more careful next time.\"\n\n\"Really, Noriko is always so careless. She often catches colds and fevers, so pay more attention to her figure.\"\n\nHayakawa Haruka took the opportunity to lightly touch Amamiya Noriko\'s head, and UU Reading www.uukanshu.com caressed lightly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was touched, she thought for a while, you are right, I confessed three times today, and I am scheduled to have a fever tomorrow.\n\nThinking about it, she put on a shy expression at the right time, buried her head slightly blushing, and said in a low voice, \"Senior Hayakawa is so gentle.\"\n\nHayakawa Haruka modestly said, \"It\'s okay, it\'s just for Noriko.\"\n\n\"Senior is so beautiful, gentle, and capable. He must have a boyfriend, right? Wouldn\'t he be just as gentle with his boyfriend?\"\n\nHayakawa Haruka looked at Amamiya Noriko as she tried to ask