(429, 5, 64, 'Chapter 63: : Best wingman, have a case? ?', 'Amamiya Noriko thought about it carefully, choose one of three? Kudo Shinichi appointed? No one is going to sacrifice to heaven?\n\nJust in case, let\'s catch the fish in the net first.\n\nThe next day, Amamiya Noriko planned the time, from the chance encounter at school, the morning exercise in the club, the lunch break, and the afternoon after school, to scoop up all the fish that had been caught in the fishing net before and put it into the fish pond.\n\nThe schedule is full.\n\nAmong them, Uda Eraser contributed a little physique to her, which is gratifying, and Amamiya Noriko also drew a chicken on his eraser as a gift.\n\nIt was collected by Uda-san, and he changed it to a round rubber. It was easier to roll on the ground. He believed that there was a small chance that it would land at the feet of Amamiya-san.\n\nEven if the confession is rejected, it can rekindle the flame of love.\n\nThen just like a dimensional hole, as long as the eraser falls on the ground, it disappears.\n\nWhen he found it again, he landed on the other side, at the feet of his brother, without your help, bah! Stop Amamiya-san from sending me to the infirmary! mean!\n\nBut his brother did smile generously, picked up the eraser and put it in his palm, he didn\'t care, his eyes were gentle.\n\nRight Tian, ​​as long as you haven\'t got Amamiya\'s heart, we will be good brothers for life.\n\nAmamiya Noriko really wanted to send them a song, but it seems that she shouldn\'t do it by herself, her position is wrong.\n\n\"Loveless Front Alliance\"\n\nClassmates are just the beginning of her goal for the whole class.\n\nAmamiya Noriko worked hard until the summer vacation.\n\nAnyway, first cast the net so that the fish can\'t escape, and then catch them one by one.\n\nShe has a relatively good mentality. Fishing is not everything she does, and she will accompany Xiaolan and Yuanzi to play when she has time.\n\nSonoko, the best wingman.\n\nFinally decided on Xinlan, so I felt that I owed Noriko. When I met the handsome guy, my first thought was not to go on my own, but to encourage Noriko to take it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s surprised expression shocked Kudo Shinichi.\n\nSonoko didn\'t think he was instantly moved when he saw the handsome guy, didn\'t he?\n\nAfter confirming that Sonoko gave it to her with good intentions, Amamiya Noriko was moved.\n\nAlthough Shinichi said no one will be interested in you Sonoko, I have always believed that people will find you Sonoko attractive.\n\nIf you take off your headband.\n\nSo when I go out to play occasionally, I have a fixed sentence pattern. Sonoko finds a handsome guy, encourages and encourages Noriko, and Noriko, who is not a cheerful type, is always embarrassed, and reluctantly stands in the sight of the handsome guy inadvertently. .\n\nCaught the attention of the handsome guy, and then the pestle was accosted on the spot. After a preliminary understanding, no one would not be tempted by Amamiya Noriko, who is soft and lovely in character and beautiful in appearance.\n\nSonoko observes her words and looks at the max, and immediately creates an atmosphere of time, place and space, so that Ou and Noriko Amamiya have a chance to get along alone.\n\nThen, it was time for Noriko Amamiya to catch big fish with a sea pole.\n\nAnyway, one confession is counted as one, and now all can be rejected by myself.\n\nShe is only 12 years old! Does the person who confessed to her know what that means? !\n\nHe even confessed to her.\n\nYou are a good person, but crawling away! !\n\nSonoko\'s handsome man radar and Amamiya Noriko\'s humanoid card issuer, the cooperation is seamless.\n\nAmamiya Noriko couldn\'t bear to let Sonoko help herself like this without asking for anything in return.\n\nSonoko, your Jinggoku Ma, I will definitely arrange it for you!\n\nFishing time always flies by quickly.\n\nThis weekend, summer vacation is approaching, Amamiya Noriko and Sonoko Xiaolan made an appointment to buy new swimwear, and then drop by the water park to play.\n\nSwimsuit Noriko Amamiya needs more deliberation, she is reserved and cute, Miss Amamiya Noriko.\n\nSexy, direct PASS, not **** at 12 years old.\n\nBut she also found it unacceptable to swimsuits that were too cute, with layers of ruffles and skirts.\n\nChieda Riho, who was traveling with her, chose a set for her young lady, a one-piece skirt with a hem, which was completely a children\'s swimsuit, tied behind the neck.\n\nThe corners of Amamiya Noriko\'s mouth twitched for a long time, but Chieda Riho was firmly opposed to the split swimsuit, so she could only reluctantly accept it.\n\nAt 12 years old, I don\'t have anything to show off anyway, so that\'s it.\n\nFortunately, Xiaolan and Sonoko are similar. After Sonoko can\'t get it right now, she wears a swimsuit that makes Kudo Shinichi\'s nose bleed.\n\nAs for Chieda Riho, a swimsuit for swimming training is so handsome and attractive.\n\nAmamiya Noriko needs to wear sunscreen when going out. This water park is not indoors, and the sun is very poisonous near the hottest time of summer.\n\nXiaolan and Yuanzi were also pulled by her to protect themselves from the sun before they were given out. One was tanning and the other was sunburn.\n\nWith Noriko Amamiya\'s constitution, a small sunburn on her skin is completely fine, but she doesn\'t want to try tanning.\n\nPerfectly prepared, Amamiya Noriko moved her body a bit. Her swimming skills, needless to say, can gallop across the world with a trident.\n\n\"Come on a swimming ring~www.readwn.com~Thank you.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko rented a swimming ring.\n\nA girl who swims like a shark, and a girl who is cute and holding a swimming ring, she thinks the latter likes more people.\n\nChieda Riho used a camera to take a picture of the young lady going into the water with her swimming ring in her arms.\n\nThe lady who can swim in the swimming pool at home and doesn\'t have to worry about drowning, but she has to hold the swimming ring on this occasion, cute いですね (oh kawaii kudo).\n\nAmamiya Noriko slammed on the brakes with her bare feet when she was about to go into the water, and turned to look at the two people sitting at the table under the umbrella over there.\n\nA somewhat rough-and-tumble old man with a toothpick in his mouth, a handsome man with slightly curly hair with an ink lens.\n\n\"What\'s the situation?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head and looked around, there were no more familiar faces, mainly these two people.\n\n\"Well, you have to get familiar with it. Take a group photo for Touko to see.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko hugged the swimming ring and was ready to go directly, but she stopped halfway, and it seemed to normal people that they were chatting and reminiscing about the old days.\n\nBut with her keen observation ability, she could see that while the two were pretending to chat and reminisce about the past, the macho man was observing the surroundings.\n\nThe other handsome man didn\'t know what the target looked like, but was driven by the corner of the eye to scan the surroundings, while opening his mouth to speak, his fingers pressed the buttons on the phone very quickly, as if he was exchanging phone numbers.\n\n\"In this case, is there a case?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, the culprit? Too bad I didn\'t bring a new one...\n\nJust thinking about it, she saw Kudo Shinichi walking over in swimming trunks.\n\nAfter Kudo Shinichi came over, the first sentence was: \"I encountered a case!?\"\n\n\"As expected of you... You must come if you have a case?\"\n\n​​');
