(430, 5, 76, 'Chapter 75: : tool man', 'Leaving the External Relations Department.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thinks she is quite a lucky person.\n\nAlthough her luck is poor.\n\nBut she has so many senior sisters who like her and Asahi.\n\nOf course, it\'s not luck either, it\'s because of her cuteness.\n\nLuckily, Yui Suwon didn\'t bring her mobile phone when she went to the sisters\' project. She wrote down the names of all the sisters in the chat room.\n\nOnly then can the senior sisters be served in one pot.\n\nFor most of the semester, Noriko Amamiya has been busy with this, giving opportunities and courage to the senior sisters, so that they have the confidence to dare to confess, and then they are rejected.\n\nAccording to the list of senior sisters one by one, the efficiency is not low.\n\nIt\'s a little more efficient than spending some time navigating the entire community.\n\nBut this is the only chance, there should be no other Noriko\'s sisters.\n\nThe second semester went by quickly with the efficiency of Noriko Amamiya. In a blink of an eye, more than a month passed. Noriko Amamiya started school in mid-October. Every day was full of schedules. The two-way road of confession galloped back and forth.\n\nBy this time, almost everywhere she went, there was a kind and doting senior sister who greeted her.\n\nOne of the things that the senior sisters are better than boys is that after being rejected by Noriko Amamiya, their hearts are just \"Ah...rejected by Noriko, obviously she is such a cute Noriko\".\n\nIt doesn\'t prevent them from taking care of Noriko Amamiya as a cute little sister.\n\nHowever, their confession with sincerity and intentions was indeed rejected by Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAttribute points are added.\n\nThis aspect is slightly stronger than some self-esteem, and it is much easier for boys who feel embarrassed after being rejected.\n\nKudo Shinichi does not belong to this type of boy, he is unique and straight.\n\nIt\'s okay to be straight. I don\'t