while, and repeatedly waved his hands to indicate that he was thinking about things.\n\nOf course, the innocent and lovely Noriko Amamiya would not pierce him, and let him go after warning him again.\n\nBefore leaving, she gave a bright smile.\n\n\"Be careful behind—\"\n\n\"Bang—\"\n\n\"It\'s okay, it\'s okay, a small problem...\"\n\nLooking at the classmates who were staggering away while covering their foreheads, Amamiya Noriko couldn\'t help but sigh: \"Interesting man.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was in a complicated mood. When will men other than him stand up in front of Noriko Amamiya!\n\nHe has been thinking about this since kindergarten, and every time he is in this situation, he feels very sad. There must be men in the world who can resist Noriko Amemiya like him, but not many!\n\nWhat a sad story, Kudo Shinichi raised his head and took a sip of the juice, which was a little too sweet.\n\n\"Don\'t be so anxious if you want to kiss me indirectly, I haven\'t had a drink yet?\"\n\n\"Pfft—\"\n\nKudo Shinichi vomited blood, and Amamiya Noriko reacted quickly to dodge without splashing at all.\n\nAmamiya Noriko brought him a tissue from her small bag: \"It was given to me by my senior, so don\'t waste it. You have to drink it up and buy it for me again.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t do anything about it, he subconsciously took a sip, even though it was caused by Noriko Amamiya.\n\nI had to go to the vending machine again to buy a drink for Noriko Amamiya.\n\n  \"What do you want to drink?\"\n\n\"Well, chocolate-flavored milk.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi coined, \"Is this the type that cute girls can drink?\"\n\nBecause Amamiya Noriko has always been drinking her unique standard type of drinks, coffee and chocolate functional drinks are not in her cute list.\n\n\"I just want to drink it. This chocolate tastes very mellow.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko crouched down and took it out. As for Kudo Shinichi, just drink the can of super sweet strawberry juice.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at the juice in his hand~www.readwn.com~ and reasoned calmly. Did Noriko Amemiya take the opportunity to put it in his hand on purpose?\n\nIt\'s not that there is no such possibility, and it is very large!\n\nAmamiya Noriko is definitely someone who can do this.\n\n\"Next week\'s school sports meeting, what project did Xinyi sign up for?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said casually after drinking a sip of chocolate milk.\n\nAfter Kudo Shinichi heard the words, he calmly thought about the reasons and various possibilities of Amamiya Noriko\'s question.\n\nThis person is not someone who can provoke a topic.\n\nThere must be some plan or conspiracy.\n\nKudo Shinichi said cautiously, \"Let\'s take advantage of the 4x100m race.\"\n\nThe relay race is a four-person sport, so it\'s not easy for Amamiya Noriko to trick him, right?\n\nAmamiya Noriko took out the book: \"Who is your teammate?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"...\"\n\nHow dare I say it, if you say a name, if you put it in your book, you will definitely confess it to you, right?\n\nSeeing that he was quite cautious, Amamiya Noriko had to put away the confession notes, \"I just want to give your teammates a buff, they will become stronger.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi nodded helplessly: \"I thank you for your kindness for them, but don\'t use the tools that were thrown away at one time for the innocent people to trick me.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shouted aggrievedly in a low voice, \"I didn\'t use their one-off tool!\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was dumbfounded by her shouting, and reflected on whether what he said had hurt Noriko Amamiya\'s heart...\n\nI heard Noriko Amamiya add.\n\n\"Twice! No matter what, they are tools that can be used twice, and I will not give them up easily!\"\n\n​​'),
(431, 5, 88, 'Chapter 87: : 2 bottles of good wine, under the skirt', 'The banquet hall on the top floor.\n\nWhen Chieda Riho was paying attention to Toko, Amamiya Noriko was trying her best to avoid being noticed by Toko, otherwise she would bubbling in front of Toko at this time, and when she turned around and did bad things on the trumpet, she would be suspicious of what a person should do.\n\nIt\'s impossible to make an appointment with the next number. She has put the new one through (backstab) without taking the number.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took Chiedariho to the side and walked around without attracting the attention of the waiters in the banquet hall.\n\nChieda Riho glanced at Toru Amuro for the last time, and took it back.\n\nLooking back, I have to investigate this person. How can someone of unknown origin approach her Kiko.\n\nAmamiya Noriko found Suzuki Sonoko in a room on the top floor, she was still trying on clothes.\n\nSeeing Noriko coming, Suzuki Sonoko happily pulled Noriko in, while Chieda Riho stayed outside the room and stood upright as a guard.\n\nShe was the doorman with her and the security staff of another security company who came later.\n\nShe is tall and straight in a suit, wears in-ear headphones and a pair of sunglasses, the bangs in front of her short black hair are naturally curled to the right, and her skin color is a little wheatish.\n\nEven through the sunglasses, you can feel the other person\'s stern gaze.\n\nChieda Riho nodded in her heart: \"A bodyguard like this is not bad, and has the qualifications to protect Noriko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was sitting on the bed in the room, watching Suzuki Sonoko pick and change her clothes. In her opinion, Sonoko would brighten the whole room once every time she changed clothes, because Sonoko took off her headband when changing clothes.\n\nSo beautiful, the light of the right path. .\n\nOf course, Sonoko Suzuki, who had finally picked her clothes, was all gone, because she had put on a headband