t they saw Noriko Amemiya, the eyes under the sunglasses also faltered, which was too coincidental.\n\nHe was even more unrecognizable by Amamiya Noriko. Amamiya Noriko knew that his name was Zhuxingda, and the name of his bodyguard was not Zhuxingda.\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya calls his name, he will be logged out of his trumpet.\n\ntoo deadly.\n\nAs a bodyguard, Shuichi Akai calmly followed Miss Suzuki and Noriko Amamiya, who were to be protected, for a while, and found an opportunity in the middle to quickly exchange jobs with another bodyguard.\n\nHe is still the captain of the bodyguard, so he can protect the important person Suzuki Sonoko, and it is easy to change positions at this time.\n\nIt\'s just that after changing Akai Shuichi, he thought about it, he may meet again at any time on this floor, and the banquet has not yet started, the target person has not yet arrived, you can go to other places first, and when the people are almost there, he is not so easy to be caught. Amamiya Noriko noticed.\n\nSo he went straight to the downstairs outside the treasure chest of gems, where almost no one came. There was no one here, and he waited until the banquet started.\n\nAkai Shuichi\'s calm gaze fell on Amamiya Noriko and Suzuki Sonoko, who were looking at the gem from downstairs.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko was still puzzled: \"Aren\'t you following us?\"\n\nAkai Shuichi\'s cold response: \"Post change.\"\n\n\"Oh, whatever, Noriko, let\'s go in.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko was stagnant for a while, then took Amamiya Noriko\'s hand and entered.\n\nNoriko Amamiya pretended not to see anything, so she glanced at Hideo Akai curiously.\n\nAkai Shuichi\'s big heart is expressionless, his face doesn\'t change, like I\'m someone you don\'t know.\n\nAfter the two of them went in, he raised his legs and left.\n\n\"Captain, where are you going?\"\n\n  \"bathroom.\"\n\nAfter leaving the gem showcase in the vault, Amamiya Noriko responded to Sonoko while thinking slightly, approaching the 360-degree