onless.\n\nTwo bottles of good wine, Chianti red wine and Cohen colorless distilled wine, a little watered, but at least not fake wine.\n\n\"What are you doing on top of my building? I\'m going to call the police.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought to herself, and turned her head to see Chieda Riho looking at her expressionlessly.\n\n\"What\'s wrong? Uh...\"\n\nChieda Riho directly reached out and searched her young lady. There were a lot of things hidden.\n\nTo be continued.\n\nAuthor\'s words: I will post a testimonial later as usual, not an update, everyone can sleep first.\n\n​​'),
(432, 5, 78, 'Chapter 77: : 123 classmates, go ahead', 'Kudo Shinichi didn\'t expect the speed of the first few bats to be so fast, and when he looked back, the distance baton was almost stuffed into his mouth.\n\nAnd the third best classmate was yelling at him with a ghastly face, so that he would not disappoint Amamiya\'s expectations.\n\nSo what exactly is Amamiya\'s expectation? ! ! !\n\nKudo Shinichi was almost at the limit of what his mental ability could bear, he turned his head to avoid the baton that was stuffed into his mouth, then caught it with his hands, and then sprinted.\n\nAs the last player, Kudo Shinichi has high hopes.\n\nIn addition, he is the ultimate leader of the unscrupulous football club after Amamiya\'s absence. At this moment, he decided to rely on his own strength to defeat the influence brought by Amamiya Noriko!\n\n\"Shinichi!! Come on, I believe you will be the first-\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked slender and weak, as if she was in poor physical condition, as if she would fall down at any time, but she was shouting strong and cheering for the people in the relay race.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was sprinting, heard Noriko Amamiya\'s cry and understood why the previous three-ranked classmates were so fast. Nominated and cheered, and the effect was doubled.\n\nIt\'s a pity that he didn\'t see Noriko Amamiya\'s appearance. He didn\'t understand that the effect was not just doubled.\n\nWhen you are standing on the runway with the hopes of the whole class on your back, facing the sprinting signal that the referee may issue at any time, the students who are surrounded by a large group of onlookers outside the runway have a rush of air in their chests, and their bodies and legs are excited and nervous. uncontrollable trembling.\n\nAt this time, someone shouted your name to cheer you on.\n\nIt seemed that Amamiya, who was so weak in the past, was cheering them on loudly, believing that they would definitely win the championship.\n\nAt that moment, the trembling was thrown out of the sky, and the body felt as hard as steel, like a machine with a clockwork full of gears and taut gears. The moment the gun sounded, it rushed out without feeling any tired sprint. Give it to the next best student.\n\nThe second bat\'s eyes followed from outside the track to Amamiya Noriko, who was still shouting cheers, and then handed over the baton to himself. While roaring loudly, he also passed on his strength to the first bat. He took it and took the baton. Hold tightly in the palm of your hand.\n\nHe rushed out, no matter how much the other players were thrown, they still sprinted to the limit, and then passed the baton to the next one.\n\nIn the eyes of the third-ranked classmates, there was absolutely no opponent or the crowd cheering and cheering around, only Yukiko Amamiya, who ran over and cheered for them with all their might, seemed to fall at any moment.\n\nAnd eyes full of confidence in him, the last stick of steely will.\n\n  \"we are the champion!!!\"\n\n  \"Roar!!\"\n\nThe third baton rushed out with their expectations and confidence. After handing the baton to Kudo Shinichi, as if all the strength in his body had been exhausted, he shouted out at the last moment to continue the transmission of faith——\n\n\"Don\'t disappoint Amamiya\'s expectations——!!!\"\n\nThe vision in front of him was gradually shrouded in darkness, and he seemed to see Amamiya Noriko wearing an apron, virtuously waiting for him at the entrance, and said with a gentle smile, \"You\'re back...\"\n\n  \"Snapped--\"\n\nFeeling a burning sensation on his face, the third classmate suddenly opened his eyes. Seeing that it was the first two, he couldn\'t help his lips trembling and said, \"Did we win?!\"\n\n  \"we are the champion!!!\"\n\nThe three of them hugged each other, their nose and tears were flowing. Kudo Shinichi stood calmly and was not ready to join in. He glanced at Noriko Amamiya next to him, and saw the disgust of the other party and the small child. The small movement of moving a step away.\n\nAfter he arrived at the finish line, he also saw Amamiya Noriko\'s tender and pitiful appearance, as if he would fall down at any time and die, and he understood what was going on.\n\nOrdinary human beings are really not enough for Amamiya Noriko to play.\n\nA simple description is that Amamiya Noriko captured the first stick, and then threw a meteor, to the second stick, the third stick, the beliefs and thoughts of the three people converged, and finally was accepted by Amemiya Noriko and rejected. Lose.\n\nIt\'s just that the hearts of the three people gathered at Kudo Shinichi\'s place, and it was completely broken, and it stopped abruptly. Looking back, they didn\'t care how they handed it over to Amamiya Noriko Kudo Shinichi, but he would not give Amamiya Noriko anything. Turn down his chance.\n\nThe dignity of men in the whole world is now supported by him. Anyone can fall, but he cannot.\n\nIt was so straight, Amamiya Noriko gave him a thumbs up.\n\nFour people stood on the podium, each with a gold medal, cordially embraced the expressionless Kudo Shinichi, accepted the principal\'s handshake one by one, and then took a group photo.\n\nThere was a little episode. Amamiya Noriko, who was watching Kudo Shin\'s praise, was kindly called up by the principal and took a group photo with them. The reason was that Amamiya Noriko worked very hard for them.\n\nAfter the end, the other three classmates were very excited about the photo of Yumiya Noriko, who was able to be upright and bright. If it wasn\'t for Amamiya Noriko still not far away, they restrained themselves a little, and they probably would have jumped high at this time.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was very dissatisfied with Kudo Shinichi: \"Why don\'t you compare your heart to me? You agreed to compare your heart? There is no tacit understanding at all!!\"\n\n\"Look what you\'re comparing!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t help but said, and said that they would take a memory together, but it turned out to be a thumbs up. Fortunately, he was wise and raised his hand to refuse.\n\nThe situation in the photo is more complicated~www.readwn.com~ Amamiya Noriko stood shyly on Kudo Shin\'s side and gave him a thumbs up to the camera.\n\nShinichi Kudo raised his hand as he looked at the camera and raised his palm calmly to reject Tomomi Amemiya\'s praise.\n\nLayers and layers of murderous intentions are hidden in the invisible.\n\nAmamiya Noriko hummed, took out her two gold medals and hung them around her neck: \"It\'s so heavy, heavy, and Shinichi\'s gold medal is also half of my credit, right?\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi really can\'t refute this, Amamiya Noriko named three sticks in front to add fuel, and the three almost ran and flew.\n\nThe results completely beat other opponents. At the same time, he broke the record of the men\'s 4x100 relay in the first year of Didan Middle School.\n\nKudo Shinichi frowned slightly, feeling that it was not easy for Noriko Amamiya to cheer, how did you chase after three 100-meter sprinters to cheer? ? ?\n\nIs it okay to be a normal girl? !\n\nKudo Shinichi was in a complicated mood. He didn\'t want to stay beside Akiko Amamiya to continue his project. He didn\'t have just one relay race. Noriko Amamiya had two gold medals. He could fall behind like that.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted and asked Xiaolan and Sonoko to cheer him on, while he was using an excuse to take a rest, and then went to the school sports meeting to cheer on him.\n\nI feel that it is very effective, so the school sports meet again and again cannot be missed.\n\nThe school sports meeting lasted for more than one day, but on the second day of the school sports meeting, Noriko Amamiya had a fever and did not come.\n\nBecause of the heroic confession of the one-two-three classmates that day, he refused.\n\nThen I had a low-grade fever of 39 degrees +, and I wanted to go to school with a bang, but was pushed back to the bed by Ch