(433, 5, 95, 'Chapter 94: : Are you excited?', 'Seeing Vodka watching the wine silently, daring not to drink or say anything, Amamiya Noriko laughed out loud.\n\nAfter frightening three bottles of real and fake wine, Amamiya Noriko was very happy.\n\nShe took a look and saw that the fat police officer from Nancun was still on the pedestrian side of the police, chatting with some wealthy businessmen or celebrities, including Zongshan Kenzo.\n\nThe old man didn\'t know whether he had a mission or was invited by Suzuki, so Amamiya Noriko didn\'t bother the old man, and went to the backstage to take a look.\n\nHer parents were chatting with the Suzuki family, and there were no other suspicious persons present, so there was no problem.\n\nMy father left the banquet, but Jin Jiu didn\'t follow or confirm his position. Obviously, Jin Jiu\'s goal is not his father.\n\nAt present, there are still two people who have not figured out the goals and tasks. One is Tou Zi, who is always running around there as a waiter. I really can\'t see who his goal is.\n\nThe other is Zhu Fu Jingguang, who left without seeing anyone after spending a while in the background with the audio equipment staff. Don\'t know where to go.\n\nBased on the current situation, the three people, Zhufu Jingguang, Touko, and Akai Shuichi may have acted together, but now it seems that Akai Shuichi\'s task is Takashi Nanmura, and he has already completed and left.\n\nThe remaining Touzi and Zhufu Jingguang may be working together to complete a task.\n\nKantoko doesn\'t seem to be in a hurry, the mission probably started after the gem was exhibited.\n\nAmamiya Noriko circled around the arena and determined that Zhufu Jingguang was indeed not on this floor. She took the elevator to the next floor, which was the sixty-fifth floor, which was the vault where the showcases and gems were stored.\n\nSimilarly, the central control room is also on this floor.\n\nI noticed it when I came down with Sonoko.\n\nShe asked Yuanzi, there are two central control rooms in the Suzuki Building, one is on this floor and the other is in the basement. The two central control rooms can also monitor each other, just to prevent someone from controlling the central control room.\n\nWhether it\'s sabotage or what you\'re going to do, the monitoring room is an important place. There are too many pictures of all the security personnel in the monitoring room being dealt with. The dangers of being on duty in the monitoring room are among the highest.\n\nHalfway down the elevator, she thought for a while. If the central control room had been controlled, the camera at the back and top of the elevator would be watching her go down to the sixty-fifth floor for no reason.\n\nSo, as if she had pressed the wrong button, she pressed the first floor again.\n\nWhen the elevator reached the fifty-sixth floor, she didn\'t move. She closed the door and continued down, as if nothing had happened.\n\nBut in a place where the camera at the top of the back can\'t see, Amamiya Noriko\'s hands are constantly operating on the buttons of the mobile phone, and touch-type emails at high speed - Matsuda Jinhei.\n\nIn the central control room on the sixty-fifth floor, Zhu Fu Jingguang was looking at the surveillance images on every screen in front of him to see if there was anything unusual, as if he was a security guard on duty in a real surveillance room.\n\nIt\'s just that there are a few real monitors in the monitoring room.\n\nHe was sorry, but in order to stalk undercover in the organization, he had to knock them out first.\n\nIt was shot at the same time as Rye Whiskey. A moment ago, Rye Whiskey transported Target No. 1 to the basement, and at the same time, he took down the central control room at the same time.\n\nNow the entire Suzuki Building is under their control.\n\n\"Buzz-\"\n\nThe mobile phone in his pocket vibrated suddenly, Zhu Fu Jingguang glanced at the monitoring screen, and there was nothing unusual. In the elevator, only the little girl was still looking at the elevator floors and noticed a few floors.\n\nHe took out his phone and glanced at it, his eyes narrowed slightly.\n\nShe looked at the contents of the email with a complicated mood.\n\n\"Good afternoon~ Are you in the central control room?\"\n\nThe sender is a mailbox with no clue at all. The only contact is a good morning he sent before, and the other party did not respond.\n\n\"Who the **** is this person? He knew my real name last time and knew that I was undercover. Now, do you even know my whereabouts?\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang frowned slightly, if it weren\'t for the fact that the other party didn\'t seem to have any malicious intentions, in order to avoid an accident in the undercover operation, which would involve Jiang Gu Ling, he would have quit the undercover operation at this time.\n\nAfter thinking carefully about everyone I met at the banquet, there didn\'t seem to be any very suspicious people.\n\n\"Looking at this tone, the other party should be a woman.\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang put his hand to his chin and thought for a while, but he really couldn\'t think of anything.\n\n\"Just reply, maybe, maybe she will come to me.\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang turned back, and then stared at anyone on the monitor who looked down at the phone or reacted with any action.\n\nBut nothing unusual was found. The only moving elevator was the little girl who got out of the elevator when she got to the first floor. She had a pretty dress and looked soft, so she definitely couldn\'t put her phone.\n\nAfter pretending to look around, Amamiya Noriko went to the toilet on the first floor to check her emails, and Zhufu Jingguang\'s little cutie confessed quite honestly.\n\nWell, Shuuichi Akai is probably also in the central control room. If the two central control rooms were invaded differently, they would have been directly exposed and invaded under the nose of the other central control room.\n\n\"I did my homework very well. I also know that there are two central control rooms, but it can be seen from the fact that Xiuyi has done everything to the team leader.\"\n\nI went down to confirm the location of Akai Shuichi and Zhufu Jingguang, and then Amamiya Noriko went back to take the elevator. Of course, she would not take the VIP elevator. Chianti and Cohen looked at the elevator with sniper scope. The feeling of taking the elevator is definitely not very good. it is good.\n\nJust as someone was about to close the elevator door after entering, Noriko Amamiya floated in a few steps.\n\n\"...\"\n\nIn the elevator, the boy who had already pressed the door close button stared blankly at the girl wearing a dress fluttering in.\n\nAfter coming in, Qingfeng seemed to have a faint scent, which made him subconsciously stare at Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head and looked at the boy who was stunned.\n\nA suit with a bow tie doesn\'t fit very well, it looks rather ordinary, and it belongs to the kind that can\'t be found in the pile of shame.\n\nAnd is this a stunned look? Young man, you look a bit young, you have to make a bold confession.\n\n  \"Hello?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised a smile and said lightly.\n\n\"You, hello...\"\n\nFacing the smiling face of Noriko Amamiya, the boy was embarrassed after speaking, and quickly turned his eyes away to see the number of floors the elevator had reached.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the number of layers he pressed, \"You\'re going to the banquet too, right? I\'m going too.\"\n\nThe boy nodded embarrassedly: \"Well... Actually, I\'m not very good at this kind of situation...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko patted him on the shoulder and said generously: \"It\'s alright, I\'ll take you. Boys are so shy, but few girls like them.\"\n\nThe young man looked at the beautiful girl in front of him and winked at him, with her playful and cute appearance, and with the soft hands on his shoulders, his heart could not help beating, and his nose could not help sour.\n\nBecause of her introversion, no girl has ever taken the initiative to talk to her and comfort her so much...\n\nFrom the reddish eyes to the tears in his eyes, the boy choked out his difficult and sad past.\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"...\"\n\nBoy, are you Lin Daiyu?\n\nThere is no way, sometimes, her charm will indeed become a burden.\n\nIt\'s too easy to shock people who don\'t usually feel love. It\'s really touching that such a beautiful person actually treats him like this.\n\nNext time you are a motivational teacher, you should also grasp the strength, otherwise it will not be good to cry human milk.\n\nWhile he was still crying and didn\'t pay attention, Amamiya Noriko took out a disposable handkerchief specially designed for comfort.\n\nReaching out his hand, he gently wiped the tears for this young man with an attribute point, and said softly, \"Don\'t cry, don\'t cry, if you cry like this, someone will be sad for you.\"\n\nLooking at the beautiful girl in front of him, who was obviously younger than him, but looked distressed for him, the attribute point boy seemed to be hit by an arrow, and the arrow of Cupid, the **** of love, pierced his heart fiercely.\n\nHow could he be so weak, how could he continue to be so weak, making her worry about herself and feel bad for herself?\n\nIn his stubborn heart, he wiped his tears with his own hands, and there were tears in the corners of his eyes. He seriously said to Noriko Amamiya, \"In order not to make you sad, I won\'t cry in the future!\"\n\nAs if it was because the boy\'s words had initially expressed his intentions, Amamiya Noriko blushed a little embarrassedly, and the young man lost his mind because of her bright and unpretentious appearance.\n\nBoy, what I said is not to make your parents sad, I won\'t be sad, but don\'t be in a daze, hurry up and confess.\n\nAmamiya Noriko put the disposable handkerchief to him, and said in a resentful tone, \"Don\'t say anything for any girl, just be yourself and follow your heart.\"\n\n  \"My regards...\"\n\nHolding the handkerchief in his hand, the young man was dazed, until the elevator reached the top floor, and saw that Amamiya Noriko was about to leave the elevator. With a distressed look.\n\nHe finally had the courage to express his heart, and boldly said to Noriko Amamiya: \"I like you! Can we be together? You are the most gentle girl I have ever met!\"\n\nThe boy\'s eyes were filled with courage, looking forward to Amamiya Noriko\'s response.\n\nAmamiya Noriko walked out of the elevator gently, the bow on the single ponytail showed cuteness and liveliness, turned to look at him, the boy was excited.\n\n\"I\'m sorry, but it\'s the first time we met. If we agreed, it would be too hasty with you. Besides, maybe one day, you will meet a girl more gentle than me?\"\n\nAs Amamiya Noriko\'s gentle words fell, the sight in front of him was slowly blocked by the closed elevator door, and the young man\'s heart was empty for a while, the arrow of Cupid, the **** of love, plucked out of his heart with a puff.\n\nHowever, he stuck the arrow in his heart abruptly, and said to himself firmly: Whether she likes me or not, refuses or agrees, I will like her!\n\nThe boy took a deep breath, reached out and pressed the button to open the door, ready to chase the beautiful figure, but found that the elevator was going down. It seemed that someone on the first floor was about to use the elevator, so he called the elevator down again.\n\n  \"Do not--!!!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko vaguely heard the screams coming from the elevator shaft. Could it be that the elevator fell down?\n\nShe just hurriedly pressed the door closing button a few times to make the elevator door close earlier to end her confession?\n\nWith 1 point of strength, she became stronger again.\n\nMake sure that the speed of the elevator going down is normal, and everyone is fine, so Noriko Amemiya will not care. The host of the banquet has already spoken on the stage, and everyone at the banquet faces the stage with their glasses up.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko noticed that Vodka seemed to have just sat down and said something to Gin. Gin nodded, and then turned to look at the place where Fatty Nanmura was watching.\n\nThe policeman was smugly holding up a woman, and he was probably also boasting about his achievements. He may not have found out that his son had already been killed by Noriko Amemiya. Where is it tied, I have to interrogate it later.\n\n\"What did vodka do?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the crowd on the vodka side, because the vodka was quite big, and most of the places she walked through needed other guests to make way, so she could see the approximate route.\n\nIt seems that he just came back from the window on the side.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, the window in that direction seems to be the window in the direction of Chianti and Cohen.\n\nBecause there are floor-to-ceiling windows on the top floor, and the curtains are not drawn up, you can see the scenery looking down from the sixty-sixth floor by the window, and there are floor-to-ceiling curtains on both sides of the glass windows.\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at a slightly fluttering curtain over there~www.readwn.com~ Vodka should put something behind the curtain, it can\'t be seen in the banquet hall, but Chianti and Cohen on the top floor of their own building Naturally, it can be seen from the sniper scope.\n\nShe couldn\'t go over to take a look. Vodka would still check from time to time to make sure no one was going to destroy his arrangement.\n\nThe vigilant Noriko Amamiya was not very interested in saving him, so it was time for him to start preparing to steal his gems.\n\nGo back to Sonoko\'s room to get the equipment.\n\nAs soon as he walked to the corner of Sonoko\'s room, he saw Kudo Shinichi rubbing the back of his neck and leaning against the wall in great pain. It seemed that Shuuichi Akai had controlled his strength a lot in order to ensure that he could faint.\n\n  \"Are you OK...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko stretched out her hand to help him, and said in a caring tone.\n\n\"It\'s alright, just a small problem.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi waved his hand and didn\'t care at all. He just took a closer look at the pretty girl in front of him, and then asked aloud, \"Did you notice anything strange at the banquet?\"\n\n\"No, what I want to say, it seems that there is a boy in the elevator who feels a little strange and is very emotional. Well, are you really all right?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head, as if she thought about it carefully, and then cared about Kudo Shinichi again.\n\nKudo Shinichi reiterated that it was all right, and without giving her a chance, he went to the elevator to have a look.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted. It turns out that Kudo Shinichi is not only targeting her, but also completely indifferent to other girls. It\'s too straight. Wouldn\'t such a beautiful girl care about you so much?\n\n\"Did it come from shaking?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko doubted.');
