(434, 5, 86, 'Chapter 85: : Hey, I\'m looking forward to it', '\"I didn\'t do anything.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her hand innocently to prove her innocence. Could she have predicted that Xiaolan came in and put on an aggrieved expression in advance? Pure coincidence.\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s nerves are too sharp, is this a detective?\n\nBecause Shinichi was already riddled with holes and had a tenacious mind facing death with indifference and tranquility, Amamiya Noriko took the initiative to explain to Xiaolan: \"Shinichi really didn\'t bully me this time.\"\n\n\"I never bullied you!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi held his mouth shut and couldn\'t speak well. Anyway, Amamiya Noriko found out once, and this was what he attracted.\n\nAfter hearing Noriko Amamiya\'s explanation, Xiaolan patted Shinichi with satisfaction: \"Shinichi, you should do this in the future, and you get along well with Noriko.\"\n\n  \"Ha ha.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi smiled reluctantly. He was very easy to get along with. It depends on when Noriko Amamiya\'s character is not so bad.\n\nThinking about it, he even saw Amamiya Noriko wink his left eye secretly at him, as if they had a tacit understanding, Kudo Shin once rolled his eyes.\n\n\"Shut up.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko immediately pulled Xiaolan and Sonoko away to chat about the weekend banquet of the Suzuki Foundation.\n\nWhen school was over in the afternoon, Amamiya Noriko was going to leave Kudo Shin for a taste of being alone, and then give him another chance.\n\nWho knew that Kudo Shinichi took out a football with his backhand and was about to go to work in the community.\n\n\"I\'m meow, straight enough...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko went back and dragged Kudo Shinichi on board. She would rather go to play with a group of guys from the football club and not know how to keep up. Then you should follow me.\n\nAnyway, the four of them screwed up everything in the ministry.\n\n  go shopping.\n\nThis was discussed by the three of Noriko Xiaolan Yuanzi in the morning.\n\nThe banquet of the Suzuki chaebols is relatively formal, and after the last meeting between the Suzuki family and the Amamiya family, Xiao Lan felt that she would also dress a little more formal this time, but her clothes were relatively small.\n\nSonoko naturally proposed to buy it.\n\nDon\'t look at Yuanzi going out to take the bus or tram, but there is still money to be had, and he went to a shopping mall in which the Suzuki consortium has shares. a moment.\n\nOf course, you can only buy things in the mall, which her father Shiro Suzuki gave her to entertain her friends.\n\nSonoko doesn\'t have much pocket money, so this is a local tyrant experience card.\n\nThis time, Noriko Amamiya was with her. Her dresses and kimonos are not bad at home. In addition to her online appearance, Amamiya Emi is eating and sleeping, and then shopping. Buying clothes for her daughter is one of the more interesting ones. an item?\n\nTo tell the truth, her mother Amamiya Emi is definitely the most carefree person. She has a super rich and loving husband. She is beautiful and tender-faced. Her daughter is also... her daughter is grown up. She\'s cute but her behavior isn\'t cute at all, and she rarely feels like she\'s a mother herself.\n\nHowever, although her daughter\'s personality and behavior are not very cute, her clothes are still cute, so Emi Amamiya is very interested in buying clothes for her daughter, usually mother and daughter... ah, no, it\'s sister clothes.\n\nKiko Amamiya\'s cute clothes are basically from her.\n\nWith a large wardrobe full of them, Amamiya Noriko occasionally has to turn to the bottom to wear a handsome dress, which is more difficult than digging for diamonds.\n\nShe also buys most of the dresses and kimonos, because Emi Amamiya herself is sometimes the image spokesperson of the Amemiya Foundation, and she also wears dresses when she attends banquets, and it is often a matter of time for her daughter.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was watching Kudo Shinichi being at the mercy of Sonoko and Xiaolan. As the only boy, she was not very active and willing to choose formal clothes. She had pockets in her pockets and looked like I could wear anything. Xiaolan and How could the garden let him go?\n\nAmamiya Noriko also dressed him, with a white shirt as a base, a azure blue dress, and a red bow tie...\n\n\"What a strange match this is!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi subconsciously felt that there must be something wrong with Noriko Amamiya\'s selection, and was very resistant.\n\n  \"cut.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko is scornful. When you become Conan\'s little brother, I will see if you will dress like this.\n\nLet Xiaolan and Sonoko step up their efforts and give Kudo Shinichi the best fit, while Amamiya Noriko went to the side to pick the earrings.\n\nShe didn\'t have her ears pierced, so she had fewer choices.\n\nThe shopping guide introduced her to her in a gentle and graceful manner, and Amamiya Noriko looked at her casually, glancing at her face from time to time. This short-haired and capable woman has traces of disguise, because some care about her professional smile every time she smiles. radians are kept within certain limits.\n\nNo matter how professional shopping guides don\'t have to be so professional, it can only be to limit the reason why they don\'t show their original smile.\n\nBecause if a simple disguise technique is used to greatly change the facial appearance, an excessively large smile may destroy the disguise technique, and the second is to show a skilled smile, which is at risk of being seen through by acquaintances.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thinks it is the second type, because the disguise technique is very good, she can\'t see the remaining traces very much, she can only judge that the smile is very deliberate.\n\nShe continued to look at the earrings while observing, and first confirmed that it was indeed a woman, at least a lot of men were pretending to be women.\n\nThere are basically three women who are good at disguise in the world of Conan, Kudo Shinichi\'s mother, Kudo Yukiko, and then Belmod, both of whom are under the tutelage of Kuroba Piichi.\n\nThe last one, her mistress Chikage Kuroba.\n\nAmamiya Noriko knew that it was impossible for Sister Pei to appear in front of her to tease her at this time, so it could only be Yukiko Kudo and Chikage Kuroba.\n\nYukiko Kudo...Although she knows how to play, she probably won\'t come to tease her.\n\nAfter the elimination method was completed, Amamiya Noriko said, \"Master, is there anything you need to come to see me?\"\n\n\"As expected of Noriko, she has a good eye.\"\n\nThe female shopping guide who introduced the earrings smiled slightly and praised Noriko Amamiya.\n\n\"Although Kiko is the youngest disciple of Pioneer, his level is already very high.\"\n\n\"It\'s alright, if Shi Niang\'s makeup is serious, maybe I still won\'t recognize it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko spreads her hands, obviously she is throwing water, so easy to see through, if it is real, the gender of the shopping guide should be male, and the hairstyle will not be this short hair directly, maybe the face is darker and the body is stronger. So what can Amamiya Noriko guess, she has never been in the alchemy furnace, and usually rarely sees other people\'s disguise techniques.\n\nKuroba Chikage refused to make herself too ugly.\n\n\"This time I came here mainly to see how Noriko is doing. I\'m relieved to see that Noriko is quite energetic and has good friends.\"\n\n\"Master, what\'s your next plan?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded and asked.\n\nAs for whether Black Feather Pirate is really dead, it\'s hard to ask, maybe he is really on his honeymoon with his wife?\n\nKuroba Chikage smiled slightly: \"Maybe in a while, I\'m going to work abroad. Noriko can go to Kuaidou to play.\"\n\n  \"Um.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, it seemed that she was going to work in Las Vegas, or to secretly investigate the organization that assassinated Kuroba Rouichi, or to go on a honeymoon.\n\nShe really can\'t determine which one it is. There are still some differences between the original book and the current world. At least she originally paid attention to the time when her teacher was assassinated, but it happened suddenly, and she couldn\'t react. At that time I can\'t do much in elementary school.\n\nKuroba Chikage chatted with her husband\'s little disciple for a while, gave her a pair of earrings, and left quietly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the direction she was leaving. Chikage Kuroba was actually more sophisticated as a thief than Kuroba Rouichi, and it was also the factor that made Kuroba Rouichi become the phantom thief Kid.\n\nAt first, Noriko Amamiya also thought about asking her to learn skills, but since Kuroba Roiichi brought her to her door when she was in elementary school, there was no way.\n\nIt\'s not bad to be Sister Bei\'s little junior sister.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a look at the earrings that her mistress gave her. The black feathers carved from obsidian are quite delicate and beautiful. They sparkle in the dark under the light. The price must be expensive, but it is symbolic. bigger.\n\nThe handsome Noriko Amamiya said she liked it very much.\n\nAmamiya Noriko put away the earrings, but when she put her hand in her mouth, she found a small box that looked like a business card case.\n\nShe found a corner and took it out to take a look.\n\nOn the top of the small box is the Kaido Kid\'s logo. To be honest, Kaikai Kid\'s icon is quite cute.\n\nAmong them, the card is a card with a white background, the icon of the phantom thief Kid and \'phantom thief キッド\' in the lower right corner, the three words \'to complain\' at the top of the middle, and the content below is blank.\n\nOn the back is a slightly larger icon of Kaito Kid in the center.\n\n\"Wow, does this mean that I\'m already an officially certified Kaitou Kid?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked around and was quite surprised.\n\nBut she saw a small note caught in the lid of the name-brand box: \"Don\'t play too early.\"\n\nLooking at the handwriting, it was Kuroba Pioneer.\n\nThis is something that Amamiya Noriko did not expect. Although Kuroba Rouichi\'s identity was disclosed to Amamiya Noriko, Amamiya Noriko would not tell others that Kuroba Rouichi also taught the disguise technique tacitly. At the same time, other technologies will also be Amamiya Noriko.\n\nBut I really didn\'t expect that Kuroba Piichi would have already prepared this for her.\n\nThis means that Amamiya Noriko can act as a phantom thief Kid.\n\nAlthough it\'s not too early to say...\n\nDid she allow her to do things when she was an adult? Or maybe after graduating high school?\n\nAmamiya Noriko thinks it should be the latter. After all, Kuroba Pioneer knows that her learning ability is beyond ordinary people\'s speed. When she becomes an adult, what\'s the point of her driving a full-level number. If she wants to steal, the Sonoko family\'s vault is probably will shiver.\n\n\"Thank you so much, teacher.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said sincerely, and backhandedly wrote the notice of stealing the gem from the Suzuki chaebol on the blank notification letter from Kaitou Kid.\n\nYou didn\'t want to steal something from a good friend\'s house, so when you turn around, \"this is not the gem I want, I will return the original\", right?\n\nJust as her debut battle, Kuroba Chikage happened to send something, and the Suzuki consortium wanted to show off gems. Isn\'t this, is it clear that she wants to appear?\n\n\"Niko seems to be in a good mood? Did you buy anything good?\"\n\nSonoko found that Kiko, who had returned, seemed to be in a very good mood, so she couldn\'t help asking.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled and shook her head: \"There are good things, but they are not bought.\"\n\nAt the same time, there is still a little guilt, Sonoko, my good sister, let me touch the gems of your house, I will rest assured that I will pay them back.\n\nShe touched her chin, and she had to prepare a dress.\n\nKudo Shinichi noticed the involuntarily raised corners of Noriko Amamiya\'s mouth, and was extremely vigilant in his heart, thinking that it was not something good happened, but something good to do, right?\n\nHe knew the smile of Noriko Amamiya too well.\n\nAfter shopping with Xiaolan Yuanzi Shinichi, Amamiya Noriko went to make custom clothes. There is no need to find outsiders. Her cousin, Chieda Riho, is very good at sewing. Sewing is only one of the thousands of skills that Chieda Riho knows. item.\n\nAs the person who Amamiya Ludou personally selected and arranged for his daughter, Chieda Riho said that he was one in 100,000 miles.\n\nChieda Riho received a strange request from her young lady, but she didn\'t ask why. There were too many strange requests. It was not a trivial matter to make a dress. She made the finished product after a few days of work.\n\nShe is not the only one, she is the chief executive of Noriko Amamiya, and there are people under her command. She makes the key parts by herself, and the rest of the production is fine.\n\nAnyway, when she finally looked at the finished product, she sighed, Noriko, why did she become addicted to fancy clothes, but when the lovely Noriko wears this dress, her style is very different.\n\nMaybe there will be a little contrast.\n\nYou can still look forward to it~www.readwn.com~ On the other hand, Amamiya Noriko not only went to Chieda Riho to make clothes, she also went to see Dr. Akasa.\n\nDr. Akasa, that is the best tool man. In fact, some of the equipment of Kaito Kidd came from the hands of Dr.Agasa, a friend of Kaneko Terai, the assistant of Kaitou Kidd.\n\nOf course it was believed.\n\nAmamiya Noriko asked Dr. Aga to make a paraglider. There is no way to make a paraglider the same as the Kaitou Kid. The only thing I can do is change it to another style. Anyway, the requirement is to shrink and open quickly, enough to slide dozens of floors, right? Gotta make it before the weekend, I\'m going to play on the weekend.\n\nIt\'s just to satisfy her curiosity as a child. If she doesn\'t do it, I think you, Dr. Aga, are a little fatter? Obesity can cause many symptoms. Is it time to control your weight or lose weight?\n\nI can totally ask a dedicated nutritionist to help Dr. make a good plan for you?\n\nMy Amamiya family has money, what is a nutritionist, ten!\n\nPlus five fitness trainers?\n\nDr. A Li was really afraid of this little girl, and hurriedly made a paraglider for her to play with before the weekend. Who can stand such a toss at an age?\n\nAmamiya Noriko left with satisfaction. Well, even if she doesn\'t ask Dr. to lose weight, she will be able to do so in the future. Doctor, let\'s be cool for a few years now.\n\nFinally, on the weekend, Amamiya Noriko packed up and went out to the newly topped-out building of the Suzuki Foundation.\n\nAnyway, it\'s an unremarkable building with dozens of floors. If you have money, you\'re done.\n\nAt the entrance of the hall at the bottom of the building, there are two rows of security guards standing guard and checking the invitations of guests entering and leaving. Even the ceremonial post feels level.\n\n\"Hey, I\'m looking forward to it.\"\n\n​​'),
(435, 5, 61, 'Chapter 60: :Spring is coming', 'Counting that day, Amamiya Noriko\'s physique suddenly increased to 3 points.\n\nIn terms of appearance, there is a relatively significant improvement.\n\nAmamiya Noriko had to put on a little make-up. After a few days of fever, her face was radiant.\n\nBut to make herself ugly, Amamiya Noriko will definitely not be able to do it, so she is still a little bit prettier.\n\nIn fact, Amamiya Noriko always believed that it had nothing to do with being beautiful or not, but temperament was the most important thing.\n\nEven if you are weak, yawning is fascinating. This is temperament.\n\n\"Amamiya-san, you...you\'re a lot more beautiful, aren\'t you?\"\n\nAt the school gate, a girl noticed the slight changes in Noriko Amamiya, and felt that her skin was much better, so she couldn\'t help but wonder.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked puzzled, but she still pursed her small mouth and said restrainedly: \"No way, it\'s just that I haven\'t seen each other for two days. Then, senior, I\'ll go first.\"\n\n\"Mmmm, let\'s go... It\'s nice to be young, her skin is pink and smooth, and she\'s super delicate. She deserves to be the first-year little beauty of Amamiya.\"\n\nHer friend nodded: \"And also fascinated the boys who only know sports.\"\n\nSenior Sister covered her mouth and smiled, \"But I heard that all the confessions were rejected.\"\n\n\"Amamiya seems to be quite familiar with that boy. Look, I went to talk again.\"\n\n\"Oh?\" Senior Sister hurriedly turned to look.\n\nHere is Noriko Amamiya who discovered Shinichi Kudo.\n\nShe wiped off her makeup, and then patted Kudo Shinichi from behind.\n\nKudo Shinichi basically knew who it was from his strength. He turned his head calmly and looked at Amamiya Ji... Who are you? Is it Akiko Amemiya?\n\nYou went to evolve in two days? ? ?\n\nKudo Shinichi can still recognize Kiko Amemiya in every detail, but it is obvious that the change is not small, he frowned: \"Have you put on makeup?\"\n\n  \"No.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko threw away the makeup remover in her hand.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at the little white ball rolling away behind her, and frowned. This person really doesn\'t need to write drafts when he speaks. Do you think he is blind?\n\nHe has a vision of 5.0 and doesn\'t need glasses at all.\n\nKudo Shinichi pretended not to see it, and said calmly, \"It\'s too early for you to put on makeup.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko flexibly took out an eyebrow pencil between her slender fingers and said confidently, \"I can make you 20 degrees more handsome.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pouted. As a detective, he does not give in to things like appearance. Wisdom, keen observation, and reasoning ability are the weapons of a detective.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pursed her lips and said aggrievedly, \"I only removed my makeup to show you.\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nKudo Shin was immune to her aggrieved soft voice, but vaguely sensed something was wrong.\n\nUntil she saw Noriko Amamiya take out a slap-sized makeup box, wiped it with her bare hands in the small mirror, and spread the cream evenly on her face with an incomprehensible technique, Noriko Amamiya was originally dazzling and pretty. It was as if the light was blocked.\n\nHe just came to understand, nodded and said seriously, \"put more makeup on.\"\n\n\"The family is still young, and makeup is not good for the skin.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko closed her vanity case and rolled her eyes at him.\n\nHowever, most of her cosmetics were produced by Kuroba Pirates.\n\nIf there is a secret recipe, the damage to the skin will probably be minus 5. Washing the face with tap water may cause more damage.\n\nHow could Kuroba Rouichi let her precious apprentice suffer damage? Belmod and Yukiko Kudo are both his students, but Noriko Amamiya is the only real apprentice.\n\nMainly, Amamiya Noriko\'s learning ability was relatively high at the time, and she learned very quickly. Even if she went there from time to time, she could feel her obvious improvement.\n\nKuroba Piichi has no idea of ​​hiding anything from the children. Since you can learn it, I will teach it.\n\nSooner or later, Amamiya Noriko was also one of the criminals who pretended to be the phantom thief Kid.\n\nBut she doesn\'t steal gems, only hearts.\n\nAfter all, let\'s not talk about girls, and there are many male mothers of Kaitou Kid, right?\n\nAs soon as Kudo Shin heard the teasing tone of Noriko Amamiya, he knew that the makeup had no effect.\n\nThinking about it carefully, Amamiya Noriko has been unwilling to bask in the sun since kindergarten. When asked why, Amamiya Noriko said she didn\'t want to get tan.\n\nAfter all, there was Touko Jingjizhen before, and Osaka Black Chicken in the back. Touko is okay to say that the skin is not tanned, but Osaka Black Chicken made me understand a truth~www.readwn.com~ The sun in this world, ultraviolet rays, is very poisonous.\n\nThe last time Noriko Amamiya went to see the cherry blossoms, she had at least two bottles of sunscreen spray and three bottles of moisturizing spray in her bag.\n\nKnowing that Amamiya Noriko cherishes her good looks so much, he knew that there was no problem.\n\nSo I still encourage Noriko Amamiya to wear more makeup.\n\nAlthough it was because she was too good-looking, she was still a little upset. After school, Amamiya Noriko asked Xiaolan Yuanzi to sing karaoke.\n\nThat\'s a place where Shinichi Kudo is forbidden to enter.\n\nOn the other hand, in school, she put on a little makeup, and the classmates could still see that Amamiya-san was a little more cute.\n\nIt can be considered that I haven\'t seen each other for two days and I miss him quite a bit, but it is certain that Amamiya becomes more beautiful day by day.\n\nAnd no one has ever successfully confessed.\n\nTherefore, just a month after the start of school, many seniors who are still watching see the gratifying growth and are ready to buy Amamiya stocks.\n\nSpecifically, for a long time to come, many seniors confessed to Noriko Amemiya.\n\nMoreover, these people also vaguely agreed that they had a tacit understanding, and rarely said that concentrating on one day would cause her trouble.\n\nThen the days when Noriko Amamiya caught a cold and fever started again...\n\nShe asked for leave for half a month in a month, and she still went to school in some cases. The school doctor from the health room took her own initiative to take her temperature in the classroom.\n\n\"Little Amamiya, your immunity has yet to be improved. Why do you catch colds so frequently?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t understand much either. After thinking about it, maybe this is spring.\n\nThe school doctor\'s sister nodded: \"Spring is indeed a time when influenza is more frequent.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, I like spring.\n\n​​'),
(436, 5, 25, 'Chapter 24: :shot!', 'A white pickup makes a sharp turn through a mountain bend.\n\n\"Bang.\"\n\nThe unconscious Amamiya Noriko felt a pain in her head. When she opened her eyes, it was still pitch black, and her eyes were covered with a layer of cloth.\n\nThe mouth was also sealed with tape.\n\nHis hands were wrapped with tape behind his back, and his legs were also wrapped with tape at the ankles.\n\n\"It\'s too rough, but the kidnapping was successful.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was still a little numb. She prepared such a large pack of outdoor survival equipment, but she was **** like this.\n\nThe place was shaking, obviously in the car, and it wasn\'t the closed feeling in the car, it could only be in the back of the pickup.\n\nShe often rolls around in turns and turns, and it seems that she is still in the suburbs where there are a lot of turns.\n\n\"Fortunately, my constitution is 16.\"\n\nI didn\'t drive too far, which means I woke up quickly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko found that her body was not tied up, only her ankles and wrists were tied, so she had something to eat.\n\nHer body is extremely flexible, her knees are curled up, and her hands behind her back are moved from the soles of her feet to the front of her.\n\nThen he bit the tape wrapped around his wrist with his teeth.\n\nSo many colds and fevers are not in vain, the little dog\'s teeth are torn apart several layers of tape.\n\nAfter his hands resumed activity, he undid the blindfolded cloth as soon as possible, and his vision suddenly opened up, as expected, it was in the body of a pickup truck.\n\nAt this time, he was driving at a high speed, and he didn\'t care about the continuous curves at all, and his driving skills were not inferior.\n\nAfter undoing the bandages on her feet, Amamiya Noriko regained complete freedom.\n\nFrom the rear window, you can see the man sitting in the passenger seat and the woman driving.\n\n\"Electrically numb me, I\'ll let you taste it later.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head to look around, she still had an impression of this mountain, and at this speed it was still about half an hour\'s drive from returning to the city.\n\n\"Hello? The target has been caught. A little accident happened, but it\'s not a big problem. Where to send it? OK.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko suddenly heard the man\'s voice on the phone, and hung up the phone after a very succinct conversation.\n\nYou can only hear what kind of employment or order the other party received to arrest her. After she is caught, she will be informed of the location to be sent to. The order can be ruled out. It should be hired, and there is no complete trust relationship with the person behind her.\n\nIn order to avoid being seen in the rearview mirror, Amamiya Noriko could only lean her head with her head tilted. How to solve it?\n\nThe woman driving the car said, \"Where are you going to send it over there?\"\n\n\"It turned out to be the No. 2 location. Well, I have already done an investigation, and the situation there is clear.\"\n\nThe woman chuckled and said, \"Hehehe, are you still afraid of attacking us?\"\n\nThe man said coldly, \"Of course, we are his evidence.\"\n\nThen the two lost their voices.\n\nWhen Amamiya Noriko heard this, she thought that if you were the evidence of the crime, then there would be no need for trouble.\n\nBut how to do it is a problem. There are also four seats in the pickup truck. There are two seats in the front driver\'s seat, two seats in the back, and then the body where she is.\n\nHow does the car deal with the two guys in front of you while it\'s driving?\n\nAmamiya Noriko climbed onto the roof of the car, lowered her body and held both sides of the roof tightly with both hands to avoid being thrown off when turning, and she was careful to make noises.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s cap was blown away by the wind, and her hair fluttered in the wind, which made her feel extremely bad.\n\n\"This should be what Spider-Man should do.\"\n\nThe man sitting in the passenger seat lit a cigarette, took a deep breath, put his arms with the cigarette **** between his fingers on the window, and took a breath out of the open window.\n\n  \"Um?\"\n\nSuddenly, he noticed that the shadow of the car was abnormal, and saw a white hand swiftly poking in from the car window, strangling his throat to death, unable to breathe.\n\nHe could clearly feel the entrapment between his fingers in several places, which was almost similar to when he was hit on the Adam\'s apple when he was on the mountain.\n\n\"Cough ka ka-\"\n\nHe opened his mouth wide, but he could only make a hoarse, dry cough.\n\nHe stared at this hand with wide eyes. At the same time, he grabbed it with two big hands and tried to take it away, but the strength of this finger was outrageous, and when it turned outward, it seemed to harden his Adam\'s apple It\'s normal to catch it.\n\nThe feeling of suffocation kept eroding his brain.\n\n\"Hurry up and stop me!!\"\n\nThe woman who was driving next to her hurriedly shouted, and at the same time she reached out to help, but she didn\'t know how to hold the steering wheel with one hand and was restrained by the seat belt.\n\nWhen she stepped on the clutch and brake, the pickup stopped in an emergency and rushed for a while due to inertia, and then she unfastened her seat belt and saw that the man had stopped moving, his hands were hanging down, and Noriko Amamiya leaned over there. The car window pointed a gun at her.\n\nLooking at the pitch-black muzzle, the woman laughed and said, \"Children, you can\'t fire bullets if you haven\'t pulled the hammer down?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head suspiciously, \"Sister, I haven\'t said that your guns are too old, but although the p220 is a gun from the 1970s, it is also single and double action, so the first bullet does not need to be overwhelmed. A hammer will do, too.\"\n\n\"It\'s just that the trigger pull is 4.5kg and the trigger travel is 13mm. If I press the hammer down, the trigger pull is 1.7kg and the trigger travel is 4mm. But for me, is there any difference between the two? And at such a close distance. UU reading www.uukanshu.com\"\n\nThe woman\'s face gradually turned blue, her face was stiff and she was speechless.\n\nThe car had already stopped, and Amamiya Noriko got off the roof, but the gun was still pointed at her: \"Take out the electric shock, it won\'t work this time.\"\n\nThe woman reached out and took out the electric shock from the inner pocket of the jacket, and Amamiya Noriko took it with the other hand.\n\nSeeing her left leg moving slightly, Amamiya Noriko gave a warning, \"I suggest that you don\'t release the clutch. This kind of old pickup with manual transmission will basically turn off when it starts in fifth gear.\"\n\nThe woman is silent: \"Well...\"\n\nAfter seeing this, Amamiya Noriko reached in through the car window and opened the car door from inside, preparing to throw the man out of the car first.\n\nBut the pickup truck suddenly moved, pinned her arm, and Amamiya Noriko shot directly, hitting the other door with a bang, and the other woman who had unbuckled her seat belt Hands lowered the seat back to dodge her first bullet.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s hand holding the gun was also knocked off by the advancing pickup, and the door that opened almost knocked her down.\n\n\"Rough!\"\n\nShe looked at the car that started in fifth gear and couldn\'t help but swear, how could she never do this when she took her driver\'s license test in her previous life!\n\nBut now it\'s really troublesome to let the other party run away, Amamiya Noriko raised her hand to aim at the tire.\n\nThe double-action pistol is already in a ready state after the first round of the hammer, so the trigger pull and stroke of her next shot are normal, and the accuracy will be higher.\n\n\"Bang! Boom! Bam!\"\n\nThree shots in a row hit the body or wiped from the bottom of the car. The speed of the pickup has been at least 40km. Because it is a .45 bullet, there are only 7 rounds. Amamiya Noriko feels that she is a novice who has not actually practiced shooting. The difficulty is too high.\n\nSo she just stared at the driver\'s seat.'),
(437, 5, 51, 'Chapter 50: : 3 Prince Charming', 'The camouflage man had a ghostly expression on his face.\n\nHow can everyone find themselves? Is the radar on?\n\nAnd Gu Ling was also surprised, I didn\'t expect it to hit, but isn\'t it just right?\n\nImmediately, he squeezed his fist, his eyes full of dangerous eyes.\n\n\"Do you have any last words you want to leave?\"\n\nThe camouflage man replied coldly, \"I\'m not going to leave any last words.\"\n\nHis chest, arms, and thighs still had the pain left by the man above, so in the face of this reconsideration of the enemy who was staring at him, he slowly fell to the ground and took out his tail dagger from his boots and held it backwards.\n\nJiang Gu Ling looked at him, this kind of short dagger is very useful in the jungle, carry it with you, it is indeed a mercenary in Southeast Asia.\n\nBut ah, he was wearing a doll costume before, so it was convenient to carry a gun.\n\nRei Furutani took out a pistol and pointed it at the opponent.\n\nThe camouflage man\'s face was expressionless, he let go of his hand and fell to the ground with the short dagger, and raised his hands.\n\nBeing pointed at by the HKP7M8, 9mm\'s pitch-black muzzle, this is the reaction that should be interesting.\n\nJiang Guling raised his chin: \"Where is she?\"\n\nThe camouflage man raised his hands and stared at the muzzle of his gun: \"It\'s too much to actually carry a gun with you.\"\n\nJiang Guling\'s patience was exhausted a bit: \"Would it be more excessive if I pierced your body while you were talking nonsense?\"\n\n\"This is the largest shopping mall nearby. Do you know how many people there are in a day?\"\n\nThe camouflage man gradually put his hands down and spread his arms as a reminder.\n\nIn a rather fearless tone.\n\n\"Aren\'t you more worried about being discovered by the police than me, a retired mercenary? No matter how useless the Japanese public security police are, they wouldn\'t allow a criminal who made a shooting case in such a place to escape, right?\"\n\n  \"yes?\"\n\nJiang Gu Ling raised the muzzle of the gun, \"Can\'t you see it clearly even if you are pointed at it by the muzzle?\"\n\nThe camouflage man raised his eyebrows, his eyes fell on the muzzle of the gun, and then his eyes gradually drifted away.\n\ntm is outrageous.\n\nThere are threads on the barrel, which means that a silencer can be installed, but who on the horse would specially modify the HKP7M9 to be able to install a silencer?\n\nCrazy.\n\nRei Furutani took out the black and long silencer from his pocket and put it on the muzzle of the gun casually, as if it was just for him to see.\n\nAs for the use of firearms, is it a problem for trough zero?\n\nHe is not only a Japanese public security policeman, but also a Bourbon of a black organization. He can use guns if it is reasonable and legal.\n\nThe camouflage man looked at the muzzle of the pistol with a silencer and surrendered.\n\n\"She was locked in the underground garage by me.\"\n\nWith a threatening gaze, Zero Tsubaki pointed a gun to signal him to walk in front: \"It\'s better to be true.\"\n\nAfter a while.\n\nKudo Shinichi and Xiaolan Yuanzi went up to the fifth floor, and his eyes fell on a man and a woman who seemed to be looking for someone.\n\nIntuition told him that there was a problem, but it took a lot of time to get up. The elevator was too busy to take the escalator all the way up, it was too slow.\n\nFrom the fifth floor to the sixth floor, the only way to go to the sixth floor is to take the stairs. Kudo Shinichi saw the silence in the stairwell, raised his hand to stop Xiaolan and Sonoko.\n\nThe door between the shopping mall and the escape stairs is very thick and the sound insulation effect is very good, and it also has a fire function. Once you enter the stairwell and the shopping mall, the noise is completely quiet.\n\nIt seemed a little strangely quiet.\n\nSonoko carefully grabbed Xiaolan\'s arm, the two leaned against each other, but still looked at the stairs going up.\n\n\"You guys go outside and wait. I\'ll just go up and take a look. If there is anything, just call the security guard at the mall.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi still left them on the fifth floor and walked up alone.\n\nSo far, he actually has no direct clues that can point to Amamiya Noriko being in danger, but that weird feeling is real.\n\nOn the sixth floor, he was about to open the door and go to the rooftop outside, but he paused and turned to look at a small utility room next to the stairs.\n\nThis door...\n\nBefore he could take a closer look, a sturdy man with dark skin in casual clothes rushed up and froze after seeing him.\n\n\"It won\'t come again...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi and him looked at each other and said first, \"Who are you?\"\n\n\"Little devil, it\'s none of your business, just go.\"\n\nSeeing that he was a normal teenager, the camouflage man was relieved, grabbed Kudo Shinichi with his big hand and pushed aside, and reached out to twist the door handle of the utility room.\n\nIt feels quite strange when twisted, as if it\'s stuck, and no matter how much you grit your teeth, you can\'t twist it.\n\nWhen he wanted to twist his hands hard, a light drink suddenly came from the door.\n\n  \"what-\"\n\nThen the door panel in front of him suddenly enlarged, and a \"bang\" slammed into his face. In an instant, he felt that the world was spinning, and he fell to the ground under the pressure of the door panel, losing consciousness.\n\nKudo Shinichi was just a few inches away from the safety distance where the entire door fell, and the door panel almost slammed in front of his eyes.\n\nAfter the door fell down, Amamiya Noriko, who was still raising her legs, revealed her slender, snow-white calves, and her thighs that were round and perfect.\n\nThen there are the white bloomers at the bottom of the skirt.\n\nShin Kudo regained his senses, reached out and fanned the dust caused by the falling of the door.\n\n\"Why did he lock you in