\"Ah, that\'s right.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko suddenly remembered with a single finger on her chin, and said crisply, \"Shinichi is also my Prince Charming.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t believe her evil at all, but he glanced at him subconsciously and blushed a little when he met the bright and clear eyes of Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked: \"Xiaolan~\"\n\nShin Kudo\'s face changed in an instant, as if I was a detective and reasoned calmly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled: \"Ahaha...\"\n\n​​'),
(438, 5, 47, 'Chapter 46: : Isn\'t this Touzi, where is the part-time job?', 'Amamiya Ludou found two chaebols from the Suzuki family, and specially invited Kogoro Mouri. Naturally, it was not just a visit.\n\nThe elders had something to discuss with the elders. Noriko Amamiya and the children sat with them for a while, and then went to play.\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t want to leave the table at all. Rather than playing with Xiaolan and the others, it was definitely better to listen to some important things, and if Kogoro Mouri was there, it had something to do with detectives.\n\nAs a disciple of Sherlock Holmes, a future high school detective, and the savior of the Japanese police, how could he miss it?\n\nBut he was thrown out by Kogoro Mouri. He\'s just a kid who just graduated from elementary school. What detective game is he playing?\n\nAmamiya Noriko was amused, and the future Conan was also taken out by Mouri Kogoro directly.\n\nFor image reasons, he could only cover his mouth and laugh softly, but it still made Kudo Shinichi more depressed.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was amused a little, then she took a good pose and showed them around her home.\n\nYuanzi used to come to visit her from time to time, and basically knew how her house was like, but Xiaolan and Xinyi didn\'t come here very often.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took them around the house.\n\n\"Kiko\'s house is not so big, and it\'s beautifully decorated.\"\n\nXiaolan couldn\'t help but praise her, because the small bridges and flowing water, the rockery bamboo forest, and the elegant environment are not good.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded: \"It\'s okay, Sonoko\'s family is bigger.\"\n\nThe main thing is that she has lived in this place for 10 years, she is very familiar with it, and occasionally needs a little freshness, just like those fish who think she is cute and weak, and occasionally see her playing football and tennis, and can\'t help but take the bait .\n\nSuzuki Sonoko tilted her head, why did she suddenly mention her home? Although her home is much bigger than Noriko\'s, it\'s a European-style manor, and you can drive a car at home, but Sonoko is not someone who shows off her wealth, so she waved her hand.\n\n\"It\'s useless! There\'s no handsome guy!\"\n\nMao Lilan looked at the garden helplessly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko did the math and counted down a thousand episodes. In the end, the one who liked Sonoko, except for Jing Jizhen, had a few good endings. Either he was involved in the case and only appeared in two episodes, or he was a prisoner himself. .\n\nSuch a down-to-earth and loyal rich lady is mixed up like this, and the garden is not easy.\n\nIt\'s not interesting to just visit at home, and Noriko Amamiya has always maintained a well-behaved state.\n\nSo Noriko Amamiya suggested that they go out to play.\n\nShe wasn\'t in a hurry for the meeting of the adults over there, she just asked her father Amamiya Ludou.\n\nAmamiya Ludou is quite confident in his daughter\'s IQ, and there is no problem in inheriting the family business in the future.\n\nSonoko is very enthusiastic about going out to play, but she is wearing a kimono now, and Noriko Amamiya takes her to change her clothes. Sonoko Suzuki is about the same size as her, so there is no problem at all.\n\nSonoko changed into a white T-shirt and black leggings. She was surprised that Noriko had this kind of clothes. She didn\'t usually look like she would wear this kind of outfit.\n\nAnyway, Amamiya Noriko was wearing a blue sweater and a black plaid pleated skirt, with round-toed leather shoes and a pair of black over-the-knee socks.\n\nThere\'s nothing wrong with this outfit, but Shinichi Kudo saw that the words on her sweater were weird.\n\nFour words \"No fishing\".\n\nThe word \"prohibited\" has not changed, and the rest should look like \"fish\", but the four points at the bottom have become \"one\", which becomes \"fish\", and then \"fishing\" should be \"fishing\", no problem , he can recognize it.\n\nBecause the two characters are similar, he can easily guess that they are Chinese characters. He knows that Amamiya Noriko is quite good at Chinese.\n\nBut what does this mean?\n\n\"It should be \'fishing prohibited\' in Japanese, but this is \'forbidden fishing\', mainly because the pronunciation sequence of spoken language is different, and the meaning should be the same, but why is it in simplified Chinese???\"\n\nKudo Shinichi fell into deep thought.\n\nAfter talking with Sonoko Xiaolan, Amamiya Noriko and Sonoko Xiaolan looked at him and touched the words on the front of the clothes, so fishing is prohibited.\n\nAfterwards, the four of them went out. This time, Chieda Riho was not there. She belonged to the category where she could and should listen to the meeting.\n\nDestination, Cuphu Shopping Plaza.\n\nThe last time I went to the nearby shopping mall was just to eat, but if it was for shopping and play, the Cuphu shopping plaza was big enough, and there was a Ferris wheel in the plaza.\n\nWell, the Ferris wheel with a story is also a miserable Ferris wheel.\n\nThis weekend holiday is also the beginning of the Golden Week. Didan Middle School will have a holiday in the middle of the Golden Week, which is a week-long holiday.\n\nSo although it was still in the morning, there were a lot of people outside, and many people also enjoyed the holiday.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and a few people took a taxi to the neighborhood, and then they walked all the way. The pedestrian street was extremely crowded.\n\nAt first, Amamiya Noriko was going to go fishing, but there were too many people. It wasn\'t fishing, it was sardines coming from inside the sardines. Then she let it go, gave herself a day off, and happily went shopping with Xiaolan Yuanzi.\n\nKudo Shinichi is a normal boy~www.readwn.com~ has no interest in shopping at all. If he has this skill, he might as well go back and study more about the cases in Sherlock Holmes.\n\nBut Xiaolan was very happy, and when Kiko Yuanzi found something interesting, they would immediately pull him with the anti-aircraft brain standing by the side to show him how interesting it was.\n\nThen Kudo Shinichi didn\'t find it interesting at all, and was thrown aside by Xiaolan again, and when he discovered something novel, he dragged him over again.\n\nKudo Shinichi never tires of it, but Xiaolan used to pull on his sleeve before, but this time, after accidentally pulling his hand once, all his impatience was eliminated.\n\nIn the entanglement, he stood on the side with a little bit of anticipation.\n\nI hope Lan can accidentally pull his hand again.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Sonoko\'s eyes are sharp, and both of them looked at these two people with ambiguous eyes.\n\nXiaolan was flustered when she accidentally grabbed her hand. She quickly took the opportunity to release it and blushed for a long time, but she was not seen by Kudo Shinichi.\n\nSonoko asked in a low voice, \"Kiko, do you think you can still hold hands today?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head for a while, and followed her meaning: \"No, unless we help.\"\n\n\"That\'s right.\"\n\nSonoko said with certainty that she has done her best.\n\nJust like Kudo Shinichi didn\'t serve her as a wingman, Amamiya Noriko wasn\'t going to be Sonoko\'s wingman either. The difficulty of more than a thousand episodes could be facilitated by this? !\n\nSo, not ready to blend in, she turned her eyes to the side, and saw a doll costume taking off her headgear, she couldn\'t help but tilt her head. This pale blond hair, wheat-colored skin, purple-gray eyes, confident but not Charming smile...\n\nIsn\'t this a tortoise?\n\nThe old part-time job is now a part-time emperor.\n\n​​');
