(439, 5, 42, 'Chapter 41: : 1st floor 2nd floor 3rd floor', 'Kudo Shinichi didn\'t need to go to the football club to ask for leave, he said hello after he was ready to investigate.\n\nImmediately following Amamiya Noriko out of school.\n\nAs soon as he left the school, he saw a black luxury car driving from a distance, very similar to the Bentley curtain opened by Chieda Riho, and Kudo Shin thought it was picking up Noriko Amemiya.\n\nThen he stopped, who was chasing after the car?\n\nHe\'s not Conan with a skateboard.\n\nBut seeing that Amamiya Noriko didn\'t mean to stop, he guessed it was just a similar car, but Amamiya Noriko didn\'t stop, but the car stopped suddenly.\n\nA young man in the car hurriedly opened the car door and looked back at Noriko Amemiya.\n\nShet, he had never seen such a pure and flawless girl with an angel-like face, who just stole his heart with a quick glance in the car.\n\n\"Follow her!\"\n\n\"Master, I got it!\"\n\nThe driver in front heard this, put on the handbrake and stepped on the accelerator to make a handsome drifting U-turn, like an F1 racing car that was ready to start and eject, the engine roared.\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi followed, he looked at the man who was thrown out and fell into the bushes by the roadside.\n\nAnother idiot who was bewitched by Noriko Amamiya\'s appearance.\n\nIt can\'t be saved, let it die on its own.\n\nKudo Shinichi continues to follow Noriko Amamiya.\n\nThen I found out that Amamiya Noriko went to the gym...\n\n\"The club asks for leave just to come and exercise???\"\n\nKudo Shinichi wouldn\'t believe such nonsense, but thinking about Akiko Amamiya\'s actually perverted physique...\n\nMaybe Noriko Amamiya is just working hard when others don\'t know about it...\n\nIt\'s still possible.\n\nKudo Shinichi thought about it, and followed him in. Although this place is easy to find, the appearance of Noriko Amamiya\'s training is really intriguing.\n\nAnd he can experience it. If he feels good, he can exercise more after getting a card. Detectives are not only in the mind, but also in physical strength.\n\nAfter entering, I was very conscientious and dutiful by the gym staff to experience all kinds of exercise equipment.\n\nAt the same time, with the detailed explanation, the feeling of sweating is quite good.\n\nWhen he has finished his experience and thinks he can get a card.\n\nWhen he arrived at the front desk where he stored his belongings, he found that his schoolbag had been passive.\n\n  \"what happened?\"\n\n\"Well, just now, little brother, your little girlfriend said that she would use a notebook to help you take exercise notes. It\'s great!\"\n\nThe muscular male staff winked when he heard this, and was quite envious of Kudo Shinichi.\n\n  \"I--\"\n\nKudo Shin took a look, and the one that was taken away was the notebook he had written down and sorted out the clues.\n\n\"Damn.\"\n\nHe instantly understood that it was being stalked by Amamiya Noriko, but he didn\'t expect that Amamiya Noriko actually found out that he was following him.\n\nKudo Shinichi thought, maybe he was going to bring him here, so he had to store his belongings.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s goal at the beginning was his notebook for keeping clues.\n\n\"What does she want clues for? She shouldn\'t want to find out the truth.\"\n\nThe muscle staff reminded: \"Little brother, do you still apply for a card? Muscle will be more liked by girlfriends.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi had black lines all over his head, so he rejected it very directly.\n\nWhen he walked out of the gym, he thought for a while calmly, what would Noriko Amamiya do when he got his clues?\n\nRed area.\n\n\"Is she also an idiot?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi scratched his head, he knew that Amamiya Noriko actually did whatever he wanted.\n\nUsually middle school girls go there, and they are found to be called by the teacher to the staff room for education, and may also be gossip by other people, Amamiya Noriko will not be unaware.\n\n\"Ah, it\'s really troublesome.\"\n\nAnd he also knew that Amamiya Noriko would do whatever she said, and she would definitely go right away, but it was almost evening now.\n\nKudo Shinichi hurried over.\n\nIt seems that it took a lot of time because he was addicted to exercise, and it was dark when he arrived.\n\nThe atmosphere in the Hongfan District was also ambiguous and hot.\n\nThere are a large number of \"unexplained cases\" ~www.readwn.com~, which is a free agency, which will introduce various entertainment venues to those who appear to be tourists or strangers, and then take a cut.\n\nKudo Shinichi was about to go in, when he saw a young man just come out. At first glance, except for his hairstyle, he had a face that was very similar to himself.\n\n\"It will definitely be easily misidentified.\"\n\nHe took a look, and was about to pass by when he heard the boy chuckle crisply: \"No need to go, little detective, your clues have been destroyed.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was awe-inspiring, turning his head to look at him with eagle-like sharp eyes.\n\n\"Don\'t be so vigilant, although we will meet again in the future, but for the first time, I am Kuroba Kuito.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi watched him bend down slightly, and then he threw a ball on the ground in a deformed way, and instantly thick pink smoke spurted out, covering the small area and blocking all sight.\n\n\"Cough cough—\"\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi rushed out of the smoke and swayed the gas in front of him, the person in front of him had disappeared, but the people around him exclaimed and sighed. This place is so lively.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked back at the red area, and it seemed that he didn\'t need to go in.\n\n\"However, Kuroba Kuito? What\'s his relationship with Noriko Amemiya?\"\n\nIn the alley not far away, Amamiya Noriko gently lifted the mask, took off the hair net, the soft strands of hair poured down, and the clear and translucent eyes closed the mask with admiration. Can be reused.\n\n\"As expected of me, perfect.\"\n\nWhile putting away the mask, he turned his head and saw a black Porsche 356 driving past the alley.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was instantly excited again.\n\n\"Master Qin, do you also have a hobby of coming here?\"\n\n​​'),
(440, 5, 13, 'Chapter 12: : refusal to bring people to salvation', 'After all, Amamiya Noriko is only 12 years old now, so the arcade is still not very safe, right?\n\nKudo Shinichi thinks so, but Amamiya Noriko is really too deep, the whole thing is a depth bomb, which has already blown up the game hall.\n\n\"Hi! Xiao Yu Gong, is this your classmate?\"\n\nA social youth who was playing games next to the entrance of the game hall found out when Noriko Amamiya entered and waved his hand in greeting.\n\n\"Well, an idiot who is worried that I will lose out in the arcade.\"\n\nStupid Kudo Shinichi: \"...\"\n\nAnd following his greeting, other people in the arcade also found Noriko Amamiya and waved their hands to say hello.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also responded thoughtfully, and then asked, \"Are there any newcomers?\"\n\nOthers winked very tacitly and betrayed the stranger.\n\nThis reaction is exactly the reaction of trying to trick other people into soothing the soul after being fooled.\n\nKudo Shinichi roughly understood that it was indeed Noriko Amamiya\'s fish pond. She caught all the fish in the wild pond and released them, and then this pond was her fish pond.\n\nSeeing that his eyes were gradually deformed, Noriko Amamiya still said: \"I didn\'t take the bait, I only expanded the business when there were no fish in the school in the fifth or sixth grade. Most of these were when I was in the sixth grade. I know each other in the competition, after all, I don’t have time to go fishing one by one, by the way, they are all my losers.”\n\n\"Yes, I know you are amazing.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi held his forehead.\n\n\"Come and play.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko sat down the arcade next to Kudo Shinichi. The arcade frame of this game is in the form of a sitting + touch screen. Players control the main general to fight through the touch screen and cards. It is a highly strategic real-time battle. The game, the game she won in the game hall before, is similar to the Three Kingdoms War.\n\nShe played it before crossing the road. By the way, because of Nissin\'s sponsorship, there was also a \"Famous Detective Lu Bu\" card with Nissin Cup Noodles.\n\nKudo Shinichi just played, he is a younger brother, so he was abused by Noriko Amamiya.\n\nHe was very upset: \"I just abused me when I came up, and I didn\'t use my intelligence. Can you familiarize me with a rule?!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko is innocent: \"The lion also does his best to fight the rabbit.\"\n\nFrom time to time, Kudo Shin and Amamiya Noriko\'s Chinese ability is very temperamental.\n\n\"Little sister, if he can\'t do it, play with your brother.\"\n\nAt this time, a blond gangster who had just entered the game hall saw the young and beautiful Noriko Amamiya\'s eyes lit up, and he approached in a buoyant manner.\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked and said with a simple face: \"Okay, big brother can give it a try.\"\n\nKudo Shin couldn\'t see Amamiya Noriko being cute, so he gave way directly, standing next to Amamiya Noriko, still vigilant against this bad boy.\n\nThe blonde gangster raised his sleeves and sat down, saying to himself: \"Come on, little sister, I am the hope of the Han Dynasty, and I won the third place in the Rice Flower Online Division.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko showed a surprised expression: \"Second runner-up, big brother is amazing.\"\n\n\"Hey, it doesn\'t matter if little sister loses, brother invites you to dinner.\"\n\n\"Well, thank you big brother.\"\n\nListening to Noriko Amamiya\'s soft and glutinous words, the blond gangster felt comfortable from the inside out, as if victory was in hand.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is too lazy to say that she lost and confessed to me, etc. Is this person\'s confession refusal really effective?\n\nKudo Shinichi still felt a bit strong for the third place in the Rice Krispies Division. To be safe, he whispered, \"Second runner-up, can you really do it?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko rolled her eyes: \"I am the champion.\"\n\nShin Kudo put his hand in his pocket and didn\'t want to speak.\n\nThe blond **** is known as the last hope of the Han Dynasty, and he really used a card from the Shu Kingdom.\n\nThen he was hanged up and beaten by the Wei Kingdom by Amamiya Noriko.\n\n\"This is historically correct.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said sweetly, smiling like a flower, as if the petals of a cherry blossom were fluttering in the wind.\n\nThe last hope of the Han Dynasty - the blond **** hugs his head.\n\nHe was in an extremely tangled state of mind. On the one hand, Yumiya Kiko\'s words brightened his proud and proud heart, and on the other hand, Amamiya Kiko\'s smile healed his broken heart.\n\nWill the future of the Han Dynasty be healed like her smile!\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t bear to look directly at the way he doubted his life. You are really a sinner, Noriko Amamiya.\n\nFurthermore, Amamiya Noriko also held the card of [Han Xiandi] and said curiously: \"Isn\'t the last hope of the Han Dynasty Emperor Han Xiandi? Big brother, you don\'t look like it.\"\n\nHan Xiandi\'s card painting style is like a young freshman who just debuted, with blond hair... The whole person only has a little bit of blond hair.\n\n\"Chirp—\"\n\nThe last arrow pierced into the heart of the blond bastard, he, he just likes to use the Shu Kingdom\'s deck! How passionate he is about this game and the brotherhood between the three brothers of the Shu Kingdom, but he was completely defeated by the super cute Wei Kingdom.\n\n  \"Um?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko sees that he seems to be very emotional. If he confesses in this state, maybe it will be effective?\n\nShe glanced at Kudo Shinichi.\n\nKudo Shin, who had been pitiful at first, understood the meaning of his eyes in an instant. It\'s simple, are you a devil?\n\nKudo Shinichi refused to help, Amamiya Noriko pouted, this is not a good wingman, Sonoko will definitely help, and I will call Sonoko next time.\n\n\"Goodbye, big brother, I\'m going to play other games.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko got up. She didn\'t set a bet. It would be too obvious to slap someone and then induce a confession. Otherwise, would he rely on him to confess?\n\n\"No—don\'t go!! I swore that my wife would definitely be the player who can defeat me, marry me—!!\"\n\nThe blond **** stretched out his hand to grab Noriko Amamiya, screaming out his dreams.\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya raised his hand, he was caught out, and Kudo Shinichi pulled him back to avoid it.\n\n\"I can see, big brother, you are a person with a story, but I refuse, they are too young to get married, come on, drive a spaceship... a big brother who plays cards! Don\'t give up, there are still many Asians Saxi\'s boys can beat you, and they\'ll make you happy too.\"\n\nNot quite able to keep up with the jumping thinking of the other party, but Noriko Amamiya refused to be professional.\n\nStrength +1, he is a delinquent boy with some sincere feelings—end.\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t keep up with the thinking of these two people throughout the whole process, but there is one thing that can be confirmed, Amamiya Noriko still let the other party take the initiative to confess, what is the rationale?\n\nWhat made him even more unexpected was that the gangster who had been rejected directly wanted to say something like \"I can wait for you to grow up\", but he was comforted.\n\nWhen other friends in the game hall saw his confession and he was rejected, they came over to comfort him very enthusiastically, and looked away. There is still a lot of beauty in the world. Rain Palace is not something he can ask for, but the joy of the game is still in his hands. In hand, the hope of the Han Dynasty, they will bear together.\n\nIn the warm greeting, the blond gangster actually felt the warmth of the world, and his heart was filled with scorching warmth. After he became a bad boy, and the game became his everything, he felt the kindness and warmth from others for the first time.\n\nShe was moved to tears, tears.\n\nThere was also a question mark on Noriko Amamiya\'s head, but she clapped her hands in relief: \"Congratulations.\"\n\nShin Kudo glanced at this man who had a cute face just now and suddenly realized it, and he wanted to ask, what happened to this world?\n\nFrom his detective\'s point of view, there is only one explanation, good luck.\n\nBut the atmosphere at this time was not easy for Amamiya Noriko herself to mix in, so she took Kudo Shinichi to play billiards, this time Kudo Shinichi will not give Amamiya Noriko a chance to abuse him, UU reading www.uukanshu .com play with others first.\n\nAmamiya Noriko frowned: \"What is this, come and play pool with others with me?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi sneered: \"You want to abuse me.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pursed her lips and said aggrievedly when A went out: \"It won\'t be good if you abuse me.\"\n\n\"Bang dang.\"\n\nWhen the billiard opponent opposite Amamiya Noriko saw this, the bar in his hand fell out of his hand and fell out of his hand. He felt the blood gushing out of his nose, which was too heart-wrenching.\n\nKudo Shin has always been masculine, his face does not change, he glanced at Noriko Amamiya: \"You are committing a crime.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the person opposite her with a puzzled expression, and replied Kudo Shinichi with her mouth.\n\n\"Is it a crime to steal your heart? Great detective~\"\n\nKudo Shinichi hated him deeply, this person is really bad, he has already started teasing him with detectives without ever saying it face to face, it seems that it has started since kindergarten.\n\nAt the same time, he decided to play in other places with Noriko Amamiya after school, which would affect his detective brain.\n\nHowever, not necessarily only outside the school.\n\n  the next day.\n\nBetween classes, Kudo Shinichi was talking to Xiao Lan about the detective novel he read last night when he heard loud shouts from the playground outside the teaching building.\n\n\"Amamiya-san!! I like it! I like you—!!\"\n\nThe corners of his mouth twitched, but then he became happy again, because Noriko Amamiya had a high fever when she went home yesterday, and she didn\'t come today at all, she couldn\'t enjoy the fun of refusing.\n\nKudo Shinichi smiled and couldn\'t wait to tell it to Noriko Amamiya to see her wonderful expression.\n\nAs for the classmate below... After confessing to the air, he was arrested by the school to write a review.'),
(441, 5, 5, 'Chapter 4: : Only 1 real gin', 'The Amemiya family had already planned to travel abroad during the holiday, so they couldn\'t see Kudo Shinichi or three children during the holiday.\n\n\"Noriko~ Mom, help you pack your luggage!\"\n\n\"No need, mom sit on the side.\"\n\n\"Wow, Noriko is still young, so she can act coquettishly with her mother.\"\n\nA certain mother, who was sitting beside her, was very aggrieved, sobbing.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was unmoved, forget about the kindergarten children, if you are a mother, can you stop being so naive?\n\nShe didn\'t want to play with little kids in kindergarten and coax her mother when she got home.\n\nEimi Amamiya pouted, there is a lovely daughter in front of her but she is very cold and not fun at all.\n\n\"No way, let\'s go to the airport with Dad.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko packed her small suitcase, and Amamiya Emi drove the two to the Amamiya family\'s company building.\n\nHer father, Amamiya Ludou, the chairman of the Amemiya chaebol, is basically a trading company under the Amamiya chaebol, mainly for various import and export business. Amamiya Ludou spends most of his time abroad, and the Amamiya family travels abroad by the way. Also deals with foreign affairs.\n\nThe mother and daughter were sitting in the car waiting for Amamiya Ludou to come down, while Amamiya Noriko listened to her mother\'s various thoughts and conversations.\n\nShe thought that it was not easy for you to meet my daughter.\n\nBut she glanced casually, and after seeing the parked black Porsche 356A across the road, she felt that it was not easy for her.\n\nShe couldn\'t see the license plate, but she had already seen the gin getting out of the car.\n\nGin was the only one, but she still had that black trench coat and black top hat. The hat and bangs half covered her face, and her silver hair was not as long as Gin she remembered, yes, it was still ten years ago.\n\nShe also probably guessed the reason why Gin appeared here.\n\nGin is always on the way to eliminate traitors or on the way to eliminate traitors. After all, there are too many traitors, and the workload is huge.\n\nIt\'s just that it seems to be related to his father\'s company, which is very rough.\n\n\"Mom, has anything happened in Dad\'s company recently?\"\n\n\"Huh? It seems there is, but it doesn\'t seem to be there. Just wait and ask Dad.\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAfter a while, Amamiya Ludou walked out of the building, accompanied by some company executives.\n\nIn the car, Amamiya Noriko turned to look at the black Porsche across the road. Gin had gone to the opposite building before, which was a hotel, and she was not sure which room Gin was in.\n\nShe turned her head and set her eyes on several executives beside her father. She didn\'t know anyone from the original book, so she could only look for those with problems.\n\nSoon one of the young executives was attracted and noticed by her. The other party\'s face was obviously a little bad when he saw the black Porsche across the road. While chatting with the others, he tried to change the angle to see the license plate clearly, and at the same time tried to hide his body as much as possible. behind the others.\n\nHe is the only young executive who hides behind other middle-aged people who are not very tall.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko felt it was him.\n\n\"Will Gin kill him in such a public situation?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was not sure, she remembered that Gin was called a lunatic by Belmod, and it was hard to say that she would not do it in broad daylight.\n\nHer little brain with more than ten points of intelligence turned quickly, and three words, eight eggs, slowly emerged.\n\nJust now, Gin got out of the car and entered the hotel without seeing what he had taken. He wanted to kill the target across the road. The easiest way is to shoot. No matter what, there is no way to hide a sniper rifle under the windbreaker. Besides, Gin The Beretta M92F pistol has an effective range of 50 meters, which is completely sufficient.\n\nBut in public, it would be too targeted to shoot only one person, and the police will definitely investigate the victim.\n\nIf the bombing kills many people with vague targets, and then leaves a warning or revenge letter to the Amemiya chaebol, it will easily confuse the police\'s investigation direction.\n\n\"If it\'s a bomb...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at the high-rise hotel across the road, just a few floors higher can easily throw across the road.\n\nWhile her thoughts were spinning, Amamiya Noriko opened the door and got out of the car, waving her hand over there.\n\nYu Gong Lu Dou actually discovered his wife\'s car long ago, but he was still talking to his subordinates and didn\'t leave directly, but he didn\'t delay when he saw his daughter waving at him. Waving to yourself on the street is quite rare.\n\nHe happily came over and bent over to hug his daughter, when he heard a loud \"bang\" from behind, and the air waves mixed with gravel rushed directly to this side.\n\nAmamiya Ludou reacted very quickly to protect his daughter with his arms, then picked up her daughter and put it in the car.\n\nAfter he confirmed that his previous wife was okay, he looked at the place where he left not long ago.\n\nA big hole was blasted out on the ground, still carrying smoke and dust, and the executives under his command almost lay on the ground.\n\nAmamiya Ludou frowned and called the police and an ambulance first.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked across the road in the car, the black Porsche started to drive away, she could vaguely see a smile on the corner of Gin\'s mouth.\n\nThis is the reason why she just waved her hand without making a sound. If she directly disturbed everyone over there, Gin would probably be more rude, and it would be more difficult to guess how to solve the problem.\n\nIt\'s not bad now, from the orange light she saw when it exploded, it was a plastic bomb, and the gin should have the power to control it, it\'s not very big, there are senior executives who have gradually sparsed after Amamiya Ludou left. In the middle of the explosion, only the three people at the center of the explosion seemed to have died directly. Among them, the young executive who was targeted by the gin was undoubtedly the most miserable and bloody.\n\nPlastic bombs are also known as C4 and C-4, which are known for their stability and plasticity and are not easy to be found by security inspections.\n\nGenerally speaking, unless it hits the detonator directly, it will not explode if shot. This powerful C4 detonator can refer to a small pencil.\n\nTherefore, if it was gin to throw it, it must have been equipped with a remote detonating device, which could accurately make the bomb explode in the middle, even if the young executive was hiding behind a little, he could not escape.\n\nAmamiya Noriko covered her eyes while looking at the miserable situation over there and thinking.\n\n\"Noriko is not afraid, it\'s alright, don\'t look at it, children.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was helplessly embraced by her mother and covered her eyes. Emi Amamiya hugged her daughter and comforted her for a while, then asked her husband in a low voice, \"Is there anything wrong with the company?\"\n\nThe explosion was found downstairs in the company, and the target was the company\'s executives. She had to worry that the other party was coming for the company.\n\nAmamiya Ludou looked at his daughter in his wife\'s arms with wide eyes, and he didn\'t seem to be afraid.\n\n\"The company did receive a threatening letter a few days ago. It was left in the name of some pirates on the high seas. Some time ago, they cooperated with the international police to solve a group of pirates. These pirates are indeed acting recklessly.\"\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya heard this, it seems that Gin has already made a fake name. Are you going to push it to pirates on the high seas? If you look in this direction, it is indeed extremely cumbersome.\n\nAmamiya Ludou then went to check the injuries of his subordinates, and the police came quickly after that.\n\nAmamiya Noriko saw Officer Megumi and Kogoro Mouri. The first search class was equivalent to the serious crime team, but they were the violent crime investigation department of the first search class, and they were in charge of the murder case. Other patrolling policemen also rushed over to maintain order at the scene.\n\nMainly the three departments of special criminal investigations, responsible for exploding bombs and the like.\n\nAt this time, Kogoro Mouri and the others were questioning witnesses. Amamiya Ludou was naturally the main one. The victims this time were all his subordinates, and he was not far from the explosion site.\n\nBut he was facing his daughter at the time, the explosion was behind him, and he couldn\'t offer anything.\n\nMouri Kogoro frowned: \"It\'s a bit of a headache, so do you have any relevant clues, or something that feels relevant?\"\n\nAs usual, Amamiya Ludou explained the threatening letter to his company before. UU Kanshu www.uukanshu.com has a record from the Second Department of Special Crime Investigation. Kogoro Mouri called and asked about it.\n\nHe said with a serious face; \"It seems that there is no doubt that those pirates are taking revenge on your company!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways. Anyone who has seen Conan understands that this suspect is ruled out.\n\nShe said casually, \"Uncle Maori, I saw that the bomb was dropped from the hotel opposite. When it exploded, I saw an orange light.\"\n\nIt was only when Mouri Kogoro noticed the little Akiko Amemiya, he asked in surprise, \"Aren\'t you Xiaolan\'s classmate?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, \"Did you just find out?\"\n\nMouri Kogoro, who was despised by the kid, was covered in black lines. While arranging for someone to check at the hotel across the road, he said to Amamiya Ludou, \"Mr. Amamiya, it\'s not good to keep children at the crime scene.\"\n\n  \"cut.\"\n\nAmamiya Emi came over to take her daughter away, while Amamiya Ludou wanted to stay and cooperate with the police investigation.\n\nWhen this kind of case happened, the trip was basically impossible for the time being.\n\nWhen Yu Gong Lu Dou came home in the evening, she casually asked the young executive, and learned that the other party had not joined the company for a long time, but he was very capable and was promoted very quickly. Before, he was also independently responsible for an export trade to foreign countries. Large business order.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is also completely certain. Most of the people with this background are cultivated by black organizations, but they are only peripheral members, and they do not have a code name.\n\nEven the political circles have such peripheral members, such as the Amemiya chaebol, a big chaebol in import and export business. She thinks it is not surprising that the black organization secretly mixes sand to expand the organization\'s smuggling channels.\n\nAfter all, you will have to deal with the winery.'),
(442, 5, 2, 'Chapter 1: : Noriko Amamiya of Conan World', 'In the dark night, a shadow was fishing by the school lake, and the moon was reflected on the sparkling lake, like a full moon.\n\nSuddenly, the fishing rod sank!\n\nImmediately following the \"bang-\", accompanied by the severe pain in the back of the head, his eyes darkened, he fell into the lake with a plop, and opened his eyes again, and he passed through as Amamiya Noriko.\n\n\"The probability of me catching a fish is the same as the probability of crossing.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who was still pulling the rod, made the action of throwing the fishing rod.\n\n\"My dear, our Noriko seems to be suddenly very angry!\"\n\n\"No, no, this doesn\'t seem to be the point. If you heard correctly, is this Chinese?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at the couple who were whispering to each other, but she could hear them clearly.\n\nIt\'s Japanese, yes, and I can understand it completely.\n\nAppears to be parents.\n\nAmamiya Noriko calmed down and walked outside with a slightly vicissitudes back to look at the yard.\n\nIt looks like an old Japanese-style mansion, with a big yard, grass, cobblestone paths, a small bamboo forest, and a pool.\n\nThe two couples looked at each other under the eaves and looked at the little back of their three-year-old daughter.\n\n\"Does your daughter not want to go to kindergarten again?\"\n\n\"That\'s not good. This is the new semester. Let\'s coax Noriko with candy.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced back at them, she was just looking at her own system.\n\nConfession rejection system 1.0: Every time you reject a confession, it becomes stronger!\n\n\"Who would confess at the age of three, let me start as a beautiful girl if I have the ability.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko frowned and looked at the system\'s only words.\n\nWhat does it mean to become stronger?\n\nAmamiya Noriko went to the entrance to change her shoes by herself and went out.\n\n\"Wait a minute, Noriko remember to put on the name tag, this year is the Sakura class.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the pink sakura nameplate, which read: Sakura Class, Amamiya Noriko.\n\nOutside the kindergarten, Amamiya Noriko looked up at the \"Rice Flower Nursery\". She, a three-year-old child, might not know all Japanese, but these words were no different from Chinese, and she felt more and more familiar.\n\nIn the cherry blossom class, the nursery teacher Migan-sensei asked the children to play with building blocks first, and then it was morning exercise time.\n\nAmamiya Noriko picked up the pile of wood at random, then built a three-story castle in front of her, and began to look out the window in a trance.\n\nOriginally, she snatched a pile of wood to make the other children very unhappy, but after seeing this castle, they all became stupid and looked at Amamiya Noriko with admiration.\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt their gaze, but she was still lazy and couldn\'t keep her spirits up. Is it interesting to hang and beat the kindergarten children?\n\nIt can only make her feel good for a second.\n\nFeeling the suffocating atmosphere among the children, Mr. Migan had no choice but to clap their hands to attract the children\'s attention from the building block castle, and took out plasticine for the children whose building blocks were incorporated into the castle to play.\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced, pushed the castle aside, and held out a glass of plasticine.\n\nThe slender fingers turn the flowers and butterflies, or knead or knead, and easily knead the plasticine into the shape you want.\n\nAfter a while, under the eyes of the children and Teacher Migan.\n\nA lifelike mecha, -01, the first machine, initial standard equipment, sprint starting position, nearly 20cm high, placed on the table instead of the previous castle.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded with satisfaction. Small hands have the advantage of having small hands, and she pinched them more finely.\n\nShe looked at the others. After a short period of silence, the children became restless and looked at her eagerly, wanting to touch her No. 1 mecha. For these little boys, the allure of mecha is countless times greater than that of the castle. .\n\nA bold boy next to her said impatiently, \"Amamiya, can this super handsome mecha play with me?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"No.\"\n\nAlthough she pinched it casually, she also knew how destructive the children were, and this was not a figure, it was soft plasticine. machine look.\n\nA circle of little boys was hit hard, trying to convince her, and even saying that she was stingy. Noriko Amamiya was too lazy to care about the childish children, so she squeezed the stool with plasticine and gave the child generously. Play.\n\nTeacher Migan watched helplessly as a drop of water poured into the frying pan.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was having a headache from the noise. It happened that Migan didn\'t know where to find a transparent plastic square box, and asked her for her opinion to put the first machine in it, so that it could be placed in the classroom for the students to watch.\n\nShe nodded directly, and asked San An to quickly pack this thing and put it aside, to save these playful children from arguing with her.\n\nAll of a sudden, it was quiet and went to see the model.\n\nHowever, there was still a little child who stayed in front of her and said timidly, \"I\'m Kokura Matsushita, can I be your friend?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her eyebrows: \"You look very afraid of me.\"\n\nXiao Cang Songzhi quickly shook his head: \"No, no...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko had to look confused: \"If you don\'t like me, you can\'t be a good friend with me.\"\n\nXiao Cang Songzhi took a moment, changed his weak tone, and said seriously: \"I like Amamiya, Amamiya is very handsome, and the building blocks and plasticine are very good!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko patted him on the shoulder with satisfaction, \"Yes, yes, very promising, but I refuse!\"\n\nThe child with joy on his face gradually turned dull.\n\nRefusing to confess successfully, random points: Strength +1.\n\nImamiya Noriko suddenly felt some subtle changes in her body, and it started to get a little hot. Although it was just the beginning, it could make her three-year-old body feel a little bit stronger.\n\nTherefore, she also patted the children in a good mood: \"Don\'t be discouraged, keep trying! You can\'t be a man by giving up because of one failure, right?\"\n\nKokura was encouraged and encouraged himself: \"...Yes! Amamiya, I will definitely become a man and become your friend!\"\n\n\"Your spirit is commendable, okay, let\'s play while you play.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved her hand, her mood returned to normal after a moment of happiness, and she just fooled a three-year-old child into lame, can you feel a sense of accomplishment?\n\nShe sat comfortably on the chair in the corner, watching the group of naive children play happily under the guidance of the nursery teacher, but she was stunned after looking away.\n\nOver there, a little girl with short hair wearing a bow headband is talking to a friend: \"Huh? Xiaolan, why is your brand like this?\"\n\nAnother little girl with long hair replied, \"My mother made this for me. It turned out that it was broken.\"\n\n\"It\'s great, it\'s exactly the same!\"\n\nThe long-haired little girl took off the Sakura name tag and showed it to her friends: \"There are pins at the back. You can take off the name tag. Look.\"\n\nThe little girl with the bow-tie headband said in surprise, \"Really! Xiaolan, your mother is a genius!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at the ceiling, \"I remembered, so it is, the world of Detective Conan, it\'s really interesting... I walk with death.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko saw the Sakura brand and was about to return it to Xiaolan, but was snatched by a few boys next to her.\n\n\"What, isn\'t this just a piece of paper? We won\'t play with people who wear this stuff.\"\n\n\"That\'s right. That\'s right.\"\n\n\"You don\'t fit in!\"\n\nLittle Suzuki Sonoko akimbo said unhappily, \"Give it back to me!\"\n\nThen he was grimaced by some naughty little boys.\n\n\"At this time, Kudo Shinichi should be-\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned around and walked to the glass door facing the outside, facing the little Kudo Shinichi who was holding hands by Kudo Yukiko and wearing a little yellow hat.\n\nKudo Shinichi was originally paying attention to the child arguing over there, but was blocked by the little girl who appeared inside the door, and the little girl smiled at him.\n\nAlthough he felt strange in his heart, he was still taken by his mother to go through the admission procedures.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned around and turned around. Sonoko, who was strong and wanted to help her friend get back the Sakura brand, had already fought against the little boy. As far as the current situation was concerned, the boys were really weak.\n\nShe remembered that at the end she was taught by Sonoko to cry.\n\nAmamiya Noriko walked straight over, hooked her ankles and knocked down the two boys who were helping, and then stretched out her hands to pull Sonoko and the two away, mainly pulling the boys and falling to the ground. UU Reading www.uukanshu.com\n\n\"It\'s too childish to play bullying girls.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said casually.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko looked at the three little boys who fell to the ground in an instant, and couldn\'t help but say, \"It\'s amazing!\"\n\nMao Lilan said in thanks, \"Thank you.\"\n\n\"Small idea.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko made an ok gesture.\n\nShe really likes Suzuki Sonoko and Maurilan, the main one is loyalty, the family is very rich, and the other is kind-hearted and good at fighting.\n\nThe three people used this as an opportunity to get to know each other. After a while, the head teacher came to mediate, but they found that everything seemed to be fine. The three little boys were clearly arranged by Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at the head teacher Jiang Zhou, you are the prisoner of this incident...\n\nSuzuki Sonoko apologetically took out the damaged Sakura nameplate and said to Maurilan: \"Xiaolan, I\'m sorry, although I took the nameplate back, it\'s already like this.\"\n\nIn order to comfort Sonoko, Mao Lilan said with a smile, \"It\'s okay, I\'ve seen how my mother folded.\"\n\nThen the two wanted to chat with Yumiya Noriko, but although Amamiya Noriko was familiar with them, they were familiar with Morilan and Suzuki Sonoko after high school students, and they did not intend to play with the three-year-olds. , so I sat alone in the corner, looking out the window and thinking about the plot.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko and Maurilan, although they will be very good in the future, they are still only three-year-old girls after all.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko whispered to Maurilan: \"Amamiya is so cool.\"\n\nMao Lilan nodded: \"And the people are very good.\"\n\nThe cool and nice Noriko Amamiya found her bed near the corridor door during her nap.\n\nThis is the location of the original victim, Xiaolan.'),
(443, 5, 79, 'Chapter 78: : Zhufu Jingguang', 'Except for the first day of the school sports meeting, it was a perfect miss after that.\n\nAmamiya Noriko originally planned to cheer on the audience and let the athletes get buffs at the price of capturing their hearts.\n\nThen, as a member of the association, I condolences to the major sports associations, except the football department.\n\nFor the athletes who have not confessed yet, the plan of handing over water, etc., etc., to the athletes after the competition, was all dashed because of a sudden fever.\n\nIt was a bit of a misstep, they should have been given a chance to confess after the school sports meeting.\n\nNow that it is like this, I have probably won a dozen or twenty attribute points steadily.\n\nFull of sadness, Amamiya Noriko was taken by Sonoko to watch a movie during the short vacation after the school sports meeting to relieve her sadness.\n\nI don\'t know if it can relieve the sadness. She was also fed dog food by the love movie that Yuanzi watched. She should have understood that what Yuanzi was watching would not be a serious movie. Should you watch it?\n\nWhy not restrict minors from watching romantic movies?\n\nIt\'s no wonder that later love brains will be serious in the future.\n\nObviously, there is a master in front of me who doesn\'t study hard, and feels that she is weak every day.\n\nIf you follow her to learn a little bit of operation, it won\'t be [no one will be interested in Sonoko].\n\nBut that\'s still what I said, taking off the headband, I, Amamiya Noriko, would like to call you the second strongest.\n\nShe slept in a complicated mood throughout the whole process. When she woke up, the subtitles at the end of the movie appeared. She saw Yoko Okino\'s name very sharply. She should be a small passer-by in the ranking. Now Yoko Okino is not very famous. .\n\n\"Kiko, do you look good?\"\n\n\"Ah, it looks good, the protagonist is very handsome, the heroine is beautiful, the plot is touching, the setting is reasonable, the picture is beautiful...\"\n\nSonoko looked at the sleepy Kiko helplessly, no matter how you can tell that you didn\'t watch the movie well just now?\n\nNoriko is obviously more beautiful and cute than the heroine of the movie, and when it comes to love experience, she is also rich. I don\'t know how many boys have confessed to Noriko since I was a child. main character.\n\nBut as a sister, she is very worried about Noriko. If she completely rejects any handsome guy like this, she will develop a habit in the future, won\'t she be tempted by handsome guys, then how can she find a boyfriend.\n\nI can\'t imagine the scene of Noriko confessing to the boy at all. Of course, what is even more difficult to imagine is the scene where Noriko agrees to the boy\'s confession.\n\nIt\'s all so difficult—\n\nWhen Sonoko imagined these two pictures, her love brain was completely overloaded and almost crashed.\n\nThis is far beyond her barren computing power.\n\nBut she is a lover, Suzuki Sonoko, and she won\'t give up her sister easily.\n\nAfter leaving the movie theater, Sonoko directly suggested to continue to go shopping until she met the super handsome guy who made Kiko\'s heart move!\n\nAmamiya Noriko twitched the corners of her mouth, it\'s over, there\'s no need to go home.\n\n\"Don\'t take the car, it will reduce the chance to meet the handsome guy, and it will make the handsome guy think that you are not approachable enough.\"\n\nSonoko stopped Amamiya Noriko from finding Chieda Riho to pick them up.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said humbly, \"Then we go shopping like this?\"\n\n\"Take the tram.\"\n\nSonoko said to himself, \"There are also unique handsome guys who are handsome on the tram. Although they travel by tram, they don\'t affect their temperament, talent and handsomeness in the slightest. Moreover, such handsome guys are generally more approachable, right?\"\n\nIs this the reason why your dignified second lady of the Suzuki consortium takes the bus and tram every day?\n\nAmamiya Noriko is now dubious. If she can really meet her, she doesn\'t mind taking it by the way. However, two little girls in the first grade of junior high school went out to take a tram and went shopping to find handsome guys. Amamiya Noriko always felt that He believed in Sonoko\'s evil.\n\n\"Look, Noriko, that boy should be a junior high school student like us, right?\"\n\nSonoko suddenly pulled Yumiya Noriko\'s hand and asked her to look behind the train.\n\n\"Junior high school student? Isn\'t he supposed to be a handsome guy?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head helplessly, it was hard for junior high school students to have any handsome guys. They all graduated from elementary school not long ago. At best, they were comparable to other boys in school, but outside the school, there was a normal-looking man. Pay a little attention to your appearance, be neat and tidy, do your hairstyle, and be more handsome than a youthful junior high school student, right?\n\nWhere are the junior high school students and handsome?\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head to take a look, and sure enough, not only was she not a handsome guy, but she was also a girl.\n\nSonoko, you are going too far. Shiliang Zhenchun is only in junior high school. How can he be regarded as a boy?\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s attention was also put there, it was actually Shiliang Zhenchun, she should have tried her best to meet the few lucky points she had.\n\n\"That\'s a girl, not a boy.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head and whispered to Sonoko.\n\n  \"what?\"\n\nSonoko was surprised and couldn\'t help looking at it a few more times, feeling that it was indeed a girl, but it was a boy\'s dress.\n\nShe looked at Noriko Amemiya, how did Noriko see this?\n\nBut I saw Amamiya Noriko\'s eyes kept falling over there, paying attention to the girl dressed as a boy.\n\n\"Could it be that Noriko... likes girls dressed as boys?\"\n\nAn idea came to Yuanzi\'s mind, whether he could dress up as a boy, maybe...\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t notice what Sonoko\'s love brain was thinking. She looked at Shiliang Zhenchun over there, and seemed to be paying attention to what was in the other carriage over there. What was she looking at?\n\nShe took Yuanzi and followed the other party and changed trains several times. When she got off the train, she finally saw that Shiliang Zhenchun did not continue to transfer, and was caught by a wheat-colored skin, long hair wearing a black knitted hat, sunglasses, and a black windbreaker. , the man with a black guitar case on his back stopped him.\n\n  \"handsome-\"\n\nJust as Sonoko was about to speak, Amamiya Noriko covered her mouth and pulled her behind the pillar.\n\nWhy is Shuichi Akai here?\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head around. If it was the plot in that memory, then the various scenes of Scotland and Bourbon Amuro should both appear here.\n\nThe three of them were supposed to be on a mission. There was a gun in the guitar case.\n\nTomomi Amemiya knew Toru Amuro and Hide Akai one or two people, and both of them knew her. If they found out that they both knew her, God knows what would happen.\n\n\"Kiko... what\'s wrong?\"\n\nSonoko cooperated and hid behind the pillar. Just as she was about to ask Noriko what was going on, she saw Amamiya Noriko turned to look at the side of the pillar.\n\n\"Noriko...Is that so? It\'s a nice name. What\'s your surname, kid?\"\n\nOne was wearing a gray coat, slowly taking off the coat and hat, and smiled at Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at this gentle voice, with a kind smile, a man with a beard on his face, and a guitar case on his back.\n\nSure enough, it\'s all the fujingguang...\n\n​​');
