(444, 5, 24, 'Chapter 23: : Xiaolan, call the police!', 'Amamiya Noriko looked down the mountain with binoculars for a long time, only to see the couple\'s car, a white pickup.\n\nThinking about it carefully, it\'s quite strange for a couple to drive this kind of car.\n\nThere are many pickup trucks in the sparsely populated areas in the United States and Canada. It is not so common in Japan, but there are more mini cars.\n\n\"I don\'t know where the people went.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave Kudo Shinichi the telescope.\n\nKudo Shinichi used the binoculars to look around the foot of the mountain here, and then looked at the forest management office next to the parking lot. He put down the binoculars: \"Do you think there will be other roads to the mountain?\"\n\n  \"possible.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, because there are many cherry trees on the northern **** of this mountain, and there is a road forming a cherry blossom road. Most people come here to see the cherry blossoms from this road.\n\nBut it doesn\'t mean that this is the only way to go up the mountain.\n\n\"What are you two looking at? Aren\'t you eating?\"\n\nXiaolan looked at the two of them strangely while holding the bento.\n\nKudo Shinichi hurriedly went back after hearing the words, \"After all, it\'s not just us here, there are many people watching cherry blossoms nearby, what can happen in broad daylight?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the other tourists around, thinking that it might not be a strange thing for a young couple to disappear in broad daylight.\n\n\"Go back early after dinner.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko also joined the eating group over there.\n\nBecause she was preparing other things, she didn\'t do anything delicious, so she made a plate of dumplings, stuffed with some diced radishes, mushrooms and chicken. Small dish of soy sauce.\n\nAfter she took it out of her bag, Kudo Shinichi seemed to have a grudge against soy sauce and would not dip it in death.\n\n\"What\'s wrong, soy sauce isn\'t heavy.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was very calm: \"I just don\'t like dipping in soy sauce.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a bite of the dumpling: \"Next time I\'ll give you rice rolls, I\'ll see if you want soy sauce.\"\n\nYuanzi heard the words and came over: \"Intestine powder, what is it? Is it better than dumplings?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko invited with a smile; \"Next time, Sonoko and Xiaolan can come to my house, and they can make it for you, it\'s smooth and smooth.\"\n\n  \"Yeah.\"\n\nSonoko agreed immediately. When she was in elementary school, she went to Amamiya\'s house, and she went with her father. One of Amamiya and Suzuki\'s chaebol was mainly engaged in foreign trade, and the other was mainly in Japan. There was no conflict of interest, so There are also many cooperation projects, which are considered as business partners.\n\nThe two families occasionally visit each other.\n\nKnowing that the youngest daughters of the two families are good friends makes them more harmonious.\n\nSonoko thought about it, and said, \"My father will visit Uncle Amemiya next weekend. Xiaolan and Shinichi will also go together.\"\n\nXiaolan nodded, but Shinichi Kudo thought that it seemed to be the relationship between Amamiya and the Suzuki family, so there was no need for him to go, right?\n\nMore importantly, at her home, Amamiya Noriko, who is playing at home, looks like...\n\nAmamiya Noriko was puzzled and looked at him inquiringly, \"Is Shinichi not coming?\"\n\n\"Go...\"\n\nAfter Kudo Shinichi finished speaking with a little guilty conscience, he saw Noriko Amamiya, who had been normal for a second, showing him a kind and gentle smile.\n\n  be cheated!\n\nAmamiya Noriko also added: \"That\'s good.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was expressionless: \"If there is nothing else.\"\n\nIf you don\'t want to go when it\'s interesting, you have to find a reason not to go.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pursed her lips and smiled. This move is hard-to-find, but Shinichi Kudo cannot be allowed to go to her house.\n\nSonoko said mysteriously, \"Shinichi will definitely regret not going. Noriko is very different at home than at school.\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wanted to cover her mouth with dumplings immediately, but she still glanced at Kudo Shinichi and said a little embarrassed: \"What\'s the difference, Sonoko eats more dumplings.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was very vigilant when he looked at him. The shy Noriko Amamiya was not charming in his eyes, but rather scary.\n\nIn school, Amamiya Noriko is a girl with a weak and soft personality on the surface, and her innocent appearance makes people naturally like him. In front of him, she is... a little witch who plays with people\'s feelings. What can I do at home? ?\n\nMust be a trap.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also changed the topic at the right time, isn\'t the cherry blossoms not good-looking?\n\nAfter a full meal, it came to the question of who should take out the trash. Dr. A Li quit first. His stomach was bloating because he ate too much.\n\nThen came the riddle part of Dr. Agasa...\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s face darkened, and then she did not lose unexpectedly. Kudo Shinichi was the absolute winner.\n\nBecause most of Dr. Agasa\'s riddles are hiragana kakana or some foreign language homophony to form the answer.\n\nThe buff language of the alien species Amamiya Noriko is very rough. After hearing the answer, the juvenile detective team will suddenly realize that it is completely a riddle at the level of a joke, but after listening to the answer, she can only suddenly realize...\n\nJust like the northerners don\'t understand that the cockroaches in the south can fly, the walls and ceilings are all water when they go back to the south.\n\nShe also doesn\'t understand why onions are so big and can be eaten raw!\n\nSonoko and Xiaolan are still going to go with Amamiya Noriko, but Amamiya Noriko let them wait here for a while. It\'s easy for her how much garbage can weigh.\n\nThe garbage is placed a little above, and it will definitely not be placed on the platform where many people watch the scenery. The forest management office at the bottom of the mountain will have someone come to dispose of the garbage every day.\n\nThere were no trash cans along the way, so they all brought their own eco-friendly trash bags.\n\nAfter throwing away the rubbish, Amamiya Noriko looked at the way to go up. This flat **** for viewing the view was only halfway up the mountainside. It wasn\'t the top of the mountain, so I didn\'t know what was on it.\n\nThinking about whether to go back and suggest mountain climbing, she saw two people coming down from the road above, a man and a woman holding hands.\n\nAmamiya Noriko recognized it as the young couple who parked a little behind the parking lot: \"Is there really any other road to the top of the mountain?\"\n\nAfter being fed dog food, Amamiya Noriko turned around and prepared to go back, but after walking a few steps, she heard the movement behind her. She sprinted forward in an instant, and glanced back at the same time.\n\nSure enough, a man and a woman were chasing after her.\n\n\"What little couple, these are dog men and women.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s running speed was not something they could catch up with at all. The two people behind her also discovered this, and immediately heard a shout: \"Stop now, or else we\'ll shoot!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, the other party was only a dozen meters away from her. If she really shoots, she can\'t expect the other party to be vodka, nor can she expect her luck against the sky.\n\nSo she stopped honestly, and turned around and raised her hand very cooperatively.\n\nThe two rushed to the front, and the man with the gun put away the gun~www.readwn.com~ After all, being seen by other people would be troublesome.\n\nHe warned viciously; \"Come with us, don\'t think about playing tricks!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said softly with red eyes: \"Okay...\"\n\nThe woman held her hand, and the two were as close as sisters, but they were actually preventing Noriko Amamiya from resisting.\n\nAmamiya Noriko whispered, \"Why are you arresting me?\"\n\nThe woman chuckled lightly: \"Don\'t worry, Miss Amamiya, if your father knew each other, he would still be alive.\"\n\nThe man glanced at her: \"Talk less.\"\n\n\"I\'m not afraid to scare Miss Amamiya.\"\n\nAs for her father, Noriko Amamiya basically knew the reason.\n\nShe quietly cooperated with them as they went down, and when she was about to reach the picnic position, she suddenly took the woman\'s hand and twisted it back, the woman\'s almost unresponsive waist was bent, otherwise her arms and shoulders would be directly dislocation.\n\nAt the same time, Amamiya Noriko swiped the back of her fist to the man on the other side of her, and slammed it **** his neck, feeling that her Adam\'s apple had been sunk in, and for a moment, the man was speechless and there was only pain in his throat. Astringent cough.\n\nBut then Amamiya Noriko was stunned.\n\nAt the last moment of losing consciousness, she saw the woman holding an electric shocker in the other hand, flashing arcs.\n\nAfter a while.\n\nIt felt like Kiko Amamiya had been gone for too long. As soon as Shin Kudo came out to look for her, he saw the zipper puller left on the road, and he suddenly remembered that it was on Kiko Amamiya\'s clothes.\n\n\"Xiao Lan! Doctor! Call the police! Noriko has been arrested!!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi rushed back. After shouting, he opened Noriko Amemiya\'s bag, took out the binoculars, and looked down the mountain, just as he saw the white pickup truck driving away from the parking lot.\n\n\"Damn!\"'),
(445, 5, 96, 'Chapter 95: : Jewelry', 'Yuanzi and Xiaolan then came out of the room, still pondering two questions.\n\nWhere did Noriko go, and why did Shinichi sleep here just now?\n\nAnd after waking up, she looked very anxious, so that Xiaolan ran out without a chance to catch him and ask.\n\nXiaolan estimated: \"It must be something related to the case.\"\n\nSonoko nodded: \"I think so too, that guy Shinichi, let\'s find out where Noriko is going first, and the banquet seems to have officially started, and Noriko may be outside.\"\n\nXiaolan nodded, and the two immediately left the room and went outside to see if Noriko was there.\n\nAfter they left, Noriko Amamiya came in and went to replenish her equipment. She had to bring her makeup. It would be hard to explain if she disappeared for too long.\n\nDon\'t go back and report the case to become a missing person, there are police at the scene.\n\nAmamiya Noriko brought something out of the room. At this time, the host of the banquet had finished the first step of the scene, and then the representative of the Suzuki Foundation, Suzuki Jiroji, delivered a speech.\n\nWith his introduction, the building has the same name as the precious gem they are about to reveal, the Azure Star.\n\nSuzuki Jiroji said that he was on time, with a confident and high-spirited tone, he waved his hand, the curtain behind him was pulled open, and all the floor-to-ceiling window curtains on all sides were automatically pulled up. Above the sapphire, it is dazzling.\n\nAmamiya Noriko watched this scene, the corners of her mouth twitched, and as the curtain was fully drawn, a white card fell from above.\n\nAn instant preview of Kaitou Kidd? It\'s weird, she put it up yesterday, don\'t these people have a rehearsal? Just fall off now!\n\nShe thought that the strict inspection downstairs had already received a notice.\n\nNot enough professional opponents really make Kidd head big.\n\n\"Forget it, this face-to-face announcement method is also very good! When the card falls, everyone present will exclaim when they find it?\"\n\n\"Crack-\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was thinking, planning, and suddenly the sound of the gate closing in the background came into his ears, and then all the lights went out instantly.\n\nAnd the top floor, with all the curtains drawn, was instantly plunged into darkness.\n\nSuzuki Jiroji looked at the pitch-dark field in shock and anger, and did not notice that a card fell at his feet.\n\n\"Little Angel Jingguang, you did a good job!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko instantly lowered her body and squatted down, picked up a disguise mask from her skirt and put it on her face.\n\nUntie the bow tie and replace it with a small black rubber band.\n\nTaking off the sandals that affected her movement and putting on gloves, Amamiya Noriko ran lightly towards the stage.\n\nIt’s a good thing, and it’s all about the body. Although it’s only a small improvement, it can still be effective when accumulated.\n\nPeople are lovable and have better eyesight, including in poor lighting conditions.\n\nAnyway, she kept her eyes open the moment the light disappeared, and her eyes adapted very quickly.\n\nIt took less than 10 seconds for her to get used to the start after changing the equipment. When she rushed to the stage and turned over, she was shocked to find that Jiro Yoshi Suzuki, who was originally on the stage, fell to the ground, and a figure with a uniform figure was beside the showcase.\n\nAmamiya Noriko directly bullied her up, and it was a kick when she flew up.\n\n\"puff--\"\n\nThe other party probably did not expect that someone would attack him at this time, and was kicked out by Amamiya Noriko a few times.\n\nAnd Yumiya Noriko has vaguely confirmed that this is Toko, because of the skin color, it is more difficult to see the outline in the dark than others.\n\n\"Tuozi, what gems are you grabbing from me?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wondered for a moment, and suddenly heard the sound of the east window being shattered by gunshots, and then the second sound of the glass detonated the east glass.\n\nA large number of glass fragments splashed into the crowd. Even if the glass was broken, the crowd became more panicked.\n\nAmamiya Noriko vaguely saw a fat man who bravely blocked a lot of glass fragments and fell down with scarlet blood.\n\nThis shows that he really didn\'t do it voluntarily.\n\nMoreover, Gin reached into Fatty\'s clothes and took something, and it could be vaguely seen that it was a flat box.\n\nMaster Qin\'s task was mostly completed, Amamiya Noriko glanced at the place and immediately turned to look at Amuro Toru, who was out of the darkness and had already covered his face with a black cloth.\n\nHer cold voice: \"Shameful thief, I won\'t let you take the gem away.\"\n\nAt this moment, she is the light of the righteous path guarding the Suzuki family\'s gem, and Kaitou Kid\'s notice has been recovered.\n\nAmuro looked at the petite woman in front of him, but he didn\'t expect that the Suzuki consortium would have such bodyguards hidden.\n\nHis eyes suddenly narrowed, and he looked behind the woman, facing the direction of the blasted glass. The task instruction he received was to wait for the gem showcase to be opened.\n\nIn this case, if it can be opened, is it a sniper rifle? !\n\nAmamiya Noriko saw Amuro looking directly behind her, and she rolled sideways to avoid it.\n\nA 7.62mm sniper bullet shot from a PSG-1 sniper rifle that spanned nearly 500 meters hit the corner of the glass of the showcase.\n\nAll the stress concentrated on one corner crushed the hard tempered glass, and by the time Amomiya Noriko got up, Amuro Toru had already smashed the cracked glass of the showcase with one punch, grabbed the gems and turned around and sprinted.\n\nAmamiya Noriko gritted her teeth slightly. Toko reminded her just now that she was very grateful, but she was really rough when the gem was snatched from the front.\n\nAlthough the winery is not a multi-wine alliance