(446, 5, 19, 'Chapter 18: : guess the riddle', 'Although the soft and waxy voice is a bit contrasting, Sonoko\'s eyes are still shining, and she finally recalls the very cool Noriko in kindergarten.\n\nXiaolan was stunned for a while, and felt that Amamiya Noriko was very powerful, but she still thoughtfully reached out and patted her skirt to smooth it, reminding her in a low voice.\n\n\"Noriko... don\'t lift your legs so high next time.\"\n\n\"It\'s alright, I\'m wearing safety pants.\" Amamiya Noriko said, seeing Kudo Shinichi\'s look of disappointment, \"...Do you have to be so disappointed?\"\n\nXiaolan turned her head and stared at Kudo Shinichi.\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t want to talk anymore. The famous detective he planned to fight for the first time was destroyed by Noriko Amamiya. Hearing this, he just glanced at this person who felt extremely good about himself.\n\nBut Xiao Lan stared at herself and couldn\'t explain it: \"What are you talking about! I\'m disappointed that I didn\'t have the chance to shoot!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko suddenly said: \"Oh, then I understand.\"\n\n\"You know a hammer, you don\'t do it anymore?\"\n\n\"I was robbed by you when I was about to shoot!\"\n\n\"I did that to protect you.\"\n\n\"I just wanted to protect you too!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"...Thank you.\"\n\n  \"you are welcome.\"\n\nXiao Lan lifted the alarm bell and helplessly pulled the two people away, reminding them that there was another person standing in front of them.\n\nThe exploding head was a bit fat, and was swept away by Yumiya Noriko and lost his center of gravity.\n\nHowever, the head of Mohigan, who was dislocated by Kudo Shin\'s twisted arm, is still there. He is already in the middle of Fan Jin\'s lift, completely lost his mind. He only reacts when he is watched. He supports the dislocated arm with one hand and subconsciously retreats two times. step.\n\nWhat happened to the current junior high school students? !\n\nIs the cuter the more ruthless?\n\nWhen he went back, he had to find trouble with that bitch. The white lotus flower that he said was just a little cuter and more beautiful. His jaw hurt when he looked at it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled at him and said, \"That...\"\n\nMo Xigan said in an instant: \"It\'s a girl from your Didan Middle School who asked us to teach you a lesson! She is in the second grade of junior high school, with short hair and long hair. She is very self-righteous! I can help you teach her a lesson. !\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"...\"\n\nCan you give me a chance and have some professional ethics?\n\nAs for who came to make trouble, she and Kudo Shinichi knew who it was, and they used you to confess?\n\nShe didn\'t hear any voice on her face: \"Since you don\'t want to say who asked you to come...\"\n\n\"I\'m willing to say it!! She gave me 30,000 yen to let us come, I can give you all the money and teach her a lesson for you!!\"\n\nMohigan held his dislocated arm and cried bitterly with tears streaming down his face. He didn\'t know if it was because of the pain or if he was frightened by Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko twitched the corners of her mouth, \"Forget it, save the money to go to the nearby hospital for the two of them to see.\"\n\nShe stopped by the taxi stop to help them call a taxi or two. It doesn\'t matter how the three of them are, she will just deal with the key people later.\n\nMohigantou was very moved in the taxi and said to Noriko Amemiya, \"Arigado!\"\n\nIt can be seen that he is sincere, and the extraordinarily sincere eyes make Noriko Amamiya feel that even the rejection of this snakeskin confession may be effective, but she does not want to be confessed by someone with tears and snot.\n\n\"In the future, change from evil to righteousness and be a good person!\"\n\nMo Xigan was very serious: \"Yes!\"\n\nShinichi Kudo was speechless as he looked at the taxi that went away: \"Is this the Stockholm effect? ​​I think he might consciously avenge you later?\"\n\n\"It\'s possible, but it\'s a piece of people\'s will and can\'t be rejected casually.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko had a serious face.\n\nKudo Shinichi knew that she definitely didn\'t care what happened to them.\n\nSonoko and Xiaolan grabbed Noriko Amamiya and asked around, isn\'t she very weak?\n\n\"???I\'m healthy, I\'m in great shape, I can run a few kilometers without panting!\"\n\nSonoko hugged Noriko Amamiya excitedly: \"That\'s great, I\'m afraid that one day Noriko\'s condition will worsen and she won\'t be able to come to school.\"\n\nXiaolan nodded: \"We are also very worried about your body, Noriko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in her heart that you should have known that I am very strong if you have the power of observation like Shinichi.\n\nNo, Shinichi knows that I am powerful, so what did you mean by rushing to protect me at first, Amamiya Noriko looked sideways at Kudo Shinichi.\n\nShin Kudo is very handsome with one hand in his pocket, and he doesn\'t look guilty at all.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko still felt it. This famous detective couldn\'t hold back anymore. If you want to say why, boys will start to have a chance of triggering the second state when they reach junior high school.\n\nThere was a little accident on the way to school. She entered the school gate a little late, but she was not late. She hurried to change her shoes. Noriko Amamiya was more relaxed because she had a patient card.\n\nMaybe because of this, UU reading www.uukanshu.com has quite a few patients. When she opened the shoe cabinet, a love letter was placed on her indoor shoes.\n\nSonoko changed her shoes and saw this: \"Wow, as expected of Kiko.\"\n\nXiaolan turned her head and smiled: \"Kiko is in love again.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko spread her hands and opened it directly this time to take a look. It was another appointment to see you after school. This time it became the rooftop. Because the handwriting was different, it was definitely not the one from yesterday.\n\nShe casually wrote a note in response to yesterday\'s note and put it in the shoe cabinet, roughly saying that she didn\'t take it apart at the time, only to find out that she was very sorry when she got home. I don\'t know if the other party could receive it. know who.\n\nBut this made her heart light up, and she gave two love letters to Kudo Shinichi.\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"???\"\n\n\"One was from yesterday, and one was received just now. The detective can help me find out who it is?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi has black lines all over his head, he is a dignified future detective, want to investigate this kind of thing? It is impossible to think!\n\nAmamiya Noriko added: \"There are very few clues. Both of them are quite mysterious. They don\'t say who they are at all. It\'s okay if you can\'t find out Shinichi.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi put the two love letters in his pocket, \"It\'s just two love letters, don\'t think that a little trick will be useful, that is, it is difficult for me to guess a riddle.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about the difficulty of guessing riddles, the kind that Dr. Akasa came up with?\n\n\"Then I\'ll know who it is before I go to the rooftop to meet after school, right?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi nodded disdainfully.\n\n\"Nice! As expected of you.\"\n\nAfter arriving in the classroom, Shinichi Kudo quickly took out two love letters to find clues, what did that guy think the riddle was so simple? Does 1+1 equal 2? !'),
(447, 5, 52, 'Chapter 51: : Raiders', 'Kudo Shinichi calmly looked at Amamiya Noriko, who was laughing while covering her stomach.\n\nIt\'s been nine years, exactly nine years. Who knows how he got here in these nine years? ! !\n\nIn an instant, a sad and lonely picture of snowflakes fluttering by the phone booth appeared in his heart.\n\nIt\'s really not easy for me.\n\nKudo Shinichi put aside the messy thoughts, and asked Noriko Amamiya to stop tidying up here and arrange it together. Otherwise, how would she explain it?\n\nDid you take a powerful pill?\n\nAmamiya Noriko still believes that Kudo Shinichi can completely disguise the scene perfectly.\n\nJust like he can always put together the truth at the scene where the clues are fragmented, all, almost, reverse.\n\nKudo Shinichi combined the rack cart and other tools inside to create a device that can kick the door open with his strength. It is similar to the lever principle and is not complicated.\n\nAfter Noriko Amamiya watched it, I would be fine with me.\n\nBut I am too strong to use this.\n\nAmamiya Noriko watched as Kudo Shin wiped away all the clues she had left behind, and nodded: \"The strongest criminal is indeed the strongest detective.\"\n\nAt least half of the sentence was complimenting himself, but Shinichi Kudo just gave her a look and felt it for himself.\n\n\"You broke the door too loudly. Stay on the rooftop for a while. When someone asks you, they say you are looking at the scenery.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi waved his hand and went down first to tell Xiaolan and Sonoko that she was alright.\n\nSerious people, who would suspect that Amamiya Noriko\'s small arms and legs are the murderer who destroyed the door, so to tell the truth, it needs to be excavated.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pushed open the door to the rooftop, and the sun came at eight or nine in the morning.\n\nShe closed the door neatly. She had such a fair skin, how could she get darker if she couldn\'t get sunburned?\n\n\"Are you all right?\"\n\nHearing the words, Amamiya Noriko turned to the stairs, the blond hair and wheat-skinned elder brother Furuya Zero.\n\nJiang Guling looked at the little **** the stairs and turned around, her eyes were as clear as blue waves, and her smile filled with joy was as perfect as a crescent moon without any flaws, and her angel-like smile brightened her eyes.\n\n\"It\'s alright, thank you big brother for your concern.\"\n\nYugu Ling stared blankly for a while, only to react under Amamiya Noriko\'s bewildered gaze, and returned Amamiya Noriko\'s cell phone to her first.\n\nAmamiya Noriko happily took over the phone: \"Fortunately, the phone is fine. The photos of me and my eldest brother are all in the phone.\"\n\nJiang Gu Ling looked at her simple smile, at least he guarded that smile: \"It\'s a pity that the bad guy was not caught.\"\n\nIn the end, the camouflage man suddenly rushed out of the stairs to the shopping mall. In a crowded place, he couldn\'t even aim lightly, and he couldn\'t shoot at all. He ran away.\n\n\"He\'s here.\"\n\nKiko Amamiya squatted down and patted the door on the ground. Ling Gu Ling kept looking at Kiko Amamiya, only then did she realize that this somewhat strange door panel had a small depression in the middle, which was obviously the hit point.\n\nSeeing that Amamiya Noriko wanted to lift the door, but looked like she couldn\'t lift it at all, Jiang Gu Ling bent over and opened the door, and saw the man pressing down below.\n\n\"I\'m so weak, I\'m Noriko Amamiya, big brother, what\'s your name?\"\n\n\"Amuro Toru.\"\n\n\"Touni sauce?\"\n\n\"...call my last name.\"\n\nAmemiya Noriko said obediently, \"Brother Amuro.\"\n\nToru Amuro was a little familiar with Noriko Amuro, and he was almost used to it. After all, he took a group photo with him from the beginning, ignoring the doll costume that was supposed to be the master.\n\nHe squatted down to check the man\'s injury, and tilted his head to see how messy the storage room was.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the appearance of Touko earnestly collecting information, Touko, your strategy is a bit difficult, isn\'t it? Isn\'t this heartwarming?'),
(448, 5, 49, 'Chapter 48: : taste the taste of the prey', '\"Sister Mingmei, what a coincidence.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the doll over there, and turned back to greet Miyano Akemi first.\n\n\"Noriko is also on vacation? Alone?\"\n\nMiyano Akimi asked Amamiya Noriko by the hand.\n\n\"Nikiko should be careful if he encounters any bad people by himself, will you come with us?\"\n\nAkiko Amamiya and Hideo Akai glanced at each other. The latter, Hideichi Akai\'s pseudonym, Moroshida, smiled a little, but didn\'t have any opinion.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pondered: \"I am a 100-watt light bulb, do you dare to have it?\"\n\nBut she wasn\'t interested in being a light bulb either, and the two became hot soon after they met.\n\nAnd I don\'t know what will happen if Miyano Akemi and Furuya Rei meet. They have known each other since they were two children, and they can be regarded as childhood sweethearts.\n\nI don\'t know if I can recognize it now.\n\nThe old thief in Qingshan is really controlled by his childhood sweethearts, and I can\'t wait to arrange for a little bit of drama.\n\nAnd at first glance, she was not arranged by Qingshan, and she had no childhood sweethearts.\n\nNo, Kudo Shinichi counted her childhood sweethearts, although it didn\'t have any useful effect, even counting the points did not contribute to her at all.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and Miyano Akimi chatted for a while, worried that Touko would not be able to catch up, so they found a reason to leave and continue to chase.\n\nMiyano Akemi looked at the petite figure of Kiko Amami in the crowd, and suddenly patted her head: \"Oh, I forgot to tell Kiko that Shiho will come after waiting, I\'ve always wanted them to get acquainted. .\"\n\nShuichi Akai looked away from Noriko Amamiya and nodded, \"There will be opportunities in the future.\"\n\nMiyano Akemi nodded, then smiled gently: \"First, let\'s introduce Shiho to you.\"\n\n…\n\nAmamiya Noriko missed, and temporarily lost Ai-chan, who was about to get it, but she still picked up Touko.\n\nSeeing the clumsy doll struggling through the crowd, she couldn\'t help but smile.\n\n\"But who is Touzi looking for?\"\n\nDue to her height, Noriko Amamiya was not able to see enough on tiptoes. The 12-year-old girl was completely overwhelmed by the crowd.\n\nIf it wasn\'t for Touzi\'s huge doll costume, she wouldn\'t be able to see it at all.\n\nYou can only find other ways to look at the overall vision.\n\nAmamiya Noriko stood on tiptoe and looked around reluctantly, and suddenly her eyes lit up.\n\nAfter a while, Amamiya Noriko crowded across the street and entered a military club.\n\nThe layout is quite distinctive. As soon as you enter the gate, there is a pile of trenches and vegetation camouflage or something, as if you have entered a jungle battlefield.\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at the ghillie suit, then turned to look at the club\'s merchandise.\n\nMainly the telescope.\n\nIn the store now, besides her, there is only one other customer and the boss who is looking at hats.\n\n\"Little sister, who are you looking for?\"\n\nThe boss behind the counter who was cleaning the binoculars looked at the little man who entered his shop and said.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pointed to the telescope he was cleaning.\n\n\"I\'m looking for a telescope.\"\n\nThe boss wondered for a while, then took Noriko Amemiya to the telescope, \"Little girl, what are you buying this for?\"\n\n\"Look at the scenery.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tried the binoculars, and chose a random one to pay, and simply made the boss face her immature face a bit unmatched.\n\nWatching her walk out of the store, the boss shook his head and received another customer in the store.\n\nHe was also a strange customer. He bought everything from shoes to hats at the store and paid for it directly.\n\n\"It\'s weird, maybe this is the holiday.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko bought a telescope and went directly to the shopping mall in the Cuphu Commercial Plaza. The shopping mall here is also very high-rise, and you can look at the pedestrian street leading to the commercial plaza in all directions. It is an excellent observation point.\n\nIn fact, the Ferris wheel is not bad, but the Ferris wheel keeps turning, and she comes down again after turning around.\n\nAlthough there were times when she stopped, it meant that a bomb was loaded, and Noriko Amamiya would not go if she had nothing to do. She hadn\'t learned the skills to defuse bombs.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was in the shopping center, looking through the glass to the crowd on the pedestrian street.\n\nThe doll costume of Rei Yugu is quite recognizable. It was found in the crowd at once, and it seemed to be besieged by a group of children.\n\n\"It\'s miserable, so where are you looking for someone?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tutted, looking for a strange person in front of Yugu Zero, but a slight footstep suddenly sounded behind her, Amamiya Noriko\'s keen hearing caught this movement, and turned slightly to look behind her. people.\n\n\"Little girl, I think the person he\'s looking for is me.\"\n\nTall and tall, wearing a camouflage T-shirt, pants, leather boots, and a grass-green camouflage sun hat, some dark skin and strong muscles, with a stern face and sharp eyebrows, he was another customer in the military store at that time.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s thoughts turned sharply, if he hadn\'t pretended to pick a hat and blocked his face, he would have noticed something wrong with him, but what should we do now?\n\nWith an uneasy look on her face, she looked at each other with her eyes, she seemed to have no weapons or tools, and she looked like she was empty-handed.\n\nBut this camouflage suit fits too well, and it fits directly with his temperament. It gives the impression that this person has fought and killed in the jungle.\n\nNot on the same level as the person who kidnapped her before.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at him in fear, and said in a weak voice, \"Uncle won\'t bully me as a child, right?\"\n\n\"Hehe, if you are obedient, maybe not.\"\n\nThe camouflage man glanced around. After all, he was still in the shopping mall. People were pulling in, so he couldn\'t do anything here.\n\n\"Hand over your phone, I know you have it.\"\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya heard the words, UU was reading www.uukanshu. com understands when this guy found out about him. It is estimated that he found them when he took a group photo with Jiang Guling. Instead of directly looking for Jiangguling, he found himself.\n\nIn the face of such a big camouflage muscular man, Amamiya Noriko, who was powerless, could only hand over the phone.\n\nBut when he reached into his pocket to take the phone, \"Da da da da-\"\n\nIn less than a second, it was sent.\n\nIn blind play at the speed of light, although Matsuda Jinping is handsome, he is definitely faster than him.\n\n  Help-\n\nAt the bottom of the shopping mall, Miyano Akimi and Akai Shuichi just met with Miyano Shiho. Before they could introduce it, Miyano Akimi felt her phone vibrate. After opening the email, she couldn\'t help but widen her eyes.\n\nKiko-chan: Help, 5F.\n\nAkai Shuichi, who had been watching her reaction to the email, said, \"What\'s wrong?\"\n\nMiyano Akemi hurriedly showed him, \"Kiko is asking for help, the fifth floor.\"\n\nThe 13-year-old Miyano Shiho said calmly next to him: \"You guys go up, I\'ll go to the monitoring room.\"\n\nShuichi Akai and Akemi Miyano looked at each other and rushed towards the elevator.\n\nOn the other side, Kudo Shinichi and Xiaolan were forcibly matched by Sonoko and failed. After they reacted, they realized that Amamiya Noriko was gone, and they hurriedly searched around.\n\nIn the shopping mall, the camouflage man confiscated Amemiya Noriko\'s mobile phone, and asked a personal shopping mall staff to let him hand over the mobile phone and a note to the doll man outside.\n\nIn the shopping mall, he used Noriko Amamiya\'s binoculars to look at the puppet-like figure in the plaza below. He was hiding in the shadows, and only a faint light could see the corners of his mouth rising and a sinister smile.\n\nShowing a set of top white teeth.\n\n\"Haha, let\'s taste what it\'s like to be hunted by prey.\"\n\n​​'),
(449, 5, 16, 'Chapter 15: : Distillery Benming Year', 'Childhood childhood friend A glared angrily at Noriko Amamiya, who was being guarded by Sonoko, meaning that this matter was not so easy to end, and immediately pulled Yamaki-san away.\n\nAfter all, he was a general in the basketball club, but the tall and tall Yamaki didn\'t resist. The relationship between the two was complicated.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smacked her lips in her heart, an adolescent child.\n\nSonoko and the others are here, so there is no way to fix the tail, and it will be troublesome to go back.\n\nXiaolan turned around and took a handkerchief to help Amamiya Noriko gently wipe her tears, while comforting her softly.\n\nSonoko, on the other hand, helped Amamiya Noriko to denounce the shrinking man, Yamaki, for venting his anger. As for the other one, he was defined as a vicious woman.\n\nAmamiya Noriko wiped off the eye drops a few times and said strangely, \"I\'m fine, Xiaolan Yuanzi, are you underestimating me too much?\"\n\nIn the hearts of these two, is she a fragile microbe?\n\nShe helped Yuanzi deal with other children in kindergarten, and she played the football team in elementary school. Isn\'t this record good?\n\nThe two continued to comfort her while saying no.\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at Kudo Shinichi.\n\n  How about you?\n\nShin Kudo put his hand in his pocket to express his stance. He didn\'t comfort him, and he felt that he didn\'t need comfort.\n\nAlthough Amamiya Noriko gave her a roll of eyes, this is the impression she should have.\n\nXiaolan and Sonoko also plan to comfort Noriko on the way back. They feel that Noriko has never suffered this kind of grievance all the time. She is treated as a treasure. Now that it seems okay on the surface, in fact, she must be very aggrieved.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko repeatedly said that she was fine, that she was OK, and then she went to participate in club activities as if she was no one else.\n\nShe originally cried a little just to let this childhood sweetheart A have a taste of being greeted by someone she likes, but she didn\'t expect that these three people were peeking at her again.\n\nIt seems that there are too many delicate settings.\n\nXiaolan and Yuanzi were very helpless and could only entrust Shinichi from the same club to take care of them.\n\nShinichi was instructed for a long time, and after being relieved, he said to Amemiya Noriko on the way to the football club: \"We didn\'t hear the voice between you very well, but you must have refused at that time, right? You know when you laugh at that time. .\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko briefly explained the story, it was harmless, and she also had attribute points. She originally planned to match the pair along the way, but since they don\'t want it, then forget it.\n\nKudo Shinichi was quite emotional: \"Woman.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways: \"Women?\"\n\nSeeing that the range attack swept to the side of Amamiya Noriko, Shin Kudo coughed dryly: \"Cough, can you exclude me? You are already beyond this level of existence.\"\n\n\"Is this a compliment?\"\n\n\"...Of course it is.\"\n\n\"Oh, man, you hesitated for half a second, forget it, do I look weak?\"\n\n\"Yes, if it wasn\'t for playing football in elementary school, I also think you are weak, physically.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi nodded with certainty, people who have a cold and fever every few days, will they be in good health?\n\nIt\'s just that he knows that playing football can test most of the muscles in his body, and if he keeps running, a sick person can\'t play like Amamiya Noriko.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a card from her pocket and threw it to Kudo Shinichi.\n\nAfter Kudo Shinichi took it, he looked at the fitness card, the golden annual svip, and he looked at Noriko Amamiya speechlessly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko invited, \"Do you want to exercise together?\"\n\n\"I don\'t even know where to start complaining, when did you start?\"\n\n\"In the fifth grade of elementary school, wasn\'t there anyone who could confess to me at that time?\"\n\n\"It\'s been two years...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi secretly looked at Noriko Amamiya\'s figure, her small arms and calves were too deceptive.\n\nNo, it was deliberately kept. If there were girls with all muscles, few people would like them.\n\nShin Kudo returned the card to Noriko Amamiya, \"You are a very successful character that middle school students will like.\"\n\n\"Ah, it\'s a little troublesome that Xiaolan and the others believe it.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t help but said, \"Don\'t get sick every day, it\'s not so easy to believe, how many times they have visited.\n\nHaving said that, Kudo Shin felt a little bad when he saw Noriko Amamiya\'s small mouth but stopped talking.\n\n  \"No way?\"\n\n\"I\'m a little sick, maybe I\'ll catch a cold tomorrow.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko explained honestly.\n\nKudo Shinichi can\'t speak, it\'s better if you have a cold today!\n\nAfter going to the football club, Amamiya Noriko just sat quietly watching them play football because she was not feeling well.\n\nThinking about the next strategy and policy in my heart, today is really troublesome enough. Although it is good for everyone to confess, the troubles left by uncertainty are also real.\n\nCompared to this, it seems like it\'s about to start, so I just put the matter here first.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked up at the sky, counted the time with her fingers, pinched her fingers, and found that the wine in the winery was starting to be filled with water.\n\nAlthough it has been mixed with water for a long time, this year\'s efforts are extraordinarily large. UU reading www.uukanshu.com\n\nIt was a magical year, with a large number of high-quality fake wines joining the organization undercover.\n\nFirst, the FBI investigator Akai Shuichi infiltrated the organization, codenamed \'Rye Whiskey\'.\n\nThen came the Japanese Public Security\'s Yugu Ling and Zhufu Jingguang, who took the pseudonym Amuro Toru and got the code name \'Bourbon\', and Zhu Fu Jingguang got the code name \"Scotch Whiskey\".\n\nThen there is the CIA intelligence officer Ei Hai, the pseudonym Mizuna Rena, the code name is \'Kiele\', her father Ethan Hondo has also been lurking in the organization.\n\nThere is another one, the top scientist of the organization who came back from the United States, Miyano Shiho, the later Ai Haibara, codenamed \'Shirley\'!\n\nThis group of undercover agents did not know each other was undercover.\n\nBut this does not prevent the only real wine, good wine, gin, said: The nightmare of labor and management has begun.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who came back to drink water after wiping away his sweat after kicking the ball, shuddered when he saw this: \"Your smile is very strange.\"\n\n\"Bah, then I really want to be a beautiful girl quietly. There are a lot of things going on this year.\"\n\n\"Do you think a sensible person like me would believe such nonsense?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi raised his eyebrows, Amamiya Noriko will stop and not let anyone confess? How is it possible, just like today\'s classmate Yamagi, he will open the door in the morning, and the group of boys who play football with him, Amamiya Noriko has been beaten by one by one just by sitting next to him.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was silent and sighed: \"No way, the increase in physique also includes appearance.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t know why, but he understood the main idea, and couldn\'t help but say, \"You can be a little humble with me, too. You dare to blush when others say you\'re cute.\"\n\n\"Che, when you are complimenting me.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: Labor and management are not praising you!');
