(450, 5, 7, 'Chapter 6: : Coach, I want to learn', 'Black Feather Pirates One.\n\nKuroba Kaito\'s father, the first-generation Kaitou Kid, is also a teacher of Belmod and Yukiko Kudo\'s disguise.\n\nIt\'s just that the so-called little tricks of the inferior Jiuliu, how could the upper-class eldest lady of the Amemiya family like these things.\n\nShe wanted to say that, but Conan\'s world of disguise is too easy to use.\n\nThe appearance and body shape can be disguised at will, and the voice can also be a voice changer produced by Dr. A Li, which is almost seamless.\n\nDon\'t you learn one?\n\nIn fact, Belmode has learned the technology of voice changing, and it is ok without a voice changer.\n\nThat night, Kudo Shinichi had already learned from Maurilan that the library was haunted at night. As a future famous detective, how could he believe these nonsense?\n\nKudo Shinichi suddenly remembered, isn\'t Noriko Amemiya sitting in the library?\n\n\"Isn\'t Amamiya from the Book Committee? What does she think?\"\n\nMao Lilan tilted her head and thought about Noriko Amamiya\'s reaction in the afternoon, and whispered, \"I always feel that Noriko listened, but she didn\'t respond.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was not surprised, and said casually: \"That guy, she must also think the ghost is very naive.\"\n\nMao Lilan was dissatisfied, but still tried to persuade Shinichi not to go, feeling very scary.\n\nBut how could Shinichi be such a half-assed person? Mao Lilan looked at his back and remembered the recent state of Shinichi keeping a distance from her, so he followed.\n\nThe two children sneaked back to the school at night, and met Kuroba Rouichi in the library who frightened the children while keeping a secret code.\n\nKuroba Rouichi\'s appearance was very exciting, sitting on a high bookshelf, holding a book called \"Gentlemen of Phantom Thieves\" in his hand, while speaking with a unique magnetic voice very similar to Shuichi Akai.\n\n\"Don\'t you think that you just read the preface at the beginning of the story and thought that the whole book was about? This world is more profound than you imagined, and many things cannot be explained.\"\n\nIn response to Kudo Shinichi\'s analysis just now that the so-called ghost phenomenon is caused by curtains and moonlight, he refuted the fact that it is not one-sided, for example, he is really here.\n\nNext, Kuroba Rouichi\'s words were filled with hints of riddles, asking Kudo Shinichi to search for the treasure and take on the challenge.\n\nIn the end, Xiaoxiu frightened the child with a flying knife.\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi was angry for his dangerous behavior, he turned his head and left, as if he had disappeared.\n\nAfter the two children, Shinichi and Ran, left, Kuroba Rouichi fell out of the window again.\n\nAmamiya Noriko climbed to the window sill from outside and sat.\n\n\"My child, this is a very dangerous move.\"\n\n\"With my skill, I won\'t fall down here.\"\n\n  \"confidence?\"\n\n\"Super confident.\"\n\nBlack Feather Pirate laughed, thinking that the children he met today were a bit interesting.\n\nA very smart little boy who is good at reasoning, a little girl who is afraid of ghosts but has the courage to do something with him, and a little girl who guards him outside the windowsill, not thinking about what to do if he falls, but is super confident that he will not fall.\n\n\"Then what are you doing to me, little boy?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was quick to talk, straight to the point: \"I want to learn the art of disguise.\"\n\n  \"...why?\"\n\nBlack Feather Pirate obviously couldn\'t hold back his smile. Want to learn Disguise? In other words, do you know that he is Kaito Kidd? But why does an elementary school student know he is Kaito Kidd and want to learn disguise with him?\n\nHe is still a magician in essence, why didn\'t he learn magic?\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that I adore your wife, Chikage Kuroba, and the reason why the phantom thief lady is cool?\n\nHeiyu Pirate thought for a moment, then nodded and said, \"Then let\'s take a small test.\"\n\n\"Test?\"\n\n\"The test, the challenge that the kid named Kudo Shinichi accepted just now, if you can complete it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways, \"Why don\'t you change it?\"\n\nBlack Feather Pirate was surprised, the little girl didn\'t look like she would be afraid of difficulties: \"What? Do you think it\'s too difficult?\"\n\n  \"too easy.\"\n\n\"Children, the world is very big, and the corner you can see now doesn\'t represent the world.\"\n\n\"Since you insist, then this is the test.\"\n\nThe Black Feather Pirate was puzzled for a moment. Could it be that the puzzles he prepared were really simple?\n\nOf course, it wasn\'t easy. After that, Kudo Shinichi, Maurilan, and Dr. A Li worked all day, running around to solve all the puzzles.\n\nBut unfortunately, Shinichi Kudo, who was still young, misunderstood the meaning in the last step. In the end, he thought that Kuroba Rouichi was his father\'s friend. The reason for these puzzles was to let them see the beautiful sunset and go out for a walk.\n\nThe last step is also the key to everything before the series. One step was wrong, and the result was that now on the roof, Kudo Shinichi and Maurilan shouted into the air to thank the uncle from last night.\n\nKudo Shinichi couldn\'t solve the puzzle in Kuroba Piichi\'s plan, and then he gave the solution to his father, Yuu Kudo, and then the purpose of sending the message was not achieved.\n\nHowever, Yusaku Kudo saw through it long ago, and before that, he had asked Yukiko Kudo to bring the letter to her teacher when she saw her.\n\nA big \"!\" in response to Kuroba\'s \"?\".\n\nKuroba Piichi: Can you stop me next time?\n\nYusaku Kudo: Of course!\n\nNow on the roof, Kudo Shin faced the air: \"That uncle last night! You should hear me! I will put my thanks in the wallet you gave me yesterday, you must come and get it. !\"\n\n\"Stop shouting, he won\'t go get it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko came up from the stairwell and looked at Kudo Shinichi with interest.\n\nMao Lilan was surprised: \"Kiko?\"\n\nKudo Shin was stunned for a moment, and then said, \"I knew you were in the library last night. Although you weren\'t interested, if you listened to it, you would have a foot in it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said with a doting face: \"You guessed it right.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s head was full of black lines: \"I guessed it right. What does it mean? What do you mean by what you just said?\"\n\n\"It means that you guessed wrong in the end. The answer is not as simple as letting you look at the sunset. If you just want to look west, you only need to draw a W. There is no need to draw S-→W.\"\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi said this, in retrospect, he really felt that the last level seemed a bit too simple.\n\nBut he is not the Shinichi Kudo ten years later, UU reading www. Although uukanshu.com pondered, it did not deduce the real way to solve the puzzle all of a sudden.\n\nSeeing this, Amamiya Noriko had no choice but to take out a sticky note and draw on it.\n\nBecause the last hint is actually a [symbol], from the beginning of the port, the ruins of the city, the water gate, the post office, the rice flower middle school, and the district office, the symbols used in these places on the map are connected together with other hints on the way to solve the puzzle, And the final direction SW is turned around.\n\nOn the post-it note is OXHIDE, which means cowhide, cowhide.\n\nThe wallet is made of cowhide.\n\nKudo Shinichi watched Amamiya Noriko draw all the way, and naturally fully understood.\n\nHe quickly opened the leather wallet and saw a letter from Kuroba Rouichi to Kudo Yusaku.\n\nAmamiya Noriko patted him on the shoulder to comfort him: \"This is not for you, a child. This gentleman expects that if you can\'t solve it, he will ask your father for help. It\'s just a letter from you, but you have to find a different way.\"\n\nDr. A Li, who was beside him, finally couldn\'t help but say, \"Kiko, aren\'t you also a child?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko rolled her eyes.\n\nKudo Shinichi carefully read the letter, but still raised his head and said to Amamiya Noriko, \"Amamiya-san, thank you.\"\n\n\"You don\'t have to thank me, you can do it too, ten years later. Besides, what you intended to write in it was to thank Xiaolan, right?\"\n\nXiaolan looked at Xinyi with a bewildered expression: \"Huh? Me?\"\n\nThe thin-skinned Kudo Shinichi denied: \"No, no!\"\n\n  \"real??\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko squinted at the two of them and flirted with them. She followed her all the way to get rid of the suspicion of saying the answer directly, and to write about the problem-solving process, so why bother? Don\'t use the plot to test her.'),
(451, 5, 71, 'Chapter 70: : Hawaiian Beginner', 'Seeing that Chie Riho was very self-conscious, Amamiya Noriko nodded, leaned her head over, and fell asleep after a while.\n\nNo matter the quiet environment, the car or the plane, both are suitable for her to sleep.\n\nChieda Riho looked at Noriko Amamiya\'s sleeping face, and she still had a mother-daughter look with Eimi Amamiya.\n\nHawaii, Oahu.\n\nOahu is the most important island in Hawaii.\n\nAbove is the largest city in the Pacific, Honolulu, or \"Honolulu\".\n\nAlthough it is here to learn skills, play is also very important.\n\nIt is not only the capital and economic and cultural center of the state of Hawaii, but also many well-known attractions are gathered around it.\n\nThere is a basin formed by an annular extinct volcano, which means \"moon crater\", as well as Gualani Ranch, \"Jurassic Park\" and \"Godzilla\" have been filmed here.\n\nSix of the eight Hawaiian islands are well-developed, and Oahu is one of them. This traditional cattle ranch has developed many recreational projects based on diverse topography.\n\nHorseback riding, ATV (all-terrain vehicle), jungle adventure, zipline... Amamiya Noriko and Chieda Riho couldn\'t play at all on the first day.\n\nShe is too young, and many projects cannot be played alone. Chieda Riho must take her with her. At the same time, she is also teaching her to ride a horse and drive an all-terrain vehicle.\n\nThen he also arranged for the retired submarine captain to open the back door and take her to the Bowfin submarine in Pearl Harbor, and teach her basic knowledge with the submarine itself.\n\nAs for the hands-on control, should I practice Subject 2, and read the subjects of Subject 1 while practicing?\n\nThere is also a USS Missouri battleship, which is also available for tour. An old American crew member and an old employee of the shipyard showed her the area that was not open to the public, and at the same time taught Noriko Amamiya.\n\nIt\'s not something that can be learned all at once. Noriko Amamiya\'s learning ability has already shocked them, but it\'s not enough to learn it in a month.\n\nThe basic of the most basic, the simple operation process of each post of a large submarine warship, the principle explanation, the precautions, etc.\n\nAmamiya Noriko spent a lot of time on these two things.\n\nI also experienced that the Amamiya Foundation can really get along on the world channel compared to the Japanese channel.\n\nShe had already decided to sleep with her mother for a month when she turned back. In order to have a honeymoon with her wife, she was actually thrown over to learn this kind of thing. The stinky father didn\'t take her daughter seriously.\n\nApart from the two overly advanced courses, Amamiya Noriko also has other somewhat normal ones.\n\nGun learning, shooting, explosives, bomb disposal, combat fighting, wilderness survival, motorcycle driving, vehicle maintenance, etc...\n\nIt is impossible to learn all of them. Even if she has dozens of points of study ability, even if she shouts to stop being a human being, it is impossible to learn all of these in about a month.\n\nThe world of Ke Xue also needs to be reasonable.\n\nHowever, the course was arranged anyway, so Amamiya Noriko just treated it as a variety of games to experience the fun.\n\nShe played with firearms casually in the gun store, her father arranged it, and his own store.\n\nTaking into account Japan\'s national conditions, Amamiya Noriko basically focuses on light guns, pistols, and submachine guns.\n\nNot to mention the pistol models, the mainstream submachine guns, MP5, UMP45, MP5K, P90, Uzi are all tried out.\n\nThe gun store is temporarily closed for the sake of her young lady\'s gun practice, basically preparing guns and ammunition for Amamiya Noriko.\n\nThe manager originally thought that it was just some eldest lady to experience life, especially after seeing the face of Amamiya Noriko, the impression of this Japanese girl was fixed on her cuteness and simplicity.\n\nBut when he watched Noriko Amamiya put her hair in a ponytail and chug around the shooting range with a submachine gun, he moved the cute simplicity back.\n\nHandsome messed up!\n\nThis is totally a battle angel.\n\nAlthough a submachine gun is a light gun, the recoil of a full-automatic burst should not be something a 12-year-old girl can bear.\n\nIt is not uncommon for him to have a wrong posture when shooting, lack of physical fitness, and dislocate his arm due to recoil.\n\nMy lady, this is really not outrageous.\n\nChieda Riho also thinks so, she\'s cute and cute in Japan, and the little devil\'s young lady will let her go abroad when she goes abroad.\n\nEvery day I wake up, swinging on the swing on the hotel balcony while looking at the sea, thinking about what to experience today.\n\nAfter making the decision, he wore shorts and a white T-shirt and a white helmet to fly to his destination on a motorcycle.\n\nIf it hadn\'t been for Amamiya Noriko\'s careful sun protection, wearing silk stockings, ice sleeves, and spraying sunscreen spray, Chieda Riho really thought she had changed her personality.\n\nThe motorcycle was sent by Chieda Riho, and the cyan Kawasaki Ninja customized mini version, so that the 12-year-old Noriko Amamiya can also drive.\n\nAfter customizing it in Japan and shipping it to Hawaii, it is definitely not allowed to drive in Japan, just in case the speed limit is limited to 60 hours per hour, which makes Noriko Amamiya very embarrassed to drive.\n\nOn her side, the coastal road in Hawaii is straight and there are very few vehicles. The drag racing is completely arbitrary, and then the limit is 60. What about this battery car?\n\nChieda Riho herself was 150% at every turn.\n\nThe main reason for driving a motorcycle is that Amamiya Noriko\'s height is a bit reluctant to drive, and not all cars are QQ.\n\nIt is expected that she will be able to drive in the next year. Of course, Noriko Amamiya can drive, but she can drive the left rudder, while Japan and here are right rudder.\n\nAs for the difference, the difference is not big. Subject two must be taken easily once.\n\nLife in Hawaii is very free, Chieda Riho will let Noriko Amamiya maintain the temperament of Miss Amamiya in Japan~www.readwn.com~ It doesn\'t matter here.\n\nExcept for rejecting Amamiya Noriko\'s little idea of ​​dyeing her hair pink, she will basically leave it to her.\n\nOf course, Amamiya Noriko mainly came to study.\n\nHappy time is always short, Amamiya Noriko has had enough fun and studies and misses Xiaolan Yuanzi a little, so she returned to Japan almost at the end of the summer vacation.\n\nAfter being locked in the house by Chieda Riho for a few days, she calmed down. When she came out, it was the lovely and lovely Noriko Amemiya. When she walked out on the street, she turned her head back with just one face.\n\nWhen I went to the shopping street, I was greeted warmly by the aunts and uncles who had not seen her for a while and missed her very much.\n\nAll kinds of snacks and fruits were stuffed into her, and she couldn\'t hold it.\n\nKudo Shinichi leaned against the wall to see this scene, and said, \"You are really liked.\"\n\n\"Ah, long time no see, Shinichi-kun, I didn\'t expect that the first person I saw when I came back was you. How many cases did you encounter during the summer vacation? Thirty?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes also lit up, and she asked while stuffing something into his arms.\n\nKudo Shinichi silently embraced a pile of gifts.\n\nAt the same time, he couldn\'t help but say: \"Thirty cases, are you an idiot? How long is the summer vacation?\"\n\nThe summer vacation of Didan Middle School runs from mid-July to the end of August, and it almost starts on September 1.\n\nIn other words, 45 days, 30 cases can\'t be completed in two days. Is Amamiya Noriko working in the Metropolitan Police Department?\n\n\"Xinyi, what you said is modest, too modest!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said angrily, being too modest is your fault.\n\nKudo Shinichi frowned, \"...\"\n\nYou, Noriko Amamiya, really haven\'t changed at all?'),
