Why do you think I\'m not healthy? It\'s still possible for me to beat your team by myself.\"\n\nA football team for elementary school students is purely entertainment, not even the football club. There is no formal training. If they can\'t play well, how can they shoot a helicopter with football when they encounter a winery in the future?'),
(454, 5, 80, 'Chapter 79: : Masamune Sera', 'Amamiya Noriko looked at the various spectacles of light coming out from behind the pillar, her eyes widened, and her eyes flickered.\n\n\"Amamiya, Noriko\'s surname is Amamiya, doesn\'t it sound good? I\'m Suzuki Sonoko.\"\n\nSonoko was shaken by Zhufu Jingguang\'s gentle smile, feeling great, and then held Noriko Amemiya\'s shoulder and pushed her to the front.\n\nYuanzi is professional in selling girlfriends.\n\n  \"Uh…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko almost didn\'t react, and shyly waved her small hand: \"It doesn\'t sound particularly nice...\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang smiled and said, \"I think it sounds good, you two, are you coming out to play?\"\n\n\"Well, we just watched the movie...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko responded by adjusting the volume of her voice to a shy character.\n\nSonoko took over: \"And then I went shopping around. By the way, big brother, are you carrying a guitar?\"\n\n\"I\'m bass, do you like music?\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang changed the angle so that the two of them could not see the bass box, and took out the white bass.\n\nSonoko nodded: \"I like it, Noriko can sing very well!\"\n\n\"Oh? If there is a chance, I would like to listen to the singing of Rain Palace.\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang cooperated with a smile and said that he had a good impression of such a cute and shy little girl and this rather lively little girl.\n\nIn addition, he was also gentle and kind, and he was quite patient with children.\n\nI don\'t doubt whether Amamiya Noriko really sings well.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pursed her lips and smiled embarrassedly. Sonoko, this is too powerful, right?\n\nIsn\'t this why she doesn\'t need to make any moves?\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang raised his head slightly and looked at the little girl who looked a little lonely because Zhu Xing had gone to buy a ticket, but she was left to stand alone.\n\nHe said to Noriko Amamiya and Sonoko Suzuki, \"Call that girl, and I\'ll teach you how to play the bass, okay?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the corner of his eyes with a gentle smile. Zhu Fu Jingguang\'s eyes were those of phoenix eyes that were raised at the corners of his eyes, and he was very noticeable when he smiled slightly.\n\nNot just talking to the two of them, but after seeing Shiliang Zhenchun being discovered by Zhu Xingda, he understood that Zhu Xingda would not be able to take this little **** a mission together.\n\nIt would be too lonely if left alone.\n\nThat\'s why I saw the two of them come up to talk later.\n\nOf course Noriko Amamiya chose to cooperate.\n\nIn addition to the dramatic use of Touzi\'s footsteps as someone else in the winery, in order not to expose his relatives and Amuro Toru, he committed suicide and destroyed the mobile phone with other people\'s contact information.\n\nBecause the scene was too complicated, Toru Amuro, who happened to see this scene, completely regarded Shuichi Akai as an enemy and believed that he caused the death of his best friend.\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang\'s belief is very lofty, of course, Akai Shuichi\'s cold sentence \"For betrayal, only sanctions can be used to repay... I\'m right!\" It is indeed full of ridicule.\n\nIt\'s just that Shuichi Akai didn\'t know that Toru Amuro was an undercover agent of the Japanese police at the time, and he said that when he was a person from a winery.\n\nSo the chaos of multiple undercover...\n\nSo of course Noriko Amamiya chooses to cooperate with Zhu Fu Jingguang, and that is Xiao Shiliang\'s pure innocence. As a high-end female fighting force in the world of Conan, she will definitely be a good sister in the future.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took the initiative to pull Sonoko up to talk to Shiliang Zhenchun.\n\n\"Hello, do you want to learn bass together?\"\n\nShiliang Zhenchun, who was originally very disappointed, looked at this girl who came to talk with a shy face.\n\n​​'),
(455, 5, 72, 'Chapter 71: :Shopping Street', 'Since it happened to happen, Amamiya Noriko grabbed Kudo Shinichi to help with the things.\n\nIt\'s not that she can\'t hold it, but there are too many, and two small hands are not enough.\n\nThe enthusiastic uncles, aunts, aunts and uncles of the shopping street, under the influence of her shopping from time to time on weekends, eating octopus balls, drinking a cup of milk tea, and eating chicken chops, have regarded her as their baby daughter-in-law and grand-daughter-in-law.\n\nAmamiya Noriko occasionally worries about whether she will gain weight like this, but she seems to be exercising a little too hard, so she doesn\'t get fat.\n\nI accepted it with great peace of mind. Everyone\'s sons and grandsons, I will give me the opportunity to confess to me.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was carrying a bunch of things, had a very dark face.\n\nCan you stop accepting other people\'s wishes? I don\'t have that many hands anymore!\n\nHe really couldn\'t take anything.\n\nFollowed by Kudo Shinichi, who was fully loaded, Amamiya Noriko leisurely took the ice cream and walked to the shadow of the shopping street to avoid direct sunlight.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at her back. Looking closely, Amamiya Noriko was still white and tender. Does this look like someone who went abroad for a whole summer vacation?\n\n\"What have you been doing all summer vacation? It\'s not dark at all, do you stay in your room every day?\"\n\n\"No.\" Amamiya Noriko shook her head, the ponytail at the back of her head swayed, then turned around and blinked at Kudo Shin, reached out and pointed at him with the ice cream, and said in a playful tone, \"I\'ve been with you the whole time. heart.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s heart skipped a beat. Is it so cute? It\'s the feeling of heart palpitations.\n\nSeeing that he was stiff rather than excited, Amamiya Noriko pouted, this person has immunity.\n\nTurning to look at the entrance of the shopping street, Amamiya Noriko\'s e