(456, 5, 69, 'Chapter 68: : Enthusiastic citizens with a sense of justice', 'The situation would be so complicated, and there were reasons why Zuo Tian\'s lifeguard was beyond her expectations.\n\nAfter whispering to Shinichi Kudo, she immediately ran back and forth to the changing room after leaving, changing her clothes.\n\nSo things like water parks are very inconvenient, and you can\'t bring them with you.\n\nShe went back and changed her face, changed into a cleaner\'s clothes, and turned into an old cleaning lady in her fifties or sixties. Even her particularly old face could vaguely show her stunning appearance when she was young.\n\nYi Rongshu, she graduated with full marks from Kuroba Pirates anyway, but her size is too small, so she can\'t grow a few tens of centimeters out of thin air for the time being.\n\nSo she looks like an old woman.\n\nThen he rushed back, passed the back of the toilet and was about to go out to see when Zuo Tian\'s lifeguard was leaving, when he happened to turn up the window from the toilet.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in her heart what are you doing in such a hurry?\n\nSeeing the old woman below staring at him, Zuo Tian rushed to catch Amamiya Noriko, stood at the window and scolded: \"What are you looking at, **** old woman, I\'ll give you another punch—\"\n\nBefore he finished speaking, he saw that the thin old woman\'s foot was kicked like an arrow from a string.\n\nJust when he opened his mouth to react, he kicked and tripped him off the window, completely lost his balance and fell a dog gnawing at the mud.\n\nThe old woman said in a hoarse voice, \"I not only want to see you, but also beat you.\"\n\n\"How can it be repaired!!\"\n\nZuo Tian\'s lifeguard stood up with a muddy face, roared like a vengeful king, raised his hand and clenched his fist and smashed at the old woman.\n\nWhat is respecting the old and loving the young? ! He doesn\'t care about this, dare to let him be so embarrassed, die! !\n\n\"Bang—\"\n\nA very skinny sound, it can\'t be said to be a crisp sound or a collision, but in terms of texture, it is the collision of solid wood and iron.\n\n\"Ooooooo-\"\n\nZuo Tian\'s lifeguard whimpered in pain and knelt down while covering his palm. The fourth metacarpophalangeal, fifth metacarpal phalanx to the hook bone, triangular bone, and pisiform bone of his right palm were hammered into dislocation.\n\nThe little finger and ring finger were completely unable to move, and the pain was excruciatingly painful.\n\nStrength is relative, but what breaks wood and iron is wood.\n\nHe clenched his fist and slammed the hammer down, and Amamiya Noriko raised his fist and hit it up. Everyone stood on the same starting line, and even Amamiya Noriko\'s strength was a little bit of a loss, right?\n\nThen he can\'t blame Amamiya Noriko for his miserable appearance.\n\nThe lifeguard Zuo Tian, ​​who covered his hands and curled up in pain, lowered his head and eyes flashed with incomparable resentment, and suddenly got up and kicked the old woman in front of him with his legs.\n\nShe didn\'t mean to be merciful at all. If a serious old woman was kicked, her old and fragile body would be broken.\n\nBut Noriko Amamiya... slanted her body to avoid this kick.\n\nThen he raised his foot to hook and swept his legs, and when Zuotian lifeguard lost his balance, he hit his back neck with a punch, causing him to lose consciousness.\n\nPhysical sleep aid, usually hitting the neck is a very dangerous behavior, and it is easy to die directly, but Amamiya Noriko is quite good at this.\n\n\"Dead, old woman...\"\n\nZuo Tian\'s eyes rolled up, his eyes darkened, and his mouth was still bitter. At the last moment, his conscious sight vaguely saw the figure in front of him picking up a brick and holding it up high...\n\nAmamiya Noriko has no mercy for the murderer who just took a life. There will be more than a thousand episodes of this kind of murderer in the future.\n\nHowever, he still gave him a sigh of relief, posing as if he was jumping on the street, looking like he was jumping through the window and jumping on the street.\n\nAs for the beating scars on her body, they were made by an old woman who passed by, and the fingerprints will not leave anything behind. Does it have anything to do with her Amamiya Noriko?\n\nAfter that, it was changed to Amamiya Noriko. The matter was done, and there was no need to pretend to be an old woman.\n\nIt just so happened that Kudo Shinichi relied on his keen observation and reasoning ability to catch up, and he stepped on Zuo Tian when he turned over the window by the way.\n\nAnd that\'s it.\n\nKudo Shinichi limped away from Noriko Amamiya.\n\nOriginally prepared to show off his skills and rely on reasoning to find out the murderer and bring him to justice, the modern Sherlock Holmes started from now on.\n\nBut halfway through, the murderer hit the street.\n\nAnd the frantic and irritable reaction after waking up was completely more frank than confession.\n\nThis is not to convict him of the crime, and he doesn\'t even need to corroborate his reasoning.\n\nForget it, at least the deceased rests in peace.\n\nKudo Shinichi limped to Xiaolan and Sonoko. Sato Mikazu took care and comforted them, and the two have recovered a little.\n\nThe road ahead is still long.\n\nOfficer Mumu looked at the murderer being detained by the police, and was a little puzzled. Who was the old woman the prisoner was talking about? It seemed to beat him badly.\n\nIt seems that there are enthusiastic citizens with a strong sense of justice and a strong sense of justice to help the police handle the case.\n\nThe murderer was beaten violently.\n\n\"After all, it was caught, and there is an explanation for the victims and their families.\"\n\nOfficer Mumu sighed.\n\nSato Mikazu has doubts: \"But what is it that beat the murderer like this...\"\n\n\"You\'ll know this when you go back and ask the prisoner. I\'ll **** him back first, and you can deal with the scene.\"\n\n  \"OK.\"\n\nSato Miwako nodded and arranged for the other police officers to start work.\n\nDate Hang said silently from the side: \"It\'s all because I found the murderer too late that the case happened.\"\n\nMatsuda Jin said calmly: \"The prisoner\'s appearance is quite different from the previous portrait. It\'s good that you can see that you have doubts at a glance.\"\n\nSato Miwako glanced at the man wearing sunglasses, \"Who is this?\"\n\n\"I\'m Jinhei Matsuda from the Explosive Ordnance Disposal Squad of the Mobile Group of the Police Department of the Metropolitan Police Department.\"\n\nMatsuda Jinhei took off his sunglasses and looked at Sato Miwako calmly.\n\n\"Hello, Matsuda-kun.\"\n\n\"Miss Sato, hello.\"\n\nThe two met for the first time, and then Mikazu Sato went to arrange work and deal with the leftover site.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at this scene and felt that Sato Mikazu was not bad. In the original book, Matsuda Jinhei confessed before his death with a seven-day relationship, and then there was Xiucheng Zhengguo Takagi Shibu and the determined Shiratori Ren Saburo.\n\nAt present, she has not seen Takagi Shibu and Shiratori Ren Saburo.\n\nAfterwards, due to the murder, the water park notified the decision to temporarily cooperate with the police and gave each visitor a free ticket.\n\nNoriko Amamiya\'s trip to the water park ended before it even started.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko has already begun to feel it, and when she comes out to play, it feels like Kudo Shinichi is there.\n\nThe experience of Xiaolan and Yuanzi is not rich enough. The first time they encountered the scene of the case, they were terrified. Amamiya Noriko accompanied and comforted them for a while. She was gentle, easy-going, and understanding. Xiaolan was firm in her heart. go soft.\n\nAmamiya Noriko kept helping her to the changing room and changed back to her regular clothes, and then went to the car outside the water park.\n\nSeeing that she was fine, Chie Riho said to