over to explain in a low voice, and then patted him on the shoulder: \"Come on!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi had black lines all over his head. He looked down at her face. He felt that he had seen his heart through his face. He never thought that you, who looked so cute and lovely, would have such a black-hearted day.\n\nThen Amamiya Noriko was in a good mood, and walked briskly to see what the scumbag looked like.\n\nOn the way, she met a kind-hearted classmate who wanted to help her get a drink at noon was limping over, Amamiya Noriko waved her hand in a good mood: \"It\'s you, good afternoon~ Is your foot hurt? Are you alright?\"\n\nThe kind-hearted classmate\'s happiness came so quickly that he almost didn\'t react, and said with joy, \"Student Amamiya? I didn\'t. You seem to be in a good mood. Did you encounter anything good?\"\n\n\"Ah, because it seems that a scumbag is going to confess to me.\"\n\n\"???\"\n\n\"Huh?\" Amamiya Noriko looked at his strange face in confusion.\n\nKind-hearted classmate explained carefully: \"That... Amamiya classmate, I\'m not a scumbag...\"\n\n\"???\" It was Kiko Amemiya\'s turn with question marks all over her head. Does it matter whether you are a scumbag or not? She said uncertainly: \"Really?\"\n\n  \"no!\"\n\n\"Oh...\" Amamiya Noriko replied in a low voice, because she had never seen it before, so she still asked, \"Are you the president of the letter agency?\"\n\nThe kind-hearted classmate was relieved: \"No!\"\n\n\"That\'s fine, then I\'ll go first.\"\n\nKind-hearted classmate looked at Amamiya Noriko\'s brisk figure again and sighed, \"It\'s so cute...\"\n\nBut he also suddenly reacted: \"No! That scumbag is the president of the letter club? And he\'s going to confess to Amamiya-san? The pure and kind-hearted Amamiya-san won\'t cheat and agree!?\"\n\nPassing by a girl dragging a big garbage bag: \"Daejeon! Didn\'t you say she was on duty to help me take out the garbage!\"\n\nThe kind-hearted classmate wailed as if he had never heard of it: \"No!!\"\n\nThen he was kicked angrily, \"If you don\'t help, you won\'t help. Do you use such a loud voice?\"\n\nThe pure and kind-hearted student Noriko Amamiya knows that she is a scumbag, and she has her own rejection buff, so how could she agree.\n\nFootball field.\n\nThe football club is ready to start training.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who came back from work, saw Noriko Amemiya sitting next to him drinking a drink, and asked, \"How is it?\"\n\n\"Scumbag biss, such a perfunctory confession has no sincerity at all. Why should I be liked by girls? Do I look like I can be easily tricked?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi is stuck, what is this, because other people\'s confessions are too perfunctory to him, and there is no sense of enjoyment even if they refuse, so Noriko Amamiya, a lover who refuses to confess, is very annoyed?\n\nThe main reason is to delay Kudo Shinichi for a long time, and it is very unpleasant to talk nonsense with the other party for a long time.\n\nAmamiya Noriko bit the straw: \"So where are you?\"\n\n\"It\'s all done. UU Reading www.uukanshu.com really found those letters he had collected in the letter agency, and then sent them out according to the interlaced object you said. I feel... he has gone far.\"\n\n\"Why do you feel lost? We are carrying out justice and helping him find his sincerity. Ten false loves are not as good as a sincere confession.\"\n\nKudo Shin said, \"That\'s you.\"\n\n\"Huh? Is it because you feel pity for him?\"\n\n\"No! I went to training.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi turned around and left, Amamiya Noriko threw the mine directly in his face, can this be picked up?\n\nAmamiya Noriko also got up and followed. Recently, the sports clubs in the high school are all in full swing, and they have already started to prepare for the summer competition of the National College Sports Conference in the summer vacation. As a result, the students in the junior high school are also very motivated.\n\nAfter school at three o\'clock in the afternoon, there is training until six o\'clock. The baseball club on the high school side often trains until seven or eight o\'clock for the summer Jiaziyuan.\n\nIn such a tense situation:\n\n\"Amamiya-san has just finished drinking, so you can sit next to her for a while.\"\n\n\"There\'s no need to start training so soon, let\'s do some preparation for exercise first.\"\n\n\"You must do more for a while to prepare for exercise, otherwise you will be easily injured.\"\n\n\"Okay, everyone, that\'s all for today\'s club activities. See you tomorrow, Amamiya-san~\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was stunned that she hadn\'t touched the football, and was coaxed to sit beside her for a long time, speechless.\n\nKudo Shinichi smiled: \"Isn\'t it good, how relaxed you are by your side.\"\n\nAfter holding it back for a long time, Amamiya Noriko finally managed to say, \"You can\'t just take care of me just because I\'m cute?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"...Yes, you are right.\"'),
(458, 5, 63, 'Chapter 62: : Eyes of Direct Death', 'When Amamiya Noriko and Sonoko came back, Xiao Ran was holding Kudo Shinichi\'s ear.\n\n\"Tell me, did you bully Noriko?\"\n\n\"No, who can bully her.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi escaped from Xiaolan\'s clutches while shouting.\n\nOriginally, she was naturally strong, and she started practicing in the karate club, so Xiaolan\'s combat effectiveness was also a plus.\n\nAfter Kudo Shinichi saw Noriko Amamiya, he pointed, \"If you don\'t believe me, ask her.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it carefully, then pulled Xiaolan\'s sleeve aggrievedly and said, \"Xiaolan, Shinichi murdered me when I was buying a drink.\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nShin Kudo was expressionless, forgetting that the person who couldn\'t be asked the most was Noriko Amamiya.\n\nXiaolan comforted Noriko, but she knew that Shinichi Kudo was still struggling with the disappearance of the recorder from the music club.\n\nIt\'s not surprising that the detective was ruthless when he reasoned.\n\nBut it\'s not right to scare Noriko. What if Noriko catches a cold and has a fever.\n\nXiaolan pulled Kudo Shinichi by the sleeve and whispered to him about the precautions for treating the sick Noriko. He is still a boy and should set an example.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked over there and probably overheard it, and from time to time he looked in agreement with Amamiya Noriko, who nodded his head.\n\nNot only can you play better than me, but your hearing is also so good?\n\nCan she act like a girl, at least not kick open the door with bare feet, fight gangsters with bare hands, and single out the kidnapper?\n\nStill sick.\n\nHere, Kudo Shinichi was grabbed by Xiaolan and lectured, and when he turned around, Noriko Amamiya had already started.\n\nWith a curious look on her face, she went to the group of boys over there and asked, \"what are you guys doing?\"\n\n\"I\'m, I\'m playing a small game.\"\n\n\"Well, it\'s not really any fun.\"\n\n\"That\'s to say, I\'ll just play when I have nothing to do after class.\"\n\nAs soon as a few boys found out that Amamiya Noriko was coming here curiously, they immediately held it back. They were all mature elementary school graduates, so how could they like to play this kind of little game to pass the time?\n\nIn the end, it\'s still a bit naive. As junior high school students, they were bored to play this kind of game.\n\nSerious people who play this?\n\nAmamiya Noriko was puzzled: \"Aren\'t you going to play? Can I be together?\"\n\n  \"Can!\"\n\n  \"no problem.\"\n\n\"Amamiya-san can totally be together.\"\n\nA few boys nodded without hesitation, because they were playing the game of staring. If Amamiya-san came, wouldn\'t they have a chance to look at Amamiya-san in an open and fair manner.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled and nodded as she looked at their promises.\n\nThere are people who can look into her eyes for a minute and not be moved—there are also, but not many!\n\nThe rule is to look at each other. You can\'t take your eyes too far from the other party\'s eyes. You can use various methods to harass them.\n\nThe No. 1 player starts with Noriko Amamiya.\n\nPlayer No. 1 stared at Amamiya Kiko with wide eyes, mainly looking at Amamiya Kiko\'s eyes, but also looking at Amamiya Kiko\'s face as a whole.\n\n\"No matter how you look at it, it\'s not generally cute, hold on...\"\n\nLooking at him, he suddenly saw that Amamiya Noriko had a handsome smile on the corner of his mouth, and blinked his right eye at himself. At that moment, it was as if a trace of electric current ran through his heart, and he couldn\'t help but open his eyes wide.\n\nIs there such a fascinating side to Amamiya Noriko, who has always been cute and lovable? !\n\nHer eyes were too wide open, she couldn\'t help but closed her eyes and rubbed them dry, she was defeated.\n\nWhen he opened his eyes again, Amamiya Noriko pursed her lips and smiled at him, as if to say sorry, I won.\n\nThe No. 1 contestant was still immersed in the appearance of Amamiya Super A, which he did not know if it was a hallucination, so he was put aside by the other two contestants, and the loser was Shichen.\n\nThe No. 2 contestant sat down confidently. Just now, they could only see Amamiya-san blinked an eye, and no one would say it was a failure.\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya loses, they have to look at each other. Compared to looking at Amamiya classmates, looking at her little friend is quite a waste of emotion.\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t play tricks this time, just stared at him with watery eyes, the second player\'s face turned red, and his eyes gradually began to wander everywhere, unable to concentrate.\n\nHe looked as if he was looking at Amamiya Noriko, but in fact his eyes were so scattered that he didn\'t know where he was going.\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head to confirm where he was looking, is it this way?\n\nThe second contestant turned his head away from Noriko Amamiya\'s gaze, UU\'s reading www.uukanshu.com was poor, and he almost couldn\'t help but blurt out a confession, his heart was beating thumping.\n\n\"It\'s only half a minute?!\"\n\n\"Well, it seems so.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, you are very good and promising, keep working hard.\n\nThe player was also taken down.\n\nPlayer No. 3, sat down and started watching Amamiya Noriko forgot to breathe because she was too nervous, and her face gradually turned red.\n\nAmamiya Noriko opened her mouth and said, \"Breathe...\"\n\nOnly then did the classmate open his mouth and gasp for breath, leaning against the table to project a sweaty figure.\n\n\"Am I that scary?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her little head, eh? Did I forget my makeup today?\n\nTake the opportunity to do some makeup.\n\nRelying on appearance to fish is easy, and there is no sense of accomplishment.\n\nAnd it\'s so pretty that it gets in the way of her fishing.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said pitifully and worriedly: \"Uda-san, shall I take you to the infirmary?\"\n\nRight Tian said excitedly: \"Okay—\"\n\nHe was dragged away by his good brother and rushed to the infirmary as he dragged the tail sound away.\n\n\"Don\'t worry, Amamiya-san!\"\n\n\"We are brothers, we will take good care of him!\"\n\n\"No-mmmm-\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the instantly empty door of the classroom: \"...\"\n\nIs this, is this brotherhood? How enviable!\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was watching a scene, slowly gave a thumbs up, \"Okay, if there are more of these kind of good brothers, the case must be quite challenging.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt a little chill on her back, and turned her head to meet Kudo Shinichi\'s gaze.\n\n\"The devil\'s eye of death?\"\n\n​​'),
(459, 5, 11, 'Chapter 10: : Be an ordinary beautiful girl', 'After entering junior high school, Noriko Amamiya is no longer going to be a class committee member. She expects junior high school to be a very busy copy of herself.\n\nI don\'t have time to take care of the class committee and other things to help the teacher, so this time I\'ll just be a beautiful girl fishing quietly.\n\nAlthough that\'s what I think, the election of the squad leader is completely based on votes!\n\n\"Everyone writes down the person you think is the most suitable person to be the squad leader. The person who gets the most votes is the squad leader.\"\n\nThe young head teacher clapped her hands, thinking her idea was perfect.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head to look, Mariko and Xiaolan both showed their cheering eyes on her, obviously they would give her the ticket.\n\nEven Kudo Shinichi looks helpless, and it seems that no one is willing to vote. The first impression is Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt that this voting method coincided with her previous plan. Because she was already the representative of the freshman, most of the classmates would know her for the first time.\n\nWho will she vote for if she doesn\'t vote at this time? Most will be her.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the head teacher as if looking forward to the final result.\n\nShouldn\'t this woman have premeditated her to be the monitor? And this method was finally chosen by everyone unanimously, and she couldn\'t refuse to be the monitor too bluntly.\n\n  \"Um…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pondered.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was not far from the seat, turned around and saw Amamiya Noriko\'s contemplative appearance, which was very rare. It seemed that she seldom encountered such a problem that required contemplation.\n\nKudo Shinichi thought that as a future famous detective, he should use his wise brain to help her.\n\nThen I saw Yumiya Noriko\'s original delicate and charming complexion, and the naked eye became weak, as if she was about to die...\n\nKudo Shinichi doesn\'t want to help anymore, it\'s not bad for him to hold back.\n\nWith Kiko Amamiya like this, it is obvious that he is going to pretend to be sick again, although he thinks Kiko Amamiya is already sick.\n\nIf health is 0, cold is 1, fever is 2, others may be 0000001.\n\nThe frequency of Amamiya Noriko is 01010202.\n\nShe has a cold and fever every now and then, but it\'s not a big problem. What does this mean? Her constitution is poor! Why are you in poor health? There might be something hidden.\n\nBut when Yu Yumiya Noriko didn\'t have a cold or fever, she was alive and well, full of aura, full of energy, and she didn\'t look like a person who would get sick frequently.\n\nAs for the kindergarten arm wrestling to kill him, and the elementary school slaughtering the football team, that is good sports and good sports, is it the same thing as poor health? !\n\nKudo Shinichi thinks that the fact that he is sick is the truth of Noriko Amemiya, but this person is quite unconscious, so if he wants to use sickness, he has to pretend.\n\nAt this time, he was very familiar, and it was impossible for him to be deceived. He knew that Amamiya Noriko started, and what she wanted to do by being weak.\n\nAs for the current class monitor vote, she wants to use her sick and tenacious appearance to be the monitor!\n\nShinichi Kudo has a hard time understanding Noriko Amamiya\'s insistence on creating such a perfect image for herself.\n\nYour health is so bad, and you have to be brave and do such a tiring errand just to enjoy the pleasure of letting others confess to you and then reject them?\n\nHe turned his head and spoke to Xiaolan in a low voice. Xiaolan looked at Noriko Amamiya, and saw that Noriko Amamiya looked tired and weak. She remembered that she often visited Noriko Amamiya who was sick. She quickly agreed and pulled Sonoko by the way. .\n\nSonoko only realized that Noriko was so weak, how could she still be tired?\n\nShe quickly crossed out the name on the note, wrote Kudo Shinichi casually, and said, \"How about we let Noriko give up? Health is important.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi shook his head: \"She definitely won\'t give up, we still have to find a way.\"\n\nThe results of the votes will be counted soon, and Amamiya Noriko won eighty-nine-tenths of the votes.\n\nAs expected, she coughed lightly, and was about to say softly to politely refuse, but saw Kudo Shinichi stand up first.\n\n\"Teacher, Amamiya\'s health is not very good. It would be too reluctant to be elected as the monitor.\"\n\nXiaolan and Sonoko agreed, worrying about Noriko Amemiya\'s body.\n\nA few of Asahi\'s elementary school classmates saw this and also remembered that Amamiya Noriko was often sick in elementary school, and they all came together to help.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was speechless, seeing that Shin Kudo always winked at herself, she couldn\'t help feeling relieved.\n\nYou are finally not so straight, you can bend over to help.\n\nThe teacher asked her, Amamiya Noriko was of course a little embarrassed by the situation. She was helpless and a little apologetic, and couldn\'t contribute to the class.\n\nAsahi\'s teacher was very fond of this well-behaved and quite responsible child, and asked everyone to take care of Amamiya classmates, and then voted again, and Kudo Shinichi, who spoke with integrity, became the monitor.\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"???\"\n\nAfterwards, Amamiya Noriko couldn\'t help but patted him on the shoulder and gave a like: \"You did a good job, it\'s perfect, and finally you don\'t have to be the squad leader. The whole job depends on your famous detective Ke... Kudo Shinichi. UU Reading www.uukanshu .com”\n\nHe almost said that he was bald, but it wasn\'t a big problem.\n\nKudo Shinichi was surprised at this moment, \"Don\'t you want to be the monitor? In the end, I became the monitor, no problem?\"\n\n\"No problem, you\'ve worked so hard.\"\n\nWhen Kudo Shin saw her reaction, she immediately understood that Amamiya Noriko was not pretending to be sick to win sympathy and becoming the squad leader, she was showing weakness and politely rejecting the squad leader. .\n\nIn the end, he stepped forward and showed his hand. In fact, he helped Noriko Amamiya and made himself a squad leader.\n\nWhat\'s his motivation to be a monitor? !\n\nWhat is he busy with? !\n\nForget it, after all, Amamiya Noriko didn\'t have to be the squad leader, so she didn\'t have to worry about her body. There was another problem.\n\n\"Why aren\'t you ready to be the monitor again?!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at him strangely, \"Junior high school!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was full of black lines: \"So?\"\n\n\"The age of longing for the taste of sweet and green first love has come. Do you know what is the best thing to do in this situation?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at her expressionlessly, already having a rough guess.\n\n\"Of course, they tricked the cute puppies into killing them and became the object of their first confession.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s slender fingers made a gunshot gesture and winked at Kudo Shin.\n\n\"It turned out to be for this, you are too bad.\"\n\n\"Huh? Xiaolan, your new one is yelling at me...\"\n\n\"What, what is my family Shinichi, please don\'t bully Noriko—!\"\n\nMaurilan, who was chatting with Sonoko, blushed, and then glared at Shinichi.\n\nKudo Shinichi smacked his lips: \"Women are really troublesome.\"'),
(460, 5, 32, 'Chapter 31: : That\'s not enough to keep fish!', 'It has been a week since Sonoko took off her headband and walked around.\n\nIn Didan Junior High School, a list of \"Most Popular Girls\" among boys gradually appeared.\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s name is placed first, so there is no controversy. The highest level of invincibility is to be invincible.\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who is committed to blowing everyone\'s favorability, is the minimum standard to close her hand is \"confession, rejection is complete\" and then start placing.\n\nThe relationship placed is \"good friends\", and then there is an upper limit.\n\nThere is currently only one person who has broken through the boundaries, Suwon Yui\'s \"resentment\".\n\nIf there is a junior elementary school girl who is quiet and well-behaved, kind, weak and lovely, the seniors in the senior years will be quite satisfied.\n\nThat\'s it for Amamiya Noriko.\n\nTherefore, she is the most popular, especially among the seniors who are not often encountered, many old snakeskin are teasing each other and confessing to elementary school girls.\n\nKudo Shinichi shook his head, feeling unfortunate for the ignorant seniors.\n\nHe didn\'t dare to take the second place with Mao Lilan, so he felt no problem.\n\nXiaolan is mainly the female power MAX.\n\nCooking, singing, piano, acting, learning, crafting, pottery, weaving...\n\nNot to mention sports, Mao Lilan just joined the karate club and has been fully recognized by the seniors, then bowling, tennis, skiing, swimming, diving, skating...\n\nIn some respects, he is a mascot compared to Noriko Amamiya, who is fishing for fish, so cute and good-looking is enough.\n\nAnd Amamiya Noriko and Xiaolan have a good relationship, and they have a bond buff together.\n\nThe third is a mysterious character. One day, a first-year school girl who was short-lived in the canteen. It is rumored that everyone who sees it says she looks good!\n\nBut the interested people who deliberately searched for a week in the first grade couldn\'t find anyone at all.\n\nSilently type a \"?\" and then add a \"!\", because everyone who has seen it says it looks good!\n\nThen there were some good-looking and caring seniors from the second and third grades. It was not until the tenth place that the first-year Sonoko Suzuki appeared. Because she was the second young lady of the Suzuki chaebol, she stood out as a wealthy background and close to the people.\n\nWhen Shinichi Kudo heard that the last one was Sonoko, he fell into deep thought. Does anyone have any interest in Sonoko?\n\nSonoko is well-known for his intelligence skills, so he naturally listened to this ranking list. He was very satisfied when he heard that he was tenth. A little bit of dislike is too low, but several outstanding seniors are all It\'s good, just accept it reluctantly.\n\nThen he ran over and talked to Amamiya Noriko.\n\n\"Niko, how do you feel about being the most popular girl?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko listened to it, and she is really strong, but she still insists: \"Could I make a mistake?\"\n\nSonoko immediately said seriously: \"Kiko has to be confident in himself, how could he be wrong? It\'s all male, so there\'s definitely no problem.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded lightly. You occupy two positions by yourself, isn\'t it a big problem?\n\nThe two packed their schoolbags and prepared to go to ministry.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko suddenly invited, \"Will Kiko come to our tennis club to play?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head and said, \"Tennis club? Is it appropriate for me to go?\"\n\n\"Let\'s go and have a look. I also asked Xiaolan to play tennis together.\"\n\nSonoko took Kiko\'s hand and urged her.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways, your reaction looks like an old matchmaker, Shinichi and Xiaolan are not very good matchmaking, and you have come to me.\n\nShe said casually: \"But I don\'t have tennis clothes or anything, so forget it.\"\n\nThere are also a bunch of boys waiting to be watched by her on the