narrowed his way.\n\n\"I didn\'t expect that Sonoko, your whole life started when you were a child.\"\n\nSonoko watched Kiko stretch out her hand to take the tennis suit and clenched her fists in encouragement, but she still saw Kiko\'s shy face, and said in an embarrassed whisper, \"Will it be too short?\"\n\nSonoko tilted her head innocently: \"Will you?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said you can do it, then I\'ll irrigate the tennis club to raise fish first.\n\nShe changed her clothes neatly and found that it was still a little longer than she thought, but she still showed a little belly, and she could see her slender waist.\n\nSonoko watched her change her clothes, and after reading it, she couldn\'t help but say, \"Noriko\'s figure is really good, but is she too conservative?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head with an innocent look on her face: \"Yes?\"\n\nSonoko was helpless, the average girl was wearing a sports vest and safety pants.\n\n\"The **** advantage of girls is gone.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko couldn\'t help reminding: \"I\'m only 12 years old.\"\n\nAt this time, what do you think about if you don\'t go pure and cute? No wonder Sonoko doesn\'t have a boyfriend, she thinks too much.\n\nShe gracefully made a pose of swinging a tennis racket. The tennis skirt was slightly raised, but she fell down again after her figure turned around.\n\nSonoko subconsciously applauds.\n\n\"Isn\'t that enough fishing?\"\n\n​​'),
(461, 5, 100, 'Chapter 100: : lonely', 'Early in the morning the day before Christmas.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was standing under a big Christmas tree in the middle of the square holding a red apple in the square of the Cuphu Commercial Shopping Center.\n\nLooking up at the staff who are hanging various decorative lights on the Christmas tree.\n\n\"Big brother, do you want Apple?\"\n\nThe staff member, Amuro, covered his cap and pretended not to know that Amamiya Noriko was calling him. Why did he meet this girl again?\n\nAmamiya Noriko snorted, reached out and shook the ladder under his feet: \"Big brother, you can\'t ignore me.\"\n\nIn order to prevent himself from falling, Toru Amuro could only take off his peaked cap to reveal his pale golden hair, and looked down at Noriko Amemiya: \"What a coincidence.\"\n\n\"It\'s not a coincidence, I guess the eldest brother will be working part-time nearby again, so he came here specially. Here, take the apple.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko handed the apple on tiptoe, then looked at Toko: \"So what about the Christmas present for me?\"\n\nAmuro looked at the bright red apple, and accepted it, pointing to a pile of gift boxes under the Christmas tree: \"You can just pick one.\"\n\n\"I thought it was just decorations.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko has long seen the gift box under the Christmas tree, but did not expect that there is really a gift in it?\n\nShe picked out a gift box tied with a red ribbon, held it in her arms, took out her mobile phone and took a selfie with Toru Amuro on the ladder.\n\n\"Successful punch-in, I wish big brother a Merry Christmas, do you feel the warmth of your heart?\"\n\nAnshitou looked at the watery eyes below him, looking forward to it, nodded and said with a slight slant, \"Ah, it\'s very warm.\"\n\n\"anything else?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko reminded that if you feel warm, you should respond with a confession, isn\'t that common sense.\n\nAmuro thought for a while: \"Christmas street is quite chaotic, you are still young, why don\'t you be alone.\"\n\n\"I\'m still young...\" Amamiya Noriko tickled the corner of her mouth and gave him a charming wink, \"When I grow up, big brother, don\'t say that again.\"\n\nToru Amuro: \"...\"\n\nIt was as if he was electrocuted by a 12-year-old little sister, and there was indeed a temptation beyond her age in that blink of an eye.\n\nNext, Amamiya Noriko went to a nearby music cafe, where Zhu Fu Jingguang played the guitar.\n\nThe brisk or melancholy tones switched at will, driving the atmosphere in the cafe, Amamiya Noriko and Chieda Riho sat down and listened for a while, and when he was resting, they gave him an apple.\n\n\"It\'s the big brother who was on the tram platform last time. You played it well.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko plucked up her courage, because she was restrained and shy in front of Zhu Fu Jingguang.\n\nZhufu Jingguang didn\'t respond a bit when he took Kiko Amamiya\'s apple, but he still remembered Kiko Amamiya, a cute little girl with a kind heart.\n\nIt\'s just that there are incidental shadows, and he still hasn\'t figured out who the mysterious person who was talking to him in the mailbox is.\n\nZhufu Jingguang\'s eyes fell on Chie Risuo for a moment, and he couldn\'t help but be vigilant. If he was with Amamiya Noriko, could it be this woman...\n\nAmamiya Noriko found that there was no chance again, why did Zhufu Jingguang always look at Chieda Risui and not look at himself?\n\nShe asked for a memory as usual, Zhu Fu Jingguang had nothing to give, and sang a song to her, but she didn\'t care at all, and she was more concerned about whether Chie Risuo was that threatening mysterious person.\n\nAfter Amamiya Noriko left, and Chieda Riho looked at each other: \"If no one confesses to me at Christmas, I\'m too bad.\"\n\nChie Riho frowned: \"The two people Kiko is looking for today are not easy, and I can\'t see through the feeling they give me.\"\n\n\"It\'s okay, it\'s all my own.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved his hand and took another apple out of the bag.\n\nChie Riho looked sideways, are these ten catties of apples going to be delivered today?\n\nIn the end, it was still not finished. She used the industrial power of the Amemiya Foundation to find two Japanese police undercover agents, but Shuichi Akai and Gin Vodka could not be found.\n\nAkai Shuuichi initially guessed that he and the Miyano sisters might have gone to other places~www.readwn.com~ Gin and vodka are slightly more difficult, and it is normal to find them.\n\nMaster Qin\'s condolence plan on Christmas Eve failed, so——\n\nIn the end, she went to send all the acquaintances, such as Sato Miwako of the Metropolitan Police Department, Date Hang, Miki Police Officer, Matsuda Jinpei, etc., everyone had a share, and then asked her father to remind the police to pay attention to the Christmas in Meihua Town. security order, increase the patrolling police force, and prevent the case of the previous Suzuki Building from happening again on Christmas Day.\n\nSpeaking of the case of the Suzuki Building, the Metropolitan Police Department attaches great importance to it, because the case has not been solved yet, and such a large case has begun to go nowhere, and the ability of the Japanese police has been greatly questioned.\n\nAt this time, if there is another big case at Christmas, the director of the Metropolitan Police Department can take the blame and resign.\n\nIn this way, on the night before Christmas Eve, the snow fell and the snow began to fall.\n\nIn a building, Jin Jiu held a cigarette in his hand, and looked a little lonely into the distance of the high-rise buildings. Because the police were so powerful, they couldn\'t go out to deal with the traitors on Christmas night.\n\nA little lonely.');
