(462, 5, 26, 'Chapter 25: : Mumu 13: emmm', 'Amamiya Noriko didn\'t do it on purpose.\n\nBut she took up her gun and aimed at the driver\'s seat and fired two shots. The white pickup lost control and slammed into the roadside guardrail.\n\nThe almost 60-hour pickup collided with it. Although it was slanted, it directly knocked the guard rails crooked, leaving the front half of the car hanging in the air.\n\nBelow is the bottom of the mountain stream.\n\nAmamiya Noriko ran over to take a look, and the woman in the driver\'s seat was so **** that she smashed the front windshield.\n\n\"Why don\'t you wear your seat belt?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head, it didn\'t look like she was hit by herself, but the front windshield not only shattered by the woman, but also had bullet marks from her bullet.\n\nIt should be that the woman was shocked and turned the steering wheel in a hurry before she lost control.\n\nSo why start in fifth gear?\n\nSimilar to what Noriko Amamiya thought, this woman\'s heart was still beating very fast after she started, and the incomparable nervousness of being pointed at by the muzzle couldn\'t go away.\n\nThen I heard the non-stop gunshots from behind, and at first I was staring at the tires and it was fine.\n\nBut then it was obvious that she was staring at her, and a bullet passed by her and hit the glass in front of her. Noriko Amamiya seemed to be very familiar with guns, which made her terrified.\n\nShe just wanted to twist the car so that it wouldn\'t be hit so easily, and then she had an accident.\n\nHe smashed into the windshield without wearing the seat belt and lost consciousness.\n\nAmamiya Noriko dragged her aside, sat in the driver\'s seat, turned on the ignition, reversed gear, slowly released the clutch, and backed the car back to the middle of the road from this dangerous position.\n\nThen the fire was put out again, only then did Noriko Amamiya realize that the man in the co-pilot was gone.\n\nShe got off the car and went back to the guardrail where she was hit and looked down.\n\nWhat a sin, the car door was not closed, and the seat belt was unfastened by her and was about to be pulled down at that time. As a result, the man threw it out and fell into the mountain stream.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is actually not sure whether the man lost consciousness or died before, but this time it must be dead.\n\nFirst, I laid out everything that should be arranged, so that the police could record a statement. After the preparation was basically completed, I reached out and touched a mobile phone from the woman.\n\nAmamiya Noriko called the rescue and said with a very flustered and crying voice: \"Help, I, I was kidnapped, and then I shot and killed people woo woo...\"\n\nThe police operator on the other end of the phone was sweating profusely. She had already received a call that someone had been kidnapped. At this time, she was stunned, but she hurriedly comforted the little sister: \"Don\'t cry, don\'t cry, where are you now? Do you know the approximate location?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko reported the approximate location weepingly.\n\nThe other party also asked her not to hang up the phone.\n\nAmamiya Noriko kept mumbling. By the way, she bandaged the woman\'s head with a cloth covering her eyes, and then took out an electric shocker and stabbed her on her body, \"Zila-\".\n\n\"I\'m the only one who discharges electricity, and no one can power me.\"\n\nAfter about half an hour, the police car finally came over from the city. After seeing the tattered pickup truck parked on the side of the road, several police cars suddenly stopped, and then a bunch of police officers with guns got off the police car.\n\nBecause of the latest news that there are prisoners\' guns, they have all obtained permission to shoot according to the situation.\n\nBut in fact, they only saw a poor sobbing and crying little girl sitting on the side of the road. The little girl was holding a gun and a stun device, and a woman with a **** face standing beside her. According to the clues reported, this The woman is one of the culprits.\n\nA female police officer approached slowly. Seeing the little girl\'s face was full of tears, she looked at herself with uneasiness in her eyes and comforted her softly, \"Don\'t be afraid, little sister, the police are here. It\'s fine.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko threw herself into her arms and wept softly, and secretly looked to the side, it was you, Officer Mumu.\n\nIt was Sato Mikazu who was holding her, and she thought that Megumi must have come too.\n\nMouri Kogoro went to work as a private detective a few years ago, and is definitely not here now.\n\nSato Mikazu let Amamiya Noriko cry in her arms, and gently took the gun and electric shocker from Amamiya Noriko\'s hand and handed them to the police officer next to Meguro.\n\nMu Mu Shisan took a look at the bullet after taking it, and there was one bullet left. As for the electric shock, it seems that the battery is running out of power?\n\nHe waved his hand to let someone investigate the clues at the scene first, and at the same time instructed Sato to comfort Noriko Amamiya first, and then ask carefully about the situation. Someone over there has already gone to check the woman\'s injury, so this situation is very strange. Ah, obviously it was the police who had been kidnapped in the first place.\n\nAnd it was the daughter of the Maori brother who called the police. UU Reading www.uukanshu.com\n\nMikazu Sato comforted Noriko Amamiya, comforting her softly, and helping her to wipe her tears with a handkerchief.\n\nIt seemed that he was still a little scared, so he could only talk about the fragmented situation intermittently.\n\nSato comforted him, then went to tell Officer Megure.\n\nAfter the prisoner kidnapped Noriko Amamiya, she tied her hands and feet with tape, blindfolded her eyes, and put them in the back seat.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko quietly bit the tape with her teeth, and then suddenly grabbed the male prisoner\'s gun and ran out of the car. The two prisoners were about to see that she had a gun in her hand, so they were about to drive forward and hit her. Noriko was terrified and kept firing. Then the woman was frightened by the bullet passing by, and slammed the steering wheel into the guardrail. Neither of them were wearing seat belts, and the man was thrown out of the car.\n\nListening to the police officer Mumu couldn\'t think for a while, he wondered: \"How did she get the gun? Why didn\'t she wear a seat belt?\"\n\n\"It seems that the robber threatened her with a gun before, and then put it in the inner pocket of her clothes. Noriko wrote it down, broke free and grabbed it from the back seat. The seat belts were exactly the two of them who stopped to get out of the car to catch Noriko Jie. Let\'s go, Noriko seems to have fired a shot before getting out of the car, which made the two robbers dare not get out of the car and grab her directly, and there were bullet holes in the car door that were shot inside the car.\"\n\nSato Miwako pondered, \"The door on the other side should be the man who was going to get out of the car and grab it, but then he didn\'t get out and didn\'t close tightly, so he threw him down the mountain.\"\n\nThere are also explanations for other general situations. As for the woman being electrocuted, it was purely because she fainted and woke up again, which frightened Noriko Amamiya to electrocute her. In addition, Noriko Amamiya helped her very kindly. Bandaged.\n\nOfficer Mumu: \"emmm...\"'),
(463, 5, 38, 'Chapter 37: : Miyano Shiho', 'Officers Sato and Meguro then went into the mall to investigate the cause of the accident.\n\nNot surprisingly, if Kudo Shinichi wasn\'t there, it would probably be over.\n\nGin is still reliable.\n\nAs early as an hour ago, the monitoring system of the shopping mall encountered a failure and could not be turned on, so the police officers and the others could only look for clues from the scene, but the only mainstay of the winery was gin.\n\nDealing with traitors is the best way to do it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko went home to sleep and went to school the next day.\n\nI happened to meet Kudo Shinichi and Xiaolan at the school gate.\n\nWith one hand in his pocket, Shin Kudo turned to see Noriko Amamiya with a soft smile on his face, \"Are you feeling better from a cold and fever?\"\n\n\"Yeah.\" Amamiya Noriko nodded, then said to Xiaolan, \"Xiaolan, see if I\'m any different?\"\n\nWhen Xiao Lan heard the words, she took a serious look at Noriko Amemiya, and couldn\'t quite see where there was a big difference. If she wanted to say, was her eyes more eye-catching.\n\n\"I can\'t see, has Noriko changed anything?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko humbly stretched out her hand and gestured, \"A little bit cute.\"\n\nKudo Shin-chan, Amamiya Noriko said a little bit, could that be a little bit?\n\nWith his keen observation, he can roughly see that his eyes are brighter, his skin is whiter, and his fingernails are more pink...\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"Boring.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko glanced at him, took Xiaolan\'s hand and walked in front, and whispered: \"When I went to the mall yesterday, a person fell off the escalator. It\'s so miserable, I still watch it. Until the last kidnapping case, the police officer\'s sister who rescued me...\"\n\nXiao Lan nodded when she heard the words: \"My dad seems to have said it last night, and it seems that in the end he still thinks the reason for his slippery feet?\"\n\nBehind Kudo Shinichi watched the two people whispering, but he could hear Noriko Amamiya from time to time in a \"shopping mall\", \"falling down\", \"miserable\", \"kidnapping\", \"police officer\"...\n\nIsn\'t this obviously fishing?\n\nHopeful takes the bait.\n\nKudo Shinichi wanted to know what happened to the case anyway.\n\nHis famous detective Kudo Shinichi will never miss a case.\n\nThen Amamiya Noriko finally told him that people just fell down accidentally, so stop thinking about it.\n\nKudo Shinichi almost couldn\'t hold back his blood.\n\nIt’s okay to fish, but kill the fish on the spot?\n\nNaturally, it was impossible for Amamiya Noriko to tell him too much. If Kudo Shinichi went to investigate now, if he did pull out the tail of Gin, it would be the tail of a rattlesnake.\n\nIf you want to get involved, you have to go to Hawaii with your father, Yusaku Kudo, to learn the eighteen martial arts.\n\nAmamiya Noriko wants to follow her for a walk, learn to drive a plane, a speedboat, and a helicopter...\n\nThere are also marksmanship, stepping on bombs, repairing computers, etc. Anyway, when there is a need, Hawaii can teach them. The most outrageous is Yusaku Kudo: a famous detective novelist.\n\nEspecially when bombs are defused, the chances of surviving in the world of Conan have plummeted.\n\nBack to school.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is back again, adding a splendid sight to Didan Junior High School.\n\nOn the way to the classroom, most of the classmates who greeted her politely responded to her, and most of them were still very concerned about her body and had to thank her all the time.\n\nAs soon as she got to the seat and sat down, Yui Suwon took the initiative to come over and give her yesterday\'s notes.\n\nAmamiya Noriko politely said, \"Thank you.\"\n\nSuwon Yui said lightly, \"You\'re welcome!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko understood why the rabbit didn\'t eat the grass at the edge of the nest.\n\nFind an opportunity to release Yui Mizuhara.\n\nA week later, only two kind-hearted classmates who didn’t know where they came from confessed in the middle of it, Amamiya Noriko thanked and refused, and then caught a cold, a little cold, wearing it. Go to school as usual with a mask on.\n\nOn the weekend, Amamiya Noriko was full of blood and made an appointment with Miyano Akemi to meet in a cafe.\n\nShe had a lot of thoughts about He Ai-chan noodles, but she didn\'t see Ai-chan who is still Miyano Shiho.\n\nMiyano Akemi apologetically ordered a plate of cake for her: \"My sister has just returned from abroad, and she has a lot of things to do, so she may not be able to introduce her to Noriko.\"\n\n\"That\'s it, what a pity.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said regretfully, thinking in her heart that Shiho Miyano had just returned from studying in the United States, has he already participated in the research of APTX4869?\n\nMiyano Shiho is only one year older than Shin. The last time she saw Ai-chan, who was only about 12 years old, in a shopping mall. She was a little older than Haibara Ai\'s form, but not a girl, so she was quite cute.\n\nAnother Akai Shuichi actually met Miyano Shiho through Miyano Akemi, and then entered the organization with Miyano Shiho\'s connections.\n\nMiyano Shiho has only just returned, and he doesn\'t have any connections yet. Most of the time he expanded his connections through research.\n\nIn other words, Shuichi Akai probably hasn\'t joined the organization yet.\n\nAfter regretting not being able to meet Miyano Shiho, Amamiya Noriko said, \"Sister Akemi, what about Big Brother Zhuxing?\"\n\nBecause Shuichi Akai was taken care of by Akemi Miyano on the grounds of amnesia at the time, it was impossible for him to know his younger sister. Akemi Miyano later learned that Noriko Amamiya was not the younger sister of Daisy.\n\nHowever, there are many stars who amnesiac can come to visit him. UU reading www.uukanshu.com Miyano Akimi thinks it is very good.\n\nThe two are already dating, and Zhuxingdai also explained that he just nodded to cooperate with Amemiya Noriko