(464, 5, 81, 'Chapter 80: : Waiting for good morning, fish fish fish fish fish', 'Shiliang Zhenchun looked at the girl in front of him who was about the same age as him.\n\nThe delicate face shyly raised her head to look at her from time to time, but then immediately moved away cautiously.\n\nIt was quite a contrast to her behavior of coming up to talk directly.\n\nYou must have the courage to do it, right?\n\nIn the face of Noriko Amemiya like this, it is impossible for people to say anything to refuse.\n\n\"Study, bass?\"\n\nShi Liang Zhenchun looked at Zhu Fu Jingguang, his eyes were slightly startled, he was dressed similar to his brother, also carrying a guitar case, and was undoubtedly his brother\'s companion.\n\nCoupled with the gentle gaze of Zhu Fujingguang, the sense of beginning is good.\n\nSonoko also helped: \"Noriko is too shy with strangers, but she is worried that you will feel lonely, so let\'s go together?\"\n\nShi Liang Zhenchun nodded, and smiled kindly at Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAfter simply learning to play scales, Shiliang Zhenjun also got to know Kiko Sonoko.\n\nSonoko was paying attention to the type of handsome guy like Zhufu Jingguang. Did Kiko like him?\n\nI feel that Noriko has become very shy.\n\nBut ten minutes after the ban was lifted, Amamiya Noriko then offered to leave.\n\nIt made the garden a little unresponsive.\n\n\"We can\'t keep delaying people\'s time to teach us this.\"\n\n\"Then, thank you big brother for teaching us music. Goodbye Shiliang.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko politely thanked Zhu Fu Jingguang, and also said goodbye to Shiliang.\n\nPulling the still confused Yuanzi away, Zhu Fu Jingguang didn\'t react a bit, but then he heard the voice behind Hou: \"Scotland, what are you doing?\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang turned his head to look at the man with a baseball cap covering half of his face, and he could only see the man with pale blond hair and wheat skin.\n\nHis good buddy, the undercover team together with the valley zero, code name Bourbon.\n\nHe smiled slightly: \"I\'ll accompany the children who are not accompanied by adults to play outside.\"\n\nJiang Gu Ling looked at Shiliang Zhenchun, \"We still have work to do, and who else is there?\"\n\n\"He went to buy a bus ticket for the child.\"\n\n  \"Um.\"\n\nJiang Gu Ling nodded, and Chao Shiliang smiled genuinely.\n\nAfter a while, as soon as Akai Hideo came back, seeing that Bourbon was also there, he gave the ticket to his sister: \"You should go home.\"\n\n  \"Oh…\"\n\nSeeing that my brother definitely didn\'t bring his own thoughts, Shiliang really had no choice, so he obediently got on the tram and looked at the three people on the platform over there.\n\n\"Brother, are you doing a band?\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang packed up his bass, opened the guitar case at an angle that passersby couldn\'t see, and put the bass in.\n\nBut a note fell out.\n\nHe picked up the small note with only an email address on it, and a small line of Xiujuan: \"Zhufu Jingguang, thank you for taking care of them. If you don\'t mind, I\'ll just say good morning tomorrow morning?\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang\'s eyes flashed, and he rubbed the small note in his palm, but when he remembered the email address on it, he still controlled his strength.\n\nNow that he knows that his real name is Zhu Fu Jingguang, he should also fully understand that he is an undercover agent.\n\nIt\'s just that I don\'t know if the other party knows about zero.\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang looked at the valley, and there was rye whiskey on the side, so it was inconvenient for him to show anything unusual.\n\nYou can only keep things in your heart first.\n\nFor undercover agents, the exposure of identity is fatal.\n\n\"Are you still using those two little girls?\"\n\nZhu Fu Jingguang\'s eyes flashed, it was unforgivable to involve those two innocent little girls in such a dangerous thing.\n\nEspecially when the shy brunette girl flashed before his eyes, it was even more unacceptable.\n\nIn view of the seriousness of the problem, although the other party did not seem to be malicious, Zhu Fu Jingguang still kept the matter in his heart.\n\nNow that I have just entered the organization undercover, I cannot contact the Metropolitan Police Department. I must avoid any exposure and be vigilant.\n\nFor his own sake, and for his good friend Jiang Gu Ling not to be exposed, Zhu Fu Jingguang decided to investigate the situation within a certain range.\n\nOn the other side of the tram, Amamiya Noriko was already looking forward to the good morning that Zhufu Jingguang said to himself tomorrow, and that he could get Zhufu Jingguang\'s email address.\n\n\"Why is Noriko walking so fast? He\'s also a handsome guy.\"\n\nSonoko was still holding Noriko\'s arm.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said she would not leave? Don\'t go, wait for Touko to come, Akai Shuichi comes back, she is in the middle, and there is the latest familiar Zhu Fu Jingguang, the three people have different impressions of her, which trumpet should she play?\n\nThat\'s really her Asura field!\n\nHere, Yuanzi is unrelenting. The word \"handsome guy\" is always in his mouth.\n\nIt is difficult for Amamiya Noriko to understand her thoughts. There is no need to rush into this for 30 years of being single with the mother and child, right? !\n\nFor the sake of being good sisters, handkerchiefs, and being an ACE wingman, Amamiya Noriko decided to give Sonoko\'s love brain a chance.\n\nIf today, Sonoko, the strongest wingman, can get the five fish to confess to her, it\'s okay to take Sonoko to see what Kaito is doing at the moment, or what Jinggoku Makoto is looking at at the moment.\n\nOf course, there\'s nothing to see in Kuaidou now, he hasn\'t evolved into Kaitou Kid, he\'s still a normal junior high school student, maybe.\n\nMainly on Kuito\'s side, she thinks that the probability that Sonoko will like Kuroba Kuito should be very small, because Kuroba Kuito and Kudo Shinichi are very similar, Sonoko likes Kaito Kid.\n\nAs for Jinggoku Ma, Amamiya Noriko herself is also more interested in his current fighting power.\n\nShe also learned one-handed karate with Xiaolan. Although Jing Jizhen will be the karate champion in Japan in the future, winning 400 consecutive battles without a defeat, and having the title of \"Kick Your Son\", but now everyone can\'t dodge bullets, so they can learn from each other. .\n\nIt depends on whether the wingman Yuanzi is doing enough.\n\nAmamiya Noriko skipped Sonoko\'s nagging handsome guy being let go, and said, \"Sonoko, where are we going next?\"\n\nSonoko raised his hand and raised an index finger: \"Of course it\'s the place with the most handsome guys on weekends!\"\n\nTokyo flea market.\n\nIn front of Noriko Amamiya is a large-scale retro market, she raised her eyebrows, there will be many handsome guys here?\n\nThere are quite a few couples and girls who come here holding hands to see these interesting gadgets. Will handsome singles come to the flea market on weekends?\n\nShe looked up at a slogan hanging on the market, \"Tokyo flea market で buy えるもの, それは, \"time\" です (at the Tokyo flea market, what you can buy is \'time\'.\n\nThe Antiques area is a relatively large area for the flea market.\n\nYou can see a lot of small antiques bought from Europe. The stall owners of antique furniture are setting up their stalls. From the daily necessities of ordinary European families such as dinner plates, spoons, forks, etc. in the 18th and 19th centuries, to retro dolls, the eyes are full of European-style objects. It feels like traveling back in time to a European market in the 18th century.\n\nSuch is the charm of the antiques section of the flea market.\n\nHowever, this has little to do with handsome guys.\n\nAmamiya Noriko squatted down and picked up a pair of delicate metal earrings on the stall and looked at them. Although it was not a precious material, the shape was rather good-looking. They looked like water droplets that fell into the water and bounced again~www.readwn.com~ It\'s a pity Only one.\n\nSeeing that she was a cute little girl, the stall owner said, \"Little girl, if you are interested, I can sell it to you at a cheaper price.\"\n\n\"Okay, I will, thank you.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded, and paid the cheaper price. It wasn\'t cheap, but the shape was quite innovative and exquisite, and there was only one, and it cost 1,000 yen.\n\n\"Will Noriko wear earrings?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head with earrings in her hands: \"I don\'t wear them, but they are very delicate and can be hung on keys.\"\n\nSonoko was puzzled, isn\'t it right to buy a key pendant for 1,000 yen?\n\nBut after walking around, she also understood that Noriko had a hobby of enriching key ornaments, although she had never seen Noriko Amamiya with a key.\n\nAccording to Noriko\'s words, small and delicate gadgets are more interesting to store.\n\n\"Kiko, this side, this side!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was still reading at the booth, when Sonoko was dragged away to a booth selling some old books.\n\nYuanzi obviously didn\'t want to buy books, it was entirely because the stall owner was a pretty boy with a somewhat melancholy temperament and a very artistic image.\n\nShe pretended to pull Noriko Amamiya to squat down and read together, \"These books seem to be very good.\"\n\nThe melancholy pretty boy glanced at Suzuki Sonoko, but he didn\'t answer. He looked at the sky from a 45-degree angle, probably because he looked directly at cosmic rays, his eyes were a little sad.\n\n\"These books are about the passing years and describe the sad past.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko murmured while looking at the quaint pages.\n\nThe melancholy pretty boy\'s eyes lit up.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in her heart that you understand it very well, so don\'t read the literature on youth pain.\n\n​​'),
(465, 5, 53, 'Chapter 52: : Toko is not heartbroken', 'Amamiya Noriko sat idle on the stairs and held her cheeks.\n\nTouko checked everywhere inside, and Amamiya Noriko said anyway that she was locked up with another person, and that person fixed the doors and opened them.\n\nAs for appearance, height and weight...\n\nIt seems to be a little bit taller than me, a little fatter than me, and of average length. The face has no special features, that is, when it is in the shadows, the face is very dark, the teeth are very white, and it looks like there is no hair.\n\nLike a stickman.\n\nGu Ling let her sit on the side, what is the difference between this and not saying anything? You just sit tight.\n\nAfter checking for a long time, the situation is basically confirmed after the valley has dropped to zero.\n\nObviously, the two people who were locked in the storage room got a bunch of things and finally broke the door open. The camouflage man just hit the door that was broken open directly outside the door and lost consciousness.\n\nThat\'s pretty much the situation. Of course, he felt that Amamiya Noriko didn\'t help much in the process, and was purely rescued by that person.\n\nAfter all, he is still too young, and his strength is also very small.\n\nBut it\'s a bit strange. When he asked about that person\'s situation, Noriko Amamiya didn\'t seem to have much reaction, but she kept looking at him.\n\n\"Are there any flowers on my face?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko put a single finger against her chin and pondered: \"Maybe there is, after all, it is the same color as the land.\"\n\nHearing this, Ling Gu tilted his head and asked, \"Is it because my hair and complexion are weird?\"\n\n\"Well, no, because he\'s so handsome.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked her right eye and gave a thumbs up, and her smile was super-A. There are not many people who can praise her.\n\nMainly because this answer is correct. When Tou Zi was a child, he was very concerned about his skin color and hair color. Although he has grown up now, maybe he has a psychological shadow?\n\nIs Amamiya Noriko the kind of person who will expose other people\'s scars?\n\nShe is either increasing others\' favorability, or she is on the way to increase others\' favorability. In this regard, she is as busy as gin.\n\nJiang Gu zero laughed, patted Yumiya Noriko\'s head lightly, then got up and prepared to take the man on the ground away. Originally, he was observing and collecting information secretly, but now he has it. Gang complete the task?\n\n\"My brother is going to take the bad guy to the police uncle. Noriko will go home early, so don\'t go with strangers casually next time.\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nThere was a question mark above Amamiya Noriko\'s head.\n\nI wasn\'t kidnapped, I was kidnapped, of a different nature, running with strangers? I\'m not a three year old.\n\nAmamiya Noriko murmured in her heart, watching Ling Gu Ling drag the camouflage man away, and she didn\'t know how he was going to leave the mall with a big living person.\n\n\"Toriko didn\'t respond to me, could it be because I\'m too young?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked down.\n\nForget it, anyway, it will be longer in the future.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at the door on the ground, it had nothing to do with her, and she didn\'t leave any fingerprints.\n\nJust now, she pretended to be weak and powerless to lift the door, but in fact she didn\'t touch the door, she was lifting the door from the air, but it was obvious that she had a very promising career in acting, and her acting skills were MAX.\n\nAfter going down the stairs, I just got to the fifth floor and didn\'t take a few steps when I saw the staff of the shopping mall go up to check the movement just now.\n\nThis speed is compared with the speed of the police.\n\nOf course, the speed of the police in the world of Conan is not bad, basically one shot is on the scene.\n\nShe just passed by, and suddenly she was hugged by Miyano Akemi with a cute face.\n\n​​'),
(466, 5, 39, 'Chapter 38: : It\'s really annoying', 'It\'s a pity that I couldn\'t succeed with Xiao Ai Mianji, so Amamiya Noriko went shopping with Miyano Akemi.\n\nThe gentle elder sister is very good. She didn\'t let Noriko Amamiya do this because she was still young. Instead, she bought her a lot of street food.\n\nMiyano Akemi is also experiencing life, tasting various snacks together, and strolling around very comfortably.\n\nBut the shopping mall is still Miyano Akimi\'s favorite place, and shopping for clothes and shoes is a pleasure.\n\nAnd you can choose cute clothes, which I definitely can\'t wear, but Noriko Amamiya can. No one is more suitable for cute styles than her. It\'s great to have a girl who can satisfy her inappropriate outfits.\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that my heart is actually very dark, and I prefer to wear black clothes, but my face may really only be suitable for acting cute.\n\nAt around six or seven in the evening, Akemi Miyano and Noriko Amemiya watched the sunset on the river and disappeared.\n\n\"Okay, it\'s all over. Shall we go to the izakaya?\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned her head, what are you talking about, gentle big sister? Have you suddenly become an uncle who goes to drink after get off work?\n\nShe actually asked her if this minor was going to drink?\n\n\"VeryGood!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave her a thumbs up in her heart. She hadn\'t had a drink in a long time, especially since she came to Japan and had never drank Japanese sake, so she had to try it.\n\nAh, but I can\'t blatantly express that I want to drink, so Noriko Amamiya reminded me carefully: \"Sister Mingmei, I\'m only 12 years old?\"\n\nMiyano Akemi smiled and said, \"It\'s okay, Noriko doesn\'t drink.\"\n\nDare I decided to let me just go to eat and not drink.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded her head obediently, and when she went, she knew whether I would drink or not.\n\nHowever, most of the chain izakayas do not allow minors to enter. Adults can enter, but they cannot order alcohol.\n\nFortunately, the most recent one is private and will be too strict.\n\nThe little brother behind the counter looked at her a few times, but didn\'t say no to enter.\n\nAnd after entering, there are also compartments that are separated by curtains. To a certain extent, it feels like a century-old store. You have to sit on your knees to eat, not a chair.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is not very used to it, but there is no work that she can\'t do, she is still sitting Qianqian, and there is no problem with being well-behaved.\n\nThen Noriko Amamiya doesn\'t care about what to eat. What kind of wine Miyano Akemi serves is her focus. As long as she greasyly says, \"Sister Akemi, is this wine delicious?\", she will definitely be able to drink it.\n\nThen I saw the waiter serving shochu (shochu syocyu), a big bottle.\n\nAnd soda and other drinks.\n\nShochu is basically above 36 degrees. It is not a strong liquor, but it has a very strong taste.\n\nサワー (Sawa), that is, sour sparkling wine, adding lemon juice and soda water can make the strong taste of shochu more acceptable, and adding other drinks can play colorful tricks, it is indeed more popular with ladies.\n\nGenerally speaking, it is the store\'s cup order, and Miyano Akimi can adjust it by herself.\n\nSeeing Kiko Amamiya looking at these wines, Akemi Miyano smiled and whispered quietly, \"Kiko wants to drink too, right?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looks like she is hesitant to say anything. Since sister, you sincerely want to invite me to drink, then...\n\n\"This cup belongs to Noriko. It is an exception. Minors are not allowed to drink alcohol.\" Miyano Akemi was serious, and then smiled: \"The plum wine in this store is all Benge plum wine, except for the use of plums, sugar, and base wine. Any addition is good for the body.\"\n\n\"It\'s good for the body...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at a glass of clear plum wine, how many degrees does this thing have? A little higher at most, right?\n\nNo matter what, it\'s done.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a sip, it was still the sweet wine in plum wine, and it could only be used as a drink.\n\nWhen there is a chance later, drink gin, vodka, absinthe, rum, rye whiskey, bourbon, keel, scotch, and sherry all over again.\n\nIf I could have another drink of \"that gentleman\", I would die without regret.\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought about it, and Miyano Akimi, who was opposite, blamed herself for not bringing Noriko, and she got drunk after just one drink. After all, she was still a child.\n\nMinors are not allowed to drink alcohol.\n\nAmamiya Noriko doesn\'t feel that she is drunk, she can still remember the wine from the winery, she is very sober.\n\nIt\'s just that other people in the izakaya are a bit noisy, and she still doesn\'t like this kind of place.\n\nBut izakaya is like this. Unlike other public places, which are extremely quiet, it is natural for izakaya to be noisy.\n\nIt\'s understandable for the social animals who get off work, the uncles who have lost their love, and so on.\n\nWho hasn\'t had a sad moment.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a sip and took a piece of cold tofu, which tasted very strange.\n\nAkemi Miyano takes a sip from time to time, and it\'s amazing to see Noriko Amamiya being able to pick up the soft tofu with chopsticks.\n\n  \"woo woo woo woo--\"\n\nSuddenly, there was a sad whimper from the position outside the curtain, which made the listeners cry, and the listeners were sad.\n\nJust as Amamiya Noriko was about to shake her head, she heard the man howling, \"But, but I love Noriko! She\'s so cute and innocent, why did you reject me woo woo...\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt her noisy head buzzing. Does anyone else have the same name as herself? The name Noriko, um, isn\'t very rare either, so it\'s understandable.\n\n\"Uuuuu—Amamiya—\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko understands, this must be from the school, what are you doing in an izakaya when you are under 20 years old? It\'s a shame to call my name so drunk! No prospects!\n\nShe rolled up her sleeves and was about to lift the curtain to beat her... to soothe the other\'s injured heart~www.readwn.com~ Miyano Akemi looked at her very kindly, holding her cheeks.\n\n\"I\'ll just say, Noriko is so cute, she\'s really popular.\"\n\n\"We definitely don\'t know him. He...he was drunk. I just wanted to go and have a look...\"\n\nMiyano Akimi said familiarly: \"It\'s okay, his companions will definitely take him away.\"\n\nThat\'s true. Soon that person was dragged away by his companions. I took you as a brother, but you humiliated me, and must be dragged away.\n\n  \"Do not--!!!\"\n\nThe howling faded away, and Amamiya Noriko didn\'t know why it felt a little familiar, but then she was forgotten.\n\nSitting down obediently, holding the plum wine and drinking slowly, be dignified. Sister Mingmei\'s attitude towards herself is directly related to Akai Shuichi and Ai-chan.\n\nBesides, in the future, I will have to rely on Sister Mingmei to bring you drinking, so let\'s focus on it.\n\nMiyano Akimi didn\'t give Amamiya Noriko a glass of other wine in the end. After all, she was a child. It was enough to taste the plum wine because of curiosity, but other wines were not enough.\n\nShe felt that the body of the child Amamiya Noriko was still very delicate.\n\nAfterwards, he also took a taxi to take Amamiya Noriko to the door of the house. Seeing that Amamiya Noriko was taken into the house, he left with confidence.\n\nChie Riho looked at Amamiya Noriko, who was walking a little, and said calmly, \"Miss, have you been drinking alcohol?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head: \"Hehe, I\'m walking around because I\'m in a good mood. Today, a boy got drunk in public and cried and shouted that he liked me. When I think about it now, it\'s really daunting.\"\n\nChieda Riho glanced at her young lady\'s radiant smile, where is your head big and swollen.\n\n​​'),
(467, 5, 3, 'Chapter 2: : Attempted victim Noriko Amamiya', 'Amamiya Noriko frowned as she looked at her position for a long time. Xiaolan failed as a victim. What about herself?\n\nIt\'s hard to say.\n\nBut Mianmian\'s sleepiness rose and haunted her mind at this time, and she lay uncontrollably on the bed\n\nLunch break.\n\nThe children fell asleep obediently.\n\nExcept for Maurilan, although Sonoko Suzuki comforted her, she didn\'t remember what Sakura Brand did at once. She couldn\'t help crying when she was wronged alone.\n\nKudo Shinichi finally appeared.\n\nSome inexperienced reasoning concluded that Mao Lilan was making a cherry blossom brand, and also said that Mao Lilan was a crying girl who lost the cherry blossom brand, and a crybaby who cried and made cherry blossoms.\n\nThen the children who took a nap all woke up and looked at Kudo Shinichi in amazement.\n\nBecause it was the first real nervous and excited reasoning in his life, Kudo Shinichi was still a child after all, and he was quite complacent, still thinking that the girl in front of him must be surprised.\n\nThen Mao Lilan retorted: \"I\'m not a crybaby!\"\n\n\"...Huh? Aren\'t you crying?\"\n\n\"I didn\'t cry.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi raised his eyebrows when he saw that there were still tears in the corners of Mao Lilan\'s eyes, and said, \"You\'re crying.\"\n\nWith tears in her eyes, Mao Lilan said stubbornly, \"I didn\'t cry!\"\n\nKudo Shinichi sweats, saying that you are still teary-eyed.\n\nAfterwards, Yukiko Kudo came in from outside to find Shinichi, and found that Maurilan was the daughter of Fei Yingri and was talking to Xiaolan.\n\nHowever, Kudo Shinichi suddenly noticed that the head teacher of Sakura, Jiang Zhou, who was behind his mother, was looking at the bed closest to the door to the corridor.\n\nKudo Shinichi\'s detective intuition told him that this look is quite bad.\n\nHe looked at the little girl over there on the bed, and found that she was the only one who was still sleeping soundly!\n\n\"Huh? Isn\'t this the strange girl who smiled at me in the classroom before?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi had a good memory, and he quickly remembered Noriko Amamiya who he had met for a short time, and he also cared about that strange smile.\n\nAt this moment, Mao Lilan looked at Kudo Shinichi: \"Hey, if you need the Sakura brand, I\'ll give you the one I just made?\"\n\n  \"Um.\"\n\n\"I\'ll help you write your name, what\'s your name?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi reacted, looked back at Maurilan, blushed a little, but introduced himself seriously: \"My name is Kudo Shinichi, from the Sakura class.\"\n\nMaurilan lowered her head and wrote \"Sakura Class Kudo Shinichi\" on the cherry blossom nameplate she just made.\n\nMore than a thousand episodes of youthful love began here.\n\nLittle Maurilan still didn\'t understand at this time, but Kudo Shinichi\'s love at first sight started from here.\n\nIf Amamiya Noriko could still be awake, she would definitely complain: \"It\'s really a green and pure feeling, it\'s the kind that can ferment a thousand episodes...\"\n\nBut she couldn\'t wake up for a while. Before she went to sleep, she noticed that the position was not right, and she was too sleepy. It is estimated that Jiang Zhoulun introduced the sleeping pills.\n\nAfter sleeping for a while, Noriko Amamiya woke up later than the others to regain consciousness.\n\nTouching her forehead, she found that it was not only Jiang Zhou who introduced the sleeping pills, but she also had a low-grade fever, and her head was dizzy.\n\nThere was no sign, she thought about it carefully, it seemed that it could only be caused by the +1 strength. Her body became hot at the beginning. Is it because of the fact that she is still undergoing body modification?\n\nTurning on the energy-saving mode, Amamiya Noriko looked even more lazy all afternoon.\n\nOn the other hand, Shin Kudo was very interested in her, but it was because of Jiang Shurensuke\'s special attitude towards Amiya Noriko that he felt something was wrong, and he had a considerable desire to solve the puzzle.\n\nThen, as soon as Kudo Shinji found out that Amamiya Noriko was really weird, he didn\'t say a word to anyone who was looking for her to play with, so he waved his hand and let people play.\n\nHe couldn\'t help but ask Mao Lilan, \"Has she always been like this?\"\n\nMao Lilan didn\'t know how to answer either. He didn\'t know each other very well before, so he basically only spoke today.\n\n\"Amamiya classmates are still very good...\"\n\nShe could only talk about how Amamiya Noriko helped her and Mariko in the morning.\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t find any clue, what is the connection between the head teacher with an unidentified attitude, and the strange character Noriko Amamiya?\n\nIn the afternoon, Jiang Shurunsuke took the children from the Cherry Blossom class to play in the garden.\n\nJiang Zhou Runsuke asked the children to line up, preparing to put Noriko Amamiya in front and lead the group by holding her hand.\n\n\"No, I want to be last.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was too lazy to cooperate with him. As for how Jiang Zhou Lunjie planned to tell his brother-in-law that he was the target, that was his business.\n\nWhen I went to the amusement park, Noriko Amemiya was sitting there watching the children slide down the slide.\n\nJiang Zhou Lunjie came here on purpose to let her slip, as if to take care of her who didn\'t fit into the group.\n\nAmamiya Noriko lacks interest: \"I\'m not interested, I don\'t know why it\'s fun to slide down there.\"\n\nFrom the beginning to the end, Jiang Zhou Lunjie\'s daughter ran away from home, so his wife was mentally ill and wanted to raise another child, so he had the idea of ​​kidnapping her with his brother-in-law, and it should have been Mao Lilan\'s.\n\nIt was good that Amamiya Noriko didn\'t directly expose their ideas, kidnapping young children, human traffickers, it\'s not an exaggeration.\n\nIf it weren\'t for this Jiang Zhou Lun Jie would finally wake up.\n\nHow could there be time to be used to them?\n\nJiang Zhou Runsuke was very helpless. How could he feel that today\'s Amemiya Noriko was not quite right? He could only indicate to his wife at the window that this was the target, and thought about whether to change it.\n\nAfter Jiang Zhou Ron-suke went to take the other children, Kudo Shinichi, who already felt that Jiang Zhou Ron-suke was not right, walked up to Noriko Amamiya.\n\nWith a curious look, he asked, \"Student Amamiya, what did the teacher say to you?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways, \"Said he wanted me to go down the slide too.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi pondered, looking back and forth between the windows behind the slide, wondering if the two are related?\n\nSeeing that the future famous detective was so attentive, Amamiya Noriko patted him and encouraged, \"Come on, I\'ll leave it to you.\"\n\n  \"pass it to me?\"\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi heard the words, the corner of his mouth twitched twice, what do you know? Do you know what I know? will you leave it to me?\n\nThe future famous detectives are still young, and they are still in the process of reasoning about why Jiang Zhou Lunsuke has a special attitude towards Noriko Amemiya, and the eyes of Jiang Zhou Lunsuke that he has seen clearly have problems.\n\nHe didn\'t even understand what Jiang Zhou\'s purpose was!\n\nWhen he got home, he couldn\'t wait to tell his father Yusaku Kudo what happened.\n\nUnlike Shinichi Kudo, whose reasoning ability is only half-baked, Yusaku Kudo\'s reasoning ability is already very strong.\n\nYusaku Kudo linked the clues provided by his son to the fans who are also surnamed Jiang Zhou at his signing ceremony today, and he has vaguely made some kind of inference.\n\nOn the second day, he disguised himself and followed Sakura Class to observe secretly, and found that Sakura Class\'s children were crossing the road with a car parked on the side, and the people in the car were taking pictures with digital cameras.\n\nThe target seemed to be the lazy little girl hanging at the end of the line. Teacher Jiang Zhou would also look behind the line from time to time. When he looked at the little girl to determine if it was the girl his son said, the little girl also noticed him. , winked at him.\n\nYusaku Kudo felt a little weird, but then the little girl didn\'t look at him all the time.\n\nLater, when he was in the garden, he found that Xiao Hei, who was secretly photographed from the window, was with Jiang Zhou\'s wife, which basically confirmed his guess.\n\n  the next day.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who was instructed by Yusaku Kudo to take good care of Noriko Amamiya today, pays special attention to Noriko Amamiya, and is always wary of Jiang Zhou Rensuke.\n\nMao Lilan wondered, \"What are you doing, Xinyi?\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko also looked suspiciously at Kudo Shinichi: \"You seem to be staring at Noriko all the time.\"\n\nShinichi Kudo rolled his eyes, it was hard to explain, the two of them still believed in Jiang Zhou Lunsuke.\n\nHe could only divert his attention and say, \"I think she seems a little more energetic today than yesterday.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko walked behind him and said leisurely, \"Is there any?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was taken aback, \"You walk silently.\"\n\n\"What\'s the matter, let\'s break your wrist?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi raised his eyebrows, \"Are you sure you want to compare with me? You\'re a girl, so forget it.\"\n\nMao Lilan, a future karate master, said, \"Xinyi, do you despise girls?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was full of black lines: \"No, then let\'s decide the outcome!\"\n\nThe two of them put their hands on the table, Amamiya Noriko pouted, \"Are you ready?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi didn\'t think he would lose, nodded, and then started to exert force, but found that the back of his hand had been pressed against the table.\n\nInstant KO.\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"This is one point of my strength.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi blurted out, \"Who would believe you!\"\n\nHe didn\'t expect that he would lose so badly. He is a man who wants to become a famous detective in the future!\n\n  \"Again!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko also placed his hand on the table lightly and won another victory.\n\nWhen Kudo Shinichi doubted his life, Amamiya Noriko was basically sure that his 1 point of strength had finally been added. Now his strength is indeed much stronger, not to mention compared with adults, at least not only for three-year-old girls Powerless. UU reading www.uukanshu.com\n\nFortunately, she had a low-grade fever for a long time yesterday.\n\nThis 1 point of strength made her feel the feeling of becoming stronger. Since this is the case, she can\'t be salty. First, she will guide the kindergarten.\n\nBut before that, Jiang Zhou Lunjie should have already made his wife and brother-in-law set a target for her, and it\'s time to attack her today.\n\nWhile eating lunch, she felt that Jiang Zhou Lunsuke\'s eyes were always on her side.\n\nShe looked down at her lunch. She should have sleeping pills in it to prevent extra troubles when she takes herself away.\n\nIt was always seen that she couldn\'t do any small movements, so Amamiya Noriko ate it without changing her face.\n\n\"Kudou Shinichi, I\'ll leave it to you.\"\n\n\"Why did you give it to me again?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was stagnant after eating and said speechlessly, what exactly is left to himself? Didn\'t you say it once yesterday?\n\nAmamiya Noriko was too lazy to explain and nodded: \"You can do it.\"\n\nThen he pursed his lips, and stopped talking when he ate.\n\nThis makes Kudo Shinichi a little crazy. Don\'t you know that the detective\'s desire to explore is very strong? What does the vague plausible say? What exactly does that mean?\n\nWhile he was scratching his head and scratching his cheeks, Amamiya Noriko, who had finished eating soon, picked up her plate and went to clean up. In order to cultivate the independence of the children, the children had to clean up the plates and chopsticks by themselves. After she came back and sat for a while, she was tired. Deliberately went to sleep.\n\nKudo Shinichi was slightly startled. Today\'s Amamiya Noriko should be in a lot of energy, so why is she sleepy again?\n\nHis eyes fell on Noriko Amemiya\'s bowl, and he glanced at Jiang Zhou Lunsuke again.\n\n\"A sleeping pill?\"\n\nYusaku Kudo didn\'t tell his son in detail his reasoning, but Shinichi Kudo has vaguely guessed it now.');
