(468, 5, 98, 'Chapter 97: : to cultivate sentiment', 'It didn\'t take long for the Azure Star building to be surrounded by a large number of police.\n\nBasically, they came to investigate the scene, and no prisoners have been arrested for them.\n\nIt\'s a bit late and there\'s nothing I can do. Will gin work procrastinate?\n\nVery neat.\n\nYou can see that after he found Xinyi, he swung Xinyi with a stick while talking, and the backhand was feeding the medicine. While feeding the medicine, he introduced the effect of the medicine intimately. Fill your mouth.\n\nA villain like Gin has lived for more than a thousand episodes, isn\'t it for nothing?\n\nIt only took a few minutes from when the gate was opened to when the sniper rifle broke the glass of the showcase, and Toru Amuro took the gem.\n\nAt the same time, the target person was also treated as an accidental death.\n\nProfessional team.\n\nAmamiya Ludou has something to do, so he and his wife left first under the protection of the bodyguards who came after he contributed a little testimonial that was of little use.\n\nSonoko\'s father, Shiro Suzuki, chairman of the Suzuki Foundation, expressed his sincere apologies and will definitely visit in the future.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked sideways, this carelessness was another cause of the case.\n\nShe didn\'t go back with her parents, she stayed with Xiaolan Yuanzi and the others.\n\nMore accurate is to find Kudo Shinichi to play.\n\nThis detective is still bothering the police to try to investigate together, but unfortunately, he is still in a state of no fame. How could the police easily trust a middle school student, let alone a junior high school student who just graduated from elementary school.\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave Kudo Shinichi a suggestion: \"You can be cute, pretend you don\'t understand anything and put forward the key clues of the discovery, like \'Alialie\' and \'Oh Garxizuo\'.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi glanced at her sideways, and he was coming up with some unreliable ideas. It was too fake. How could anyone believe it?\n\nMore importantly, he can\'t find any particularly important clues now.\n\nThe window that was blown out does feel that there will be gains, but the police have cordoned off to prevent someone from falling through the blown window, and the corpse of the Nancun police inspector is also close to that side, so he will not be let go at all. .\n\nMost importantly.\n\nMouri Kogoro: \"Go, go, go to the side of the little ghost, just leave it to my detective Mouri Kogoro.\"\n\nKudo Shin rolled his eyes.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said in her heart that the two of you have not yet become famous detectives.\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at Amamiya Noriko: \"Have you found anything strange? Provide clues.\"\n\n\"Well...Actually, I not only know a little clue, I even know their code names, and I also know the approximate plan and number of their actions...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was talking and saw Kudo Shinichi turning her head and leaving, \"What are you doing! You asked me?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi said that he was very busy and didn’t have time to listen to Amamiya Noriko’s eyes open and talking nonsense.\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted in dissatisfaction, these days, no one believes the truth.\n\nA gray-faced young man passed by, and at first glance, he was stunned on the spot. It was really cute. His lips were slightly pursed with dissatisfaction and grievance. His small cheeks, his lovely nose were slightly wrinkled, and the sparkling glittering eyes attracted attention. people pay attention.\n\nAmamiya Noriko felt the sight, turned to look at him, and blinked, isn\'t this the elevator boy? It doesn\'t look like anything, but, does this rut ​​look recognize him?\n\n\"It stands to reason that no normal person can see through my disguise, unless my cuteness is too conspicuous.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko and the other party looked at each other, with innocent eyes that were innocent and puzzled.\n\nThe elevator boy was intoxicated, he strode over, stretched out his hand to Amamiya Noriko and bowed: \"Please hang out with me!\"\n\n\"Ah, sorry I refused.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was a little surprised, then refused, learning +1.\n\nIt\'s actually sincere, and he changed his mind so quickly. She remembered that this person was quite shy, how could he suddenly become a scumbag.\n\nShouldn\'t you still love my trumpet? !\n\nIsn\'t this changing the fish pond in front of her?\n\nThe elevator boy kept smiling after being rejected. Even if he was rejected, he still moved forward according to his heart. He had boldly stated his heart. This was taught to him by that girl!\n\nAmamiya Noriko watched him leave without changing his color after being rejected. He committed sins. He only knew that he had no skills in confessing, and his future was worrying.\n\nTurning to look at Kudo Shinichi\'s side, he was still trying to shine.\n\nIf it is an ordinary case, there may be some clues that the police can\'t notice and he will discover, so as to deduce the truth of the case, and gradually embark on the road of a famous detective.\n\nBut this was a crime committed by a winery, and there were few clues left. It was doomed that Kudo Shinichi could not use this to open up his fame.\n\n\"You still want to be open. It\'s okay to start with the little three lovers of cats, cats and dogs. How can they directly let you find clues at the crime scene.\"\n\nAmiya Noriko enlightens Kudo Shinichi.\n\nIt\'s just a pity that Kudo Shinichi is not a person who gives up easily, especially in detective reasoning, he firmly believes that there is only one truth, and the truth of this case is not as simple as it seems on the surface.\n\nAmamiya Noriko shook her head. It\'s not that simple. There are multiple alcohol linkages. They are all cross-tasks that they don\'t know about each other. You have to start from where to find out the truth.\n\nShe went to play with Xiaolan Yuanzi, and let Kudo Shinichi slowly find the truth and finally think about life.\