(469, 5, 43, 'Chapter 42: : Do Not Disturb at Gin Work', 'Amamiya Noriko hurriedly took off the boy\'s clothes, there was still a shirt and shorts inside, and a sportswear jacket.\n\nShe is a lovely girl who is running and exercising.\n\nGoing out of the alley, I saw Kudo Shinichi\'s back with doubts and incomprehension.\n\nXinyi had to thank her for her quick action, otherwise she would be slapped ahead of time.\n\nShe turned to look at Gin. The Hongfan district was very lively, and Gin\'s Porsche couldn\'t drive in.\n\nThe open-air parking lot near this point is basically full, only the underground parking lot of the building next to it is still possible.\n\nOf course she won\'t look for it.\n\nBut you can create a chance encounter.\n\n  Underground Parking Lot.\n\nGin got out of the car, expressionless, and glanced around the parking lot with sharp eyes, but found nothing suspicious.\n\nVodka also got out of the car, and his eyes under the sunglasses swept around: \"Brother, do you need to come back and take a look?\"\n\n\"Well, I feel like a hyena is staring at me.\"\n\nGin looked grim, and walked towards the elevator in the underground parking lot.\n\nVodka looked around again for no reason. There were only one or two parked cars. Where are the dogs?\n\nGin\'s gloved hand was about to press the elevator, and he saw that the elevator was going from 3F to 2F, and then to 1F, and there was still no tendency to stop.\n\nHe squinted his eyes, reached out and grabbed the Liberta pistol in his arms, and installed the silencer on the muzzle under the cover of the windbreaker.\n\nSeeing this, Vodka hurriedly left the elevator door directly opposite, and was ready to draw a gun at any time.\n\n\"Cough cough.\"\n\nThe elevator door opened slowly, the lights illuminated, and there was a slight coughing sound.\n\nSeeing that it was a rickety old woman, Jin Jiu took a deep look at it, then stretched out her hand in the windbreaker and pressed the elevator button. After the old woman left the elevator silently, she walked into the elevator.\n\nVodka breathed a sigh of relief and followed suit.\n\nGin glanced at the elevator, then pressed the door-close button, and watched the old woman walk slowly in the gap between the elevator doors that slowly closed and narrowed.\n\n\"Big brother...\"\n\nVodka couldn\'t help but say, is there any need to be so cautious...\n\n  \"Do not talk.\"\n\nJin Jiu was expressionless, watching the elevator from -1F to 1F, raised his legs and walked out.\n\nHe will not be superstitious about intuition, but when there is danger, intuition is the accumulated feedback of experience.\n\nGlancing at the lobby on the first floor of the building, his dark green pupils narrowed slightly and landed on a girl over the counter.\n\nEven the back, with his memory, can\'t remember wrong.\n\n  \"Walk.\"\n\nGin said simply.\n\nVodka quickly followed.\n\n\"Ah Lie?\"\n\nJin Jiu paused, because there was a very exaggerated and childish voice behind him. He remembered that soft voice quite clearly.\n\nThe windbreaker was pulled, Jinjiu tilted her head and bowed her head, her half-banged eyes swept coldly and ruthlessly across Amamiya Noriko\'s face, it was indeed a very characteristic face.\n\nNow the little devil, use some disgusting exaggerated tone.\n\n\"Uncle Gin?\"\n\nGin ignored it and walked out with her legs raised.\n\n\"Uncle Big Star (in a low voice), where are you going?\"\n\n\"It\'s not right to go there. Mom said you can\'t come to such a place.\"\n\n\"Are you going to do that kind of thing?\"\n\nVodka followed in shame, seeing that Gin\'s eyes were full of chills, he stretched his hand into the windbreaker, and quickly reminded him carefully.\n\nThere are not many people around this place.\n\nAmamiya Noriko casually accosted as she was walking around. Seeing Gin looking like she was about to draw a gun, although she knew it was impossible to shoot in this environment, she hurriedly moved to the side and needed to find cover at any time.\n\nYou can\'t bet that Master Qin\'s marksmanship is not allowed.\n\nBut what happened next was something she didn\'t expect. Gin and vodka went straight to the policemen who were patrolling on bicycles.\n\n\"So fierce? Shooting at the police?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko hurriedly thought about what to do~www.readwn.com~ and then saw Gin pointing at her at the police.\n\nTo be honest, the patrolling police were very wary of these two men in black at first, and they didn\'t look like good people.\n\nBut these two people actually told him that the girl had lost her way and wanted to follow him inside. Immediately, he saw that the two of them were much better.\n\nAlthough he looks a little fierce, he is still kindhearted.\n\n\"In the future, you must never judge people by their appearance.\"\n\nHe secretly blamed himself in his heart, and whispered to the lost cute girl in the past, \"Little boy, are you lost? Do you still know where your home is? Uncle police can take you back.\"\n\n\"...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko stood on tiptoe to watch the two wines go away, and the police were still stopping her in front of her.\n\nThe world is going down and morals are declining. What kind of world is this? It\'s too young, and Jinjiu is actually helping the police.\n\n\"That, Uncle Police, I didn\'t get lost, I know where my home is...\"\n\n\"It\'s okay, it\'s okay, even if you don\'t remember, uncle will definitely help you find it.\"\n\nThe patrol policeman comforted, in his opinion, such a cute and simple little girl must not understand how chaotic this place is.\n\nSaying that you know where your home is is definitely embarrassing to admit that you are lost.\n\nHis justice made him have to take care of the child\'s heart.\n\n\"…\"\n\nWhat did the policeman say, the donkey\'s lips are not the horse\'s mouth, and I said that I knew where my home was and didn\'t get lost.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at him blah blah blah and comforted herself, her heart was not fluctuating,