ted Yumiya Noriko\'s head, \"Is Noriko here too? We happened to be nearby, so we came first after receiving the report.\"\n\n\"It seems that a person accidentally fell off the escalator.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s simple words are not to justify Gin. The main thing is that Gin does things. Without Kudo Shinichi, it is not leaking, and even if you know that Gin is a murderer, is it so easy to catch?\n\nMikako Sato said seriously to Noriko Amamiya: \"You can\'t draw conclusions just because of the surface, otherwise the prisoners who faked the accident will be able to get away with it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko, who had watched Conan\'s thousand episodes, nodded her head to show her understanding: \"Understood.\"\n\n\"Okay, we\'re going to get busy. Noriko and your sisters, let\'s go play.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko blinked: \"That\'s my mother?\"\n\n  \"……real??\"\n\n  \"real.\"\n\nMiwako Sato had black lines all over her head, and quickly said to Emi Amamiya, \"Hello, Mrs. Amamiya.\"\n\n\"Hello, police officer, I bothered you about Noriko last time. Come to the house when you have time.\"\n\nEmi Amamiya thanked Sato Miwako by the hand.\n\nWhile responding, Sato Mikako wanted to ask Mrs. how do you take care of it?\n\nAmamiya Noriko wondered, she made all three meals at home by herself, where did mom get the confidence to invite others to be a guest at home?\n\nEmi Amamiya is still seriously inviting Mikazu Sato, \"My daughter Kiko\'s cooking is very good. Officer Sato will definitely like it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko gave a compliment, it\'s really yours, can you not wear JK to praise my daughter for my cooking?'),
