 No downward trend.\n\nPutting these thoughts aside, Amamiya Noriko achieved the achievement of riding the Ferris wheel with Ai-chan.\n\nThe process, the process is not charming, the two are simply chatting, exchanging their favorite food, hobbies, specialties, and views on what things.\n\nMiyano Shiho nodded from time to time, and his calm appearance probably also remembered everything that Amamiya Noriko likes.\n\nThe two have a little in common. They scan women\'s fashion magazines from time to time. They like exquisite, beautiful and distinctive ones, not limited to big and small brands and art. For luxury, high-end, art and other names, design the style. Extremely ugly, and colors paired with ugly things are very scornful.\n\nGoing a little deeper, Shiho Miyano will teach Noriko Amamiya science.\n\nAfter all, Amamiya Noriko told her that she wanted to become a scientist in the future, and Shiho Miyano was himself. It was just right to teach Amamiya Noriko.\n\nOn the other hand, Miyano Shiho is essentially a technical nerd, and he is too young. Although he is mature and calm, he still has a generation gap of about ten years with most young scientists.\n\nAnd most children of the same age have a ten-year IQ gap with her.\n\nAs for Kiko Amamiya... It seems that the generation gap has been erased unconsciously. Although Shiho Miyano sees her as a simple and lovely little sister, she is similar in aesthetics to her.\n\nAnd after a few simple questions and answers, Miyano Shiho found that Amamiya Noriko\'s knowledge level is high in the general category of science.\n\nBecause Miyano Shiho is very talented in computer, chemistry, and physics, Amamiya Noriko can basically keep up.\n\nIf you were really only a junior high school student, chatting with Shiho Miyano would probably only be smeared in the face of knowledge.\n\nNo matter what, Amamiya Noriko has learning points, and in the spare time when fishing and other fish are hooked, she will also upgrade her knowledge