ake a difference with your rye whiskey Shuichi?\n\nHurry up and go to the winery to shine.\n\nThe relationship between the two is purely sneaky, no age.\n\nMainly, when Hideyoshi Akai touched porcelain and was hospitalized, he knew part of Noriko Amamiya\'s quirky appearance, not as cute and cute as she looked.\n\nAfter that, Amiya Noriko found Kudo Shinichi and Maurilan and Suzuki Sonoko in the dessert shop.\n\nKudo Shinichi didn’t say that she was kidnapped in order to avoid Xiaolan and Sonoko worrying about Amemiya Noriko, only that Noriko met her elder relatives to accompany her, so that Xiaolan and Sonoko, who had been told the truth by him. Don\'t worry~www.readwn.com~ And then they were almost killed by Xiaolan and Sonoko with their eyes. When Shinichi took them to find Noriko, they were already nervous enough.\n\nSo as soon as Amamiya Noriko came in, Kudo Shinichi stared at him with rather resentful eyes, Amamiya Noriko rolled his eyes, as if he saw a **** pot behind him, full of ashes.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a few glances, ordered a strawberry puff pastry, then went over and sat down.\n\nFirst of all, I apologized to Xiaolan and Yuanzi, and I was very moved that they were worried about themselves. Xiaolan and Yuanzi didn\'t mind at all, and they even brought her over to recommend the desserts from this dessert shop.\n\nKudo Shinichi held his chin, his eyes fell on the smiling face of Amamiya Noriko, and the detective began to activate.\n\nHe asked Amamiya Noriko to stay on top for a while before coming down so early, but Amamiya Noriko seems to have stayed for too long. What did she do during this time?\n\nAmamiya Noriko is direct enough to him that he often wants to die together, but he can still feel the mystery of Amamiya Noriko.\n\nIf he hadn\'t known each other since kindergarten, knowing that Amamiya Noriko was sincere to the people he cared about, his curiosity could no longer be suppressed.\n\nAfter thinking about it for a while now, I haven\'t continued to think deeply.\n\nMy disciple of Sherlock Holmes, the future detective Kudo Shinichi, gives you a chance to confess.\n\nKudo Shin took a look at the shoes that came over from under the table and stepped on the chair between his legs.\n\nJust then Amamiya Noriko retracted her feet under the table, as if she happened to meet Kudo Shinichi\'s eyes, and showed a gentle smile to Kudo Shinichi.\n\nFrom the way your brain is spinning fast, you know that you are deciphering the truth. It is forbidden to play Conan mode on me.\n\n​​'),
(472, 5, 58, 'Chapter 57: : Hey, don\'t fight', 'The cheerleader sister didn\'t ask Amamiya Noriko to do any difficult moves, she just made her jump and lift a colorful ball.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took out the mobile phone from her pocket first, and then just stood up and patted her skirt, and there was a feeling of attention, as if the spotlights were instantly drawn to her.\n\nOn the basketball court, it\'s the same as slow motion. Everyone tacitly slows down the attack, and the rebound can not be covered. The cute girl can\'t miss it.\n\nThe football team members on the opposite side burst into cheers and all stood up at once.\n\n  see it! Rain Palace is the social treasure of our football club, no, you are not qualified to watch it.\n\nSometimes Amamiya Noriko still thinks that they are really second-hand. With this aggressive appearance, they can all put on cheerleading clothes to cheer.\n\nRegardless of them, Amamiya Noriko held colorful **** in both hands, and the seniors from the cheerleading team cast encouraging glances.\n\nThe captain, Aoi Motohashi, even taught her how to dance by doing movements for her.\n\nIn general, it is impossible to let passers-by Noriko Amamiya dance any professional cheerleading dance.\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t intend to go too far, so she just followed her sister\'s way, jumping, jumping, shaking the colored balls, cheering, jumping, jumping, cheering, jumping, jumping, cheering...\n\nAs the only person sitting on the opposite side, Kudo Shinichi, who also has an IQ, thought about it carefully, and Noriko definitely didn\'t know how to dance.\n\nIn my impression, I can remember very clearly that the only thing Amamiya Noriko can\'t do is not to refuse other people\'s confessions.\n\nIs she going to capture the hearts of this group of sports men with this simple and cute simple action of bouncing, cheering, bouncing, cheering?\n\nNo matter what, it\'s not that easy...\n\n\"Owoooooooooooo!\"\n\n\"Hoohoho-!!\"\n\nWhen the two teams on the basketball court were waving the colored **** by Amamiya Noriko, they burned the small universe to the extreme!\n\nA fierce collision is imminent, the basketball will smash, Rukawa Kaede VS Sakuragi Flower Road!\n\nAh, no, there is no Rukawa maple and cherry tree flower path, everyone is Rukawa maple, and everyone is a cherry tree flower path.\n\nAmamiya Noriko stopped dancing and watched their top games with two balls, which was comparable to the NBA, wonderful.\n\nBut without her buff, the basketball level of the players on the court dropped from NBA to ABC in no time.\n\nWater fish!\n\nAmamiya Noriko slapped her thigh, jumped, and held a colored ball. Come on!\n\n  \"Oh oh oh oh!\"\n\nThe situation on the court suddenly exploded, and the war of the century broke out around a basketball.\n\nThe football club members in the opposite auditorium kept cheering for their pride. Their football club\'s lovely Amemiya Saigao!\n\nAs for the school basketball team?\n\nI\'ll go back and settle the account with you, but dare to trick our simple Amamiya into watching you play. What\'s your motive? If they still can\'t beat the basketball team of the other school, then they will change the name of the [Football Department] to [Basketball Department Change].\n\nThe only serious artificial Fuji Shinichi\'s head is sober.\n\nThere is no such thing as Rukawa Kaede and Sakuragi Huadao, that is, the game on the basketball court has become fierce. A group of snakeskins on his side are watching Amamiya Noriko cheering as a cheerleader over there. Miyajiko also cheered them on.\n\nKudo Shinichi just wanted to say that you guys are going to confess, and let me be happy to see how you were rejected.\n\nAmamiya Noriko jumped and jumped over there, shouting for a long time, and found that she didn\'t seem to be sure of the subject.\n\nSo she shouted a little: \"Come on, Didan Middle School!\"\n\n\"Huh—\"\n\nThe power forward general of the basketball team of Didan Middle School had his