Motohashi was still very embarrassed and asked Noriko Amamiya, who is not very outgoing, to dance and cheer, and only then did the school basketball team win.\n\nSo Amamiya Noriko was brought by the seniors to prepare to sing karaoke.\n\nIn the basketball court, the members of the basketball team from the other school held a rainbow tightly in the shadow of failure, the girl who shone their colorful light.\n\nThe exchange competition can be lost, that girl must realize that!\n\nAnd the members of the basketball club of Didan Middle School watched Kiko Amamiya go away like this. Their hearts felt like colic, and the taste of victory was slightly bitter.\n\nObviously just won the victory now, especially the players who scored a few goals, thinking about how well they played, putting on the cloak of victory and preparing to confess to Noriko Amemiya handsomely, the success rate must be very high.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko was taken away by other girls.\n\nToo rough.\n\nAt this time, the football club went to negotiate with them. How could you let our members leave club activities to watch your games?\n\nThe basketball team was full of question marks, and Amamiya Kiko was called by the cheerleaders, but they were not to be outdone. They poked their necks and said that they could beat the teams from other schools. It would be better for Amamiya Kiko to come to their basketball club in the football club.\n\nThe football club suddenly became popular. You can also grab our Amamiya?\n\nAfter the victory of the basketball club, everyone was proud of it. Only their basketball club deserved to have Amamiya join.\n\nThe basketball team from the other school trotted over and probed their heads. Brothers, is that girl\'s surname Amamiya?\n\nThe basketball team and the football team turned their heads and stared at them, brother, this is our territory, and your path is narrow.\n\nKudo Shinichi, who had already got up and was about to leave in the auditorium, patted the hem of his clothes and sat back calmly. This is a good show to watch.\n\nBecause she was going to jump around, she put her phone on the seat on the other side of the auditorium. Noriko Amamiya, who forgot to take it, came back to get her phone.\n\nThen it seemed that the sardines and tuna schools were **** for tat, and there was a school of salmon beside it, and there was a shark watching in the distance...\n\nHe almost couldn\'t help opening his mouth to laugh.\n\nSeeing that all her eyes fell on her at once, Amamiya Noriko held back her smile with a small face, and said seriously, \"Hey, don\'t quarrel.\"\n\n​​');
