(473, 5, 6, 'Chapter 5: : Black Feather Pirate 1', 'Amamiya Ludou put down the information about the young executive in his hand. Although the other party has a high academic background and a high starting point, his promotion went too smoothly.\n\nThere are basically no mistakes in the position, and the work is completed faster than the average person.\n\nThe feeling of being efficient is not like he is alone, but there are people behind him to help.\n\nIn this explosion downstairs in the company, the other party was one of the three people who died. Although his position was not very high, he was in the real power department.\n\nHe couldn\'t find anything from the previous transaction completed by the other party, which is strange. Even the company\'s record was lost because of the previous information database error.\n\nAmamiya Lu Dou vaguely sensed something.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also gave a vague hint. It\'s nothing right now, just a little preparation for the black organization to become active in the next few years.\n\nAmamiya Ludou was just as she imagined. On the surface, he cooperated with the police to provide information about the pirates, and conducted a quiet investigation in private.\n\nThe organization is rigorous, so naturally he can\'t investigate anything, but he understands that there is such a force.\n\n  the holiday is over.\n\nAt the entrance ceremony in April, Amamiya Noriko delivered a speech as the representative of the freshmen. She memorized the manuscript in an old-fashioned manner and won applause from teachers and classmates.\n\nIn order to reject the plan of the whole school\'s elementary school students, first of all, she must be known to everyone.\n\nEmi Amamiya, who came as a parent, is proud of her daughter\'s excellence: \"Kiko is great!\"\n\n\"It\'s just beginning.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said lazily when she got off the stage.\n\nKudo Shinichi also ran over, and as soon as he opened his mouth, he was an old detective, \"Niko, long time no see. I heard that you were there for the explosion at the Amemiya Building when the holiday started?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her eyebrows. Anyway, she probably knew it from Kogoro Mouri or Ran.\n\n\"My child, this case is too early for you. Let\'s talk about it when you become a famous detective.\"\n\nKudo Shin suddenly felt that this guy was still familiar, even though he was still reading his speech seriously on the stage just now.\n\nHowever, he also treats other children as children. The two of them are almost the same, except that Amamiya Noriko is a bit worse.\n\nNo matter how hard Kudo Shinichi asked, Amamiya Noriko wouldn\'t tell him anyway, with the current Kudo Shinichi, his skill is not enough.\n\nThe plain elementary school life arranged by Noriko Amamiya is on track.\n\nBut this track is very easy to derail...\n\nFirst, there were a group of little kids who clearly had a crush on her, but they didn\'t confess, and they always came to provoke her to attract attention.\n\nShe was very happy when it annoyed her, then ran and played the ghost game with her.\n\nHas Noriko Amamiya, who had increased strength and agility, were able to run?\n\nShe caught the little kid sitting behind her who always liked to pull her hair, and bluntly locked her hands and pressed him to the ground: \"Do you like me?\"\n\nThe little brat blushed for a while, not willing to admit it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko sneered, \"Then I\'ll move your seat to the corner.\"\n\nShe is the monitor, and she talks to the teacher casually.\n\nThe little boy wanted to sit next to Amamiya Noriko, so he mustered up to admit it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko refused, and found that the system didn\'t respond, \"Be careful!\"\n\nThe little brat blushed and confessed awkwardly.\n\nThe main idea is that I think she is cute and powerful, so I like Yunyun.\n\nThe Japanese are more reserved, and when it comes to this, it is already very good.\n\n  \"well said.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko encouraged, \"But I refuse.\"\n\nRefusing to confess successfully, random points: Agility +1.\n\n  \"what?\"\n\nNoriko Amamiya has seen this kind of bewildered reaction a lot, and the group of children in the kindergarten also reacted the same way, as if she should agree.\n\nBut for the sake of contributing a little bit of agility, and to encourage other children to make bold confessions, she said seriously.\n\n\"The weather is bad today, let\'s try another person another day, maybe I\'ll agree.\"\n\n\"…\"\n\nAfter playing with this kind of children one by one, Amamiya Noriko found that this kind of thing is not bad.\n\nThe other type is a very snake-skinned person, who clearly has a favorable impression of her, but somehow a group of little boys are full of superiority and superiority, and they feel that it is naive to play with girls.\n\nThis is a bit troublesome. It is a group behavior that stems from the self-esteem of young boys, and it is the same for most boys after it has become a trend. The core of which has been rejected by her before. It is quite cohesive and restricts other boys. Yu atmosphere is also involved in drifting.\n\nTo put it simply, Kudo Shinichi is also one of them.\n\nHe also felt that he was no longer a child. Recently, he stopped calling him Lan directly, and changed his name to Maori. He also asked Lanbie to call him Xinyi directly.\n\n\"Mori-san, Amamiya-san, that\'s it, you girls, go play by yourself.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was going to play football with other classmates with a soccer ball in his arms, but he wasn\'t going to bring the two girls with him.\n\nAmamiya Noriko leaned on Xiaolan\'s shoulder and squinted at him: \"Childish.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi snorted, turned around and went to play football with his friends.\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head and said, \"He\'s the one. The rebellious period is over. He thinks it\'s naive to play with girls all the time, but he\'s actually very naive.\"\n\nMo Lilan replied in a low voice, thanking Noriko Amemiya for her comfort, but she was obviously still a little sad.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also thought it was a bit difficult, so she refused to catch any fish.\n\nAfter school, Amamiya Noriko spends her time reading books in the library. She is a member of the library committee.\n\nOriginally, school committees usually don\'t start until the fifth and sixth grades, but she is so capable. The teacher seems to think that being a monitor in the class can\'t show her talent, so she asks her if she wants to join the student committee, Amamiya Noriko In line with the idea of ​​one more copy, a more leisurely book committee was selected to join.\n\nHowever, the other students on the library committee were at least fifth graders, and a few boys always had an inexplicable sense of superiority in front of her.\n\nA few girls are better, take care of her as a little sister, Amamiya Noriko originally refused, but it is too comfortable to eat snacks while reading.\n\n\"Niko, have you heard? There is a ghost in the library, the one with a creepy voice and a weird hat!\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko was rubbing her snacks at this time, while still doing the work of an intelligence dealer.\n\nMao Lilan was surprised and said, \"Eh? Really?\"\n\n\"Of course it\'s true! It will appear at night!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko\'s eyes didn\'t look away from the book. She was from the Book Committee. She didn\'t even know about the rumor. Where did Sonoko hear about it.\n\nHowever, there are no ghosts, but the phantom thief Kid does have one.\n\nAnd it\'s also the first-generation Kaito Kid, Kuroba Pirates.'),
(474, 5, 34, 'Chapter 33: : It\'s all genetic', 'The senior sisters in the tennis club are very temperamental, gentle and generous, and they are almost treating the elementary school girl Amamiya Noriko as a member of their tennis club.\n\nAmamiya Noriko resigned for a while, and she will definitely come back to play with the seniors next time, so she can leave her enthusiasm.\n\nA group of people in the football club felt that they were in a big crisis. After the ministry was over, when Noriko Amamiya left, they immediately got together to study how to keep Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAt the gate of the school, Yuanzi was very depressed: \"Is it true that Noriko is so good at tennis?\"\n\nHowever, it doesn\'t seem like she\'s too frustrated after losing to Noriko Amemiya, maybe she\'s used to it since kindergarten...\n\n\"Sure enough, although Noriko catches cold easily, her health is still very good.\"\n\nXiaolan nodded on the side.\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled embarrassedly, thinking that I will catch a cold tomorrow, and I will get some physique from the head of the tennis department.\n\nWhen the physique is added, the physical condition is generally a little more serious than others. Most of the common attributes have a small cold, and they can still go to school wearing a mask.\n\nWith this constitution, it is easy to have a high fever.\n\nBut she is definitely not too much. The physique adds up, and she also has good looks. This is a **** profit.\n\nAt the school gate, I saw Chieda Riho coming to pick up the car driven by Noriko Amamiya, a black Bentley Mulsanne.\n\nSonoko obviously owns a mine at home, so she is quite knowledgeable. \"Sister Chie\'s car is very beautiful.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded: \"Sonoko will be there in the future.\"\n\nBecause, although the second lady of the Suzuki consortium who travels by bus and tram, one of the cars after Suzuki Sonoko is a pink Bentley Mulsanne.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko didn\'t know, but she felt that Noriko was right, she would have to buy one herself in the future, and pink would look the best.\n\nAfter Amamiya Noriko and Xiaolan Yuanzi said their goodbyes, they blinked at Kudo Shin before getting in the car, and the latter looked wary.\n\nThen the next day, Amamiya Noriko had a high fever and asked for leave. Kudo Shinichiro was worried all night, and he had to follow Xiaolan Yuanzi to worry about Amamiya Noriko.\n\n\"It\'s not comfortable, it\'s not comfortable, wink at me.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi speculated that Amamiya Noriko felt unwell yesterday afternoon and felt that she would be ill the next day, so she deliberately winked at him to make him worry in vain.\n\nVery bad behavior.\n\nThe Amamiya family.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was lying on the bed, and her mother Amamiya Emi was eating melon seeds beside her. Although she was very worried about her daughter, baby, you are getting used to being sick.\n\nIt is estimated that I still take the medicine and sleep for a day, and it will be fine after a night.\n\n\"Kakaka…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko fell asleep and listened to the sound of nibbling melon seeds for a long time. Unable to bear, she lifted the quilt and pointed to the door: \"Mom, go outside and nibble!\"\n\nEmi Amamiya is quite innocent: \"Mom will take Noriko\'s temperature later.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko pouted, I imported your melon seeds from my hometown.\n\nEmi Amamiya wondered while eating melon seeds: \"Baby why do you always catch a cold and have a fever?\"\n\n\"I\'m sorry for not inheriting from my mother.\"\n\nSeeing that Amamiya Noriko was out of sleep, she lifted the quilt to get up and stretched.\n\nEmi Amamiya looked at her daughter\'s cherry-red skin in the white snow because of the fever, and the slender waist that she held tightly, and nodded earnestly: \"This is what inherited me.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko straightened the hem of her clothes and said calmly, \"If mom doesn\'t exercise, she should gain weight, right?\"\n\nEmi Amamiya\'s hand froze while holding the sunflower seeds, and she pinched her waist quietly. Fortunately, it wasn\'t a fleshy feeling.\n\n\"The attack is invalid~\"\n\n  \"childish.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t look back and started changing clothes.\n\n\"Do you want to go out?\"\n\n  \"Have a meal.\"\n\nIt is impossible to expect this mother to cook, and she herself has a high fever and does not want to do it.\n\n\"Mom will go too.\"\n\nEimi Amamiya also jumped up when she heard the words and ran to change her clothes.\n\nWhen Amamiya Noriko was changing her shoes at the entrance, she noticed that her mother in JK uniform came out~www.readwn.com~ Her brows were raised, and she said, \"Mom, how old are you.\"\n\nAmamiya Emi stroked her face with her palms in a shy expression: \"I hate it, I\'m only 17.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko exhaled.\n\nSo it is difficult for her. To a certain extent, the two are on a more lovable path than the other, and they are quite rivals.\n\nJust like the current Emi Amamiya, after a little make-up and dressing up, she actually looks comparable to the very temperamental senior sister in the tennis club, and she is a little more cute.\n\nBut Amamiya Noriko is still the cutest.\n\nBecause I only added a little physique, my appearance++\n\nAmamiya Noriko put on a mask and said in a muffled voice, \"If that\'s the case, let\'s go together.\"\n\n\"Remember to call my sister after Noriko goes out.\"\n\nAmamiya Emi didn\'t know where she turned over a pair of shoes to put on her jk, and she didn\'t know if it was her high school uniform.\n\nChieda Riho was waiting in the car at the entrance of Amamiya\'s mansion. After seeing someone dressed too young, she calmly said, \"Auntie, are you going to the high school party?\"\n\nEmi Amamiya pointed her finger at the mistake: \"Don\'t use such an old-fashioned name, call me sister.\"\n\nChieda Riho didn\'t want to speak, she sat in the driver\'s seat, reached out and moved the rear-view mirror, not wanting to see an elder in the back seat.\n\nAmamiya Noriko fastened her seat belt by herself: \"Today, I want to capture more people\'s hearts.\"\n\nChie Riho turned a deaf ear: \"Where are you going?\"\n\n\"Mihua Commercial Plaza, have a meal.\"\n\nEmi Amamiya was looking forward to it, \"I don\'t know if she will talk to her mother. Young people nowadays should be very bold, right? How can my mother refuse them?\"\n\n  \"Um?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wondered if my system was inherited.\n\n​​'),
(475, 5, 62, 'Chapter 61: : Detective Shark', 'Didan Middle School.\n\nAt the vending machine at the end of the classroom corridor.\n\nKudo Shinichi put in a coin to buy a can of oolong tea, pulled off the tab with a click, and took a sip.\n\nWith a contemplative expression on his face, he pressed his index finger and thumb to his chin after taking a sip, his eyes sparkling with wisdom.\n\nLeaving from the school doctor\'s sister, because she and Xiaolan Yuanzi lost again in boxing, when Amamiya Noriko, who came to buy a drink, found out, Wei Wei was surprised and calmed down.\n\nIt seems that this is the seriousness of the murder.\n\n\"Which classmate suffered misfortune?\"\n\n\"None of the classmates suffered misfortune!\"\n\nKudo Shin knew it was her as soon as he heard the voice, and said angrily.\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her eyebrows: \"You murdered me.\"\n\n\"No, I\'m just wondering who took the recorder from the music club.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi denied that it was troublesome to be entangled by Noriko Amamiya.\n\nAmamiya Noriko didn\'t expect him to be bored enough to struggle with this kind of problem, because there really is no place where he can use his detective abilities?\n\nBut in this small case, she has some clues: \"It might be Brother Octopus.\"\n\n  \"Who?\"\n\n\"It\'s nothing, you continue.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko waved her hand and went back after buying drinks.\n\nIt turns out that the best detectives also start by looking for things to find cats and dogs. It takes experience to level up.\n\nAmamiya Noriko also continued to add experience to herself.\n\nThe initiative of the seniors has been brought into play, and there are people who are hooked without her manipulation. The rest are the boys of the same grade who have just graduated from elementary school.\n\nDuring class, Amamiya Noriko, who was drawing a flowchart on her notebook, felt that there was a line of sight looking at her, and then she suddenly raised her head to look at the blackboard, as if she was looking at the teacher, and then turned her head to look at him naturally, meeting the eyes of the other party. .\n\nThe boy subconsciously avoided his gaze, lowered his head and pretended to read a book. After a while, he raised his head, only to see Amamiya Kiko wink cutely at him, then smiled softly and turned back.\n\n\"Amamiya may like me.\"\n\nThe boy\'s heart thumped, and he thought excitedly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko turned around and ticked a name on the paper.\n\nThen, she kneaded a small paper ball, and with a flick of her finger, she knocked down the eraser at the adjacent table. It fell to the ground and then bounced a few times and landed on her shoe.\n\nThe boy at the next table widened his eyes, wondering why his eraser dropped to the ground without warning.\n\nAnd it just landed on the side of Amamiya-san\'s shoe. Could you please help me pick it up? How should I call out Amamiya-san, do you want to pat her? Do you think I fell at her feet on purpose? ?\n\n\"What if Amamiya-san thinks I like her!\"\n\nDid you pick it up yourself?\n\nBut if I picked it up from somewhere, would Amamiya-san think I did it on purpose? What do you want to see? Dirty?\n\nThe boy hugged his head and fell into a whirlpool of thoughts.\n\nAt this moment, a quiet voice came into his ears: \"Student Uda? Is this your eraser?\"\n\nPutting down his hand and looking to the side, it was Noriko Amamiya who was talking to him softly with a small mouth.\n\nThe small hand covered his mouth slightly, and the appearance of whispering with his eyes open made his heart move in an instant.\n\nHe nodded unconsciously throughout the whole process, took the eraser back, and only woke up when Noriko Amamiya had returned to listening intently.\n\nHe covered his head in annoyance: \"Ah, ah, it\'s too disappointing, did Amamiya-kun touch her finger when she returned the eraser just now!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a look at the classmate who was holding his head and beating the table. Are you okay?\n\nIt is very important to give courage. Without this blessing, even if the other party likes him to the extreme, he will not be able to have the courage to confess.\n\nAmamiya Noriko can\'t tolerate such a cowardly person.\n\nShe pulled the other person\'s sleeve on her body and whispered, \"That, rubber, can you lend me a hand?\"\n\nRight Tian Eraser immediately replied from an annoyed state, and tried his best to say in a normal tone: \"Ah, it\'s alright, anyway, it was Amamiya-kun who helped me pick it up, of course it\'s okay.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko smiled sweetly: \"Thank you.\"\n\n\"No, it\'s fine.\"\n\nWhen Uta-san found out that Amamiya Noriko was looking at her, her face flushed, and she panicked and took the eraser and used it.\n\nHe couldn\'t help but his heart skipped a beat, \"Student Amamiya... do you like me...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko slowly ticked the name.\n\nWhen you feel that the other party also likes you, the courage to confess will be much greater, because most of the reason for not having the courage to confess is the fear of embarrassment after the confession fails.\n\nAfter Amamiya Noriko finished the hook, she felt that someone was looking at her, so she turned her head and saw Kudo Shinichi.\n\nKudo Shinichi watched her operate the whole process, and at this time, he was no longer emotional.\n\nMainly, these guys are all willing, and he can\'t save them.\n\nAmamiya Noriko has always confessed to her willingly, and she has the ability to eliminate the embarrassment and helplessness of most people who refuse the confession.\n\nLearning to reason and being a detective can\'t save the confessor.\n\nAmiya Noriko and Kudo Shin looked at each other, Amamiya Noriko looked innocent, Kudo Shin looked calm.\n\nXiaolan happened to see this scene from the third perspective, how does she feel that Noriko looks innocently wronged to Shinichi...\n\nDid Shinichi bully Noriko again? !\n\nWhen Sonoko saw this scene, she covered her mouth subconsciously. Noriko was acting like a spoiled brat to Shinichi? ?\n\nWhen she saw Xiaolan, she also saw it, and she felt a shudder in her heart, Xiaolan and Kiko...\n\nSonoko felt as if things were starting to go bad, and she was struggling extremely in her heart.\n\nIt never occurred to me that Noriko also likes Shinichi?\n\nThinking about it carefully, indeed, I often see Kiko and Shinichi whispering, and there seems to be some little secret between the two of them~www.readwn.com~ She even took Kiko to match Xiaolan and Xinyi before. New one!\n\nSonoko felt that she was too vicious.\n\nBut Xiaolan and Noriko are her friends since kindergarten!\n\nWhy, why do you fall in love with the same person!\n\nWho should she support? !\n\nYuanzi stood on the cliff in a trance. Between the cusp of the wind and the waves, the high waves continued to beat, and his heart was in chaos.\n\nAfter class, Amamiya Noriko, who was about to continue fishing, was pulled out by Sonoko.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko looked serious: \"Kiko, are you... ready to fall in love?\"\n\n  \"Um?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko wondered, what kind of love do I love? I\'m still giving others experience cards of falling in love.\n\nThe one that ends the validity period after confession.\n\nIs this love?\n\nForget it.\n\nAmamiya Noriko tried to nod her head to see what Sonoko said.\n\nSonoko\'s eyes turned dark, and it was her lifelong wish to match Xiaolan and Shinichi, apart from being confessed by all the handsome guys!\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, but she probably understood, raised her hand and said, \"Well, I\'m not ready to fall in love, what\'s wrong with you, Sonoko?\"\n\nWithout struggling between the two best friends, Sonoko saw a ray of light in front of his eyes: \"Really? What do you think of Kudo Shinichi?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head: \"Shark?\"\n\n\"?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko explained: \"Sharks are not easy to catch.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko nodded suddenly, in short, Noriko doesn\'t have that kind of relationship with Shinichi!\n\nThat detective maniac, who else would like it except Xiao Lan?\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, did Xiaolan have any record of fighting against sharks? And because of the handkerchief in front of me.\n\n​​'),
(476, 5, 89, 'Chapter 88: : Winery Reception!', 'Amamiya Noriko was trapped in the corner by Chie Riho and searched her body, smoothing her skirt uneasily.\n\nChieda Riho tried her best to speak in a calm tone, \"Thank you for daring to take it. If you search downstairs, what will you do?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko patted her skirt and pouted, \"I am so cute that I have to search my body, am I a person?\"\n\nThe only thing Chie Riho admires about her Noriko is that she will never get fat, but she can swell with a breath of air.\n\n\"What do you want to do with so much stuff?\"\n\n\"Just in case, I might be persecuted by a bottle of wine.\"\n\nChieda Riho calmly closed her voice, and when she swelled up, she stopped talking.\n\nIf you are persecuted by alcohol, you see that I will not drink that bottle of wine on the spot.\n\nThe mobile phone in Noriko Amamiya\'s skirt pocket vibrated. She opened it and saw that it was Xiaolan who sent it to her. Said that she and Shinichi had arrived downstairs.\n\n\"Kiko, you\'re coming out so soon, eh...do you still have pockets in Kiko\'s dress?\"\n\nSonoko also just came out of the bathroom, seeing Noriko playing on her phone, she said.\n\n\"Sister Riho helped me bring it.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko said embarrassedly, and then told Xiaolan and Xinyi that they also went downstairs, let\'s go pick them up together.\n\nChieda Riho was holding the cell phone that Noriko had stuffed, and there was nowhere to put it at all. The pockets designed by her suit and dress were really not for holding things.\n\nToday\'s flip phones are quite thick!\n\nPutting it in the pocket is absolutely bulging, affecting her image. So Chieda Riho simply held it in her hand, full of style.\n\nHowever, the mobile phone in this world will still be a brick after a few years, and then it can evolve into a full-screen display in a few months. It is about the principle of Ke Xue, which is not a problem.\n\nKudo Shinichi came in the car of Dr. A Li, at least in a small suit, but it was obviously not Conan\'s suit, but an ordinary black suit. The 12-year-old Kudo Shinichi was still a little fresh.\n\nAs for Dr. Li, there was nothing he could do with a big belly. He was barely able to put on a suit, but the buttons couldn\'t be buttoned.\n\nXiaolan was in the car rented by her father, Maori Kogoro, a ten-year-old fan of the car rental company.\n\nXiaolan wears a blue dress, which is not conspicuous or too plain, but it can also make people see this little girl\'s gentle and kind temperament.\n\nSonoko and Jikiko went over to pull Xiaolan\'s hand, dipping into the luck of Emperor Ou, no, they chatted about each other\'s clothes, everyone was pretty today.\n\nXiaolan looked at Kiko\'s skirt seriously and said, \"It\'s still Kiko\'s cutest, and Kiko is definitely the brightest.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko scratched her head, while Chieda Riho looked at her lady\'s skirt.\n\nIt\'s not just beautiful, it can hide a lot of things.\n\nKudo Shinichi put his hands in his pockets, and subconsciously observed the surrounding environment and terrain, and some small details would not fall.\n\nThis is a good habit for detectives, and every little point you notice can make a huge difference in the final reasoning.\n\nMouri Kogoro patted Kudo Shinichi\'s shoulder angrily: \"Little brat. Don\'t look around, you are short-sighted?\"\n\nKudo Shinichi: \"…\"\n\nAfter he finished speaking, he looked up at the building, raised his legs and walked towards the gate.\n\nAmamiya Noriko is a good and polite boy, of course he will not forget to say hello: \"Uncle Maori Kogoro! Long time no see!\"\n\nMouri Kogoro\'s back froze, recalling the time when she was completely banned by Amemiya Noriko at the detective office, her hands trembling.\n\nThat\'s why he hated the kid and wanted to pretend he didn\'t see her, but now he can only wave his hand angrily and say, \"Okay, I see.\"\n\nXiaolan raised her fist when she saw that her father had another opinion on Noriko.\n\nMaori Kogoro could only give the invitation and hurried a few steps into the hall. How could he be preached by his 12-year-old daughter on this occasion.\n\nAmamiya Noriko simply blinked, she was the nemesis of Kogoro Mouri, who had not yet slept.\n\n\"Isn\'t this the second lady of the Suzuki family? Thank you very much for the invitation.\"\n\nA voice came from the side, and Amamiya Noriko turned her head. It was a tall, white-haired grandfather in a black suit. When squinting, his smile was very kind and contagious, and his face was very good, not like sixty at all. Multi-year old man.\n\nAmamiya Noriko twitched the corners of her mouth, good wine.\n\n\"Oh? Is the young lady of the Amamiya family too? That\'s right, you are good friends, aren\'t you?\"\n\nThe other party also noticed Noriko Amamiya, and was a little surprised, because of the recent cooperation between Amamiya and Suzuki, it is not very surprising that the people of the Amamiya family are here.\n\nIt\'s just that Amamiya Noriko is relatively rare.\n\nBecause of events such as the banquet held by the Amamiya family, the eldest young lady, Amamiya Noriko, will basically not appear. The reason is that she is still young, but the next door Suzuki Sonoko is also of the same age.\n\nWhat he knew seemed to be because of a previous kidnapping case, that the Amemiya family was very protective of their young lady.\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded timidly, and Sonoko returned the gift generously. This old grandfather Sonoko also met recently, and came to her house as a guest.\n\nOf course, the people who can come to Suzuki Sonoko\'s house are not ordinary people, except for the victims, the victims, and the prisoners.\n\nThe tall grandfather in front of him is the fine wine Pisco, a strong distilled wine produced in Peru.\n\nZongshan Kenzo, a big man in the financial world, the chairman of the automobile company, has a deep relationship with that adult, and is an old wine with deep experience in the winery.\n\nIt is not surprising that he was invited to the banquet of the Suzuki consortium.\n\nMatsuyama Kenzo looked at Amamiya Noriko and nodded. She is a reserved and easily shy Miss Amamiya.\n\nThe education of the Amemiya family is not very good, or it is because of the psychological reasons of the kidnapping case.\n\nZongshan Kenzo had a simple chat with these children, and then he handed over the invitation and went in first.\n\nAmamiya Noriko and the others are almost ready to go in, mainly because Dr. Agasa is telling the parking staff to park his car.\n\nIn fact, it can be painted black, which is very similar to Qin Ye\'s car, and the protective color is nice.\n\nThinking, Amamiya Noriko saw a black Porsche 356A parked on the side of the road across the road from the building.\n\nUpon seeing this, Dr. Li praised the other party\'s car as well.\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"…\"\n\nThis is not a banquet for the Suzuki Foundation, but a reception for a winery, right?\n\nWhat\'s wrong with you, Qin! Master Qin, aren\'t you going to kill the traitor? !\n\nAmamiya Noriko borrowed Dr. Agasa\'s round body to hide behind, feeling that the encounter with Gin again would be a fatal encounter.\n\nThe group went up to the building first. In the elevator, Amamiya Noriko watched the black Porsche across the road open the door, and the two got off.\n\nGin and vodka in a suit dress, high skin!\n\nThe two of them held the invitation cards in their hands, and when they saw Kiko Amamiya and the others left downstairs, they passed the invitation cards and entered the building when there were not too many people.\n\nThe quality of security is really worrying~www.readwn.com~ Akai Shuichi mixed with a security captain, and here he only recognizes invitations and not people. Amamiya Noriko must advise the Sonoko family not to invite this security company.\n\nIn the elevator, Amamiya Noriko tilted her head after counting the number of people. The row of the winery is a bit big. Can this building be bombed?\n\nKudo Shinichi tilted his head calmly and whispered in Kiko Amemiya\'s ear: \"The old man downstairs and the people in the car across the road, although I didn\'t see them, they all have problems, right?\"\n\nIn particular, the old grandfather of Noriko Amamiya who looked timid, he felt that there was a big problem.\n\nSee how Amamiya Noriko responds to him this time...\n\nAmamiya Noriko covered her ears to avoid, whispered: \"Shinichi don\'t do this, it\'s so itchy.\"\n\nAlthough it was quiet, everyone in the elevator could hear it.\n\nKudo Shinji looked calm: \"...\"\n\nLike Conan\'s refusal to confess Conan\'s refusal to confess.'),
(477, 5, 14, 'Chapter 13: : Senior, take everything?', 'On the second day of school, she had a high fever and asked for leave. Noriko Amamiya\'s impression of being weak was firmly established in the class.\n\nAs a result, when she came back to school, she was cared by many classmates.\n\nKudo Shinichi was also one of them. He came over and said, \"It\'s a pity that you didn\'t have someone to confess to you yesterday.\"\n\n\"Shinichi, you are too red, don\'t you care about my body? Sonoko told me last night.\"\n\n  \"cut.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was disdainful. As expected of a professional intelligence dealer, he turned around and said, \"Then? That classmate was arrested by the school to write a review.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at him strangely, \"Of course, I want to thank others, and I have paid a lot of courage to confess to me.\"\n\nKudo Shinichi was not fooled: \"What else?\"\n\n\"Teach me what a confession should look like. That idiot confessed without even knowing whether I was in school or not.\"\n\n\"Teach me a confession...\"\n\nKudo Shinichi feels a little familiar. Isn\'t this what Amamiya Noriko often did when she was in kindergarten? You can do it in junior high school too? ?\n\nAmamiya Noriko whispered quietly, \"I can also teach you how to confess to Xiaolan.\"\n\n\"What nonsense...\"\n\nAlthough he has a high IQ, Shinichi Kudo, who is emotionally thin-skinned, blushed honestly.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was in a good mood, humming a song, and went to Sonoko to find out which idiot was yesterday.\n\nShe\'s actually still a second-year senior, and Amamiya Noriko doesn\'t know when she\'s flirting with someone. She\'s innocent.\n\nSonoko winked and actively matched: \"Senior Yamaki is also the main general of the basketball club. He is very sunny, tall and handsome.\"\n\nEvery day, seeing Noriko reject all kinds of boys, her heart is itching, and now she can\'t wait to see who has the ability to make Noriko fall in love.\n\nThis is one of her lifelong wishes!\n\n\"And he dared to confess to you in front of everyone!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko scratched her head, she just came to ask about the person\'s situation, why does it feel like she is going to go on a blind date?\n\nSeeing that she was unmoved, Suzuki Sonoko said dejectedly, \"What are you going to do, Noriko?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head: \"What if you don\'t prepare.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko\'s eyes widened: \"People have confessed in public! Is this really good?\"\n\n\"First of all, he confessed in public, I respect him as a man, but it doesn\'t mean I will agree to confess in public, and he didn\'t think about my presence or my feelings, maybe Sonoko, you may think this is very romantic , but I won\'t.\"\n\n\"Well... Then Noriko, how do you feel?\"\n\n\"It\'s such a pity! I wasn\'t there at the time, and the experience was extremely bad!\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko suddenly felt hopeful: \"Yeah, do you want me to go and make him do it again?\"\n\n  \"No thanks!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko refused, because in terms of judgment, she had to let the other party receive her rejection of the confession.\n\nAnd if she shouted a confession downstairs, she just didn\'t respond by shouting, then at least a loudspeaker was needed to reply, right?\n\nIt\'s embarrassing in every way.\n\nAnd as long as she doesn\'t reply, the other party will naturally look for her face to face once.\n\nEven from an economic point of view, it has already been shouted like this, and it would be too much of a loss to not try it again.\n\nShe was even more anxious than she thought, waiting for her outside the classroom after school.\n\n  \"Uh…\"\n\nSurprisingly, Amamiya Noriko had no choice but to go out under the ambiguous eyes of others in the class.\n\nWithout waiting for the other party to speak first, Amamiya Noriko bowed. He said apologetically: \"Senior, I\'m really sorry for my confession before, because I had a high fever and was not at school.\"\n\nSeeing that the person she likes is very apologetic, classmate Yamaki hurriedly explained to her: \"No, no, no, it\'s because I was too reckless. I confessed without understanding, which caused you trouble!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko hurriedly waved her hand: \"No, no, it\'s wrong that I didn\'t receive the senior\'s determination so much.\"\n\n\"It doesn\'t matter! I can say it all over again!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko raised her head in astonishment, looking very surprised and nervous, with a bit of shyness: \"Eh? Really, really want it?\"\n\n\"Yes, no matter what, I will convey my thoughts to you!\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko buried her head and whispered, \"I can\'t be here...\"\n\nSeeing her shy look, classmate Yamaki knew that the girl was embarrassed, and quickly said, \"Then change the place...\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko nodded lightly: \"Well...\"\n\nThe two left.\n\nSuzuki Sonoko sighed, \"Yeah, I feel stable, Kiko was very nervous and shy when she saw Senior Yamagi!\"\n\nXiaolan also felt similar, but seeing Xinyi\'s expressionless expression: \"Xinyi, what do you think?\"\n\nKudo Shin put his hand in his pocket without any surprise: \"It\'s definitely a refusal.\"\n\nSuzuki Sonoko stared: \"How come? Shinichi, please don\'t talk nonsense. UU reading www.uukanshu.com\"\n\nShinichi Kudo rolled her eyes, just now Noriko Amamiya apologized as soon as she opened her mouth, indicating that she was not at school that day, and that the confession was not accepted successfully, so Yamagi-senpai couldn\'t have any resentment.\n\nThe second sentence aggravated that I didn\'t know the other party\'s intentions very well, and led the other party to want to say it again to express their intentions.\n\nThen he pretended to be shy, as if there was a high probability of agreeing, and considering the pressure of the other party to confess in public again, he went to a place where no one was there.\n\nIt\'s too stable, the poor senior Yamagi will definitely confess very seriously, full of heart, and then expect Noriko Amemiya to shyly agree to fail, but instead wait until she refuses.\n\nAmamiya Noriko may have arranged for the other party to be rejected without any resentment.\n\nHe is too familiar.\n\nWhen Suzuki Sonoko saw that he was very sure, his heart was itching, and it was the old suggestion to go and watch!\n\nOriginally, she was in junior high school, not elementary school. She seldom watched others confess to Noriko, but Xiao Lan was also a little curious at this time, so she said to Kudo Shin, \"Go.\"\n\n  \"Row.\"\n\nShin Kudo nodded and went to see if his script was correct, or if Director Amemiya had arranged something else.\n\nFacts have proved that director Amamiya\'s script level is always beyond his imagination.\n\nBehind the teaching building, not only Amamiya Noriko and Yamagi-senpai, but also a third person, a second-year girl, the scene was very embarrassing.\n\nYuanzi opened his eyes wide and whispered, \"How do I confess this?\"\n\nXiaolan also looked confused, she turned her head around, could this girl be Noriko\'s rival in love?\n\nKudo Shinichi looked at Amamiya Noriko\'s speechless expression over there, and thought thoughtfully, \"Has she finally attacked girls too?\"'),
(478, 5, 55, 'Chapter 54: :interesting', 'Miyano Shiho and Amamiya Noriko each operate in front of a claw machine.\n\nMiyano Shiho tilted his head to look, Amamiya Noriko was carefully moving the operating lever, gently pressing the grab button, and then his claws slowly grabbed a doll.\n\nShe looked at Noriko Amamiya\'s eyes for a moment, and then she grabbed the doll with her paws and pushed it against it, and the doll shook off.\n\n\"…\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko was going to die of anger, just like her fishing.\n\nMiyano Shiho\'s calm \"click\" operation arranged for a bear doll to come out and hand it to Amamiya Noriko.\n\n\"What do Noriko like to do when she has nothing to do?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko lost her mind by this operation. She took the bear and thought about it, eating, drinking, and fishing—it was zero points, so she looked distressed and came up with the answer: \"fishing.\"\n\nFishing is her true love, and true love is greater than everything else.\n\nMiyano Shiho looked at the Chinese on the front of her clothes: \"...\"\n\nAccidentally, Amamiya Noriko doesn\'t look like a fisherman, so cute, doesn\'t she have a cute hobby?\n\n\"Don\'t you like to sing this?\"\n\n  \"Sing?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko tilted her head, saying that she also has a talent called \"world music\".\n\n\"I\'ll sing you a song I like.\"\n\n\"Huh? Okay.\"\n\nShiho Miyano nodded, and if Kiko sang, it should be something like Luri ちの日に (the day of departure), right?\n\nAfter elementary school, everyone sang together or said some other nursery rhymes.\n\nThen Amamiya Noriko sang \"Previous Life\" softly with a small mouth.\n\nMiyano Shiho opened his eyes in surprise, completely beyond her expectations, quietly listening to Amamiya Noriko\'s unique soft voice brought her thoughts to the starry night, in the distant universe, like a dazzling light. Meteors streak across the world.\n\nWhen Noriko Amamiya\'s soft singing stopped, Shiho Miyano felt that he had just experienced a gentle past and past life.\n\nShe looked at Noriko Amamiya\'s delicate profile, her eyes shining like stars: \"Kiko\'s past life was also very gentle and lovely, right?\"\n\n  \"How about it?\"\n\nAfter she finished singing, Amamiya Noriko turned her head and smiled softly, looking at Shiho Miyano. She is not the kind of audiophile like Kudo Shinichi, and secondly, her [physique] is really a good thing.\n\nMiyano Shiho thought about it for a while, then nodded and said, \"It\'s beautiful, it\'s a voice that can make people instantly fall in love with Noriko.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko opened her eyes with pure eyes: \"Is that Shiho-san\'s heart moved?\"\n\nWith a smile in Miyano Shiho\'s eyes, he raised his index finger: \"I was moved in an instant.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while, is this a confession? It seems to be just a declarative sentence, but then it doesn\'t matter, even if it is a confession.\n\nAi-chan\'s confession, I accept it!\n\nMiyano Shiho then asked Noriko what song it was, but she didn\'t seem to have heard it before.\n\nAmamiya Noriko said that she learned this from her mother. She has no burden on her shoulders, and she can move forward completely.\n\nHowever, Amamiya Noriko\'s habit of letting her mother take the blame made Miyano Shiho think of his mother.\n\nAmamiya Noriko looked at Miyano Shiho\'s slightly missed appearance, and realized that she had made a slip of the tongue.\n\nPulling Shiho Miyano\'s hand, Noriko Amamiya said, \"My mother is your mother.\"\n\nMiyano Shiho nodded quietly, then asked, \"Does Noriko have any dreams?\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko thought for a while: \"Becoming a scientist?\"\n\nShiho Miyano, a 13-year-old scientist, nodded slightly.\n\nIf Noriko likes this and wants to become a scientist, she can teach it in the future, but is there any problem with such a cute scientist?\n\n\"Noriko is so cute, it\'s a waste to be a scientist.\"\n\nAmamiya Noriko: \"Well...\"\n\nShe can\'t agree with this, your 13-year-old Ai Jiang can\'t say this to me.\n\nThe two looked at each other for a while. Forget it, don\'t talk about such a topic. Everyone is lovely and has no position to say such a thing.\n\nShiho Miyano and Noriko Amamiya chatted while strolling around. As for Shuichi Akai and Akimi Miyano, they hadn\'t been walking with them for a long time, but they didn\'t go far. They were basically behind them. Does not hinder the development of feelings.\n\nOn the other side.\n\nIn the Ferris wheel of Cuphu Commercial Plaza.\n\nVodka sat upright, and his eyes under the sunglasses fell between the distance from the ground. In his opinion, the Ferris wheel was a very dangerous place. The space was narrow and it would be located at a high place, and there was no way to escape.\n\n\"Brother, here...\"\n\nGin, who was wearing a black top hat, raised his hand to tell him not to speak, and his cold gaze fell through the binoculars on the garbage disposal staff who was dragging a large black garbage bag near the mall.\n\n\"A new member of the organization, Bourbon?\"\n\nVodka was surprised: \"I heard that his intelligence search ability is very strong?\"\n\nJin Jiu put down the binoculars and said coldly, \"Perhaps, it\'s just that his intelligence search mission has directly solved the target person, but that\'s it.\"\n\nVodka: \"...\"\n\nAnd this kind of operation? Intelligence searches kill people directly?\n\nIs this an out-of-context or a new problem-solving idea?\n\nGin picked up the binoculars and continued to observe the surrounding environment. There are several mall staff on the rooftop of the mall over there. It should be the influence of Bourbon\'s actions. It didn\'t take long for him to get on the Ferris wheel. He didn\'t see everything, just glanced at it. Bourbon and Camo Man chasing down the stairs.\n\nGin looked at Bourbon in the clothes of the garbage disposal staff and threw the large black garbage bag on the co-pilot. Bourbon\'s white Mazda RX-7FD3S is a two-seater, so it can only be put in this way.\n\nLooking at Bourbon in a work hat, he glanced around and drove away. UU Reading www.uukanshu.com Gin also retracted his sight and put away the telescope.\n\n  \"gone.\"\n\n\"Brother, the Ferris wheel is a little slow.\"\n\nGin said calmly, \"I know.\"\n\nAfter the two of them sat on the Ferris wheel, they finally returned to the ground. Gin opened the door and stretched out his legs first, and then an icy aura emanated. Vodka shivered and followed out. When he saw the current person, he couldn\'t help but be stunned.\n\nAmamiya Noriko was also held by Miyano Shiho, looked at Gin, and slowly blinked her eyes. Is this really right? Gin why are you here?\n\nAre you working? Are there traitors in this place?\n\nIt\'s not going to come on a Ferris wheel with vodka.///.\n\nNo matter what, Amamiya Noriko\'s eyes lit up instantly, as if seeing the gaze of an idol star.\n\nGin looked away from her face with a cold face, and caught sight of Miyano Shiho.\n\nMiyano Shiho still maintained a calm expression, but Amamiya Noriko could feel that she was holding her hand gradually.\n\nAmamiya Noriko took a step forward, but Miyano Shibao grabbed her hand tightly, as if telling her not to approach Gin.\n\nShe didn\'t resist either, her other hand took out a paper and pen from her pocket...\n\n  \"gone.\"\n\nJin Jiu withdrew his gaze indifferently and walked away from them.\n\nVodka glanced at Noriko Amamiya and Shiho Miyano, and quickly followed, but heard the little girl behind him say crisply: \"Uncle driver, see you next time—\"\n\nVodka stumbled under her feet.\n\nGin tilted her head, her cold eyes fell on Amamiya Noriko and Miyano Shiho, one with a cute smile, the other looked at him calmly.\n\n  \"interesting.\"\n\n​​');
